votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501243200.0} {"text": "JOGO BOM ,RECOMENDO", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198273419367", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Хороший эпизод,но сильно короткий.", "appid": "380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198274190821", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483531200.0} {"text": "oynaması zor da olsa güzel oyun arkadaşlarınızla rahatlıkla oynayabilirsiniz", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198369267606", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1513598400.0} {"text": "Really enjoying the game overall, but if you're not the kind of person to replay levels in order to see different possible outcomes it's just not the game for you. You only get 5 levels if I'm correct in the main bundle..", "appid": "863550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198830963679", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582200000.0} {"text": "9 разе_ба_нных клавиатур из 10", "appid": "657200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198357469522", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561377600.0} {"text": "This a great game to play with friends (at the time of writing I only play regularly with 1 friend but that's going up to 2 soon). If you're looking for something with gameplay a little like L4D2, but themes from Alien, Star Troopers, burly dwarves and casual alcoholism, this may be the game for you and your friends. For those concerned by the Early Access tag (if it still applies), don't worry about that too much - after 2 years in public testing and development, the content in this game has grown explosively and it pretty much a reflection of the final product by this point. There's only 4 classes to play, 8 weapons to master and 8 tools to help you do it, but if you think that this means you'll be finished with DRG's content in an afternoon you'd be sorely wrong. The sheer difference in gameplay, from one build to another, makes the grind to complete that build feel appropriately spaced and appropriately rewarding. Single player is available, but while it's kinda fun to make the drone do all the more boring work for you, multiplayer is where this game is at.", "appid": "548430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198178517897", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1575547200.0} {"text": "A fun, fast-paced 2D action game.", "appid": "280010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086313488", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1443787200.0} {"text": "Fun detective game", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198106244516", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604577600.0} {"text": "Da", "appid": "311690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198383228376", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546171200.0} {"text": "ooooh boy do i like this game, neaa por qué en inglés? está buenisimo para jugarlo solo y con amigos, y estan todos los personajes que quieras de peliculas de acción clasicas y algunas algo modernas, mis favoritos son: Machete, Raiden, Predator, y el mismisimo Alber Einstein (? no mentira ese no está, pero igualmente este juego te va a traer muchas horas de diversión. no tiene muchos modos además de la campaña y su versión sin cinematicas ni mapa (Arcade) pero entre ellos se incluye Iron Bro perdiendo personajes para siempre si mueren y terminando para siempre la partida si los pierdes a todos, siempre estando la posibilidad de elegir la dificultad entre normal y dificil. y el modo versus que está buenisimo para jugar con amigos. hay un montón de cosas mas por nombrar pero es mejor descubrirlas por su cuenta, comprenlo si está en oferta, no se van a arrepentir.", "appid": "274190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308478854", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578744000.0} {"text": "amazing but i usually get rage due to ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ up inna mission", "appid": "238090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095539632", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1423310400.0} {"text": "Очень хорошая игра,веселая,энергичная,многостороняя в геймплее,но рокет лига имеет слишком много минусов,при отсутствии которых игра была бы идеальной. 1.Очень плохой переход со Steam на EG(Epic Games).Мало того,что многие и так недолюбливают EG как игровой магазин и лаунчер по многочисленным причинам(я в том же числе),EG решили сделать обязательную привязку аккаунта EG,даже если у вас игра в стиме. 2.И опять же,о великие сервера EG не выдерживают наплыв фортнайтеров и любителей халявы.В итоге,получаем:ужасно долгий поиск игр,нестабильный пинг в играх на многих серверах,баги со входом в турниры,packet loss'ы с идеальным интернетом. 3.Большое количество багов получилось и в трейдах,которые обкуренные psyonix уже не могут пофиксить больше 4 суток.Например,как вам скам с забиранием ваших вещей через баг с отменой трейда?А,ну да,это же калоникс,мы слышим,но мы слепые. 4.Еще больше токсичных игр и страданий.Шкильники фортнайта пришли в бесплатную соревновательную игру.Да,я умер. Но,в целом,если вы ветеран игры,то можно через неприхоть пожевать ракетные сервера Epic Gays.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255417441", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603713600.0} {"text": "Твой противник здесь не какой -либо там Мартинес на карыте, разгоняющейся за долю секунды до 999OVER m/h. Твой враг - камушек. Один подскок и ты скокнул уже на Донбассе. FlatOut 2 впитывает всю твою злость и очищает тебя. После каждого поворота - ты злишься, а FlatOut 2 впитывает злость в себя, после каждого тарана, который урон должен был нанестить предполагаемой машине, нанесся тебе - FlatOut 2 впитывает всю злость в себя, после каждой проебанной гонке, ты жмешь рестарт - ты злишься, и FlatOut 2 впитывает всю злость в себя. FlatOut 2 оставит вас без грехов и осветит вас ибо заменит оно вам все святило вашего понимания в гоночной индустрии движущихся картинок в сложной программе под название FlatOut 2.", "appid": "2990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198227106348", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523707200.0} {"text": "💔When I die You'll love me💔", "appid": "429570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198129522789", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589976000.0} {"text": "Very good game, gg", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198027727873", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1439380800.0} {"text": "годно.", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198817163763", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "This game is pretty much a pill gulping simulator... But it's a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ good one as the gameplay elements will have you jumping round more corners then a rainbow six siege player on crack Overall a amazing game 8/10", "appid": "204100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092576496", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495022400.0} {"text": "Great game fellas, highly recommend it :)", "appid": "222880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086957486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1442750400.0} {"text": "ТОP игра", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201219961", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511697600.0} {"text": "olha tentaram fazer um versão de warz, só que não deu muito certo não muitos bugs poucas armas, muita comida etc ale de graficos muito ruims ao meu ponto de vista, warz pelo menos nos graficos e em outros atributos da de 10 a 0 nesse gamer mais vale a pena baixa possa ser que eles melhorem", "appid": "349700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085460318", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1443268800.0} {"text": "2d minecraft but better. Very fun game to play with friends. Have many weapons and many bosses! I recommend this game.", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198240207858", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529582400.0} {"text": "The game just keeps calling me. I'm a solo player but recently been doing some dungeons and they are so good. This game is a big time sink and it also has its pros and cons but for me eveything just works.", "appid": "306130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050714430", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "E fain jocul insa poate deveni enervant uneori !", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198321493683", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545652800.0} {"text": "Zajebista gierka", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198999039440", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579694400.0} {"text": "Fun Game!!", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198838888453", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594209600.0} {"text": "A simple and fun card game.", "appid": "646570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198434628192", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Stone Cold Steve Austin is probably the best Undertale character in this game so far...", "appid": "391540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077442966", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470139200.0} {"text": "GIVE ME THE FINAL GAME!", "appid": "992310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198434402693", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592740800.0} {"text": "Very fun game the dlc is worth getting in my opinion.", "appid": "233740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010363497", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483531200.0} {"text": "Snake Pass is cute and colourful 3D platformer. Main hero - very flexible snake - is lovely and pretty fun to play. Levels are well designed and look great. If you're using gamepad you won't have any troubles with camera and controls. The only thing that Snake Pass lacks is good story. This game is great for kids and casual gamers, you should give it a try if you like relaxing games.", "appid": "544330", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977048333", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598702400.0} {"text": "Bastante divertido ..", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198289272364", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528545600.0} {"text": "Jednoduchá odpočinková hra, kde, jak samotný titul napovídá, vybarvujete dané obrázky od jednodušších po složitější vzhledem k celkového počtu pixelů či barev. Herní styl je přizpůsobitelný, tudíž si můžete vybrat jakýkoliv obrázek k vybarvování, případně i pracovat střídavě na více obrázcích. Není tak nutné svoje rozpracované dílo dokončit, abyste mohli začít s novým. Díky neustále vydávanému novému obsahu, týkajícího se vždy určitého tématu (vesmír, Vánoce, vlajky aj.), není o nové obrázky nouze.", "appid": "897330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050666947", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Is Ok.", "appid": "449220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198258790927", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1559390400.0} {"text": "cool game if you can stand russians", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198376903915", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1513857600.0} {"text": "Beuatiful game, Amazing soundtrack.", "appid": "361420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135070133", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576411200.0} {"text": "Incredible game, one of my absolute favorites. Very relaxing to play, and the gameplay never stops. If you somehow manage to get bored after some hundreds of hours, slap on a friend and it's a whole new experience again.", "appid": "413150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198125322342", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577880000.0} {"text": "Best game in the franchise for solo experience", "appid": "254700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049151472", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498478400.0} {"text": "игра очень понравилась с захватывающим сюжетом вообщем всем советую", "appid": "1222700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198419253166", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606305600.0} {"text": "LIKE A BLYAT WITH ♥♥♥♥♥", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198353636199", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530619200.0} {"text": "not bad", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198828574525", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546603200.0} {"text": "Apasionante, intenso, bien ejecutado. Una obra de arte que invita a reflexionar. (amo el modo foto)", "appid": "414340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053519503", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578225600.0} {"text": "Recommended.", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561197966349270", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1462104000.0} {"text": "Best of the best Endless game $-) 11 of 10 :)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003836693", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "Спасибо Humble Bundle за игру!", "appid": "239200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135935687", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516968000.0} {"text": "9/10", "appid": "675260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198382933066", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563278400.0} {"text": "Очень фановая игра если играть с друзьями, да в неё надо долго учится играть но оно того стоит.", "appid": "236850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198274172783", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589716800.0} {"text": "i mean its kinda okay i guess", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198221032568", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597579200.0} {"text": "Awesome Game, I love it!", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198067829894", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1395576000.0} {"text": "Zajebista gra polecam. Dużo akcji.", "appid": "587830", "steamid": "profiles/76561198154978129", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1567771200.0} {"text": "En gros, c'est exactement la même chose qu'avant, mais ça n'a rien à voir avec les versions CD/HD. En bien. A défaut de faire de bons jeux, Microsoft nous sert de bons remakes. Points positifs : Globalement, tout les petits problèmes qui avaient le potentiel de vous agacer inutilement ont été réglés, et rien que ça, sachant que c'est toujours le même moteur qu'en 99, ça change énormément de choses. Les animations, de destruction notamment, sont somptueuses (pour un moteur vieux de 20 ans !). Les nouvelles civilisations sont sympas, je sais pas encore Couman jouer les comments, mais bon... Le choix du type de carte est désormais un écran dédié avec un représentation miniature de la carte, ce qui permet de comprendre bien mieux ce qu'on y trouvera. Beaucoup de choix de menus ont enfin une indication, j'ai enfin pu répondre à la question de la différence entre civilisation aléatoire, aléatoire inv. et aléatoire complet. Globalement le jeu est moins austère et plus clair qu'avant. Le renouvellement automatique des fermes (et pas simplement le stock d'avance). Fini les moments type \"ATTAQUEZ CE CHÂTAL MES VAILLANTS HUSKA*chiki chiki chiki*AAARGH LES FERMES !\". Et ça, c'est bien. -25% pour les possesseurs de la HD, je trouve ça honnête. Points négatifs : Bien qu'il utilise encore et toujours le même moteur que la version CD, il ne tournera probablement pas très bien sur votre PC Packard Bell et son fier Windows Millenium - le meilleur de tous - à la pointe de la technologie du siècle dernier. Le jeu me semble néanmoins plus optimisé qu'avant, j'ai moins de problèmes de performances que sur la HD avec le même PC quand il y a 4000 unités sur une carte dérisoire. Néanmoins en multi ne rêvez pas, si c'est \"moins injouable\" que sur la HD, l'expérience reste assez mauvaise : il n'est toujours pas possible de jouer en dérisoire à plus de 15 fps. Problèmes d'IA : lors de certains tests avec 8 IA (c'est possible de mettre une IA en joueur 1) pour comparer la nouvelle IA avec les anciennes, il m'est arrivé de voir des IA se bloquer et cesser toute activité. En dehors de mes tests je n'ai pas vraiment eu de soucis, c'est possible que ça ai été patché... Sans edit de ma part, considérez que je n'ai pas eu le problème depuis et que vous pouvez ignorer le soucis. Edit : pas eu de cas aussi flagrant, mais j'ai surtout fait le zouave en commençant à l'âge impérial avec ressources illimitées (nouvelle option idéale pour se défouler) donc bon... Points meeeh : La bande son totalement refaite. Alors, pour les musiques et tout c'est cool, mais ça inclut aussi les taunt audio (Wololo...) et... C'est pas pareil... Alors d'un côté ça m'a fait tiquer, de l'autre, garder les sons d'origines qui ont sacrément vieilli aurait aussi fait tâche... Donc bon. Meh. En vrai c'est totalement positif, mais bon... Le menu d'assignation des touches est toujours aussi mal conçu. Sachant que les assignations de base sont pour les claviers QWERTY, il est nécessaire de réassigner pas mal de touches. Conclusion : Perso je regrette pas de l'avoir acheté.", "appid": "813780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090032437", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603972800.0} {"text": "Great game.", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198880289078", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "One of the best gtas", "appid": "12210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198334827433", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572868800.0} {"text": "+1000000 к красноречию", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135796839", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491393600.0} {"text": "私たちは中国語が必要とします", "appid": "460160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198315649084", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542456000.0} {"text": "Jogava esse jogo no PS3, 9/10", "appid": "351970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198304478263", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601121600.0} {"text": "Игра в игре.", "appid": "41070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198145269030", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "love it", "appid": "389730", "steamid": "profiles/76561199009683886", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589457600.0} {"text": "10/9 puanım", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561197960574476", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572436800.0} {"text": "Играю в неё в 2001 года", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198268324266", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487505600.0} {"text": "Great game, just takes some practice and a great team, loving it!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080774565", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1471435200.0} {"text": "Gutes Spiel! Bock!!", "appid": "238370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198139621443", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606132800.0} {"text": "much amaze, such wow, 9000/10 would recommend", "appid": "582010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198041311907", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Deceit", "appid": "466240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198839832603", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588075200.0} {"text": "Гра шедевр від id ,вже з самого початку починає захоплювати сюжет ,протягом цілої гри можна пограти в дуже багато міні ігор (бойові ралі, гонка на час, гра з ножом ,гра в колекційні картки і тд. і тп.) , цікаві персонажі, красиві локації ,гонки в пустошах , в грі надзвичайно багато секретів і всяких пасхалок, великий вибір зброї, суперова озвучка, можливість проходити в кооперативному режимі легенду пустошей. Мінуси: криво зроблений двіжок гри і недороблена прорисовка текстур DLC: The Scorchers не русифіковано, могли б вже доперекласти докінця тупарила кінцівка Моя оцінка: Сюжет - 8/10 Графіка - 7/10 Геймплей 8/10 Озвучка 9/10", "appid": "9200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044292111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1415448000.0} {"text": "Bruh", "appid": "40800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198279044094", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "nice game", "appid": "333930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132018307", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434456000.0} {"text": "My Little Brother Love it ! Worth the money now at least he not playing fornite anymore", "appid": "969990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198106336685", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596801600.0} {"text": "Wer wie ich als kleiner Jupp damals Anfang der 80er schon auf dem Atari Space Invaders gespielt hat, der wird sich mit diesem Spiel wohlig an diese Zeit zurück erinnern... Hach :D Ist eben SI mit knalliger Grafik und Musik, das beschreibt es zu 100%. Für mal zwischendurch absolut genial...", "appid": "744050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039255359", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592654400.0} {"text": "recommended to everyone really good game i don't know why this game so much hate, GG bethesda i like the game so much!!!", "appid": "1151340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073917764", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586865600.0} {"text": "The last good CS game, and one of the best fps games out there.", "appid": "240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198152402732", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526126400.0} {"text": "Fun With Friends", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198215002213", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562414400.0} {"text": "Если отойти от концепта \"Настоящего Резидента\", то это объективно лучшая часть серии", "appid": "418370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198262989805", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586779200.0} {"text": "Ох уж эта непередаваемая словами и чувствами атмосфера этого прекрасного деяния 2К . Как же круто вспоминать о пройденном пути данной игры, содрогаться, услышав парочку фраз персонажей, и просто биться в конвульсиях от божественных саундтреков...", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255076971", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529841600.0} {"text": "having a constant existential crisis as a dad sim while also being a ♥♥♥♥♥ dad who sleeps with everyone in town while you try to raise your daughter who you are a bad influence to 10/10", "appid": "654880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198173714817", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "22", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502712000.0} {"text": "Hardcore but fun and addicting game ;)", "appid": "262060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198204544344", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "Forget Age of Empires IV: This version of Age II will live for eternity. It's so good that we should send a copy to every extraterrestrial life in the universe to experience this beauty. 10/10", "appid": "813780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063437060", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573905600.0} {"text": "yeah very good game.....but mostly this game is very positive and good game.", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198329119372", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514808000.0} {"text": "Me surpreendi de mais com esse jogo, iniciei ele quando estava sem internet e só parei quando zerei. fiquei feliz em saber que o 2 já está em desenvolvimento. O game tem um visual belíssimo, a historia é bem intrigante a todo momento, padrão telltale A trilha sonora também é maravilhosa, combina com a vibe do game", "appid": "250320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086649454", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588161600.0} {"text": "Храни вас Аллах", "appid": "1281930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198245792638", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589716800.0} {"text": "it's been a long time since a find a perfect game for me, if you love to explorer, grinding/gathering , built bases, fly spaceships and exocrafts, to play as you feel like, and with friends option too, i recommend it. But you must be a patient person and not a spoiled child that want \"everthing his way and right now\" since the devs works on new content and fixing bugs and new bugs, but nothing that realy kills the game. I see great future to this game, you only have to have patience to get there and enjoy the ride as i do. Cheers to the Devs, keep working hard to perfect this unique game", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198382099363", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1540900800.0} {"text": "What can i say about this game ? This is not only game this is something which hitted me so hard the deep inside that I will never forget. In end I was angry on all my decisions but couldn't change them. It is a beautiful game along with characters, story, concept, choice of decisions, and most beautiful SOUNDTRACK . It is worth paying and playing. Most of the things about this game can't be expressed in words. In the end Life is Strange : )", "appid": "319630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198355204421", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539950400.0} {"text": "ну что скзать... на этой игре я вырос, каждый раз когда захожу, чувствую невероятный оргазм глаз и ушей, саунды просто пизд*тейшие. помню такое воспоминание из детства, захожу в комнату, специально пораньше, чтоб брат не дал пи*ды, захожу в игру, кончил раз сто. этой игре пожизненный ре$пект за атмосферу. олды меня поймут)", "appid": "17390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198439306159", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543665600.0} {"text": "This game is what dead island tried to be. Great graphics along with good gameplay and controls. I like this game a lot and am excited to play it more and upgrade my guy to make him more badass", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198102058636", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517400000.0} {"text": "Процес гри дуже методичний, мінімум дій, мінімум екшену. Проте гра про інше вона про дзен та насолоду від життя. Гру частенько порівнюють з тамагочі, це справедливо, весь ігровий процес спрощений до декількох операцій: - Саджати та прибирати рослини - Поливати рослини - Прибирати бур'яни - Слухати чудову музику Рослини можна купити за реальні гроші чи отримувати по одній випадковій безкоштовній рослині кожен тиждень ( ) Рослини також, як і інші предмети (картинки, смайли, фони і тд.) можно обмінювати, тому завжди є можливість непотрібні рослини обміняти на потрібні. За гроші можно придбати додаткові горшики та фони навколишнього середовища. Загалом рекомендую гру та хочу поділитись власною методикою гри. Особисто заходжу в гру один раз на тиждень, прибираю траву та поливаю рослини, забираю подарунок , якщо треба, то прибираю вже не потрібну рослину та саджаю нову. Все! Свою порцію дзену отримав, музику послухав, можно повертатись до стрімкого життя.", "appid": "375950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135576170", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1440676800.0} {"text": "Pretty good civ. Interesting mechanics, some things feel a bit rough around the edges, but all in all a real solid civ, would recommend 8/10", "appid": "289070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198112959363", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519041600.0} {"text": "Годная утлита, живущая благодаря мастерской.", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198330077256", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1513080000.0} {"text": "Ne Ne", "appid": "222880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081621929", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1510401600.0} {"text": "Best Drunk purchase i have ever made i missed this game", "appid": "32440", "steamid": "profiles/76561197963152529", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595937600.0} {"text": "Polecam fajna prosta gierka", "appid": "438040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198113440522", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "I really do like the game quite alot as its a nice but quite cheap driving type game sort of like jalopy but well less features. of course very very soon there will be what seems to be a large update which im looking forward to!", "appid": "1062960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198351890656", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1573560000.0} {"text": "Çoğu oyuncu bu serinin hikayesinin olmadığını veya önemli olmadığını söyler. Onları dinlemeyin, oyunun muhteşem bir hikayesi var fakat size diğer oyunlarda olduğu gibi altın tabakta servis edilmiyor. Bize 1000 parçalık bir yapbozun sadece 1 parçasını veriyorlar. Kalan parçaların bir kısmı NPClerle olan diyaloglarımız, item açılamalarından oluşuyor ve son dokunuşlar ise parçaları birleştirme kabiliyetimiz ve hayal gücümüze kalıyor. Şunu söyleyebilirim ki dibi görünmeyecek derinlikte bir hikayesi var. Irithyll zindanlarında yalnızlığı iliklerinize kadar hissedeceksiniz. Undead Settlment'ta gözü dönmüş kasaba sakinleri tarafından defalarca öldürüleceksiniz. Irithyll manzarasına dalıp gideceksiniz. fakat aklınızda sadece bir tek şey olacak \" lordları tahtlarına döndürüp ilk ateşe ulaşmalıyım \" pvp sistemiyle, kimi zaman duygulandıran, kimi zaman gaza getiren muhteşem soundtrackleri, Tadı damağınızda kalan boss dövüşleriyle defalarca sıkılmadan oynayacağınız, Oyunu her buildle en az bir kere bitirmek isteyeceğiniz gerçek bir başyapıt. Atmosfere değinmiyorum bile. o anlatılmaz yaşanır.", "appid": "374320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198210007307", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511265600.0} {"text": "Game dead af but very real graphics", "appid": "823130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198146967076", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Si le tiras una peineta al jefe te dan un logro. 10/10", "appid": "252350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074995651", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1438689600.0} {"text": "Best game ever <3", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090345274", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549886400.0} {"text": "Jeżeli masz dużo wolnego czasu i nerwy ze stali, ta gra jest dla Ciebie.", "appid": "40800", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998518992", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1419854400.0} {"text": "sumamente adictivo, tiene la idea principal de OW pero para ser gratis esta muy bien desarrollado, apesar de su mal balanceo constantemente suman personajer y mapas tiene distintos modos de jugo, ademas es liviano, recomiendo darse una vuelta por el juego al final de cuentas es gratis", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117177489", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1495022400.0} {"text": ".", "appid": "221380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198325449966", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600257600.0} {"text": "В целом игра хороша и минус в ней один,это стрельба", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198305953386", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1537185600.0} {"text": "Интересно, красиво, качественно, реиграбельно.", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198835791296", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575028800.0} {"text": "игра конечно не стоит своих денег ,но если вам с другом скучно то эта игра вас развеселит в кооперативе", "appid": "312670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068170779", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "ПАТРОНЫ", "appid": "1172470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198318025350", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606305600.0} {"text": "why dance when you can spin faster in this game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198241873986", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1450008000.0} {"text": "Definitely recommend this one!! Excellent game for more casual players, or more serious gamer's wanting something they can finish in a night or two. Enjoyable story, characters, art style, choices, etc. I'm glad the new studio is working on the sequel, and several of the voice actors will be returning to reprise their roles!!", "appid": "250320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198806763545", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "A small price to pay for salvation", "appid": "413150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198249101150", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562155200.0} {"text": "Played as a kid, never finished it. Now that I finally did, I can say, very, very great game, you never know what is going to happen next. Buuuuuuuuuut it gets a little borring over time, as you keep encountering the same enemies and they are pretty much not a threat to you after some time. 7/10.", "appid": "285500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198033906327", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "30", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435406400.0} {"text": "co-op super meat boy", "appid": "343560", "steamid": "profiles/76561197983952629", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594900800.0} {"text": "eğlenceli", "appid": "559650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198389682145", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1588161600.0} {"text": "What a nice game", "appid": "386360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198197294528", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511352000.0} {"text": "10/10 one of the best games from 2019! + graphics + coop + 100% + all challenges and loot! 55 hrs gameplay!", "appid": "939960", "steamid": "profiles/76561197972799294", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589025600.0} {"text": "Ach Starbound. Als Spieler der die Zeit vor dem großen Update gesehen hat finde ich doch das sich das Spiel um weites entwickelt hat und das zum guten. Wer eine gute Mischung haben möchte aus allem bisherigen Spielen wie Terraria oder Minecraft dem sollte diese Spiel aufjedenfall gefallen. Auch die Story ist sehr interessant und gut erzählt meines erachts. Es ist ebenfalls auch sehr schön wie lebendig die Community ist. Für alle die sich überlegen das Spiel zu kaufen, tut es. Es ist definitiv ein sehr schönes,interessantes und geniales Spiel wie ich find. :D", "appid": "211820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120424216", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1408795200.0} {"text": "Güzel", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198396503764", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606046400.0} {"text": "You can have sex on a unicorn. 10/10 Would Bang.", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092605031", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1451822400.0} {"text": "Решил катануть на бесплатных выходных и понять за что же просят так много денег. Поиграл ровно 1 минуту, т.к. застрял в первой же попавшейся текстуре. Игра супер", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126690315", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "159", "votes_funny": "261", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544788800.0} {"text": "one of my favourite games", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198205881456", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1482580800.0} {"text": "Все что сказано в этом обзоре мое личное мнение, возможно вы будите не согласны со мной. Мне игра понравилась так же как и 2 часть, ну 3 часть конечно же лучше, графика нормальная, сюжет сделали лучше чем в 2 части, текстуры крови от выстрелов тоже улучшили, ну и добавили многое, чего не было в 2 части. Тем кому понравилась 2 часть могу сказать одно, берите не задумываясь, а тем кто еще не разу не играл в эту игру, то тут вы должны сами для себя решить, если вам нравиться такая тематика , убивать врагов со спины что бы вас не заметили, оттаскивать трупы врагов, то я советую взять. Моя оценка 8 из 10.", "appid": "238090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073387782", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "29", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434110400.0} {"text": "needs a second game.", "appid": "32470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008459865", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577016000.0} {"text": "反恐天下第一", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198286358945", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Si vous aimez l'espace, foncez.", "appid": "359320", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971424010", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511870400.0} {"text": "Imagine Fallout or New Vegas set in the dark ages, and you have the start of Skyrim. A free roaming game which gives the player control of where they want to go, what they want to do, and how to do it. This game is long. Really long. Longer than the Fallout games. I can't stress that enough. If you had a choice of only buying one game during summer break, this would be your best bet. There is always something to do, or some place to explore. I bought this on sale for $7.50 and it was every penny well spent. It is annoying getting attacked at random times by dragons. Plus there are a few bugs/glitches, but that always comes with free-roaming games. Your partner in the game can get lost sometimes or stuck on objects. Also your partner will block you every time you want to go back through a door. Those problems are small potatoes though. 8.5/10", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561197973614154", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387886400.0} {"text": "Ну игра мне зашла, но после часа игры стоновиться как-то скучновато, но затягивает. Первые головоломи решал сам, а потом уже приходилось с подсказами от мамы, всё потому что головоломки тупые! (хотя вазможно что я тупой просто) Короче без маменой головы тут не обойтись) 7 маминых подсказок из 10!", "appid": "795100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198228866896", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523620800.0} {"text": "(F2P Battle Match-3/RPG/Card Collector) If and -- both highly-addictive -- had a love child, I imagine that this game would be the outcome. There are separate tabs for Options, and include separate sliders for Music and SFX, Speed (default 1.5x -- I keep mine at 4x), Hints and more. Under the Graphics tab you'll find a place where you can turn off the holiday themes (such as clown skulls for international clown day or pumpkin skulls for Halloween). If your game looks wonky and is flickering, etc., make sure that there's nothing sitting on your controller. ;) : Let's face it, is not about the story. Each kingdom that you explore has a storyline, and these range from amusing to exasperating (looking at you Princess Elspeth!) -- some are even interesting -- but the stories never were meant to be the driving focus of the experience. It's all about the... ! The basics of the are simple: Match gems to gather mana in order to cast spells, and match skulls to do a direct attack on your enemies. You take a turn, your opponent takes a turn. Nowhere in the game will you be required to have quick reflexes. The game starts off with a very good that will teach you what you need to know in the beginning. At this point it's very linear, but after you finish the story in the first kingdom, you'll have a bit more freedom. At this point you can choose which kingdom to unlock next, or you can do one of the following in your completed kingdom(s): : You MUST be connected to the internet to play this game. There are multiple reasons for this, the primary of which is the fact that there are and . : A new troop-of-the-week is released every Monday. This troop can be obtained via chests or from the shop in the tab (purchase with glory). The a releases. Let me explain: is indicated by the color of the border on each card in the following order: White, Green, Blue, Purple, Orange, Turquoise, with white being common and Turquoise being a mythic quality (and the hardest to get from chests). Don't worry, there are stars at the top of the cards that show you how rare they are. The more stars that are colored in, the rarer the card. Every 5 weeks we get a new to play in, which you'll find in... : As you get close to completing all of the kingdoms in Krystara (our main map), you'll be able to unlock the underworld. There you will find , each having its own mini-story. Once you complete the storyline, you'll be able to do a at the site. : Delving is a different kind of gameplay than what you've experienced thus far. You'll still be fighting battles, but this time in a series of 9 rooms -- each with its own rewards -- culminating in a chest of rewards when you either lose your whole team or complete the delve by finishing the boss room. ! It cannot be changed, and if you lose a troop, it's gone for the rest of the delve. This is a love-it or hate-it type of gameplay, and while it make me really anxious at first, once I obtained some reliably-good troops, I really started to enjoy them! ! If you don't want to talk to anyone and don't want to have requirements, there are guilds out there for you, and you can still get some of the basic rewards, just join one that is the highest level possible so that you can have better stat boosts. If you really like this game and want to play it daily, . : is easy -- Just play the game! An active guild will require you to collect your seals every day or two 'til you hit your minimum-required for the guild or the game limit of 2000. The reason for this is the number under Guild Weekly Seals. When you hit 40,000/40,000, your , which will get you the highest possible quality out of those seals. You'll get some of the best troops in the game from those chests, which is why an active guild is recommended! : Use guild seals in the Chests area : Do you have to do PvP? Nope, but it's a great way to see some interesting troop combinations, and trust me, it's not as painful as you think ;) The AI handles the other team. Wait... All of this is free-to-play? Why yes it is! You can play this game every day of your life and never pay a penny. There are of course things that you can buy that will help you along the way and/or make your progression faster, but I don't feel like these things give an unfair advantage. Everything available for purchase is something that you can earn yourself eventually. : This is a highly-addictive battle match-3 game with card collecting (troops) and some RPG aspects (upgrading your classes, kingdoms, troops, etc). Beware, oh ye of OCD, for your playing of other games ends here! Gems of War has a surprising depth to it that keeps me coming back day after day, a great community, and above all else, FUN! Full review located", "appid": "329110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198034193738", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603972800.0} {"text": "Best ARPG on the market. 4 years later and its still being updated.", "appid": "219990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008934375", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "This is a good game for one taps .....", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198892317572", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587297600.0} {"text": "it's ok", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198122027867", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "20", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472644800.0} {"text": "If you love Battlefield series and you wish to get more simulation experience but you dont want to involve yourself with hardcore sim game like Arma 3? Squad is perfect to you. it requires no BRAIN to play. Seriously. Stop using your brain and listen to Squad Leader and you will be just fine. Dont forget to complete game tutorial and spend like 10 hours in training map. it DOES help alot when you know how to use all the weapons and equipment. 7 out of 10 times, if you are in a good squad with decent Squad Leader. Even if you fail the game, it still deliver solid experience. Be a part of the unit and play objective. You will be just fine.", "appid": "393380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198041201867", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1594296000.0} {"text": "The game becomes more complex each year, which has probably limited my play time. I'm looking to get stuck into a long career over the summer and I can't wait. SI: Please consider making the game a bit faster because not all of us have the time to sink into it. Saying that it is a great game if you have the time.", "appid": "872790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198002649681", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Absolutely stunning!", "appid": "751780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119013711", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Great game especially with friends", "appid": "548430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047911461", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594900800.0} {"text": "- экономическая стратегия, в которой необходимо, взяв под контроль небольшой отряд колонистов, отстроить базу на одной из 4 планет. Сначала открыта только одна планета, в процессе развития колонии необходимо достигать различные цели, например, произвести 10 роботов или построить особое здание. После достижения определенного количества целей открывается следующая планета. На каждой следующей планете играть немного сложнее (дается меньше стартовых ресурсов, некоторые здания хуже работают в условиях новых планет), но, в целом, разобравшись в процессе развития колонии, пройти все планеты не составит труда. Игровой процесс условно можно разделить на два периода. При высадке на планету играть достаточно нервно - колония может погибнуть из-за неправильных решений или случайного метеорита, неудачно приземлившегося в столовую. Зато спустя 10-15 минут, когда основные производственные линии уже налажены и начинают прибывать новые колонисты, игровой процесс становится медитативным и расслабляющим. В этот момент начинаешь получать истинное наслаждение от игры. Кроме основного режима игры также есть 4 испытания, в которых обычно колония уже построена и необходимо либо добыть заданное количество ресурсов, либо продержаться определенное время. Также поддерживаются пользовательские испытания через Steam Workshop. В игре очень красивая для экономический стратегий графика и минималистический интерфейс. Музыка приятная и умиротворяющая, создает прекрасную атмосферу для строительства и созидания. В качестве минуса можно отметить отсутствие какой-либо связной кампании и сюжета как такового. Кроме этого есть ощущение незавершенности игры, ощущение, что в игру можно было запросто добавить больше контента: дополнительные технологии, ресурсы и прочее. Итог: любителям космоса и экономических стратегий брать в обязательном порядке, думаю, 50 часов геймплея обеспечено.", "appid": "403190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045482572", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "...", "appid": "211820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198177445726", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "i like this game its very cool", "appid": "20920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198123203357", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1392638400.0} {"text": "This game is for Guns lover , but it's hard for casual gamer", "appid": "311690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038474772", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572696000.0} {"text": "Amazingly fun and addictive. Play with friends for more fun!!!", "appid": "113020", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039839368", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1393243200.0} {"text": "Nice story, and nice gameplay. Even though this game is more than 16 years old i really enjoy playing it. Cant wait to playHalf Life Alyx. Just need a Valve Index for that.", "appid": "220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198280294736", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585569600.0} {"text": "good ♥♥♥♥", "appid": "8870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198114647403", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480248000.0} {"text": "Desire довольно легкий Point-and-click квест. Но иногда страдает частой проблемой для этого жанра - нелогичностью, когда нужно выполнить определенные действия в правильной последовательности, что бы продвинуться по сюжету. Эти действия никак не связаны между собой и догадаться практически невозможно. В игре интересный визуальный стиль, при этом он объясняется сюжетом, так видит мир главный герой. Так же отличная атмосферная музыка. Сюжет конечно на любителя, с первых минут игры тебя окружают персонажи с различными психическими расстройствами: гомосексуализм, религия, феминизм и т.д. Главный герой не исключение, у него есть несколько воображаемых друзей и он видит галлюцинации. Вполне нормальные персонажи в игре это мама, папа и брат главного героя в 1 главе. В итоге Desire это неоднозначная игра, которая стоит потраченного на нее времени. В ней собраны все пороки нашего современного мира, разработчик игры заявляет это прямо в описании игры. В ней собрано много специфичных извращений, эта игра исключительно 18+. И в заключение гениальная цитата из игры \"Держи меня подальше от этой своей гомосятины\".", "appid": "805760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198088777244", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533556800.0} {"text": "Very Good Game!", "appid": "759740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071775687", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Beautifull competitive game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198151830178", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1471694400.0} {"text": "OMG", "appid": "627510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198337413304", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502366400.0} {"text": "10/10", "appid": "220240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198287644612", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595592000.0} {"text": "★ 　　★ ° ☾ ☆ ¸. ¸ 　★　 :.　 . • ○ ° ★　 .　 *　.　.　　¸ .　　 ° 　¸. * ● ¸ .　...Где то　　　° ☾ ° 　¸. ● ¸ .　　★　° :.　 . • ° 　 .　 *　:.　.　¸ . ● ¸ 　　　★　　★☾ °★ . 　　　　.　 °☆ 　. ● ¸ .　　　★　° .　 • ○ ° ★　 .　　　　　　　*　.　 ☾ ° 　¸. ... в этой игре...* ● ¸ 　　　　° ☾ °☆ 　. * ¸.　　　★　★ ° . .　　　　.　☾ °☆ 　. * ● ¸ .　　　★　° :.　 . • ○ °★　 .　 *　.　　　　　　. 　 ° 　. ● .　　　　° ☾ °☆