: "profiles/76561198068135013", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "60", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "It is mostly pretty good. The puzzles are sort of tricky. Fans of the Walking Dead will probably enjoy the references and licensed characters. Fans of bridge constructor will get to do that some more. Not my jam but a solid game.", "appid": "1336120", "steamid": "profiles/76561198019816374", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605873600.0} {"text": "Игра очень классная и затягивающая много геймплея , можно играть с друзьями или же познакомится с кем то в игре , круто сделаны анимации и много другого", "appid": "24960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198272504483", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470657600.0} {"text": "Fikirler çok güzel fakat böyle büyük ve oyuna her detayın sığdırılmaya çalışması iyi bir optimize olmadığı zaman sonunda böyle oluyor. Ve sadece kötü bilgisayarlarda değil çok çok iyi bilgisayarlarda bile donma kasma gerçekten sinir bozucu oluyor oyunun en baştan tekrardan teker teker her şeyin optimize edilmesi gerek gerçekten. Oyunun grafiklerini GPU'nuzu en çok zorlayacak (kastırıcak değil %100 ünü kullandırıcak şekilde) ayarlarsanız CPU ve RAM ınızden biraz daha yük kalkar daha iyi sonuçlar alırsanız Online için tüm grafikleri aşağı çekmek daha iyi bir performans veriyor ( GPU Online da daha önemli diyebilirz aslında)", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198169483551", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1586433600.0} {"text": "Best game ever made! ♡♡", "appid": "220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198422251824", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543406400.0} {"text": "Better then WWE.", "appid": "285900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198332626156", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1493985600.0} {"text": "Strife – Це пародія на League Of Legends (Графіка більш подібніша) В звичайній грі 5 V 5 немає ігорового донату , який впливає на ігровий баланс , но є скіни на героїв які в своє число нічого не дають. Нажаль гра мертва , та і не була популярна в середньому онлайн з 2015 був около 50 к. з 2017 став ледве ледве набирати 1к. Моя оцінка 4/5 1 за графіку 1 за індивідуальне придумування героїв ( без копій з лола , доти , хотс) 1 за швидкість матчу (зазвичай матч триває около 15-30 хв) і 1 за ігровий баланс. В кожному оновленні немає нових багів , як в доті (1 фікс багів + 9 нових багів) Но якщо онлайн малий то і багів відповідно нема )0) Гра мені зайшла в душу аж цілих 14 годин <3 Но чим дальше , тим гірше :с", "appid": "339280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189652999", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511870400.0} {"text": "yellow is sus", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198064229648", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601726400.0} {"text": "🔲 3 yaşındaki kardeşim bile oynayabilir 🔲 Kolay 🔲 Normal ✅ Zor(multiplayer) 🔲 Dark Souls ~ GRAFİKLER ~ 🔲 Paint'le yapılmış gibi 🔲 Kötü ✅ Fena değil 🔲 Oyunun çıkış tarihine göre çok iyi 🔲 İyi 🔲 Çok iyi 🔲 Ustalık eseri ~ İNDİRİMSİZ FİYAT ~ ✅ Bedava 🔲 Hak ettiğinin altında 🔲 Mükemmel fiyat 🔲 Daha ucuz olabilirdi 🔲 Aşırı pahalı 🔲 Para israfı ~ SİSTEM GEREKSİNİMLERİ ~ 🔲 Hesap makinesiyle bile oynayabilirsin ✅ Ortalama 🔲 Yüksek donanım gücü istiyor 🔲 NASA bilgisayarı ~ OYNANIŞ SÜRESİ ~ 🔲 Çok kısa (0-3 saat) (Oyunun kendi haritaları.) 🔲 Kısa (3-15 saat) 🔲 Ortalama uzunlukta (15-50 saat) 🔲 Uzun (50-90 saat) 🔲 Aşırı uzun (90-200 saat) ✅ Bitmiyor (Atolye haritaları ile sonsuza kadar oynanabilir.) ~ EĞLENCELİ Mİ?~ 🔲 Kuru boya izlemeyi tercih ederim 🔲 Zar zor eğleniyorsun ✅ Kendini tekrarlıyor 🔲 Aşırı eğlenceli 🔲 Hayatında oynayabileceğin en eğlenceli oyun", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198364336570", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597752000.0} {"text": "Много слышала про Life Is Strange, но желанием играть не горела. Но всё-таки мне было интересно, почему игра про подростков, хипстеров и неформалов наделала столько шума, получая сплошь восторженные отзывы. Поиграв в Life Is Strange, могу теперь высказать своё мнение. Это не квест, не интерактивное кино. Это самый настоящий, мать его, интерактивный сериал с 3D графикой. Почему сериал? Потому что игра поделена на эпизоды (их 5), на момент написания отзыва вышло 3 эпизода, а 2 оставшихся приходится ждать. Да-да, ждать :( В игре есть немного квестовой составляющей, когда порой надо действительно подумать, но основное время тратится на исследование игрового мира, просмотр роликов/кат-сцен и разговоры. Уфф, как же сложно что-либо писать о сюжете без спойлеров. Главный герой игры - девушка Максин (Макс) Колфрид. Ей исполнилось 18 лет и она учится в высшей школе. Мечтает обзавестись крутой фототехникой, фанатеет со своего препода, любит винтаж, ретро, селфи на полароид и инди музыку. В общем, Макс - хипстер. Вроде кажется, да что тут интересного, типичное начало любого подросткового шлака, если бы не одно но... В игре есть детективная составляющая сюжета, которая начинает постепенно раскрываться. Появляется тонна вопросов, и что удивительно, на все эти вопросы игра постепенно даёт ответы. Сюжет проработан до мельчайших подробностей! Хвала сценаристам! Никаких недоговорок и упущений. Значительный упор сюжета сделан на том, что вы сами решаете его дальнейшую судьбу. Все ваши поступки имеют последствия (хорошие, нейтральные или плохие). О некоторых последствиях вы узнаёте практически сразу, в остальных случаях гораздо позже, вплоть до следующего эпизода. Поэтому в Life Is Strange надо мыслить масштабно, принимая какой-либо выбор. Но порой, даже при скрупулёзном обдумывании того или иного выбора, сюжет преподносит неожиданный поворот. Угадать дальнейшее развитие сюжета невозможно. Приятная картинка, красивые локации и пейзажи. В общем, глазам приятно. Но если вы гурман в сфере компьютерной графики, то можете сразу проходить мимо Life Is Strange. Эта игра создана для погружения в сюжет и атмосферу, а не ради гонки за качеством графики. 1) Управление меня не совсем устраивает. Точнее его часть, где мышью выбирается нужное действие. Когда надо быстро выполнить действие и счёт идёт на секунды, это вообще неудобно. 2) Не совсем понравился 1-й эпизод. Он через чур насыщен этой подростковой жизнью, \"масштабными\" проблемами подростков и ежедневной школьной рутиной. Возможно, будь мне лет 15-18, я бы прониклась глубиной проблем персонажей игры. Но теперь мне кажется всё это смешным и нелепым. К счастью, все эти \"глобальные\" проблемы в дальнейшем забываются и уходят на дальний план. Хотя, тут можно найти плюс: наверняка игра напомнит о вашем подростковом периоде, вас посетит ностальгия о славных беззаботных деньках, встретятся знакомые ситуации из прошлой жизни... Или вы просто сделаете фейспальм от такой ностальгии. В общем, если игра вызывает хоть какие-либо эмоции, это хорошо. 3) Деление игры на эпизоды. Некоторые считают, что это способ выкачивания денег, другим это не нравится из-за ожидания. Мне не нравится именно по 2-й причине. Если вы тоже не любите ждать, пока забудьте про игру. Купите её после выхода всех эпизодов. Конечно же любителям быстро пробежать тупо по сюжету, не обращая внимания на сторонние вещи и их исследование. Если вы предпочитаете быстрое прохождение игр, лучше не покупайте. Какое мнение может сложиться об игре, если её пройти забивая на всё, кроме основного сюжета? Правильно, никакое. В эту игру надо погрузиться и вникнуть, чтобы собрать все факты и сложить всё вместе. Ещё игра может не понравиться людям, привыкшим к сплошному экшену. И просто нетерпеливым людям, не способными монотонно выполнять одни и те же действия без возникновения негатива/злости/бешенства. Игра меня поразила и просто затянула. Life Is Strange моя первая игра в подобном жанре, поделенная на эпизоды. Что ж, она смогла меня заинтересовать и оставить положительные впечатления. Она смогла подарить ощущение, когда тебе настолько интересно, что пусть весь мир подождёт! Заслуженно ставлю игре 9.5/10 и продолжаю примерять на себя роль Хатико. Ждать, ждать и ещё раз ждать.", "appid": "319630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048795324", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "953", "votes_funny": "115", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435492800.0} {"text": "this the game is amazing it combines great graphics with a storyline that puls u in once u start playing u just can not stop. I often find that when i start a game i cant finish because im easily board how ever this is one of those rare games that enthralls me until the end definitely worth playing over and over again.", "appid": "17460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198024354933", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1357128000.0} {"text": "A fun game with lots of replay value. You'll spend hours unlocking all the characters, traits, items, and super abilities. Then you can create custom characters made out of everything you unlocked. The game has you travel through a city eventually reaching the Mayor's location and then you have multiple ways to proceed. I just played through as the zombie character. I was supposed to kill and zombify everyone. Instead I was elected into the position of mayor by the voters I had won over when traveling through the city. This required saving up a lot of money from like selling bats and knives and using the money to remove traits that made my zombie unable to speak and one that made people either flee in terror or attack me when seeing me. So I was a friendly zombie. Though of course killing and zombifying everyone would have been the easier option. This game is a lot of fun. There's some grind but you do it just by playing the game. Unlocking traits and items require chicken nuggets which you get my leveling up as you travel through the levels. You just do a run through the city and you get several nuggets just by playing. I highly recommend this game.", "appid": "512900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008929643", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1562673600.0} {"text": "Its like CS:GO", "appid": "222880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198056951289", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589025600.0} {"text": "Dear Sick Chicken Studios, I absolutely loved this love letter of a game. Please make more games, and give me review keys to sing your praises. Everyone, this is a short but extremely sweet game to those who are lovers of science fiction, fantasy, the 80's, the 90's, LucasArts, and Sierra. To get even more specific would be spoiling the fun. Let's get to the particulars. For a pixelated game, it's looks great. The game has a serious Sierra fantasy/sci-fi look. The cut scenes are those wonderful pixelated but cartoon cut scenes that reminded me of Saturday morning cartoons. The voice acting is very good. Considering a very small group of people did so many voices is an achievement. I enjoyed listening to all the background stories, even if they had nothing to do with the main plot. There were many laugh out loud moments, which hasn't happened in a while for me. The dialogue is great. I took so many screenshots not just because the game looked great but that the dialogue was so funny! The soundtrack is DLC for a reason. It is very good. It covers both genres of medieval fantasy and 80's-90's techno dark fantasy very well. I fully intend on purchasing the soundtrack. Now the puzzles. Unlike Sierra and LucasArts, you won't be banging your head in trying to figure them out. The emphasis is the story. There is also an ingame journal to keep track of what you are supposed to be doing, but it is there for comic effect more than anything else. Now, the story is a complete cliche. However, when you have got a great script, great music, and wonderful characters, it doesn't matter. It is paying homage to a beloved genre. This is a game I will be buying/gifting to give my monetary support and to spread the word about this great little indie title. Sick Chicken, I look forward to what you will be doing in the future!", "appid": "872750", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006176581", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "36", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1556971200.0} {"text": "Un muy buen juego.", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561197966014126", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561118400.0} {"text": "Das Spiel ist meiner Meinung nach, besser geeignet zum lernen, für Personen unter 18, da es in der realen welt im umgang mit waffen zu unfällen kommen kann. Ich empfehle es jedem der von Waffen jeglicher Art begeistert sind und mehr darüber erfahren wollen.", "appid": "262410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198154037132", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1411905600.0} {"text": "The game looks like it's from the 90's but it's a funny new puzzel game. You move the boats from point A to B using Wind and the Current of the Water to move them along. The Mechanics and physics of the game is very well done. You'll have reef/sandbar in the way that you'll need to move around. So controlling a few ships at a time helps. Now I can see how the early settlers felt like in the Ocean. Like the God's were F*cking with them. Would love to see some achievements for the game.", "appid": "416080", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977083756", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446811200.0} {"text": "Uma dlç de jogo, mesmo sendo antigo continua divertido!", "appid": "223710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090917393", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491307200.0} {"text": "top", "appid": "666220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004148486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "ĐẢM BẢO......chiến tranh chưa kết thúc", "appid": "418460", "steamid": "profiles/76561197966140447", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562241600.0} {"text": "It's a nice game :) i love the way it plays yrs gameplay modes every thing is nice BUT! we cant BHOP xD", "appid": "550650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198418538512", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1546171200.0} {"text": "good game to play if you like matching tiles games.", "appid": "567140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032162080", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1565956800.0} {"text": "good gameeeeee", "appid": "397900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120266134", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Has some potential. Its a standard builder like Ark, Empyrion, 7 Days to die, Osiris new dawn, Conan exiles etc. Farm materials, build a hut, Snap together walls etc, this unlocks constructors and auto-miners that make this process easier. It doesn't stray much from conventions and I would argue Empyrion is better in almost every way. A few things Nomads adds over Empyrion; -Better graphics in general. -Slightly less indoor rain. -Conveyors (basically tubes that connects Constructors to containers, this adds hours of fun and complexity). -Electrical connections, every device must be manually connected with wires to a power source. -Great physics engine that lets you do funny things like frame a tree then pick it up. -The ability to just dig a hole anywhere and find resources. -I also found it very accessible and easy to understand. But in almost every other respect, Empyrion is a much better builder, has enemies, weapons, quests, multiplayer (100 player servers), Poi’s, multiple planets, multiple systems, Blueprints, etc. I would also argue Conan Exiles has better graphics and lighting with similar building (just no airships or vehicles) The game is also crippled by lack of multiplayer. I personally find this the biggest issue But, the game kept me entertained for 50 hours. I enjoyed it more than some AAA (£39.99) titles so it gets a thumbs up at £10.", "appid": "504050", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970685560", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "63", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1527854400.0} {"text": "A huge spinoff of your regular Hack'n'Loot genre, Book of Demons is a very fun, skill driven and funny game. The thing that Drives me playing this game the most is the way the game progresses with you, as you level up the lesser enemies become weaker, but at the same time it becomes more challenging with the introduction of new mechanics and enemies. The paper like graphics reminds me of Guild of Dungeooners, but unlike that game this is way more balanced and fun. I recommender this game any day of the week.", "appid": "449960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045598071", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545220800.0} {"text": "Gra warta polecenia :X", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198281892726", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517400000.0} {"text": "not bad", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198342563765", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "who else reviewed the game just for the achievement? lmao", "appid": "322170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198382782636", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530360000.0} {"text": "The definitive version to get for this trilogy of remakes. Looks and plays great. PC does what consoles don't.", "appid": "731490", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971158734", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "yehh sta buenardo falta q le metan mas cositas con el tiempo", "appid": "739630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198294262241", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1602331200.0} {"text": "Merhabalar canlar, sevgili arkadaşlar, değerli oyuncu ablalarım, abimlerim, beyefendiler ve hanımefendiler 🤗 Rusyadan hepinizi Selamlıyorum. 🤚😊🙂 Herzamanki gibi bu oyunada incelemeyi Türkce yazacayım çünki Ben yarı Türküm ve biliyorum ki Türkler oyun incelemeyi Ruslardan daha çok okuyor ve seviyor. Bunu Rusyalı ve Türkiyeli arkadaşlarımdan örnek biliyorum. Neyse Geçelim oyuna olan incelememize: Mount & Blade II: Bannerlord isimli bu oyun Türk yapımı bir oyun olmasının yanında yıllarca oyuncuların özelliklede Türk oyuncuların çok beklediyi bir oyundur. Daha önce çıkmış olan Mount & Blade Warband oyunu çıkmış olduğu yıllarda çok sevilmiş bir oyun ve türk yapımı oyun olarak piyasaya sürülmüş olan ilk oyunuydu diye biliyorum yanlış biliyorsamda kusuruma bakmayın 🙂 bildiyimi söylüyorum. 😊🙂 Yarı Türk olsamda Mount & Blade II: Bannerlordi oynayarak Türklere bi nebzede katkım olması için oyunu oynama kararı verdim ve iyikide vermişim. Mount & Blade Warband oynayan arkadaşlar oyunun atmosferini biliyor oynamayan ilk kez oynayacak arkadaşalara şunu söylemeliyim ki oyundaki atmosferler o kadar güzel ki sanki Bir oba beyimişsin yada Viking dizilerinden gördüyümüz bir at üstünde yağmacı ve ya Tarihi filmlerdeki gibi bir silahşörlük yaparak kendini adeta oyuna kaptırıyorsun. Oyunda ister eşkiyacılık yaparak gelene gidene sataşmak elindeki mallarını paralarını elinden almak daha kötüsü köylere baskın yaparak yağmalamak oluyor adeta bir bela oluyorsun millete🙂 Oyun size bu özgürlüyü veriyor. Yada bir Kralın emirlerine girmek, onun verdiyi emirleri istekleri yapmak yada Kendi ordunu kurmak kendi Kralığını beyan etmek tamamen senin elinde. Oyundaki Grafiklerden tut savaş mekanikleri, at üstünde okçuluk yapmak, kılıç salamak adeta eski zamana giderek o yılı yaşıyormuş gibi bir havası var. Ben Total war ve rol yapma oyunlarını sevenbiriyim bilen biliyor beni. 🙂😊 Bu oyunda haritada özelikle Total War oynuyormuşsunuz gibi bir havasıda var. Kaleler feth etmekden tut savaş mekanikleri, at üstünde süvarileri yönetmek, piyadelere hücum yada geri çekil emrinin vermekler hepsi, hepsi var. Bazı hataları var ama daha Oyun daha erken erişimde inşallah düzeltmeleri dileyiyle herkese tavsiye ediyorum. Türk Yapımı Olmasıda gurur verici birşey. İnşallah dahada iyi yerlere gelir.🤗🙂😊 Herkese İyi Oyunlar... 🤗", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198231765324", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "389", "votes_funny": "53", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1586347200.0} {"text": "无MOD，不游戏", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198317085598", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485864000.0} {"text": "Pra descrever esse jogo, me vem a mente 3 outros: Battlefield + Grand Theft Auto 5 + Minecraft Logo teremos veículos, e daí sim será mais parecido ainda. Rust é o melhor jogo de survival que eu já joguei!", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198056466199", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1443009600.0} {"text": "Distraint is a game that tells a story about how greed destroys the soul of its main character, Price. It is a short yet terrifying look at how the guilt and emotions a person may feel from hurting others for their own gain cannot be erased or suppressed. No matter the lip service a person might give to others to compensate for taking advantage of them, the guilt of their conscience will chase them down and kill them. As the scenarios in Distraint show, those most likely to be abused are poor, elderly, or vulnerable in some way. Ultimately, \"what goes around comes around.\" A nice little story with a lesson on morality, set in uniquely terrifying environments.", "appid": "395170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198001782126", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578744000.0} {"text": "One Of The Most Best Open World Game (~_^) But My First Piority Is GTV 5", "appid": "307690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198824601934", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1531742400.0} {"text": "Великолепное место где дети узнают много нового о свои матерях. А специализированные врачи ставят диагнозы ничего не подозревающему человеку.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130933961", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555070400.0} {"text": "Very well !", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030295026", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1386244800.0} {"text": "Вполне себе не плохая игра. Много конечно свойственных жанру затягиваний в геймплее, но история интересная.", "appid": "436160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198314659238", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554552000.0} {"text": "Это можно сказать \"культовая игра\" от достаточно известной компании ТелТейл Итак , перейдём к обзору Сюжет+: Он просто прекрасен. Это нужно видеть , его нельзя описать Геймплей+: Как такового его нет , иногда просто есть Квик Тайм Ивенты , и выбор ответа и искать улики. Графика+: В лучших традициях ТелТэйл . Иногда конечно , картинка пропадает(Небольшие графические баги) Раскрытие персонажей и их мотивы+: Вы узнаём разных персонажей понимаем их мотивы , они перед нами раскрываются. Сюжетные повороты+: Нет таких прям неожиданных , но есть достаточно резкие. Диалоги+: Диалоги здесь зависят от нашего выбора и как этот персонаж к нам относится. Можно сказать и так , но здесь вы увидите черезмерную жесткость , но как именно нуарный детектив он достаточно не подходит , но как квест он просто прекрасен. Конечно , прекрсный сюжет , хорошие персонажи (раскрытые) , хорошая графика , прекрасные диалоги. Минусов я не нашёл. 9.5 из 10 В это нужно сыграть.", "appid": "250320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110675054", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "108", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1451044800.0} {"text": "very nice yes", "appid": "240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082244511", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498651200.0} {"text": "Отличный баланс в игре, всем рекомендую! Пожалуй время с хорошой командой можно провести сколько угодно!", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198831875441", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1527595200.0} {"text": ":D", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198207745188", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Eskiden pek beğenmezdim kötü derdim ama harika,efsanevi,epik,çok güzel ve 10/10 !!!", "appid": "8870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198443859039", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584273600.0} {"text": "good =)", "appid": "224260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051871016", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1414843200.0} {"text": "Один из лучших шутеров ,что я когда-либо играл ( И как я вообще его упустил в 16 году ?..)", "appid": "1237970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198137032552", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595764800.0} {"text": "Шикарная игра", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198128065199", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582200000.0} {"text": "Es de esos que engañan un poco: ves tantas lucecitas que crees que mueres sí o sí, pero siempre te dejan un agujerito para protegerte. Los enemigos tochos te resisten lo justo para que los mates y desaparezcan sus disparos. Aunque sí es cierti que en los últimos niveles a ver quien es el macho que aguanta sin que te toquen xd. Muy divertido", "appid": "285440", "steamid": "profiles/76561197995926709", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": ".", "appid": "48700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198023128890", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "LOVE THE GAME, this game has made me have times of joy and happiness. but it has also given me times of hate and rage perfect game for anyone who wants to rage a lot :D!!!", "appid": "200210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198216979169", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1510920000.0} {"text": "Simulator Overwatch", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198116049967", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1497873600.0} {"text": "топ", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198867494272", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562414400.0} {"text": "Nice game.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198864480579", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1556625600.0} {"text": "very good game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198274882813", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "If you think about it, Gordon is a simp for Alyx The dude went and grabbed larvae to heal his queen 15/10 Gordon the type of guy to pay for Alyx Vance onlyfans", "appid": "380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198303514452", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587643200.0} {"text": "Bone crunching stickmam arcade action, bigger and better than the first one.", "appid": "980300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007342553", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Not a bad game. For the price I hope they intend on contuinuing to expand it, as its currently not that deep. Ignore the negative reviews, most if not all try to compare it to dwarf fortress, which it is not. While DF will always be the king, it is really showing its age at this point, and I dont mean the graphics. DF is really really spaghettified and still single threaded. Dont get me wrong, the depth of DF is great, and I still play it, this mornign in fact. But I like Dorf corp as well.", "appid": "252390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084416564", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550232000.0} {"text": "resident evil 3 remake is a good remake but not as well as resident evil 2 remake. i'm an old school fan of resident evil franchise , i played the original games and it's one of my favorite franchises of all time and i enjoyed these remakes but Capcom removed lots of content from them specially this game. don't get me wrong it's a good game but for new players that want to understand the story of the classic games these remakes are a little bit confusing but other than that gameplay is very smooth like the RE2 remake , the game optimization is awesome , story is not long like the classic one but not that short like some people say , overall playtime depends on how you play the game , if you know how to play a resident evil game your playtime will be over 7-8 hours for sure but if you don't like searching every corner for items and just want to complete the game your playtime will be under 5-4 hours. overall if you are an old fan of this franchise this is a hell of a ride for you and if you are the new member to the family it's gonna be a very fun experience but these are remakes and story is not exactly the same story from the original games , they added and removed lots of content so beware.", "appid": "952060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198278288461", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600689600.0} {"text": "This is an awesome game - i recommend it , awesome solo games , hard ones, and ITS FUN!", "appid": "10680", "steamid": "profiles/76561197999939426", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1324987200.0} {"text": "gud", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198353930498", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590148800.0} {"text": "I only got this game to get the TF2 hat, but is a nice game", "appid": "99900", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970580992", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595246400.0} {"text": "Jogo esta muito mal optimizado em varias partes mais vale a pena", "appid": "311210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062677205", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446811200.0} {"text": "this game is awesome, just amazing. so much references to great anime and games, you will have so much fun playing this game that you will love this game instantly.", "appid": "1089980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198311970341", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598011200.0} {"text": "Muito bom o jogo, recomedo.", "appid": "374040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198040191809", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1465387200.0} {"text": "한국서버가지마 그냥 전투민족밖에 없다 서양섭에서 진정한 원시인생존해봐라", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198139993837", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1483099200.0} {"text": "Dontnod clearly has a lot more heart to share and story to tell after this lovingly narrated (and free) teaser for the highly anticipated sequel to Life is Strange.", "appid": "845070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018634267", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "29", "votes_funny": "20", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535803200.0} {"text": "画面虽然不够吸睛，对人物也无法流畅操作。但是不错的剧情架构和单调的背景音乐（笑），让玩家在游戏中并不会太在意这些缺陷。 期待2017年的新作。", "appid": "206440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148803427", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "This game has a lot of Mojo packed in $2.99! The updates have Mojo too! Sexual Void - spread the Mojo!", "appid": "1310910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052975604", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600689600.0} {"text": "very fun", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198944637809", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577707200.0} {"text": "good", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032935710", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529409600.0} {"text": "любовь - это отдавать ей последние зелья любовь - это поднимать ее первой любовь - это позволить добить ей элитного босса <3", "appid": "552500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198444896670", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521288000.0} {"text": "Признаюсь, каюсь - сперва ставил ператку, еще когда игра была в крайне раннем виде. Купил, потому что такие вещи нужно иметь в библиотеке, потому что таких разработчиков нужно поддерживать. Играя в Атом, со скупой слезой вспоминаю второй фолыч и санитары подземелий. Игра не для всех, но ценители рпг (а рпг элементов тут больше чем в 3м и 4м фолычах вместе взятых) будут довольны. Сюжет довольно простой, но вечера провести за Атомом - крайне приятно, особенно после тяжелого рабочего дня, когда не хочется заходить ни в какие онлаен шутаны\\мобы\\выживачи. По производительности вопросов к игре у меня нет, за все время игры на пиратке не было проблем. Советую? Да, но прежде оцените демку. Жду продолжения игры Стим заставляет обновить обзор - ну ок, игра по прежнему хороша, разработчики по прежнему молодцы) ждем апдейт ^^", "appid": "552620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057084199", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": ".", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198355021861", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573214400.0} {"text": "short game with a good story. :(", "appid": "417860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198147835042", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577188800.0} {"text": "可能是德国线路里风景最美的一条线了，但是附带的机车就有点坑了，特别是189简直没法玩。如果钱包允许的话建议买virtual railroads的111和189替换掉原装的。但是还是比较推荐购买这条线路。", "appid": "621922", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051926885", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549368000.0} {"text": "A super fun game where you can download mods in game with the click of a button, and pretty much do whatever you want! Super cool physics and its fun just doing random things! 11/10 -IGN Game of Dah YearZ", "appid": "4000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198128997177", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1424088000.0} {"text": "Хорошая игра чтоб играть на онлайн уроках.", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198875276910", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595160000.0} {"text": "Nice", "appid": "438130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198449211757", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519992000.0} {"text": "Sono veramente rimasto colpito da che cosa può nascondere la copertina di questo titolo.Devo confessare che a prima vista pensai che fosse il classico gioco di serie B.Già le mie idee cambiarono quando vidi il trailer e decisi di acquistarlo(sotto consiglio di Vesler) poichè vedevo che conteneva tutti i generi:azione,survival horror, coop,ecc.Soldi spesi veramente bene ACCIDENTI! Gameplay:fantastico,meccaniche di gioco:semplici da imparare e punta del piccolo(purtroppo)diamante e la personalizzazzione direi abbastanza varia delle armi del personaggio.L'unico difettto(che poi non è neanche del gioco) è che bisogna avere almeno un altro amico con cui giocare poichè da soli è difficile e ammesso che siate bravi dopo poco stufa e poi è veramente difficile trovare una partita in multiplayer anche solo con un altro giocatore.Consiglio caldamente di comprare questa piccola Perla(con la P maiuscola) perchè merita veramente molto.", "appid": "205550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057331600", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1364558400.0} {"text": "1990'larda çıkan kült FPS'leri kaçırdınız mı? Abilerinizi/ablalarınızı o efsane oyunları çıktığı günlerdeki heyecanıyla oynayabildikleri için kıskanıyor musunuz? Eski model FPS'lerin göz bozan grafiklerini, acımasız dinamiklerini, mekaniklerini merak ediyor ama o oyunların kurulum ayarlarıyla uğraşmak istemiyor musunuz? O zaman Project Warlock'u sizin için yapmışlar. Müzikleri çok güzel, aksiyonu sert ve 1990'lardaki gibi insana afakanlar bastıran alanlarda geçiyor çoğunlukla. Grafikleri daha fazla \"eskitebilmenizi\" sağlayan özel ayarları bile bulunuyor. Eski oyunlara göndermeler yapan easter egg'leri falan var. Birçok silah çeşidi var, özel güçler var, bazıları bir halta yaramıyor ama olsun :D 1990'larda çıkan oyunlar da her yönüyle konforlu oyunlar değillerdi zaten. RPG elementleri içeren FPS'leri ve retro-piksel oyunları sevenlere tavsiye ederim. En az 5 - 10 saat eğlenirsiniz. oyunda kalıcı ölüm var. Sınırsız can hakkınız olsun istiyorsanız Casual mod'da başlayın, diğer mod'larda yedek canlarınızın hepsi biterse oyun bitiyor haberiniz olsun.", "appid": "893680", "steamid": "profiles/76561198159985611", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587038400.0} {"text": "This game is excellent i really enjoy it.", "appid": "859570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198171988255", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588248000.0} {"text": "top o jogo", "appid": "243800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198398709802", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1540987200.0} {"text": "Dobrá survival hra hlavne keď hráš s kamošmi, veľmi sa mi páčil výber postáv a všetky tie monštrá zo sanity ale aj bossovia, doporučil by som ale hrať s niekym kto tam má už niečo nahrané :D", "appid": "322330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198931464762", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587297600.0} {"text": "BEST MMORPG GAME !", "appid": "306130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198315729818", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554984000.0} {"text": "Just M O N I K A.", "appid": "698780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198237542568", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519387200.0} {"text": "its gud", "appid": "582660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138841394", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "갓!겜!", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079240930", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1404302400.0} {"text": "Is this game a masterpiece? No, not yet, it is still in Early Access, but it will be one when it is finished. At least when they do not ruin anything anymore. The gameplay is already fanatstic. A hectic roguelite FPS experience in a beautiful (Ancient Egyptian inspired) Pyramid. Or Ziggurat? Crypt? Mausoleum? Whatever, you start already inside (whatever mission you choose) and have to defeat hordes of enemies intent on killing you. The rooms are not only elaborately decorated but also rather large and give you much room to maneuver, which helps avoiding all those projectiles hurled at you. So you can fight - until you die. Fans of the genre know what to expect - frantic FPS action. You take a few coins with you after death and can improve your unlocked heroes and their equipment. Before you start a run, you can select your hero, his equipment and one of the available quests. I played with m+kb (gamepad supported, but I am not sure if this is the best choice in a FPS) and had no problems on 3440x1440@100Hz. The devs plan to add more content to the game, updates are released regularly (at the time of writing). Candidate for the new roguelite FPS champion. Challenging, beautiful, smooth - as it should be.", "appid": "1159560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198019466684", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1606132800.0} {"text": "Trotz einigen Bugs/Glitches absolut empfehlenswert und spielbar. Werde es auch weiterhin spielen! ;-) Updates kommen regelmäßig.", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967400760", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1421409600.0} {"text": "bellísimo", "appid": "413150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092095534", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "Abzu es una oda a nuestro hermoso planeta azul, una odisea donde de manera magistral os presentarán las maravillas y misterios de nuestro océano acompañadas de una música sublime, es un juego que debes disfrutar un viernes o cualquier día en el cual busques simplemente relajarte. A pesar de su simplicidad es un juego que oculta un misterioso lore y te hace pensar en todos los tesoros naturales que tenemos por descubrir como especie en nuestro planeta y también concientizarnos en el cuidado de nuestro mundo hogar. El juego no dura más de 5 horas pero vale cada minuto que inviertas en el. Cómpralo se que te va a encantar.", "appid": "384190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198246250848", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579867200.0} {"text": "5/10 good game *Wolololo* 10/10 best game ever", "appid": "221380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198311868067", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "64", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545480000.0} {"text": "Like Skyim but with no guns 12/10", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271271824", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "Lisa is so palanced and powerfull as well. But Ace is a bit useless. Overall, The new map is awesome!", "appid": "554381", "steamid": "profiles/76561198273356985", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481284800.0} {"text": "кал, почему не запускается??", "appid": "65540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065009366", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1396353600.0} {"text": "meilleur jeux de survie de zombie créé ?", "appid": "108600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198353181037", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1563969600.0} {"text": "best time of my life 100 kills in one game", "appid": "391460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066273646", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1458388800.0} {"text": "Una obra maestra proveniente de Japón, especial para machos pechos peludos que se respetan. No ♥♥♥♥...", "appid": "1226530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198061831134", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595160000.0} {"text": "Бесподобство в чистом виде! Восхищение,Гордость и Наслаждение - это то,что игра мне подарила. Спасибо большое за игру!", "appid": "355880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198198507455", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518177600.0} {"text": "Very Kewl Kanye", "appid": "568970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198937581245", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577275200.0} {"text": "Farm Together is one of the best if not the best farming games out on the market. The relaxing nature that this game provides is outstanding, it's simple it's fun and most of all very addictive. The games features are most enjoyed while playing with a personal friend rather than a randome player. Overall if you are looking for a farming and casual game for you and your friend this is it. 10/10 - Simply the best online farming game.", "appid": "673950", "steamid": "profiles/76561199066869520", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594555200.0} {"text": "Jogo bem legal. Novos movimentos de batalha. Skins mais atualizados. Modos de jogo divertidos. Uma pequena história bem formulada e interessante. A falta de um modo história realmente pesou no julgamento da maioria, mas não que dizer que não seja um bom jogo. Particularmente o game me agradou, mas porque sou fã. Recomendado.", "appid": "272510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087644034", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1418558400.0} {"text": "Hand of Fate 2 - это шаг вперед. Графоний завезли Появился сюжет - теперь мы не просто побеждаем очередного Босса, а каждое испытание является отдельной историей со специальными правилами. Добавили мини-игр: Кости - надо выбросить число равное или больше цели \"Колесо фортуны\" - карты бегают по кругу Маятник - Лучом маятника надо попасть по успешной платформе и не попасть по платформе провала Больше видов оружия - Тяжелое (Топоры, булавы) - двуручное оружие против бронированных (да, да они добавили броню) врагов Одноручное (меч + щит) - Позволяет не просто блокировать, но и контратаковать атаки противника Парное (два кинжала или дубинки) - Против быстрых врагов Спутники В игре есть 4 спутника, они дают бонусы в мини-играх и участвуют в бою, но главное это история. У каждого спутника есть своя история, пройдя которую мы улучшим своего спутника Маг-бард - бонус в \"Колесе фортуны\"пуляет магическими сферами и накладывает щит, который может выдержать один удар. Северянин - бонус в костях, воин ближнего боя ломится вперед и оглушает врагов Имперская солдатка - бонус в маятнике, воин ближнего боя, стреляет из пистоля, дает большой шанс казнить противника Дочка кузнеца - бонус в старой доброй перетасовке карт, танк с молотом, наносит большой урон броне Боевая система - Добавили казни, у каждого оружия своё умение. Игра заставит вас бомбить, здесь нет легкого уровня, поэтому будете перепроходить уровни раз за разом.", "appid": "456670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198102838848", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "19", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511352000.0} {"text": "i am a duck i play it cause duckey told me its cool", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198337443772", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499256000.0} {"text": "Good", "appid": "42680", "steamid": "profiles/76561198967905345", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604404800.0} {"text": "Bom jogo!! Mesmo sendo antigo ele é ótimo, recomendo!!!", "appid": "200260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198127017914", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1406289600.0} {"text": "A great game with good mechanics fantastic story and cleaver way to keep you replaying. Recommended.", "appid": "439190", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992170690", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1560945600.0} {"text": "Игра в стиле первой части. Из минусов - долгая загрузка заданий.", "appid": "268500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198054408899", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1461240000.0} {"text": "Забавно, как одинаково наш мозг реагирует на некоторые раздражители. Достоверно известно, что большинство словоформ провоцирует образование одинаковых кластеров нейронов в одинаковых частях мозга. Таким образом, чтение, например, этого самого текста вызывает в ваших нейронах и нейронах вашего соседа через дорогу практически одинаковую реакцию. Известно также, что, имея возможность выборочно взаимодействовать с отдельными цепями нейронов, в теории можно добиться почти любого физиологического эффекта в организме. Все, чего мне хотелось сейчас - поделиться этим блаженством с каждым человеческим существом вселенной. Бог рассказал мне о Пророчестве. Пророчество представляло собой комбинацию слов, совокупность смыслов которых заставила бы совершенно любое человеческое существо, независимо от пола, возраста и национальности, сразу и полностью воспринять смысл существования. Понимание происходило не напрямую. Все, что делал текст - активировал в нужной последовательности цепочки нейронов в человеческом мозге, на подсознательном уровне конструируя \"Путь в Ничего\". После прочтения всякий человек необратимо принимал свою изначальную форму. Простыми словами, навсегда исчезал из этого мира, расплетая узлы лоз бытия, составляющих все его существо.", "appid": "1392170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198379985551", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598702400.0} {"text": "the best game played", "appid": "952060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126809153", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586260800.0} {"text": "Fun free game, has it's influxes, then dies down though", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126379870", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544356800.0} {"text": "КАЭФ", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198127158229", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "Bardzo trudna i nie wybacza błędów. Przy czym ani trochę nie frustruje. Chce się grać i grać. Taki skirmish z zombiakami. Tryb Survival genialny, wciąga jak bagno i tutaj polecałbym zacząć. Pamiętać o aktywnej pauzie, bo ta błogosławieństwem. Kampanii jeszcze nie próbowałem i jakoś nie ciągnie. Po 270 godzinach zabawy szczerze polecam każdemu, kto lubi zbierać surowce i budować bazę :) mury, wieżyczki, kopalnie, garnizony - wszystko tu jest :)", "appid": "644930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198203201529", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586520000.0} {"text": "Кс,как кс.Ничего плохого в этой игрульке не вижу.Только жаль что она стала бесплатной и появились \"ЧИТЕРЫ\".Кто ни знает кто такие читеры : Читеры – это игроки, использующие специальные программы, которые ломают клиентскую версию игры, что, позволяет им лучше играть.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198967159258", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574424000.0} {"text": "Видно, что разрабы сделали ставку на сюжет и у них это весьма недурно получилось. 47ой стал человеком с чувствами, а не просто машиной для убийства. Графика тоже на высоте, просто восхитительная картинка. Геймплей очень хардкорный. Но все же структура игры уже не та. Эти перекаты и пребывания все время в укрытии, делают ее больше похожей на Splinter Cell. Из минусов выделю пожалуй только недосмотр разработчиков по поводу контрольных точек, после загрузки которых восстанавливаются враги и идеально зачищенная территория идет коту под хвост. Вообщем игра получилась неплохой, но если честно мне лично не хватало: 1. Идеи прошлых частей серии, без линейности, с кучей разных способов убийства, идеальными несчастными случаями, где каждая локация в вашем полном распоряжении. 2. Старого инвентаря с шприцами и удавкой.", "appid": "203140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198021707454", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1388318400.0} {"text": "I know it is an older game .. I know that Battlefield V was released .. This game outperforms Battlefield V in all aspects. Unfortunately, Dice did a horrible job with the overall impression of Battlefield 5. This game is much more engaging to play and the atmosphere always attracts you. Give it a go. You will not be disappointed. The single player is great and leaves nothing to be desired. Graphics, gameplay, sound effects and scenery are excellent.", "appid": "1238840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198959867806", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598443200.0} {"text": "The best City builder game out there. It tops SimCity by a mile and at a fraction of the cost.", "appid": "255710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063098814", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446984000.0} {"text": "Simply the best multiplayer FPS game of all time. Vastly superior to the sequel.", "appid": "1200", "steamid": "profiles/76561197965388486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "Such Love, much Peens <3", "appid": "469820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198175488455", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562155200.0} {"text": "Saint seiya game is a simplistic fighting game if you're a hardcore player looking for huge combos footsies etc you might not enjoy it. Pros: -Its Saint Seiya -The graphics while not great their flashy and colorful -I really liked most of the soundtrack of the game especially some\"pump me up\"tracks before the big battles. -A plethora of unlockables such as costumes,new abilities,stages etc Cons: -The game doesnt do a good job explaining the story -Online is dead -Too much grinding if you're a completionist Verdict: I enjoyed my time with Saint Seiya,it was a refreshing blast from the past but it has its shortcomings its gets 7.5/10 Try to get it in a sale the original price is very steep for what it offers.", "appid": "348710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118964515", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "101", "votes_funny": "12", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1467720000.0} {"text": "n1ce gamee", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198242415852", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1449662400.0} {"text": "Todas las ventajas de matar zombis con todas las desventajas de matar zombis 9/10", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198197003066", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1466856000.0} {"text": "第一次认认真真的写游戏评测。 这个游戏从一发行我就在观望，最近有时间可以玩了，趁着打折就果断入手，但是游戏体验和我预期差别比较大，大概玩了有10个小时，我不知道是我不适合玩还是对游戏理解有问题，处处小心翼翼，过程担惊受怕，人品不好了就会墓园走一波，整个人就都不太好了，感觉不到游戏的乐趣，对我这种抑郁症患者来说是有些折磨的。 不过画风还是很吸引我的，算是目前让我继续玩下去的唯一动力吧，如果某天我感受到了这个游戏的乐趣，我会来改评测的。2017.10.31 ------------------------------------------------------------- 终于无法继续进行游戏了，原因并不是游戏性的问题，而是一点活动日志游戏就无响应，把mod都关掉了也不行，只能把游戏改为英文才可以继续，中文无法继续。2017.11.14 ------------------------------------------------------------- 日志无响应的问题，又做了一个任务之后恢复正常。2017.11.14 ------------------------------------------------------------- 又到更新评测了，今天是为了做2017秋季特卖的任务。2017.11.23 ------------------------------------------------------------- 游戏进展缓慢，关键在于游戏速度太慢了，只有开加速软件才能玩的爽快，效率起码提高2倍，但是有这么一个问题，只有在家里的台式机上开加速软件不会出现无响应，在我笔记本上一开加速软件游戏就会无响应，在办公室的电脑上同样开加速软件游戏会无响应，所以我每天只坐在家里的台式机前玩，我更想躺床上用笔记本开加速软件玩好不好呀，我已经离不开加速软件了，没有加速软件这游戏我已经不想碰了。2017.11.28 -------------------------------------------------------------- 自从上次好不容易培养的人物被灭队之后再也没打开过这个游戏，虽然从一开始玩的时候就已经知道了这个游戏的规则：“那些冒险者只是炮灰而已，不要在意，我们有驿站。”但事实是灭队之后还是让我一直失落，再也提不起打开游戏的兴趣了，可能我无法面对失去的痛苦吧。2018.3.18 --------------------------------------------------------------- 好久没有打开这个游戏了，现实的痛苦已经让我很难受了，不得不说这画风还是深得我心，我很中意你啦，但不想陪你走下去啦。2018.7.6 ---------------------------------------------------------------- 发现了2个加速mod，让我又提起了继续下去的兴趣，这样就能解决我用加速软件加速游戏卡死的问题，可以愉快的加速游戏了，评测改为好评。2018.11.19 ------------------------------------------------------------- 没看任何资料一点一点自己摸索这个游戏，感觉策略性有点低，不知道是不是我是新手的原因。2018.11。24", "appid": "262060", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961172849", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509364800.0} {"text": "Смысл игр от Telltale описывать нету. Сюжет по комиксам. Рисовка по комиксам, не нужно удивлятся что они выглядят не как в фильмах. Кароче просто расскажу про первые 5 минут игры. Получаем п*зды от Таноса. Через минуту даем п*зды Таносу. Минута прошла снова меняемся. Енот резко чинит свою пушку способную уничтожить планеты. Стреляем в Таноса и убиваем. На след день продаем его на органы. Симулятор для тех кто не довелен концовкой Войны Бесконечности 10/10 ... потому что тут нет жалких мстителей.", "appid": "579950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009474670", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533470400.0} {"text": "Очень крутая игра, всем советую поиграть, 10/10", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198390457046", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518004800.0} {"text": "Yeah you need to steal a PC from NASA if you want to run this game above 10FPS.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117619542", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1496923200.0} {"text": "There's no reason *not* to buy this", "appid": "976730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198022454635", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601380800.0} {"text": "I prefer sayori died with her cloths off.", "appid": "698780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132899595", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "THis game remids me on my childhood. Usually they destroy old games by remaking them... but this is not the case! I love this game! Thank you for bringing this game back to life!", "appid": "300380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198059418513", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511179200.0} {"text": "I don´t know if this game is for everyones taste. If u are into Rythmgames I think u should give it a try. I´m a Huge Fan of DJ Max since PSP title DJ Max Portable. This DJ Max almost combines every title (With DLC´s, hope they will add now everyone song still missing some on PS4...) At the end it should have more than 400 songs. I find the 8 Key mode a little bot complicated without a Controller.", "appid": "960170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198000894780", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1577361600.0} {"text": "i like sex", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198137982631", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590235200.0} {"text": "Still a good game after all these years !", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198839293827", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Could become a good training game, if the developers would work on this game.", "appid": "772540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198245595802", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515326400.0} {"text": "AWESOME GAME!!! one most gratest game ever!!!", "appid": "238010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198022683077", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403870400.0} {"text": "Vingue, Vingue Isabel agora", "appid": "236850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198327980041", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1567944000.0} {"text": "Előszöris, több mint 5000 órám van a játékban. Jelengleg 3100 van Main accon, és 2000+ néhány smurf accountrol. 3 éve csapatom ezt a játékot, és elég sok mindent tapasztaltam. Jót - rosszat egyaránt. Naszóval. Hmm.. Hol is kezdjem. :/ mondjuk a játék FŐBB hibáinál: - Undorítóan szar hitbox - A versengő szerverek 95%-a szar. - Ha egyedül mész versengőt vagy bármilyen kompetitív módot, 90%- ban biztos, hogy retardált csöves oroszokat, törököket, meg más egyéb rákos nemzetiségű emberkéket dob be neked csapattársnak, magyarul elmentél loseolni, és fél-1 órát elpocsékolni az életedből. - A smoke buggokról sem feletkezzünk el, bele dobom a molotov közepébe a smokeot és baszik \"kipukkanni\". Rengetegszer haltam meg emiatt is (Főleg mikor profi meccsen van ilyen.. khm) - A sok fölösleges megfizethetetlen skin/kesztyű meg apámfaszáról ne is beszéljünk. - A csalókról inkább nem is beszélek, mindenki ismeri őket. Élettelen faszmalac az összes akiknek az anyjuk bankkártyájáról vásárolnak cheateket gg. - A folyamatos fegyver nerfektől is égnek áll a fas... akarom mondani a hajam. nerfelik az awp-t, az ump-t, tec9-et. gg volvo Na hát ennyit a negatív dolgokról, van még több is, de azokrol inkább nem is beszélek mert a végén felkötöm magam.. Pozitív dolgok is vannak, de azt mindenki ismeri. Aki nem ismerné nem játszana a CS:GO -val. Bármilyen hiábai is vannak, nagyon szerethető játék, de néha tényleg elgondolkozok, hogy kinek verjem szarrá a fejét egy jó kis versengő után (Ez már mostanság elég ritkán van:D 10 ből 1 szer :P) Minden leírt ócsárolásom ellenére, csak ajánlani tudom a CS:GO-t. Ha találsz magadnak egy jó csapatot, és meg tanulsz játszani, és szerencsés vagy.. akár meg meg is tudsz belőle élni, és valljuk be eléggé álom munka lenne. :D (Persze ehhez sok-sok idő, és erőfeszítés kell, de ha összejön a végeredmény akkor a kurva szádat mert nekem még nem jött össze semmi v.v. [MÉG])", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198114849350", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502625600.0} {"text": "神げー　なぜ有名にならないのか、疑問でしかたない。 悪いことは言わない、買いましょう後悔します。", "appid": "389510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198365816388", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529841600.0} {"text": "AWESOME GAME!", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198279984814", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497268800.0} {"text": "\\[T]/ Absolute Masterpiece \\[T]/", "appid": "335300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198331133037", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575806400.0} {"text": "Что теперь?", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090039121", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465214400.0} {"text": "I was a sceptic when I first saw this on the steam store, thought it looked a bit simplistic for the heavy price tag (£17) for something that looked like a VR low gravity dodge ball remake. but i got it on sale for (£8), and boy oh boy do I not regret it. I have to say though my only concern is the player base decreasing. With a game that solely relies on the player-base (for PvP) it seems a bit steep to set the price tag at £17. I say this because I know that if I'd stumbled across this masterpiece when it wasn't on sale I would have most likely ignored it, this game needs more players, and it needs a lower price tag to allow for such. the players are what make this game. Game rating: 8.5/10", "appid": "601770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105346273", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563278400.0} {"text": "Папич рекомендует", "appid": "238960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198395865128", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "is funny gaime", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198157878212", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533470400.0} {"text": "Batman Arkham Asylum GOTY 9/10 - One of the best beat em up games that I've played - Graphics are great and presentable specially the cutscenes - Camera angles are bad sometimes - Quite entertaining because of the easter eggs - Breaking the 4th wall! - Epic soundtrack - Linear gameplay, not repetitive, will keep you entertained - Puzzles and riddles are not that hard to find - Controls are nice - Very informative on Characters - All in all, Probably the best Batman game that I've played so far, Highly recommended for batman fans out there", "appid": "35140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198865036027", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590235200.0} {"text": "nice anime", "appid": "339800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198104825028", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "Game interessane, Lembra bastante games da série mário", "appid": "296910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063282400", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562414400.0} {"text": "gra fajna jest podobna do fortnite polecam grajcie", "appid": "893520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198267619828", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594814400.0} {"text": "Мегашикарная игра! Она стоит того, чтобы купить ее и за полную стоимость, не то что по скидке. Очаровательная графика, яркие запоминающиеся персонажи, интересный сюжет и увлекательные дополнительные квесты, музыкальное сопровождение на высоте, огромный выбор оружия, идеальна как для сольного прохождения, так и для коопа с друзьями. А кроме того, она переполнена юмором, я давно так не смеялась))", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198309125574", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562587200.0} {"text": "Doporučuji, je to fakt hustácká střílečka :)", "appid": "388520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198015423768", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1440936000.0} {"text": "Ya podrochil i chustwuyu sebya izvrashencem,spasibo", "appid": "1127900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198403771675", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "굳게임", "appid": "766370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198028403381", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1580212800.0} {"text": "A basic test simulation with incredibly random questions. I found it quite funny that I was told \"Obviously, you know this topic quite well.\" upon completion of a test labelled 'Truth or Fiction' with a score of only 57% correct. Which itself contained a myriad of completely bizarre random questions containing no correlation to any specific subject. I decided to play through another test labelled 'Animals' to which I was given questions ranging from relatively easy common knowledge to things only a zoologist would know the answer to. I can't say I enjoyed my short play through very much but for what it's worth, it does what it says on the box as some might say and it does have some saving grace with being able to craft your own test for friends to play through. Overall, it's not something I'd personally play when trying to unwind after work but I suppose it's what it says it is, a Brain Test and being able to create and share your own tests is pretty cool so I'll give it a thumbs up. If I could make a suggestion though, it would be to add achievements and personally, I'd advise lowering the price from £2.89 to something more reasonable like £0.79.", "appid": "1350390", "steamid": "profiles/76561197982273259", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601467200.0} {"text": "Gün Geçmiyor ki bir soygunluk vakası ile karşılaşmayın :) Hergün her saat ayrı bir macera ayrı bir soygun Arkadaşlarınız ile oynanabilecek zevk veren güzel oyun.", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198331431432", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1540468800.0} {"text": "Better than CS:GO", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198256052404", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521806400.0} {"text": "Dobry program na naukę rosyjskiego języka częściej angielskiego :) xd", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198266720841", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472644800.0} {"text": "Don't let the graphics mislead you. This is actually a well packed Zombie survival game. It's frequently updated by one of the most responsive dev i've seen in Early Access. It's Free to play but no 'pay to win.' It has workshop, marketplace and even a map editor for you to build your own zombie apocalypse. I know it's free. But go buy the gold upgrade, it's worth supporting Nelson so he keeps updating this nice game.", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561197978136978", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "161", "votes_funny": "21", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1449576000.0} {"text": "THE DEVS ARE BACK YES please add skins c: (for players you know like do something special like kill 3 dragons and you get a player skin :D pls nerf zambies", "appid": "253430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198158369434", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446811200.0} {"text": "- 10:00 - \"Ты заходишь ?\" - 10:05 - \"Да\" - 19:00 - \"Ты скоро?\" - 19:05 - \"Почти зашёл \" - 20:30 - \"Зашёл!\" - 22:14 - \"У меня лагает , я спать.\"", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198805482405", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "Достоинства: Отличная графика, сюжет, экшен, да в общем всё тут просто классно! Недостатки: не обнаружено; Да уж, как много в этом названии и сколько уже лет мы знаем эту девушку, внешность которой всё лучше и лучше. Многие долго ждали продолжения серии, чтобы оценить игрушку и посмотреть чем она может удивить, потому что, как никак трейлеры внушали) Поэтому я её и опробовал! Сразу, что бросается в глаза это крутая графика, которая просто радует глаза и может похвастаться своей детальной прорисовкой и текстурами! Здесь да, она просто на высоком уровне! Так что смело можно ставить плюс и за оптимизацию! Сюжет и экшен как всегда крут, интересные герои и диалоги, постоянно что-то стреляет, падает, рушится, от чего-то убегаешь и тп) Короче, просто круто и держит тебя в напряжении, за что тоже можно ставить пять баллов! Много оружия, врагов и действий тоже не оставляет ни каких отрицательных оттенков! Таким образом получилась добротная игра, а точнее классное продолжение серии, в которое можно играть, которая держит в напряжении и думаю, что соберёт не мало новых фанатов!", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077140881", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454760000.0} {"text": "Бывает скушновато в Основном но затянула", "appid": "322330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198387645684", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575374400.0} {"text": "Değeri bilinmemiş efsane oyun.Keşke yeniden bir akım çıksada tıpkı Minecraft gibi popüler olsa ;(", "appid": "230860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198183345986", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566388800.0} {"text": "Con 175 horas de juego aun no logro acabarlo y al parecer aun le quedan muchicimas horas mas. He jugado la saga completa ya que los anteriores y me refiero a todos los tengo el formato fisico CD/DVD. y este juego se lleva mi respeto. Es Un juego Completamente magnifico su basto mundo abierto me ha dejado muy buen sabor de boca, la mecanica esta muy bien ajustada tanto por todos lo que puedes farmear hasta los combates ya sean cuerpo a cuerpo u por armas, los compañeros influyen mucho en el personaje, todo lo que agas influye en la historia ya sea si te unes a la hermandad del acero, minutmens o cualquier otro. cada respuesta tienes sus consecuencias y sus proesas. los graficos son de lo mejor que he visto hasta la fecha ya que con el DLC de Texturas HD es un verdadero deleite en el aspecto grafico y mas si tu pc cumple con los requicitps pára este DLC, Los mods y DLC Le dan mas tiempo de juego he historias alternativas para poder seguir enganchado ya que con el season pass puedes tenerlo todo y seguir disfrutando de esta grandiosa obra. recomendado ampliamente no te defraudara", "appid": "377160", "steamid": "profiles/76561197982253836", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487073600.0} {"text": "Best Pool game i have played. Its worth the price even 9,99 €. There is good tutorials for beginners and lots of game modes to play. Graphics are also nice and music too. So if you are Pool fan or not or just wanna try this one out, i recommend this for you.", "appid": "254440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026619345", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1406808000.0} {"text": "Eğer bu oyunu birlikte oynayabileceğiniz arkadaşlarınız ve iyi derecede bir bilgisayarınız varsa, arkadaşlarınızla beraber çok eğlenceli vakitler geçirebilirsiniz.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121056356", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526385600.0} {"text": "It's a great game, I quite like the souls series.", "appid": "335300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198378292670", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530619200.0} {"text": "good gmae", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561197960667090", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543147200.0} {"text": "I sacrifice myself to the will of our dance", "appid": "889510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198088594409", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602504000.0} {"text": "güzel", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198452397266", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587816000.0} {"text": "I had a great time with friends. A must buy!", "appid": "48700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081532633", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493553600.0} {"text": "Про эту игру можно сказать, что она великолепна! Не только графически, но и сюжетно. Rockstar всегда делали и делают хорошие, привлекательные игры, где есть смысл, производительность и качество. Игра получилась, как некое кино, только герой в нашем управлении, 1-ая и 2-ая части остаются лучшими играми, хоть и старыми. Я не играл в предыдущие игры, но могу сказать только одно... Купите!!! 10 из 10", "appid": "204100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031815749", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1340280000.0} {"text": "미드를 보는듯한 멋진 연출. 미드 출연진들의 목소리. 물흐르듯 들려오는 음악소리. 간간히 보이는 뚜렷한 액션. 마지막은 미드처럼 모두를 절망의 구렁텅이로... 재밌네요. 속편이 기다려 집니다.", "appid": "330840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198025761475", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480852800.0} {"text": "Good graphic, fight mechanic, and walktrough. Hope they made somekind of sequel cause this game just awesome and it has so many potential.", "appid": "302510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198238059840", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528632000.0} {"text": "Ничё так, под пивасик сойдёт.", "appid": "296300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198237840614", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502798400.0} {"text": "Este juego me trae muchos recuerdos desde la pelea contra mudface hasta laultima batalla contra el Joker en una iglesia abandonada......sin enmbargo es un juego bueno para su epoca :,) 10/10 -Agos", "appid": "21000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198020319689", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1494504000.0} {"text": "knife go brrrr", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198182715389", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600344000.0} {"text": "Daha önceden ikinci oyunu defalarca bitirmiş biri olarak ikinci oyuna nazaran bu oyunda bosslar daha hızlı. Oyunu speedrunlayarak bitirmeye çalıştım çünkü bossların ikinci oyundaki gibi yavaş kalacağını sanıyordum fakat pek de öyle olmadı. Bazı bossların kendisi kolay olsada gidiş yolları canınızı çok sıkacak. Özellikle oyunun en kolay bossu olarak gördüğüm Deacons of the Deep bossuna ulaşabilmek için saatlerimi harcadım. Lifegem, Bonfire Ascetic gibi şahane itemların bu oyunda bulunmuyor olması da bir hayli üzdü beni. DLC'lere gelecek olursak ikisi de gerek haritaları, gerekse boss dizaynları olsun şahane. Yalnız...Darkeater Midir'e çok küfür ettim. Yüksek ihtimalle siz de bilgisayar başında cinnet geçirip çeşitli küfürler edeceksiniz bu yaratığa. İncelememi okuduğunuz için çok teşekkürler ve iyi oyunlar diliyorum. PRAISE THE SUN!", "appid": "374320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143758497", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1583409600.0} {"text": "Şimde kadar oynadığım co-op oyunlar arasından, en iyilerinden biri diyebilirim. Oyunun mantığı uzay gemisinde kalan ve hayatını kazı yaparak geçiren 4 cüceyi(dwarves) oynamak diyebiliriz Ana mantığı ise : merkezden görev seç > zorluğunu ayarla > takım arkadaşlarınla yada Solo bosco ile (yardımcı robot sadece solo oynarken geliyor) görevi bitirip sağ salim eve dönmek. Oynayabildiğiniz 4 dwarves sırasıyla: 1-gunner 2-driller 3-engineer 4-scout Her klasın kendine öz silahları ve takım içi görevleri var. Gunner silah gücü ile düşmanları tek başına alabiliyorken , Driller özel kazı aletleriyle bütün her yeri saniyede kaza biliyorken , Engineer taret koyup bölgenin korumasını sağlaya biliyorken Scout ise hook atıp spider-man gibi gezip madenleri toplayabiliyor. Bazıları ise bir biriyle çalışıyor mesela engineer bulunan platform silahı ile scout için yer oluşturup madenlere ulaşmasını sağlaya biliyorsun.... Oyunda silahlarımızı ve bir çok ekipmanımızı geliştire biliyoruz bunları ise görev içerisinde bulduğumuz özel madenler ile ve görev sonunda aldığımız para ile yapıyoruz. Silahından tut zırhına kadar her şeyi geliştirebiliyorsunuz ve tabi kosmetiklerde mevcüt Oyunun topluluğu çok iyi çoğu yardımsever ve mikrofonunuz yok ise merak etmeyin çoğu iletişim oyun içinde bulunan lazer pointer(ctrl) ile yapılıyor ve gayet iyide çalışıyor o yüzden bu oyunu kesinlikle öneriyorum. Dikkat etmeniz gereken tek şey görev zorlukları, 2 lvl iken en zor göreve girmeye çalışmayın yeter :D Daha uzun yazmak isterdim ama bunu sadece oyun hakkında ufak bir fikir sahibi olmanız işin yazıyorum. Devamını siz kendiniz keşfedin. ROCK AND STONE !!", "appid": "548430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096369821", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1588507200.0} {"text": "Is very nice", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198136961429", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1459684800.0} {"text": "Das Game is R.I.P seit dem ,,Overwatch-Update\". #GameAwards2017 #jadassindmirdie25XPwert", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198055480768", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "Fajna gra Rosyjskiego można sie w tydzień nauczyć", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198410810306", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Ну что тут писать, КС как КС, афигенная Все покупайте, будем вместе играть!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198208598712", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483185600.0} {"text": "Always wanted this game since it came out. This game is brilliant!", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198810994886", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1570104000.0} {"text": "Un juegazo, para ser gratis, lo amo <3 O_O 24/7 PALADINS", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198325568289", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "Recomendado", "appid": "225260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084197150", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497441600.0} {"text": "作為一位從仙杜瑞拉一路體驗過來的玩家，老實說，在風魔米娜內我看見非常多前兩部的影子，熟悉的金幣、熟悉的AB攻擊手段、熟悉的更衣室、當然還有那熟悉的PLAY，這些都是前作的優點，使用從前的優點不是說不好，只是當這些影子被拔除後，我找不到新內容了，只記得那位傳奇四掌，偏偏四掌只是個彩蛋，他並不是風魔米娜本身想傳遞的內容，挺可惜的。 風魔米娜和仙杜瑞拉相比雖然沒有飛躍性的突破，但還是一款相當好玩的遊戲，本作沒有性愛，但有很多惡趣味擦邊球，另外製作人也有準備的露點的DLC，給喜歡的紳士們使用，DLC不影響玩法，只單純用眼睛吃福利，讓你視力不下滑，無副作用，視力立馬見效", "appid": "1184990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138377255", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592654400.0} {"text": "Good game, worth to try", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255790101", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558180800.0} {"text": "Coooles game man. Vieler neuer content man", "appid": "361420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082329392", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Its alright, didn't spend to much time on it.", "appid": "265930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048081814", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481112000.0} {"text": "Oyun Yeni oyuna göre kötü yani çok birşey beklenemez zaten 2011 yılında çıkmış yeni mapler olursa ve payday 2 gibi silah alma değiştirme vs vs şeyler olursa iyi bir oyun olur ve son olarak ben para hastasıyım bankalar elmaslar çalarım diyorsanız bence oynamanız gerekli", "appid": "24240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198083566403", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1413547200.0} {"text": "♥♥♥**** awsome!", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198205689471", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483617600.0} {"text": "И сказать нечего", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141136707", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1468843200.0} {"text": "best game", "appid": "203770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044047989", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543147200.0} {"text": "Just be warned: This game can ruin your friendship if you are not tossing this salad quick enough!", "appid": "448510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030446827", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593518400.0} {"text": "买游戏送美剧！每一根毛都看的清清楚楚！", "appid": "474960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198343092040", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514635200.0} {"text": "МАКСИМУМ ГРАФОНА И НЕМНОГО НОСТАЛЬГИИ", "appid": "1282690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198847038609", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592913600.0} {"text": "Ну если быть объективным, то есть минусы и плюсы. Как бы сама вотэта ваша онэмэ игра, ну такая, наманая, как бы разок опробовать можно, но потом к ней не вернешься. Сюжет, ну сюжет как сюжет, монахи, которым нужно идти больше в яой режим нежели в натуралистику. Ну насчет минусов и плюсов: Минусы: -Звук на кнопочка в меню, его можно искажать таким образом, что твой дед умрет от первых секунд прослушивания. -Плохо, что озвучка только чайниз, ну кетайская, я не сильно люблю звучание китайского, но это уже чисто мое мнение наверное. -В некоторых местах косячит текст и анимация. -Опенинг не очень. -Дороговато для такой то игры, еще и ДЛС закинули, уууу. Плюсы: + Сами персонажи нарисованы нормально, сойдет. + Можно выбрать имя персонажу, очень даже большой плюс, ну объяснять почему не буду, сами поймете. + Внешний вид главной героини, ну рили такая чисто краля, я бы ей под кардан дал бы, дааааб, даааааб. Хоть плюсов и мало, но я не считаю, что продукт какой-то низкокачественный, на один раз сойдет, единственное что цена кусается. но я ее не покупал, хых, но так бы не купил бы, только если по скидке. Вообщем, оценка 8.9/10.", "appid": "520850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079579062", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553428800.0} {"text": "good", "appid": "240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138563857", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "im not explaining ♥♥♥♥.... you're gona love this game.. end of.", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198265511432", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573992000.0} {"text": "Dobry las polecam", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198237233782", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562328000.0} {"text": "MUHTEŞEMMMMMMMM", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198326047183", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1527249600.0} {"text": "С Бласковицем знаком очень давно и \"The New Order\" - дала очень большой глоток в серии \"Wolfenstein\" В игре сюжет оч