es_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572523200.0} {"text": "Good game but need's some work but i do recomend this GAME!", "appid": "333930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076560351", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1452081600.0} {"text": "A great game for friends and couples as well as children and family", "appid": "204360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198098510717", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480420800.0} {"text": "Fajna Gra", "appid": "322170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198200114921", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480248000.0} {"text": "Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin Vote for Putin", "appid": "1070330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198198912675", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579867200.0} {"text": "Like game sometimes", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198382826200", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1552305600.0} {"text": "Классная игра ))", "appid": "647980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198158499806", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497787200.0} {"text": "Я играл немного стелс игр и для меня самой тяжелой оказалась tom clancy's splinter cell blacklist. Плюсы: -отличная графика -отличный стелс -много возможностей -Можно поиграть с другом в кооперотив Минусы: -не интересный сюжет (моё мнение) Нууу.....Кому не интересен сюжет,но интересен стелс,тогда эта игра для вас :)", "appid": "235600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198248230870", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1482840000.0} {"text": "Excellent jeu pour du solo ou multi si des \"fermiers\" veulent vous rejoindre à gerer une agriculture dès plus réalistes ! Un régal !", "appid": "787860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062383606", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543147200.0} {"text": "custom zombies > everything", "appid": "10090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198339763706", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569153600.0} {"text": "Игра норм все понравилось 9 из 10", "appid": "299740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198175152486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1422014400.0} {"text": "....", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198277300694", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485950400.0} {"text": "Com o modo online sem funcionar, jogando solo, o jogo é bem dificil e as vezes até desbalanceado, mas é um bom jogo e deve ser melhor quando consegue jogar com alguem", "appid": "557040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048793527", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593950400.0} {"text": "The game's honestly awesome. It's got its flaws, but if you enjoy management games, you'll more than get your money's worth.", "appid": "600480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031385276", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539000000.0} {"text": "Be weebs and get horney on it", "appid": "771920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198240015782", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593172800.0} {"text": "Chocola and Coconut <3", "appid": "385800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198170394914", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508241600.0} {"text": "First strategic game i've ever played. Still in love with this game and it will never grow away from my childhood. i even remember the good ol days cheat codes \"Howdoyouturnthison\" :,).. Aaahh memories", "appid": "221380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007234501", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "I absolutely adore this game. Every round is a fresh experience, you never know what the outcome will be, nothing is ever set in stone. Some rounds feel like a thrilling game of hide and seek, others are an all out war. The learning curve is somewhat steep, and rather unforgiving since you only have one life per round. But eventually you learn, and you start to win, and the satisfaction that comes from looking back at where you started, to where you are now, is simply immesurable. But let's get something straight right now. If you are interested in this game. DO NOT BUY THE STARTER EDITION. BUY AT LEAST THE STANDARD EDITION. The Starter Edition is cheaper to buy, but the grind to unlock new operators is much higher, so it's really not worth it.", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042872523", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1534075200.0} {"text": "Weapons are fun to use especially throwable melee weapons. Kick and shotgun instakills even most bigger enemies. Zombies are surprisingly fun enemies in this game. Gasmask makes me claustrophobic. There is tons of combo attaks (kill enemy by kicking arse get hillbilly rampage) Yes it looks bad gameplay has some bad things normal difficulty gets easy after finding 20 vampire artifacts. If you like somewhat stupid mindles games buy this.", "appid": "7860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093474893", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1417262400.0} {"text": "just good", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132414295", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575115200.0} {"text": "Wow, I was single before this game.. but now look at all my girlfriends.", "appid": "339800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052160217", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1463313600.0} {"text": "War ein kurzes aber sehr cooles spiel :). was a short but really cool and awesome game :).", "appid": "436110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030615940", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1456574400.0} {"text": "beautiful", "appid": "493540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060415950", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602936000.0} {"text": "Hack kullananlar arttı report etmemize rağmen ban yemiyor", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198338380960", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490961600.0} {"text": "gbbngkgtfmb", "appid": "301520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198272081239", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602763200.0} {"text": "довольно интересно хз через скоко окончательно надоест", "appid": "307780", "steamid": "profiles/76561199027802273", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594555200.0} {"text": "В данный момент игра работает нормально. Но проблемы были в течение последнего месяца. Если до июля всё будет ОК, поменяю знак обзора. ********************************************************* Ну что, в принципе всё работает нормально (для этой игры). Изложу вкрации что нужно знать людям, которые собираются в это поиграть 1. Долгая, для прохождения надо минимум полгода. 2. Требует многих часов. 2, 5, 8 тысяч часов - это вполне нормально 3. Как и любая бесплатная игра настырно требует вложений. У меня итого получилось примерно 6 тысяч рублей ($90), и все те с кем я общался донатили так же или больше. Несмотря на все недостатки палец поднят вверх потому что игра клевая, затягивает, дарит эмоции. Берите, если у вас есть много свободного времени и доната.", "appid": "627690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030785627", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591012800.0} {"text": "+", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074297410", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1406721600.0} {"text": "\"It's playing computer poker by itself, Sam. It doesn't have friends\" Единственное, чего не хватает этой классной игре, так это мультиплеера. Очень жаль, что в Steam не разрешены азартные игры, но наверное это и к лучшему? P.S Если кому надо: \"Он играет сам с собой в покер на компьютере, Сэм. У него нет друзей!\"", "appid": "234710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198054661710", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "50", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1404129600.0} {"text": "Auto-Clicker while I had my way with all the costumes and m0anage!!! 12/10 *****", "appid": "383080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198156543282", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1440331200.0} {"text": "The best simulation of driving the trucks. All I recommend you do is to boil the coffee, let some cool radio station and maximize relax your mind. Great game for relaxation and even better when playing in mp with friends. All recommendations from me :)", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150371215", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563624000.0} {"text": "Très bon jeu, avec une histoire qui s'emballe bien comme il faut vers la fin. La durée de vie est très bon, techniquement si vous avez un PC sympathique c'est plutôt joli. Une ambiance très bien reproduite de l'univers Mad Max.", "appid": "234140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198176350774", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501588800.0} {"text": "gg", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198967517624", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585051200.0} {"text": "게임은 단순한데 인생의 의미가 담겨있네요. 힘들게 경쟁해야하는 젊은 시절. 배려없는 사회에서 부족한 체력과 경험을 바탕으로 생존해야하는 노인. 그리고 항상 위험에 노출되어 있지만 밝고 생동감 넘치는 아이들..", "appid": "310370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198098177497", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1420372800.0} {"text": "Seré directo: un juego arcade repleto de acción con la particularidad de que conducimos un vehículo con un disparo multidireccional. Todo conjuga y cumple con el objetivo de darte un rato de diversión. Me gusta especialmente la física de los vehículos, sencilla pero creíble, La historia no es nada del otro mundo pero al menos hace subir la ambientación varios enteros. Y si te picas con los amigos a ver quién hace mejor puntuación, mejor que mejor.", "appid": "99300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072545540", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539604800.0} {"text": "It's a good game, fun even without internet. But real money shopping should be cheaper Otherwise it's a great game.", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198798276517", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522497600.0} {"text": "Warto przejść kilka razy, a jeszcze bardziej warto zagrać co-opa z znajomym. I jest to faktycznie co-op, nie jak w większości gier gdzie trzeba się wciąż rozdzielać i robić wszystko samemu. Co do gry jednoosobowej i całej gry w pewnych momentach trudna, lecz do przejścia. Podoba mi się efekt portali, pewnie nie tylko mi ale tak czy siak mi się podoba. Gra warta uznania i zagrania polecam ją każdemu. <3", "appid": "620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198282784073", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573214400.0} {"text": "Én nagyon örülök a képeknek. Köszönöm a fejlesztőknek.", "appid": "798543", "steamid": "profiles/76561198097245767", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519214400.0} {"text": "The games a ton of fun. Ignore all the hate. The lootboxes can be ignored entirely. Its a fun game to grind and its rewarding. Buying lootboxes would actually take away from the experience. So dont buy them. Its that simple", "appid": "356190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070971728", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508587200.0} {"text": "Her ne kadar grafikleri daha çok mobil bir oyuna anımsatsa da, arcade havasıyla harika vakit öldürüyor! Direksiyon vs. lazım değil. Sonunda birinci GRİD'i tadını veren bir oyun buldum!)", "appid": "635260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198281855035", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549540800.0} {"text": "So I was hesitant about buying a video (Movie) from steam, But I was not disapointed. Now this movie starts off very slow, But it gets alot better later on. 10 minutes in or so. This movie brings elements of Psychadelic trips, Pop culture, Movies and Video games from the 80's to the present. If you like the 80s-90s era you will hear and see alot of refrences and you will love it . It also has refrences from the 2000-present. The movie also has a ending that will make you want to rewatch it. I highly recommend this movie , and with a low price of 5$ you will not regret it.", "appid": "359410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003213686", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1427889600.0} {"text": "This game was absolutely beautiful. Gorgeous artwork and a moving, heartwarming story. It was so detailed and so simple at the same time. I loved it! <3", "appid": "916900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031922253", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579694400.0} {"text": "Spend 3 year prepare for Barbarossa , losing at the gate of Moskow, and Stalingrad , and the rest is history 10/10 would go to war again", "appid": "25890", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006485065", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "59", "votes_funny": "23", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1415275200.0} {"text": "I love this game way too much, it's been a while since i got a game and didn't stop playing for such a long while in my 'first sitting' of playing the game.", "appid": "646570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071130114", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1516017600.0} {"text": "- est selon moi, un bon . L'univers de la chasse est omniprésent dans le jeu de base et si vous avez apprécié , le nain alors vous serez comblés. Ce DLC se déroule sur la seconde partie de la carte, à Nurn Il vous proposera 5 nouvelles quêtes secondaires afin de pouvoir activer le destrier ardent, no spoil je vous laisse découvrir ce que c'est. Il vous offre également 5 nouveaux Chefs de Guerre Uruk; des Dresseurs où vous devrez accomplir une grosse quête afin de pouvoir l'affronter le but du DLC étant de tous les éliminer. De nouvelles créatures s'ajoutent (disponibles uniquement dans le DLC - Seigneur de la Chasse) comme des Caragath; cousins des Caragors, des Graugs Malsains qui ont une petite spécialité très croustillante! Ce DLC vous ouvre l'accès à pas mal de succès; ce qui peut en intéresser certains je pense... Je veux quand même préciser que j'ai rencontré un gros bug durant l'une des quêtes, je me suis retrouvé hors map derrière un mur invisible, je ne sais pas si cela vient du DLC mais je dois quand même le préciser. En le terminant de fond en comble, ce DLC vous offrira une dizaine d'heures de jeu supplémentaires ce qui n'est pas rien! : 8/10", "appid": "318390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035825843", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "54", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1421323200.0} {"text": "en iyi 5v5 çatışma oyunu", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198317344118", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1557489600.0} {"text": "ban the hacker ，save the game plz :) We need an anti-plug-in and reporting system 我们需要反外挂与举报系统 反外掛と通報システムが必要だ 우리는 외부 접속과 신고가 필요하다 Nous avons besoin d’un système anti-collant et de dénonciation Wir brauchen ein system zur meldung Нам нужна антивнешняя подвеска с системой подачи жалоб Necesitamos UN sistema anticolgante con reportes Precisamos de um sistema anti-periférico e de relatórios Abbiamo bisogno di un sistema di denuncia contro l’esterno Chúng ta cần hệ thống chống ngoại vi và báo cáo Kita butuh sesuatu yang bisa dilaporkan نحن بحاجة إلى نظام مضادة للاتصال الخارجي والإبلاغ", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198361786978", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597406400.0} {"text": "Раки даже через год)", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198140371164", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588766400.0} {"text": "Good Games I love Multi and History modes <3", "appid": "234670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198164315662", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435147200.0} {"text": "好玩！", "appid": "333600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198358806310", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563624000.0} {"text": "tak", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198861310720", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603886400.0} {"text": "This game is just awesome :D", "appid": "11330", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977121521", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1413806400.0} {"text": "22 hours in and I feel like I have bareley scratched to sruface of whats to come!", "appid": "238960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198113675730", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523102400.0} {"text": "This game is very good. good story, amazing graphics. no problems with it.", "appid": "883710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117693076", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1548504000.0} {"text": "How tf was this made in 2003???", "appid": "13230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198211097551", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1459252800.0} {"text": "Отличная игра, даже без скидки стоит своих денег. Плюсы: -Сюжет -Эпичность -Боёвка -Графоний, даже в 2020, вполне себе... -Не припомню Римлян-нeгров (порадовало) -Не припомню намёков на ЛГБТ (тоже порадовало, но исторически в РИ мужеложство имело место быть) Минусы: -Онлайн дохлый, только поиск в сообществе. -Есть плохо оптимизированные уровни. -Есть одна боевая самка (можно закрыть глаза). -Игра не почему-то не видит ни Дуалшок1, ни Дуалшок2, только пад от ИксБокса, может лечиться заходом в игру через Бигпикчер, не пробовал. -Минус мне, за то что ещё не прошёл игру на максимальной сложности.", "appid": "302510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198033439449", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603281600.0} {"text": "So, I personally do not have a lot of hours on this game. but dear god is it fun. if I ever have the urge to play a space survival game it usually is this one. if anyone is looking for another good one try HELLION. but I still think this game beats Hellion. I dont see an issue with the game, its kinda buggy sure but its a game so you can't freak out. either way, I have a suggestion.... What will it be you ask. When is the game coming to VR?", "appid": "244850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198280853624", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554984000.0} {"text": "Игра на уровне, получше некоторых игр 2018-2019 годов. Ну тут всё понятно, 3 сюжетки, все полностью отличаются друг от друга. За Талиона можно залипать 100 часов и больше. За Баранора часов 30-50. За Элтариэль не успел поиграть, но могу сказать, что на часов 40 точно займёт.", "appid": "356190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198392606611", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550750400.0} {"text": "+", "appid": "331470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198286152402", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "Хэдшот ему в жбан! Поклонники Counter-Strike — публика особая. Многие из них до сих пор спорят о превосходстве версии 1.5 над 1.6, чего уж говорить о полном ремейке на новом движке! Прошлая попытка заместить морально устаревшую 1.6 случилась в 2004 году и скорее провалилась: Counter-Strike: Source выглядела здорово и щеголяла правдоподобной физикой, но киберспортсмены ее яро отринули. И бегают тут, мол, не так, и гранаты летают не эдак... Source и GO разделяет целых восемь лет. У Valve было предостаточно времени, чтобы взвесить, осмыслить и смастерить вменяемый ремейк, в котором все было бы правильно. И потому базовая концепция в GO не сдвинулась ни на миллиметр: две команды по пять (и более) человек, «злодеи» и борцы с терроризмом. Сражаются до последнего выжившего. Террористы в основном развлекаются подрывом ключевых точек и удержанием заложников, а «силы добра» заложников пытаются освободить, а бомбу и ее хозяев — обезвредить. И ни в коем случае не наоборот.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198302470978", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465819200.0} {"text": "Programma multifunzione molto utile. Complimenti agli sviluppatori.", "appid": "400040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093558451", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498996800.0} {"text": "Ez 1 kurva jo jatek", "appid": "744430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308128154", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1564142400.0} {"text": "I'm a god LUL", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198215145847", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535284800.0} {"text": "Nice hab schon ein Kneiv", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198145717737", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446638400.0} {"text": "Есть беларуская мова. Основные акценты проекта - безудержное веселье в противоборстве с роботизированными противниками. Сразу же нас бросает в гущу сражения и постепенно наращивает волны, дает нам больше возможностей в битве. Планировка напомнила мне старые игрушки, где были уровни небольших масштабов. Всё \"мясо\" на расстоянии выстрела. Да еще и здоровенные боссы. Эхъ, что-то ностальжинка защемила из-за личных ассоциаций. Противники достаточно разнообразные, чтобы не успеть надоесть или иметь прямые претензии к их интеллекту. Появляются в разных точках и за счет своих характеристик могут неплохо так прижать в любом месте. А чтобы прохождение не заканчивалось на половине пути, тут есть платформы для прыжков, можно вложиться в оборудование арены. Мелочи, которые дают немного к тактике и к поведению. Сюжета нет, но есть некоторый бекграунд и возможность дособирать коллекционные предметы после прохождения.", "appid": "805590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198061254669", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597060800.0} {"text": "Good Game", "appid": "48700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198800233243", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600430400.0} {"text": "Recommend playing if you like long run VN. I Also recommend: [Key]: Rewrite Little Busters", "appid": "326480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096245285", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496318400.0} {"text": "Best game 2019 i love this game :D", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561197979573642", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574769600.0} {"text": "sim", "appid": "4000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198295499388", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584014400.0} {"text": "The game has an amazing soundtrack, great songs from the time period (70s) love running round killing ♥♥♥♥ and driving to these tunes lol the story pretty good not finish it yet but will do....... its one to play. will ya look down the reviews its amazing how many bad ones bye people who have no hours playing the game and av a list ov bad things to say , how do ya even know what ya on about", "appid": "360430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198253640399", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1552046400.0} {"text": "Im finished with the base game and its after RDR2 the best story game i´ve played so far... the game is really nice and i like every mechanic of this game! The graphic is absolutely stunning and the 3d sound is clean as hell. I would totally recommend buying this game! Just keep in mind that this game has a kind of morality system so avoid killing to much people and dont kill someone whos surrendering... unless you want the bad ending :) Just try this game out and you´ll be stunned! To all my brothers who have arachnophobia: maybe think twice before buying Metro Exodus because the Spiders in this game with the 3d sounds freaked me out.. GOOD GAME :)", "appid": "412020", "steamid": "profiles/76561198840778094", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602936000.0} {"text": "Story is ok, followed by an ending ruined with Put the story aside and just make crazy weapons and kill stuff.. you'll have fun. Fully worth the $20ish sales price.. $60 though.. not so much.", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070100975", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491652800.0} {"text": "Tragam mais fraldas, as minha acabaram.", "appid": "238320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198014051807", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "Ключевая особенность \"Дикой охоты\" - огромный, открытый и почти бесшовный мир - оказалась невероятным пшиком. Так, его размеры поистине впечатляют, но что с того, когда на квадратный метр нам дают откровенно мало всего. Дополнительные квесты или вывешиваются на досках объявлений, или разбросаны вдоль дорог.", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038304869", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "Man of Medan is definitely a strange one to review. Personally, I enjoyed my time playing it but I can see the flaws in it. It isn't that scary, if you figure out the plot twist then the game becomes easy and has zero replayability, and the characters are pretty unlikable. However, if you have a friend to play online with, it is pretty fun and can be finished in one sitting. Couch coop isn't great however, so only play online. If you just have fun with the game, you are in for a good time, but if you take it too seriously then it won't be great at all. Play if you have a friend who also will get it!", "appid": "939850", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997641256", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574769600.0} {"text": "fun game", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168884671", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1494590400.0} {"text": "puerto rico simulator", "appid": "220240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198324683102", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596283200.0} {"text": "Построил дом сегодня? - завтра его не будет. Пошел на рейд один? - вернулся голый. Пошел спать/ отошел? - вернулся голый и без дома. Что-то сделал сегодня? - завтра этого не будет. В этой игре ты добьешься только с друзьями, т.к. одному тебе здесь делать просто нечего. Играешь один - голый и бездомный. Ну и под конец... Здесь очень много \"Честных и добрых\" людей. Советую испытать мир RUST на себе.", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198187119459", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465300800.0} {"text": "上流游戏，差点被愉♂快送走了", "appid": "1293230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198281143189", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "59", "votes_funny": "67", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592481600.0} {"text": "très bon dlc on se croit dans les émissions américaines avec des convoi de ouf", "appid": "558245", "steamid": "profiles/76561198305678773", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550577600.0} {"text": "Старое доброе ультранасилие! Очень классная игра по сети с друзьями! Зомби-апокалипсис грядет!", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110257575", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521720000.0} {"text": "Merci EA, ça fait patienter en attendant la sortie de CyberPunk en 2022 !", "appid": "1172470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135505841", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "9", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604577600.0} {"text": "Juego 10/10", "appid": "436150", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977297801", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480075200.0} {"text": "simple puzzle in the style of browser games with very interesting pictures of naked girls))", "appid": "1426240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198190462675", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602590400.0} {"text": "Gameplay is Awesome, A refined version of Arkham City..yet optimization needs serious attention..Assassins Creed Unity is optimized well compared to this", "appid": "208650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198078081961", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435060800.0} {"text": "갓겜입니다 닥치고 사세요. 저는 타이즈를 정말 좋아합니다. 이 게임에는 타이즈가 많이 나오더군요. 갓겜이라는 증거입니다.", "appid": "963690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198260024214", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555675200.0} {"text": "Гимн аутизму. Медитативный геймплей, грузовики. Включаешь радио Радонеж и катишь себе.", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048442486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499688000.0} {"text": "Bei Counter-Strike Global Offensive braucht man eigentlich nicht mehr viel sagen,es ist und bleibt ein sehr gutes Spiel. Ich empfehle es Leuten die: -Shooter mögen -oft und gerne mit Freunden Spielen -Lust auf 5 gegen 5 Competetiv Matches haben Nicht empfohlen für Leute die: -Nur Solo Spielen -Wert auf eine Kampagne legen -Viele Spielmodi wollen -sich nicht auf neue Spiele (Shooter) einlassen Man sollte ... haben: -Man sollte sich auf jeden Fall 4 oder 5 Freunde suchen die mit einem Competetiv spielen,da die Zufälligen Teammates meist Trollen, kein Headset benutzen oder einen kicken. -Man braucht auf jeden Fall ein Headset um die Gegner hören zu können -Man sollte Ehrgeiz haben und nicht nach einer Niederlage aufgeben -Man sollte ein bisschen Zeit mitbringen um Karten- und Waffenerfahrung zu sammeln", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086556743", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1452254400.0} {"text": "Insane Game", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168374851", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480075200.0} {"text": "Это безусловно об ; Это абсолютно , каждый из которых хорошо цепляется за душу, которых будет очень жалко потерять по мере прохождения игры; Это , всякими внутриигровыми фичами. от чего можно схватиться за сердце, так это от ценника в 1049 руб (конечно, она же в 2 раза больше предыдущей цены!). Но я, купивши, не жалею о потраченных деньгах. Сам я полагаю, что моё прохождение затянется на одну сотну часов. Поэтому, думаю, если по скидке её брать на распродажах, то можно Вам отрадно провести время.", "appid": "567640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271738124", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "34", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506427200.0} {"text": "yes good", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090599491", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595937600.0} {"text": "really gets the lava flowin in ur veins", "appid": "382560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077196473", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586347200.0} {"text": "Huge improvement in terms of performance, good job on that devs", "appid": "507490", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998065890", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522497600.0} {"text": "En güvendiğiniz arkadaşınız bile arkanızdan oyun çeviriyor olabilir. 9/10 9 vermemin sebebi oyunda biraz bug var", "appid": "466240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198220248540", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593777600.0} {"text": "canela en rama¡¡¡¡", "appid": "952060", "steamid": "profiles/76561197989862671", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585915200.0} {"text": "13-я пятница на минималках, но не менее забавная. Игра не цепляет гейплеем, но это не страшно. Убийства веселые на кроваво-корявые. Хотя донат это лишнее.", "appid": "795100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198199738334", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523707200.0} {"text": "Short , Fun and Free Enjoy it. Dont Forget Complete Achivments.", "appid": "1383270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198227185656", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598097600.0} {"text": "The music is good. I just wish the fourth level boss had checkpoints between forms.", "appid": "242820", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977724919", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572436800.0} {"text": "Игра удалась на славу! Есть 2 режима игры - креатив и сурвайв ( + доп подстройки ) Креатив я так понял используется для: обеспечения себя в режиме выживания / для проектирования новых кораблей и баз. Сурв это отдельная тема : - тающая на глазах енергия и попытки нарыть побольше урана чтобы не помереть. - скоростное распиливание собственного стартового корабля на запчасти для заплпнированой базы. - инерция ( заноза в одном месте ))) ) - с появлением кислорода всё стало намного интереснее и сложнее ( не любим сложности отключаем кислород в настройках карты ) - возможность играть с друзьями (16 человек одновременно ), соревноваться или выживать вместе можно даже воевать дпуг против друга. из минусов их 2 : - отсутствие нормальной голосовой связи ( приходится пользоваться или скайпом или звонилкой в стиме ) - наличие горы школьников которые так и норовят забраться на твою базу и поломать всё ( лечится настройками приватности)", "appid": "244850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198106769367", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1429272000.0} {"text": "it's work", "appid": "384300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198142446921", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "Very fun game until you get put on a team of people who don't know what they're doing. Conteplated ending it multiple times due to game bugs. 10/10 would recommend", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198373953735", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1540900800.0} {"text": "+ Pełne spolszczenie /dubbing + napisy/. + Dialogi często zabawne, choć czasem niedopracowane - sztucznie przyspieszone. + Lepsza gra niż w poprzedniej wersji (2), po latach nie ma co się dziwić. Dwójka była nieco ociężała w graniu. Jakoś szybko porzuciłem granie. Skyrim był bliski ukończenia, jednak chyba nie skończony. W Wieśku 3 będąc ociężałym ze śmieci, aż tak wiele nie przeszkadza w walce. Do ukończenia gry jeszcze zostało trochę. Autozapisy czasem psują grę. Zbieranie kart też nie łatwe. Jeśli od razu się nie zbiera, to ciężko uzbierać całość.", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030876312", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "плюсы: совместное прохождение сюжета хорошая графика минусы: плохой сюжет эту игру можно взять только ради мультиплеера", "appid": "49540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198101285535", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1389787200.0} {"text": "Хорошая игра, вот только комп соответсвует рекомендациям и все равно лагает TF2!", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198930889445", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577102400.0} {"text": "This game its one of the best game i have ever play in my intire life. I love it !!!!!", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198272579309", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1468065600.0} {"text": "gg", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198283677437", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575115200.0} {"text": "Fun party game, especially when you’re all in comms on discord or another platform that operates with in game voice mechanics. When in doubt, cyan out.", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198145567624", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600948800.0} {"text": "Всем рекомендую данную игру, потому что над ней можете работать вы и другие игроки, которые создают очень много потрясающих модификаций.", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062523009", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435147200.0} {"text": "This game became the Emblematic game for me as a streamer and youtuber. Wayn June who voices the narrator is also the nicest dude. This game has really changed my perception of gaming and indie studios. It will forever remain in my heart as one of the all-round best games I ever played!", "appid": "262060", "steamid": "profiles/76561197974061308", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "It good", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198188859219", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562241600.0} {"text": "Dzielnice fajnie rozbudowują rozgrywkę, zwiększając znaczenie lokalizacji miasta, nie trzeba budować już dróg, bo robią to karawany, zdecydowanie na plus, chociaż jak zwykle AI kuleje.", "appid": "289070", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961924647", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579521600.0} {"text": "Zasjebiste", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198978426501", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571745600.0} {"text": "Harcadığınız zamandan dolayı asla pişman olmayacağınız bir oyun mu arıyorsunuz? \"To the Moon\" bu sorunun cevabı olmayı kesinlikle hak ediyor. Aslına bakarsanız yanlış oldu, çünkü \"To the Moon\" bir oyundan daha fazlası. Görsel ve duygusal bir şölen. Fazla söze gerek yok sadece daha fazla vakit kaybetmeden deneyin. “I'm Not Crying, There's Something In My Eye”", "appid": "206440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118821938", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "It's not that great... ololo... It's the best game ever.", "appid": "221380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198101490018", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "awesome game", "appid": "242860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130813988", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1427716800.0} {"text": "game is pretty fun , i loved single player tho , gonna try multiplayer soon", "appid": "346110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198440199246", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604836800.0} {"text": "Challenging and fun", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163176139", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580126400.0} {"text": "Armed with a new engine, looks great, plays smoothly, and will be a challenge to both veterans and novices.", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196784323", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595505600.0} {"text": "Um pequeno jogo que ainda precisa de muitas updates, mas e divertido com o pouco que tem, eu recomendo esperar algums meses ate mais funções serem adicionadas", "appid": "1139980", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981822329", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1596888000.0} {"text": "masterpiece. majestic atmosphere. great music.", "appid": "282070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062518487", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573732800.0} {"text": "It's good", "appid": "207610", "steamid": "profiles/76561198024987741", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403438400.0} {"text": "30 fps и куча читеров, всем рекомендую.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198167660750", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572609600.0} {"text": "From my first impression of the game it seems like an amazing game. I would highly recommend this game to any of my friends. As you fight for survival from the crazy cannibals, making a fire on a cold night and making something you can call home, a roof over your head. I think once the game is updated a little more, will be one of the best games I've played. I have played games such as DayZ, and the Forest in my opinion is better. It has more of a realistic feel to the game. You have to be quick. Or the canables will get you! How you start: You're on a plane heading to a unknown destination. Then the plane starts to fall from the sky. With what appears to be your son. After the plane chrashes a man is standing over you, and takes your child. After this has happened. You fight for survival!! The only problem with the game is... Some times when you sleep, it says the game will save. But infact it doesn't )': *UPDATE* The game now allows you to save, but. When you exit to Windows, then rejoin your game, all of your Items that you have picked up will be missing D: Sadly. Maybe the Dev team can fix this very soon :D Aitchy: I approve of this message. Go easy on the game, after all it is still in alpha...", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060764145", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1401710400.0} {"text": "Кирпичный завод был в трех моментах, ожидал от игры большее, но тоже неплохо", "appid": "238320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198245646994", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511524800.0} {"text": "game good you kill people till there dead again dead and dead and more dead but sometimes alive and shot at you not good hide then kill ez clap kappa", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198369019310", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580904000.0} {"text": "Para aquellos a quienes les gusten los juegos tipo Metal Slug y/o no puedan permitirse comprar Broforce, ésta es una opción genial.", "appid": "312990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062318511", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1423224000.0} {"text": "trash", "appid": "304050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093977369", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472126400.0} {"text": "Эта игра интересная и может затянуть, хоть в нем и много доната. Но там есть новые идеи , которые ещё не были использованы в других MOBA играх. Например: таланты ,получаемые после сражения или в саду талантом, они дают возможность игроку сделать уникального героя , который будет отличатся от других. И также в игре присутствуют и другие фишки, которыевы узнаете , скачав эту игру.", "appid": "235340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077267468", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1404561600.0} {"text": "This game is great. I had a great time testing it out. I enjoy the crafting and collecting. I love that I have a little hubble. I do however miss how you could craft more things on the go. Like broken items turn into not so broken but then it got changed and now the broken items are kinda useless. Quick 3 hits and then its gone. You might as well get rid of broken items. Anyway I ramble. I enjoy it a lot. I like collecting. Lots of collecting especially after you buy a storage system. Limited bag space is a little annoying..wish I could get better bigger inventory..but oh well.", "appid": "667890", "steamid": "profiles/76561197985600363", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518523200.0} {"text": "난 존이 아니야", "appid": "1174180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080838667", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587470400.0} {"text": "An early review since I only have around 10 hours in this game so far. Firstly, I want to confirm a few facts when people say that this game seems impossible to play or is extremely difficult to the point of quitting very early. >> This game requires a lot of patience and understanding before you can actually start one-shotting enemies. It's not like your average RPG wherein you just rush into enemies and beat them to death or just take them out via indirect attacks. >> The game is very close to the Souls Series since the mechanics are quite similar but instead of rolling and dodging, you have to deflect or counter all enemy attacks and then take them out. >> Be aware that the game is VERY MUCH based on Stealth Tactics. There are several methods which can make your journey throughout the game very easy and satisfying if you can come up with strategies or even rely on a few walkthroughs if you feel like you are stuck at some point. >> There are definitely several unique stages including boss fights which are quite difficult and test your limits and skills but then again, if you have the patience, understanding and practice, your journey would be extremely enjoyable. >> Like the Souls Series, I have also been playing Sekiro using a Mouse and Keyboard and not a controller (Just my personal choice and I was never a big fan of controllers to begin with), and so far it's been very satisfying for me. I am not sure how the difficulty or the handling of mechanics and controls would alter the gameplay for me but for some people it does matter so it's upto you to go ahead and check it out. So far, I have been really enjoying this game. It's definitely challenging but extremely fun and satisfying at the same time. You get a variety of techniques which you can unlock and play around with, a fair share of fun yet difficult moments and combined with the amazing graphics and lore; this game has been very very well-worth for me so far! Rated :- 9/10", "appid": "814380", "steamid": "profiles/76561197999448753", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "One of my most competitive games in my library (that I play) as well as the most loved game in my library, definitley worth getting if you like a competitive play!", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068096517", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514980800.0} {"text": "後悔沒買Rabi-Ribi Super UPRPRC Edition只買了本體", "appid": "400910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198149062649", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562155200.0} {"text": "ne penser pas qu'il s'agisse d'un concurrent de farming ,voyez le comme un jeux a ajouter a votre collection si vous aimez l'univers des simulateurs agricole .le coté social de farmer's dynasty va vous distraire entre les longs travaux aux champs.au niveau du gameplay ont peut le comparer a farming 2013 ,de par sa physique un peut maladroite (je suis rester coincer 10 minutes dans un fossé ,a avancer et reculer jusqu'à sortir enfin) mais en dehors de cela je le recommande car l'idée est intéressante", "appid": "678900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198102367075", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590062400.0} {"text": ")", "appid": "500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198815522439", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601121600.0} {"text": "Good game.", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198277944245", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1453464000.0} {"text": "Me costó mucho tener este juego fue estresante tenerlo pase por mucho pero ahora que lo poseo les digo vale la pena amigos es un gran juego, te la pasas súper bien jugando en tu equipo de 4 ladrones es un excelente juego le doy un 8/10 porque siempre hay cosas que mejorar pero el juego vale la pena si pueden gastar su dinero en un juego así háganlo vale la pena ;) ..", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117960951", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1425988800.0} {"text": "Old but still a great game", "appid": "12210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198131569307", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585310400.0} {"text": "Купили игр