 give a honest truth on this but if you are into games that take long periods of your time than go for it. if not than stay away from it and save your money for something else.", "appid": "251570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198108275222", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1573560000.0} {"text": "un monument a ne pas louper", "appid": "70", "steamid": "profiles/76561198187191741", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499342400.0} {"text": "---{Graphics}--- ☐ You forget what reality is ☑️ Beautiful ☐Good ☐ Decent ☐ Bad ☐ Don‘t look too long at it ☐ Paint.exe ---{Gameplay}--- ☑️ Very good ☐Good ☐ It‘s just gameplay ☐ Mehh ☐ Starring at walls is better ☐ Just don‘t ---{Audio}--- ☐Eargasm ☑️ Very good ☐ Good ☐ Not too bad ☐ Bad ☐ Earrape ---{Audience}--- ☐ Kids ☑️ Teens ☑️ Adults ☐ Human ---{Difficulity}--- ☐ Just press \"A\" ☐ Easy ☐ Significant brain usage ☑️ Easy to learn / Hard to master ☐ Difficult ☐ Dark Souls ---{Grind}--- ☐ Nothing to grind ☐ Only if u care about leaderboards/ranks ☑️ Isnt necessary to progress ☐ Average grind level ☐ Too much grind ☐ You‘ll need a second live for grinding ---{Game Time}--- ☐ Long enough for a cup of coffee ☐Short ☑️ Average ☑️ Long ---{Price}--- ☐ It’s free! ☑️ Worth the price ☐ Wait for sale ☐ If u have some spare money left ☐ Not recommended ☐ You could also just burn your money ---{Bugs}--- ☐ Never heard of ☑️ Minor bugs ☐Can get annoying ☐ Full of bugs", "appid": "863550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198382636494", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591099200.0} {"text": "Рогалик с данжами, чем-то похожий на айзека, но теперь все зациклено на пушках и там свои механики (От переворачивания столов до пустышек и падающих люстр) В игре присутствует отличный саундтрек, хороший юмор, да и графика в игре не на нижнем уровне!", "appid": "311690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110329919", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508932800.0} {"text": "its scary", "appid": "871720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198828444508", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1568894400.0} {"text": "Finally joined the bandwagon concerning this game, and I'm glad I'm aboard. It's one of the most immersive experiences I've had in a while, and I'm sure one which will have lasting effects. This is the kind of game which will plant seeds. It becomes embedded in your psyche, Not coincidentally, the psyche is at the forefront of every interaction you will undergo while playing. Disco Elysium requires a smart player. And not just because of the mountains of text you're required to read, but because of the many concepts and references (many only in this fictional universe) interspersed throughout. Plus, many of the moral choices and considerations require great thought. And it's all rewarding. First of all, the writing is superb, and deserving of a pulitzer. I don't say this lightly. It's better written than most books. The myriads of diverse dialogue choices all are done with conviction, and you really feel like your choices have consequence. And most of the time, they do. Failing skill checks often brings about unforeseen rewards, and seemingly inconsequential pieces of dialogue come back later. It's really not so much an RPG as it is an adventure game, however. It has RPG elements, similar to Quest For Glory and the skill advancements. It's astonishingly deep and emotionally intelligent. If you don't get the feels from this game, you are soulless. There is much humor, laden through this waltz of despair. You and your character will have many sinking feelings and dawning realizations up until the final curtain. All the characters are unique and likeable/loatheable/multifaceted. You really begin to care about your character (and Kim) and the world around you, The influence from Planescape Torment is palpable, and that's A-ok by me. They even thank Chris Avellone at the end. It also reminded me of QFG (as previously mentioned), Divinity Original Sin 2, True Detective (especially with their misanthropic Bukowski-like banter), Shutter Island, and the miniseries Mosaic.", "appid": "632470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198273762327", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594555200.0} {"text": "prosta agonb", "appid": "533300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138063111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Government of the people, by the people, for the people", "appid": "255710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062394807", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576497600.0} {"text": "NICE", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198366254685", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1489320000.0} {"text": "jmk", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196066627", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Игра классная, хотелось бы увидеть еще игр от этого художника Рисовка 10/10", "appid": "1289310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198359520000", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592395200.0} {"text": "Half-Life, ne çevrimiçi olarak oraya buraya fırlayarak; ne de hikayesini oynamıştım. Oyun eski fakat senaryo ve düşünüş bakımından evren sonsuzluğunda bir sistem var. Pek eleştirilecek yanı yok, gayet güzel. İndirimdeyken alıp, bu yılların eskitemediği oyunu oynayabilirsiniz. İyi Oyunlar!", "appid": "70", "steamid": "profiles/76561198364191207", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597147200.0} {"text": ">Buy CSGO >Promise myself I wont spend money on stupid skins. >Buys cheap skins just to have some. >Gets addicted and spend a month salary on skins. >Doesn't have money to pay rent and gets kicked out. >Has to move back to parents house. 10/10 Would ruin my life again :D", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198192583682", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1460721600.0} {"text": "Olmuş bu. Oyun güzel. Hikayeyi az buçuk herkes biliyordur zaten. O yüzden değinmeyeceğim pek. Hikayesi güzel, ancak aktarılışı daha güzel. O yüzden ana görevler oldukça zevkli. Başka yerlerde görmüş/duymuş olabilirsiniz, sonu daha etkileyici olabilirdi. Oynanış olarak Unity'den pek farkı yok dövüş sistemi dışında. Oyunda birincisi kılıç yok. Bu da demek oluyor ki combat sistemi tamamen farklı ve maalesef kolay. Unity'de gerçekçiliğe yaklaşmışlardı ama burada yine çok hızlı şekilde öldürülebiliniyor düşmanlarımız. Jack the Ripper DLC oldukça hoş 10 adet görev var ve yine yan görevler de var. 10 görevin bazılarında Karındeşen Jack olarak oynuyoruz, ki o görevler harika zaten. Genel olarak 'korkutma' temalı bir DLC ve buna uygun birkaç yenilik var. DLC'nin kurgusu daha çok hoşuma gitti benim. Ana oyun da bu tarzda yapılmış olsaydı daha iyi olurdu bence. Uzun lafın kısası, Assassin's Creed Unity'den bazı yönlerde daha iyi olsa da hikaye konusunda geri kalıyor bence. Unity'nin hikayesi epey güzeldi. Puan:7/10", "appid": "368500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077134325", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454673600.0} {"text": "лучшее что может быть", "appid": "976310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198164768982", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584619200.0} {"text": "BEST SAINTS ROW EVER", "appid": "206420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119614965", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1451563200.0} {"text": "very epic", "appid": "581320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065957057", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "гучи флип флап", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198326380654", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598270400.0} {"text": "yes", "appid": "1172470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198856831887", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604750400.0} {"text": "I finally can quench my thirst for game like Freelancer. This game had high steps of learning curve. Like how to get your enemy stay on your target, how to do mining and exploration (this I hadn't done it yet). Patient is the key and after few hours of the tutorials, you will get the general idea how to play this game. Because the veterans that I know from Twitch said to me, they to still learning many things even after playing this game for years since release. Help Me. I'm Addicted xD", "appid": "359320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082851799", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509624000.0} {"text": "Не смотря на плохую оптимизацию , это просто отличная игра. Немогу оторваться , затягивает до жути. Надеюсь в будущем оптимизацию всё таки завезут , ждём патчей.", "appid": "268500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038958319", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454673600.0} {"text": "♣", "appid": "532210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132012668", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544184000.0} {"text": "best game ever!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119314070", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480334400.0} {"text": "liked the battle-hardened version of Lara more than in the first game. In general, a very enjoyable game.", "appid": "391220", "steamid": "profiles/76561197988407686", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599307200.0} {"text": "其實挺好玩,但BUG太多,經常斷線........", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198300260913", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1468238400.0} {"text": "WHAT GREAT GAMe i play it in past still fun.", "appid": "323370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198078479604", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514289600.0} {"text": "7/10", "appid": "746510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049647172", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Всем привет, в игре интересный необычный сюжет(развитие внимательности и логики) Будет ништяк когда подвезут оптимезацию! Графика хороша слов нет. Чуть больше посижу там и обновлю обзор до более раскрытого. P.S. своих денег стоит однозначно.", "appid": "323190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198125274479", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535284800.0} {"text": "Su multiplayer es lo que más me gustó del juego", "appid": "202970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198403363237", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543320000.0} {"text": "Nice Game!", "appid": "298110", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993468367", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1419163200.0} {"text": "Bu oyunun bedava olması Allahın size bir lütfudur", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198269473880", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519041600.0} {"text": "witziges und gutes game ^^ es gibt nur 1 problem DIE HACKER aber da sie jetzt ein anticheat hinzufügen bald. wird es hoffentlich besser ^^", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141967369", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599566400.0} {"text": "Неплохо. Мне понравилось ;)", "appid": "1124980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198165697280", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572436800.0} {"text": "cute chars and nice environment. just something to pass the time", "appid": "207690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198212154143", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490788800.0} {"text": "Keep in mind the game is in Early Acces so stop crying because the game have actually problem. the possibility save your outfits are fixed now what you make it actually via the advanced customization weapon and character but is one of the strong points of this game because the customization are really deeply and the weapon have their own weight and this penalizes your way of running faster or slower This game use some gameplay since some others game, you will killed the others player or capture the flag and you will won some score with this score you can call a supply vehicle other type surgical strike Participate at this World War 3 will giving you some money virtual and with this money you can unlock the stuff as Armor, Weapon, Skins, etc... plus you get new grade by level. You have a strategic war map what show consequences of every battle, a performance player is rewarded with resources to conquer or defend a territory. Gain additional bonuses via the metagame and turn the tide of war! Every destroyed vehicle, every kill, every bullet fired, every achievement affects the big picture presented on a constantly evolving, interactive war map. It's possible join a server via the steam browser server! On the side the optimization I have no problem the games are very fluid and pleasant to play. I will update the review with the time and keep you informed about game developments modifed at 22/10/2018 - 2:52 AM GMT+2.", "appid": "674020", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003385505", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "20", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1540123200.0} {"text": "best for achievements hunter", "appid": "508900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198144345124", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "мам ... мам кажется я покекал", "appid": "214490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105538059", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446465600.0} {"text": "great game", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198112563077", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1430481600.0} {"text": "Best game,", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561199013285386", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595937600.0} {"text": "dig it", "appid": "617290", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004524666", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566302400.0} {"text": "游戏很爽，但剧情方面V哥还是和3代一个逼样，亲妈和抛瓦之间，他选择了后者。", "appid": "601150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198146524056", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1552564800.0} {"text": "Stupidly fun game, use telekinesis to throw people around, or mess around with cheats, BIGHEADMODE! everyones a bobblehead, its hilarious. 1337/10 Would buy the game with all dlc. Its a saints row game, its worth buying...", "appid": "206420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085765161", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1442059200.0} {"text": "Been playing CS for many years. Loved 1.6 (and earlier), Source and now I'm loving GO.. Not much to say that people won't already know about the game. Just make sure your mouse sensitivity isn't too high and preferably an English speaker.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198024307197", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1443441600.0} {"text": "I Recomend", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198844355161", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578744000.0} {"text": "Игра реально затягивает! Уровни разные, много челленджей, динамика и адреналин шкалят. Нет присущего жанру однообразия, в игре есть реально светлые идеи, которые развлекут скучающего геймера. На первый взгляд кажется, что в ней нет ничего особенного, но эта мысль почти сразу после запуска вылетает из головы.", "appid": "449440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069170604", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465905600.0} {"text": "This game is such a blast!", "appid": "1172470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198012774835", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604577600.0} {"text": "It is a very good game and you can really tell your own story", "appid": "294100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198800592374", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598875200.0} {"text": "Definitiv eine Pfote nach oben für dieses Spiel. Ja man hat keine Möglichkeit die Geschichte zu beeinflussen, aber mal ehrlich! Das hat man in sogut wie keinem Spiel und in anderen stört es ja scheinbar auch nicht. Dies ist eine traurige Geschichte und wir können/müssen ihren Verlauf miterleben. Die Kombination aus niedlicher und knuffiger Darstellung und süßen Charakteren mit deprimierender Story wirkt am Anfang etwas befremdlich. Trotzdem (oder vielleicht gerade deswegen?) nimmt einen das Spiel mit und berührt einen. Und auch wenn ich jetzt nach dem Spiel alles andere als glücklich bin, kann ich für dieses Spiel absolut nur eine Empfehlung aussprechen und ich hoffe, dass die Entwcikler noch weitere solche Spiele machen. Vielleicht erfahren wir, wie es hier mit den Charakteren weitergeht?", "appid": "623810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035401629", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518091200.0} {"text": "🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑 🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🌑🔘🌑🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🔘🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘 🔘🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘🔘 🔘🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🔘 🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑 🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑🌑 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤💚💚💚💚💚💚🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💚🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤💚🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💚🖤🧡🔘🔘🧡🧡🧡🧡🔘🔘🧡🖤💚🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🧡💛🔘💛💛💛💛💛💛🔘💛🧡🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🧡💛🔘💛💛💛💛💛💛🔘💛🧡🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🧡💛💛💛💛🧡🧡💛💛💛💛🧡🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💚🖤🧡🔘💛🖤🖤🖤🖤💛🔘🧡🖤💚🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💚💚🖤🖤🖤💚💚💚💚🖤🖤🖤💚💚🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💚💚💚🖤💚🖤🖤💚🖤💚💚💚🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤💚🖤💚💚💚💚🖤💚🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤🖤💚💚💚💚🖤🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤💚💚💚💚🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤💔💔💔💙💙💙🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤💔💔💔💔💙💙💙💙🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💔💔💔💔💔💔💙💙💙💙💙💙🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💔🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤🖤💙🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤💔🖤🧡🔘🔘🧡🧡🧡🧡🔘🔘🧡🖤💙🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🧡💛🔘💛💛💛💛💛💛🔘💛🧡🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🧡💛🔘💛💛💛💛💛💛🔘💛🧡🖤🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘 🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🔘🖤🧡💛💛💛💛🧡🧡💛💛💛💛🧡