 artbooka, concept arty oraz uroczy przepis na naleśniki ;) . Jeśli ktoś lubi takie typy gierek to będzie bardzo dobrze sie bawił :D według mnie gra zasługuje na 10/10, jedno z największych zaskoczeń roku POLECAM ( ͡~ ͜ʖ ͡°) (jedyny minus gry to taki że tą gre robił ♥♥♥♥♥ a nie ma polskiego języka ale wystarczy poszukać w necie :p ).", "appid": "1289310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198859038609", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599393600.0} {"text": "Very fun game, the combat feels real and the sniping is the focal point of the whole game, and to get a great use out of it I recommend using mouse and keyboard, from the trajectory of the wind to the distance of your target, its as real as it can possibly get. The story is good, but I've played better stories than this, but its not bad either. Weapon selection is okay not a lot to choose from beside the snipers, the assault rifles there's at least 6 I think? And a few pistols, the skill system for upgrading your character was implemented pretty well, the upgrades you buy actually work on your character, And, a decent sized map you go to a couple of different areas in the game, there are bounties in which you hunt down a list of Most Wanted people in Georgia (The country not the state), and yeah I think this concludes my review. 9.3/10, the graphics are really good too. And this game and the the other two and Sniper Art of Victory are underrated games, give them a try.", "appid": "368070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198128085739", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574164800.0} {"text": "I have no idea why i played it, but i quess i got all achievements from it.", "appid": "463390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198354005423", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598184000.0} {"text": "It's a waste of time. But i ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ love this game", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198380752473", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "212", "votes_funny": "101", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "Игра очень приятная! Мне понравилось! Занимательная! Расслабляет :)", "appid": "343360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134614322", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458216000.0} {"text": "Played this game for almost 21+ hours and got 100% completionist, and i'm not surprised that this game will get a remastered version soon, why? 1. The mechanical on this game is almost perfect after Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag 2. The map on this game has some big landscape and some interesting place for taking a screenshot or completing the place like opening chest etc. And i'm so grateful that the uncharted thing like memory sync and chest on different map only less than Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag (i mean AC IV: Black Flag has over 50+ chest and memory sync on uncharted island/place to complete the map, and it's so boring..) 3. This game is easy to complete especially for the collectibles and main memory sync, all of them has some easy task except for Man O' War mission and Hope's Mission that got me some trouble to get 100% sync. 4. I recommended to buy the Deluxe Version to get all of the DLC, i mean if you get all the DLC you don't need to worry about other things like unlocking outfit, equipment, pistol etc that you always want 5. The song on this game is the best thing that i heared after previous Assassin's Creed game, like the opening theme and the Agnus Dei song, it's so calming to hear especially if you're down after you work/study hard on your real life. 6. For the battle ship map thing, i like the way they added a button to skip it so we don't get bored to see the battle. 7. It's easy to farm the materials and the money of this game, i mean if you want to try opened all of the region, you will get almost 35k per 30 minutes if you play the game, and in total you don't need to hunt again, just buy the material to craft all items that you need. For the materials, you just need going to the north atlantic map and farm Man O' War there for like 30 minutes, if you work hard, you will get your ship 100% complete upgrade after like 3 - 5 hours. For the minus thing that i still didn't like: 1. The synchronization thing on some map like Ruisseau du Renard viewpoint, it's always got a bug that after you sync to the viewpoint, you will see that the viewpoint sync still locked but you just sync it before. This bug is also same like on AC IV: BF on Cat Island, i don't know why that this bug still exist to this day, either no one reported it or the game team is lazy to fix it, but i'm very glad that the support ticket that i send got replied saying that they will look into this bug again, but for now to get 100% completionist, you need to make a new game slot. But yeah, that's my experience that i play for this game, i'm recommended all of you to buy this game especially if you like the AC series. For the remastered version? Worth? YES!!", "appid": "311560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198232357740", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "37", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520337600.0} {"text": "I can't do my own models/characters its not working for me at all", "appid": "438100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263322568", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1515499200.0} {"text": "Mankini.", "appid": "251890", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093834363", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1420200000.0} {"text": "Ta gra jest spoczko polecam Magda Gesller", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198179285249", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1480852800.0} {"text": "тупо 10/10", "appid": "107410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006435934", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588075200.0} {"text": "ТОП", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198439175341", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590148800.0} {"text": "best survival game ever come play with me", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007563498", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1388836800.0} {"text": "Really good game!", "appid": "602960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048922625", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1574769600.0} {"text": "Jeu fun et gratuit tout en restant sympa a tryhard.", "appid": "884660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198267277356", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1569153600.0} {"text": "GAME", "appid": "219150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198061471466", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562241600.0} {"text": "After so many years waiting for the sequel to the first RoR game, the comes with an masterpiece. Though it is in Early Access and lack things like the that enable you to freely change the style of gameplay, RoR2, now in a beautifully designed 3D, is already one of the best games that I've played. The always changing outcome of a single run based on player choices and luck, the rising difficulty based on time played and the secrets/challenges to uncover, fulfill me with will to play again and again. The changes on connection, , made it very easy to play with friends. The new , although a big laggy sometimes based on the \"host\" connection, works absolutely fine and adds extra fun to the trip. The price may be a bit high for now, but that's understandable for a game in EA that needs players who are willing to share opinions and help the game growing process. After playing many hours, discussing and discovering the secrets and new content that doesn't was in the first game, my conclusion is that Risk of Rain 2, after a great week on its debut, has conquered almost everyone that played it. With 6 playable characters at the moment, it can fit a very large variety of playstyles. And the devs shall be making it even greater with new content and bug-fixing updates.", "appid": "632360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198098440825", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1554292800.0} {"text": "nicu gamu", "appid": "280160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087351365", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "Jogo bom , as vezes da vontade de enfiar a merreta no c* e rodar de tanta raiva.", "appid": "240720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198428648325", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "30", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593086400.0} {"text": "It may be the most random steam game since they removed deadpool from the platform. the powers, which you will be unlocking progressively and satisfactorily, give you absolute mobility over the city. So much freedom that you prefer to kick the city from end to end trying uracans, forcing civilians to dance dupstep and proving worthy explosions of the same magnitude as chernobyl. Contains a system branches evolved for literally anything in the game. ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ fun with a million references to pop culture and an impressive soundtrack that fits perfectly with the situations that occur in the game. Despite its graphics has aged very well. Worthy to keep it in a time capsule so that in the 3460 humanity knows that we were made ofContains for me the best weapon in the history of mankind, the dupstep gun. Definitely kek.", "appid": "206420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198933872371", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575720000.0} {"text": "If you're into the whole Souls-like genre and you want a bit of Science Fiction thrown into the mix, what better game to start with than The Surge? There are a few additions made to make the experience a little more tolerable, but I won't describe them here. Play the game if you want to learn more.", "appid": "378540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006986113", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584273600.0} {"text": "지지리도 할거 없을때하면 죽이는 맛 하난 찰진 시간 죽이기 좋은 무한 좀비 디펜스 게임 싼 사격에 비해 나름 괜찮은 그래픽에 놀랐네요", "appid": "449090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198220483131", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515672000.0} {"text": "ns game )", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110867803", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1519214400.0} {"text": "Sehr tolles Spiel aber leider viele Bugs bin schon 4 mal an irgendwelchen bugs gestorben", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271867389", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1489320000.0} {"text": "Gran juego como toda su saga, a precio de risa.", "appid": "41070", "steamid": "profiles/76561197978253840", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480075200.0} {"text": "One of the good, old RTS classics! :)", "appid": "40950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121161049", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576584000.0} {"text": "KAUFT DIESES SPIEL NICHT - noch nicht. Und nie meinte ich diesen Satz positiver, als leidenschaftlicher RPG Spieler und DND Fanatiker wurde ich hier natürlich doppelt gefesselt. Nur warum noch nicht - nun ganz einfach ich hab soviel Spaß gehabt das ich jetzt nichts mit mir anzufangen weis bis die 1.0 raus kommt. Act 1 hat mit sehr viel Detailliebe und Interessanten Orten / Charakteren voll überzeugt. Mal was anderes ein Kind sterben zu sehen oder deinen Augapfel zu verpfänden - Leute die schon Spaß am absurden Reichtum der Lore von Spielen wie Divinity Orginal Sin 2 hatten kommen hier voll auf ihre Kosten. Das das spiel auch unglaublich gut aussieht und sehr nah ran gezoomt etwas von einem Göttlichen Überwacher hat der euch über die Schulter guckt ist natürlich erwähnenswert aber heute kein Kauf Argument mehr . Nein, Kaufen solltet ihr das spiel (sobald die 1.0 draußen ist ) wegen seiner Kreativen Geschichten, den Charakteren die sich anfühlen als hätten Sie ein leben gelebt bis du plötzlich das Sims Ding über ihre Köpfe gehängt hast, und dem alt bekannten Rollenspiel Flair das im Modernen gewand mein Herz höher schlagen lässt. Zu den Bugs, die Charaktere waren geladen ihre Kleidung nicht 10/10 fixt das nur bitte im fertigen Spiel das die Kleidung nach lädt.", "appid": "1086940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198024013400", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1602676800.0} {"text": "good :D", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198284211000", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1456488000.0} {"text": "Oynarken Açın Bi Aleyna Tilki Kamyonla Giderken AA Aleyna Tilki Geçiyor Dersiniz Ve Oynarken Açın Bi Şarkı Ohh Mish... Gerçekten Çok Güzel Bir Oyun Direksyon Setiniz Varsa Hemen Almanızı Tavsiye Ediyorum... Oyun Bildiğiniz Üzere Euro Truck Simulator Yani Kamyon Sürme Oyunu... Oynerken Canınızın Sıkılcağını Sanmıyorum Gerçekten Harika Bir Oyun... Açın Bi Arkadan Şarkı Gerçekten Gerçek Hisi Veriyor... -------------------------------Tavsiye Ediyorum-------------------------------------------", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198314217407", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1478606400.0} {"text": "Played this game for about a million hours on my xbox, and I always wanted to own it on pc to use mods and such. No matter how old this game is, it still is very fun to play and will always be one of my favorites.", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198359800022", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1503057600.0} {"text": "топовая игра, советую", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198900719268", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575028800.0} {"text": "Veramente stupendo!! Un gioco epico, divertente, difficile e appassionante da non perdere (soprattutto per la grafica 3D \"retro\" che adoro)", "appid": "225140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198023777005", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387800000.0} {"text": "Was soll man sagen, wer auf WW1 steht und CoH mag wird diesen Mod lieben so wie ich.", "appid": "314420", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971384006", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1422100800.0} {"text": "Das spiel ist echt geil macht laune es ist witzig echt zu empfehlen :D:D", "appid": "55230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082064880", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403265600.0} {"text": "in this game......pay 30 money for.......say oh it ok because no dlc........wait......now dlc for 15 money......game never go on this game....you build colony....then naked poeple attack.....then u kill for fun....and then the boring part of no kill come....do random sh?t like build home......then finally 10 naked people volunter for DEATH....then 100 now it get interest...NOW ROBOT COME and he HIT UR COLONST but ur colonst is masokist and he say haha +999 mood i am dead", "appid": "294100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130617581", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586952000.0} {"text": "For a long time I played DOA 5 Ultimate through the PS3 emulator. I like the DOA game series. The game is very cool music,interesting characters (most of them are very beautiful girls hehe) Of the characters, I prefer Naotora, Hayate, Mai Shiranui and Nyotengu(She has a pretty “big” potential and she is only 1000 yo) Japanese thanks :) I apologize in advance for my English :D", "appid": "311730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198326115981", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1560945600.0} {"text": "O quarto e último jogo da saga Arkham (até então) trouxe uma infinidade de melhorias e novidades em comparação com os anteriores, mas não conseguiu marcar tanto nos personagens e história qnto os dois primeiros (Asylum e City) embora ainda assim proporcione muitas horas de diversão e uma trama interessante. Sobre os acréscimos, o open world nesse jogo é bem melhor, o mapa da cidade de Gotham maior e há muitas missões secundárias espalhadas a serem concluídas, embora a maioria seja repetitiva tem também algumas bem elaboradas, como as do Charada cm vários enigmas e pistas de desafios qe precisam ser superados afim de libertar a mulher gato. Houveram mtas melhorias no combate, ficou ainda mais dinâmico e frenético cm uma gama imensa de perks qe aprimoram os golpes, armadura e equipamentos do Batman. A cereja do bolo, no entanto, foi a possibilidade de dirigir o batmóvel cm suas várias armas no modo de combate e turbos de alta velocidade no modo de carro... e realmente focaram bastante nisso, durante toda a campanha e missões secundárias o batmóvel vai sempre ter um papel crucial seja para resolver puzzles simples, seja para auxiliar no combate explodindo tanques inimigos e salvando a pele do Batman em emboscadas lotadas de soldados (tem até mesmo Bosses qe só podem ser derrotados usando o batmóvel). Até certo ponto essa foi uma boa jogada, porém se vcê não gostar mto de dirigir e sair atirando cm o veículo o jogo não vai te agradar tanto, apesar de ter mtas partes em qe vcê controla o Batman normalmente, é impossível ficar sem usar o batmóvel prqê focaram bastante nessa nova mecânica qe não existia nos jogos anteriores e qe proporciona bastante liberdade para vcê dirigir pela cidade inteira atropelando tudo qnto é bandido pelo caminho. Fora isso o qe surpreende mto nesse jogo são os lindos gráficos, super detalhados e cm uma atmosfera profunda, além de conter um modo foto qe permite tirar lindas capturas de tela caso queira brincar de fotógrafo. Já com relação a história, tenta ser mais complexa se comparado aos anteriores, mas ainda assim não conseguiu prender tanto a atenção, vcê se preocupa mais cm a jogabilidade e em se divertir derrotando os vilões do qe cm o enredo em si... faltou carisma nos personagens principais e a fórmula de te fzer sentir dentro do jogo vista em Arkham Asylum e Arkham City.. sendo tão genérico qnto o Arkham Origins nesse quesito, sem nada de muito marcante ou de tirar o fôlego. Ainda assim esse é um ótimo jogo para passar o tempo e mergulhar no mundo do Cavaleiro das Trevas, cm mta coisa pra fzer, mtos cenários para explorar e mtos personagens famosos para rever (incluindo o Duas Caras, Espantalho, Pinguim, Gordon, Hera Venenosa, Robin, entre outros). Recomendo demais a franquia do Batman Arkham, vale mto a pena jogar todos, seguindo a ordem certa de lançamento qe se inicia pelo “Asylum” para melhor experiência.", "appid": "208650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198375029180", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "82", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598961600.0} {"text": "nice game", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198816021224", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "This game's soundtrack is composed entirely of the percussion instrument the Wood Block. You're a woodblock dodging woodblock shaped Woodblocks. 10/10", "appid": "221640", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970418619", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387540800.0} {"text": "Note: My hours have mostly been offline on this game. Decent, fun, fast side scroller that should appeal to fans of the genre. Not as deep a game like Jets n Guns Gold but few are. Not difficult either (bordering on easy) and easily played with KB and mouse (though I prefer this method of controls to any other). Great weapon effects, customization and mech designs keep the game interesting. 4 game modes adds to the fun as well as the replayability. Although I have not participated, I’m sure 4 player co-op is also blast. Some of the levels are simply gorgeous and you can tell the developers took a lot of time on them. Probably the strongest part of the game is the attention put to the upgrade path and skill tree. With several options and paths, you can customize your warrior to your liking. I agree with all the tags applied to this game except for bullet hell. This is NOT a bullet hell game by any stretch of the imagination. Enemy fire is sparse, slow and easy to dodge which leads me to one of the faults of the game is that it really is not hard enough. Enemies are plodding and predictable and your ship, even when not upgraded, is a bullet sponge. Characters are not funny with unnecessary presence and narration. If not included, they probably would not even be missed. You can tell there were attempts at humor which just don’t go over well. I would have liked to see some kind of heat management system. There are literally no consequences to holding down both mouse buttons throughout an entire level. Is it a good game? Yes. Is it a great game? No, not by any means. It is not without it’s flaws but overcomes these with a great fun factor, game modes, and replayability, which is very important to me as a person who puts a lot of hours into games that generally don't get a lot of hours from other people. Unfortunately, the biggest blemish against it is that it really looks like the developers spent more time on the visuals rather than focusing on the mechanics, gameplay, and story, except for the level progression, which is well done. I was a bit surprised when I used the windows key to exit the game and came back to find myself dead. I would have assumed the game would have paused but this isn’t that big of a deal, just a bit surprising. I recommend the game but with reservations. A strong candidate to pick up during sales… 6/10 Fun Factor Fun powerups Good character (mech) design Weapons customization Well thought out upgrade path Sound Beautiful Scrolling landscapes/backgrounds Game Modes Too easy at times No heat management system Underwhelming enemy design Ineffective enemies Unnecessary, uninspiring, forgettable characters Predictable/repetitive level structure", "appid": "389650", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961395783", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "12/10 пропаданий корабля з.ы. Пропал корабль нахуй,весь его экипаж в воздухе летал.", "appid": "242050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198154299239", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "19", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519128000.0} {"text": "ヤ・シュトラ・ルル はとてもかわいいミコッテで、エオルゼアの世界をディシディアに表しています。ミコッテは最も美しく象徴的な種のもので、とてもスタイリッシュな猫の特徴があります。全体としてミコッテとエオルゼアを表すヤ・シュトラを持つことは本当に素晴らしい追加です。", "appid": "1022469", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050836578", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1556193600.0} {"text": "Hyper Hippo - Teaching children how to easily pull off capitalism since 2014.", "appid": "346900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198046556294", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1430568000.0} {"text": "best game this summer 10/10", "appid": "414340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198046188880", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1503403200.0} {"text": "Best RPG game and the best part is free :D", "appid": "238960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198343272306", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584964800.0} {"text": "As the typical belief that a +18 game will only be linear and without much history is true in most such games, but in \"acting lessons\" broke the typical paradigm of the +18 game, it is a game that made a home run into space, has an immersive story, \"porn\" is part of the relationship and interaction between the characters, it has twists, dramas, scenes that worry\"s you about the good being of some of the people. Not only this, besides laughing out loud, you cry in several scenes, the plot has a few twists (not spoiler), despite just showing almost images and scenes it is a game that I can recommend to anyone who can buy it, plus if you analyze it well, it gives several lessons about life itself, it is a beautiful game, my CONGRATULATIONS TO THE CREATOR, (although It kills me with the half bitter end ) I hope that DR. PINCKCAKE continue creating such beautiful games. 9.0/10", "appid": "1045520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090321265", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571745600.0} {"text": "This game is an awesome and is addictive with Starbound and Terraria elements to it, but with its own type of flavor. The game is early access has occasional hiccups, but can be easily fixed with an update or two. It’s a refreshing take on 2D sandbox/rpg type of games which is a good commodity. Let’s start with the gameplay. It starts out rather easy as you can get a short tutorial on what to do. You can easily manage controls on an Xbox controller or PlayStation controller which can be helpful. The graphics are pixelated like any other retro game. I’m a fan of these retro games as I grew up in the 80's and 90's playing those console games in their prime. The skilling up/leveling up system is very unique and different from Starbound and Terraria which makes this game stand on its own. I enjoyed exploring and creating my homes, teleport points, forges, and loved the crafting aspect inside of it. This game is very time consuming and can be very addictive at the same time. The game isn’t perfect and still is an early access game which comes with its bugs and glitches. The game has unusually long load times when you first start out which I found awkward knowing this is a pixel 2d sandbox game and isn’t a really big game that should be doing so. I found that it did take much more memory than expected as well which I heard the developer is seeking to fix. In terms of the multiplayer aspect, there should be some dedicated servers steam side to help everyone connect with each other to make this game even more fun. I hope that this is also fixed and implemented in the finalized version so I can even give this a higher grade on my review. Anyways I found this game to be quite fun, addictive, time consuming, and refreshingly new. I hope this game can fix these glitches and whatnot to make this an even better game. 7.5/10", "appid": "280520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044920564", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465732800.0} {"text": "I adore this game. It's one of a kind and found myself laughing quite a bit at the humor. For the price point it's more than worth the purchase.", "appid": "1290200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011733265", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598529600.0} {"text": "gooderest game", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071430182", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522497600.0} {"text": "Such an addicting game. :)", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198202223741", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1488974400.0} {"text": "Highest quality VN that i own right now. That is the factor of the kind of high price. You are the only person not attacked by zombies that are roaming everywhere. How do you exploit this? Getting around with ease earning others respect and of course the most important thing, SEX. H-scenes are fully uncensored, same goes with Vol. 2 I don`t think that the game is fully done yet because Vol 2 ended in a big cliffhanger. If you`re buying this only for the H-scenes then buy Vol 1 it has more pictures.", "appid": "942850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271080192", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594641600.0} {"text": "This game is so fun to play but when this game was being played for free it became chaotic in a way were cheaters are taking the advantage of it.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148741649", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549108800.0} {"text": "good game :)", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189486369", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Хароший квест . Сюжет я бы сказал на 7/10 . Давольно странно поначалу что туда вплели сюжеты про гейство , фименизм , зоофилию и педофилию . но это выглядит не навязыванием , а скарее обяснением со стороны в чём загвостка со всем этим дермом т.к. большенсво персонажей говорит что это мерзко но признаёт что не стоит гнобить за подобное . Феменизм там унижают показывая его проявления ввиде одменистратора который не шута не знает об нём но при этом называет себя фименисткой ну и на примере жены еврейского задиры . Женщины показывавются отнють не в лучшем свете хатя и в реальности именно то же и произходит . Тебе пытаются навязать что извращения это не так плохо , да но большая часть героев не потдерживает это а просто мирется так что они и не дают прям однозначного мнения что всё хорошо вон никто не должен быть против представлены все мнения . Только загвостка в том что с уклоном в то что это норм во всяком случе так думает большенство судя по другим обзорам а значит на это и расчитано . Главный герой бисексуал в кругах которго инвалиды , пидафилы , геи и пидофилы . Он мудак который ради своей выгоды и своих чуств ворует и портит другим людям жизнь . Он голюцинирует и постоянно говрит с собой или с воображаемыми друзьями пытаясь разобратся в себе и в своей жизни . Но когда он достигает понимания и того что он хочит а хочит он видет цвета он отказывается от этого и говрит что он хотел просто попробовать это и слишком долго живёт в чёрнобелом мире что бы видеть цвета . Эт овыглядит интересно и именно это нужно от истории вызывать интерес и быть не похожей на что то другое", "appid": "399700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068530814", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470052800.0} {"text": "good game but alot of sad ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ hackers", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198421210097", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514289600.0} {"text": "Jogabilidade Muito Boa Varios Tipos De Itens Para Craftar Monstros Variaveis Jogo Ta Nota 10/10 Imagina Agora Com o Multiplayer Jogar Nossa Vai Ser Muita Aventura Recomendo", "appid": "219740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198136652172", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1418990400.0} {"text": "Apesar deste jogo ser antigo ainda podemos apreciar a campanha ou criar batalhas com o modo Editor", "appid": "91330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198232936848", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "Very gud", "appid": "219101", "steamid": "profiles/76561198353193348", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575288000.0} {"text": "Einfach nur nice! : )", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198172716301", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454500800.0} {"text": "Clicker, incremental a jakoś tak wciąga.", "appid": "685310", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992575759", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "elite", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993759586", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1511784000.0} {"text": "До чего может дойти человечество? Полёт к звёздам, изучение миров и великие научные открытия? Это в лучшем случае. А что если люди уйдут в себя, где виртуальный мир будет преобладать над реальностью, ведь зачем себя утруждать и что-то делать, если можно следовать правилам и не думать о последствиях? Мир, где есть свобода, но нет желания. Есть всё, но нет ничего. О чём это? Понять это можно только сыграв в бесплатный... можно назвать симулятор ходьбы про будущее, которое может быть не так уж и далеко как кажется.", "appid": "1052070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308627039", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "29", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555934400.0} {"text": "a horrible zed🤡", "appid": "1250", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042675286", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485172800.0} {"text": "под насваем класс", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198434695920", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574337600.0} {"text": "nice game", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198275295745", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472731200.0} {"text": "Cute", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263675625", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "A truly gripping story with beautiful narrative. All RPG elements are played to their greatest strengths and the gameplay is exciting, but equally gripping. The moment of shock when you realise you can't takedown that patrolling enemy, then you realise that you can also sneak past them through a hidden shortcut. This game truly keeps strong to the style of Deus Ex AND I WANT A SEQUEL. YOU HEAR ME?", "appid": "238010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011447457", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1417176000.0} {"text": "Chceli ste niekedy navštíviť divoký západ ? Áno ? Tak to si musíte vypočuť príbeh starého bounty huntera, Silasa Greavesa ktorý si prišiel vyrozprávať do \"saloon\"(u) svoje životné highlighty a posťažovať sa na to, že moderná doba už nieje preňho. V hre je niekoľko coltov, brokovníc a pušiek a s každou zbraňou sa inak strieľa. Proti vám budú nabehovať pištoľníci, apači a aj rôzny bossovia. A práve bossfighty sú úplne perfektné. Odohrávajú sa ako pravé 1v1 tasenie zbraní. Kým netasíte, musíte sa starať o vašu presnosť a rýchlost čož dá zabrať hlavne pri vyšších obtiažnostiach. Napríklad na obtiažnosti True west nemáte crosshair a odporúčam si to prejsť každému. Príbehy ktoré Silas rozpráva sa stále nachádzajú na výborných lokáciach. A ako to niekedy býva niekto ten príbeh počul inak alebo si ho už presne napamätá. To znamená že sa cesta tvorí rovno pred vami. +gameplay +grafika +príbeh +lokácie +zbrane +boss fighty -dľa mňa mohla byť obtiažnosť \"true west\" ťažšia 8/10", "appid": "204450", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093090028", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480248000.0} {"text": "Super gierka!", "appid": "420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198292466608", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586001600.0} {"text": "👌", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198043281959", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1497528000.0} {"text": "A fantastic game can have funny scenarios with your friends and you are able to show your tactical prowess with the long game plays. Fantastic game.", "appid": "8930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168910948", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496836800.0} {"text": "The most fun game you can play :) Sniping is love, sniping is life", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077340302", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1411473600.0} {"text": "The best indie game I've ever played!!!", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198037313111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "PLAYISMでプレイ済み。steamで配信されたのでレビュー。 進化を続ける廃校監禁ホラーアドベンチャー・コープスパーティーシリーズに時間軸を進めた完全新作が登場！ コンシューマで制作が続けられている\"天神小編\"最新作と並行して進む、数年先のストーリーが語られる！システムは3D探索エンジンを採用、前作を上回るゲーム性が付与され、一層没入感のある廃墟探索の恐ろしさを体験するゲームですね。 チームグリグリに加え、システム構築にオガワコウサク、キャラクターグラフィックに神城咲弥、BGMに濱本麻央、そして、脚本・演出に祁答院慎。と豪華な陣営で、内容、ゲームシステムも安定していますのでご安心を。 本作はchapter1とEXchapterが収録されています。 しかしそこに問題点が、、、、それは本作のchapter1が配信されたのは2013年！！6年前！！ それからchapter2は配信されていません。chapter1は序盤の序盤なので完結にはあと何十年もかかるんでしょうか？ その点を踏まえて我慢できる方は、安価なので購入してみてはいかかですか？ ※本製品はPLAYISMで配信中のキャラクターやシナリオなどが追加された『コープスパーティー2 DEAD PATIENT NEUES;』と同一です。", "appid": "940310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198276208241", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571918400.0} {"text": "fasza", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198984276788", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588334400.0} {"text": "Gran bel gioco, peccato che gli sviluppatori abbiano deciso di spegnere i server...", "appid": "461910", "steamid": "profiles/76561197994361730", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "this game is highly amazing I recommend it to anyone who likes Infantry based tactics and good combat as well as Squad developing and leveling and teamwork and its very tactical 10/10 would get my whole squad blown up by a grenade again", "appid": "495580", "steamid": "profiles/76561198170889659", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1503489600.0} {"text": "What Are Lua Errors? A Lua error is caused when the code that is being ran is improper. There are many reasons for why a Lua error might occur, but understanding what a Lua error is and how to read it is an important skill that any developer needs to have. Effects of Errors on Your Scripts An error will halt your script's execution when it happens. That means that when an error is thrown, some elements of your script might break entirely. For example, if your gamemode has a syntax error which prevents init.lua from executing, your entire gamemode will break. Lua Error Format The first line of the Lua error contains 3 important pieces of information: The path to the file that is causing the error The line that is causing the error The error itself Here is an example of a code that will cause a Lua error: local text = \"Hello World\" Print( text ) The code will produce the following error: [ERROR]addons/my_addon/lua/autorun/server/sv_my_addon_autorun.lua:2: attempt to call global 'Print' ( a nil value ) 1. unknown - addons/my_addon/lua/autorun/server/sv_my_addon_autorun.lua:2 That is because Print is not an existing function (print, however, does exist). The first line includes the path to the file that is causing the error - addons/my_addon/lua/autorun/server/sv_my_addon_autorun.lua Afterwards, the line that's producing the error - sv_my_addon_autorun.lua:2 (Line 2) Lastly, the error itself - attempt to call global 'Print' (a nil value) Below the error, we have the trace of the function. Simplified - If the error is inside a function/chunk of code that is called from somewhere else, it will state where the code is called from. If the error happens serverside, the text color will be blue. If it happened clientside, it will be yellow. If it's menu code, it will be green (not a typical scenario). Messages which look like errors but are colored differently, such as red or white, are not Lua errors but rather engine errors. Printing Your Own If you want to print your own error messages, there are three functions to do it: error will print your message, halt execution, and print the stack. Normal error behavior. ErrorNoHalt will print the file/line number and your message without halting the script. Useful for warning messages. assert will check to make sure that something is true. If it's not, it will print your message and halt just like error does. Common Errors Attempt to call global '?' a nil value Description: You tried to call a function that doesn't exist. Possible causes: Your function might be defined in another Lua state. (e.g Calling a function on the client that only exists on the * server.) You're using a metafunction on the wrong kind of object. (e.g. Calling :SteamID() on a Vector) The function you're calling has an error in it which means it is not defined. You've misspelled the name of the function. Ways to fix: Make sure the function exists Make sure your function is defined in the correct realm Check your function calls for spelling errors Attempt to perform arithmetic on global '?' (a nil value) Description: You tried to perform arithmetic (+, -, *, /) on a global variable that is not defined. Possible causes: You tried to use a local variable that was defined later in the code You've misspelled the name of the global variable Ways to fix: Make sure you define local variables before calling them in the code Check for spelling errors Attempt to perform arithmetic on '?' (a type value) Description: You tried to perform arithmetic (+, -, *, /) on a variable that cannot perform arithmetic. (e.g. 2 + \"some string\") Attempt to index global 'varname' (a nil value) Description: You tried to index an undefined variable (e.g. print( variable.index ) where variable is undefined) Possible causes: The variable is defined in a different realm The variable is local and defined later in the code You've misspelled the name of the variable Ways to fix: Make sure the variable is only accessed in the realm it was defined in If the variable is local, define it before accessing it Malformed number near 'number' Description: There is a malformed number in the code (e.g. 1.2.3, 2f) Possible causes: An IP address was written as a number instead of a string Incorrect writing of multiplication of a number and a variable Trying to concatenate a number to a string without a space between the number and the operator. Ways to fix: Store IP addresses as a string Multiply variables with numbers by using the * operator Put a space between the concat (..) operator and the number. Unexpected symbol near 'symbol' Description: You typed a symbol in the code that Lua didn't know how to interpret. Possible causes: Incorrect syntax (e.g. Forgot to write \"then\" after an if statement) Not closing brackets and parentheses at the correct locations Ways to fix: Make sure there are no mistypes in the code Close brackets and parentheses correctly (See: Code Indentation) 'symbol1' expected near 'symbol2' Description: Lua expected symbol1 instead of symbol2. When 'symbol2' is , Lua expected a symbol before the end of the file Possible causes: Not closing all brackets and parentheses before the end of the file Wrong operator calling (e.g. \"==\" instead of \"=\") Missing comma after table item. Ways to Fix Close brackets and parentheses correctly (See: Code Indentation) Use the correct operators Add a comma after a table item", "appid": "4000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042984428", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1405684800.0} {"text": "From the same company that brought us Pac Man. This short but bittersweet horror platformer is as creepy as it is beautiful. The concept is brilliant, and once completed made me crave part 2. A solid 9 out of 10", "appid": "424840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198180633494", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493726400.0} {"text": "Hi Freunde! Kurz und schmerzlos. Eines der besten PvP und Koop Spiele die ich getestet habe ! Im Einzelspielermodus kann man sehr gut Hubschrauber testen ehe man sich unters Volk mischt ! Für jeden anpassbare schwierigkeiten ! Hubschrauber schaltet man nur im PvP oder Koop Modus frei weil man im Kampanienmodus unter Anleitung der Basis agiert ! Fliegen ist mit Tastatur sehr gut möglich,hab es mit dem Extreme 30 Pro Joystick getestet ,ist aber umständlich und unter Umständen kompliziert einzurichten, also zurück zur Tastatur ! PvP und Koop macht mächtig viel Spass ich bin nicht mal traurig wenn ich abgeschossen werde weil man mit drei Hubschraubern in die Schlacht zieht und man sich auf den nächsten freut. Schlachten gehen für die Einsteiger 1ne Stunde..gut zu händeln! Grafik und Gameplay sehr gut ....Skala 1-10...ist die Grafik ungefähr zwischen 7 und 8 und das Gameplay 9. Ich glaube aber da kommt noch was in Sachen Patches. Alles in allem gut gelungen...habe gerade gelesen..im ,,Anflug'' ist noch einiges mehr...ach an Hubschraubern !", "appid": "433530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053950473", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514721600.0} {"text": "Virar um traficante roubador de bancos nao tem nada melhor heimmmmmmmm FICAR CHAPAD111111111 TENEBROSO", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198099057777", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "Talks like Duke Nukem in his 3D Reminds me games like Blood, Hexen, Heretic ... Secret places like in Wolfenstein 3D If you like all games above you should try this game!", "appid": "893680", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992016121", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584273600.0} {"text": "Никогда не начинайте играть в нее(нет)", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074830273", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387540800.0} {"text": "Короче прошёл я это д*рьмо бл*ть.Игра конечно шедевр,НО,играл я в стандартной броньке,зелья почти не варил,но мечи хоть крутые были,почему эта игра г*вно ? на боссов я тратил где-то попыток 20-30, но это я ещё мог пережить (спасибо Dark Souls за это) но ещё что просто выбило под стол это ОТРАЖЕНИЕ УДАРА,ВЕЗДЕ И ВСЕГДА ОТРАЖЕНИЕ УДАРА,ПРОСТО НЕВОЗМОЖНО ДРАТЬСЯ С МУТАНТАМИ КОГДА Я ОДИН РАЗ УДАРИЛ ОНИ МЕНЯ УЖЕ МЕНЯ ПО 2 КРУГУ НАЧАЛИ кхм,но что хуже всего это-то что Геральт после отражение удара,просто удара,оглушения стоит как д*ун, как я победил Азара (вроде так его зовут) я вобще молчу, у этой игры главная фичя это \"Нету добра и зла\" серьёзно? ребят хотите расскажу тайну? наш мир ещё жёстче будет, ведь нету ведьмаков которые помогут в плохое время,но я продолжал быть дерзким ( Хотя шайка яевина в банке меня просто пых пых делала ) , но из-за крутых поротов сюжета,за мир представленый злым и не дружелюбным,трагичная сюдьба ведьмаков и эротические карточки >:) , я ставлю игре пале верх,она это заслужила пойду проходить вторую часть надеюсь мои нервы выдержут ещё порции хардкора,всем пока все свободны!", "appid": "20900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198200107515", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502798400.0} {"text": "This is so much fun with friends.", "appid": "376210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201146121", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1594296000.0} {"text": "It's a great game. Running on a 1050ti, FX 8350 and 8GB of RAM, I can run it with a smooth 60FPS with settings between Medium-Very High. No stuttering and the game loads in fine with an SSD. A few months ago I would not have been able to say the same thing as there used to be a horrid FPS, the game would not load textures in properly and it would just be a bad experience in general. Cheaters? I have seen some cheaters, but really it's not as bad as people make it out to be. About 1 in 30 matches I encounter a cheater (if I made it into the top 5 more often that number may have been different) The new map was also an amazing addition to the game and, for me at least, increased my game's performance a lot. Loot crates are in the game and they are not at all worth opening, but I have made some quick money by selling the crates themselves on the community market. Overall, it's a great game in its best state ever since launch (in my opinion). Worth buying now or getting back into it if you quit because of the many issues the game used to suffer from.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198140831696", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532520000.0} {"text": "I ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ HATE THIS GAME PLAYED 5 HOURS AND FORGOT TO TAKE THE WOOD OUT OF THE FIREPLACE TO KILL THE TWIN VLADIMIR VAMPIRE AND NOW I HAVE TO START FROM BEGINING WELL ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ STUPID GAME but whatever.. the game is high quality entertainment (he he ) 10/10 would forget wood again", "appid": "396790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198131951554", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "9", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1447675200.0} {"text": "Very fun", "appid": "686810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035516164", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1581854400.0} {"text": "The best game that was ever made, still going like a mad man.", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072767701", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511352000.0} {"text": "Fun game", "appid": "204360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255286672", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458907200.0} {"text": "XD", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163503489", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "Amazing game with great story and fun gameplay, the characters are really nice and the graphics are beautiful too. The character customization could be way better (i guess they know that and thats why they charge so much for skins DLC). The game itselft it's not challenging at all, you probably won't have trouble with any battle (even at the highest diffficulty) but its fun anyway.", "appid": "429660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080965953", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600344000.0} {"text": "8 из 10", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198184442925", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "legen wait for it =)))) . . . . . daaaaaaaaaaaaary", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198384108696", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606305600.0} {"text": "This game is a easy game to dive into and play for an hour. Smash TV + Gauntlet with a cool retro soundtrack. It's difficult enough to keep me wanting more, and easy enough for me to in progress far enough where I feel like I'm improving and getting further with each and every attempt. I've heard people say that it's too short. I don't think its short at all, I keep playing more and more trying to garner enough coins to purchase upgrades for the next time I play. This game definitely has that \"one more try\" kinda feel. Only knock I have is that windowed mode doesn't work for me but not a huge deal. I've enjoyed this game quite a bit and I'd definitely recommend it.", "appid": "306700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053359938", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1417176000.0} {"text": "Dost triviální, ale skvělá oddychovka, spíše pouze pro fanoušky, hra vás nechá projít prakticky většinou zásadních soubojů, které se odehráli za dob Narutova dětství, nicméně nijak nezachází do podrobností, takže kdo nezná kontext soubojů z předlohy, tak ten si je tak neužije, pro ostatní se bude jednat o ohromnou nostalgii, free run vesnicí už je jen takovou třešničkou na dortu. :) P.S. Hodně lidí si stěžuje na optimalizaci, nicméně já jsem takové problémy nepocítil, takže v tomto ohledu bohužel nemůžu soudit, možná bych také jinak hodnotil negativně, nicméně v mém případě pro cílovku určitě doporučuji.", "appid": "495140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198024242217", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506513600.0} {"text": "Матюки, убийства и 100% рандом!", "appid": "282800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198256630757", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558785600.0} {"text": "Bestes Spiel", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561199069277608", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596888000.0} {"text": "Oyun Bence gayet iyi .d", "appid": "1101140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198322011637", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572782400.0} {"text": "Best Arena based game out there, very uniqe way of playing but for the better! worth much more than it costs", "appid": "504370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074219447", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1480766400.0} {"text": "One of the best simulator games ever.", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198144489168", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1427544000.0} {"text": "CS GO Super Game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198136009579", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454846400.0} {"text": "Nunca había odiado tanto a mis amigos desde el Mario Party :D", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038236094", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599480000.0} {"text": "(-_-) Моя Оценка: 10 из 10", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198109840842", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1412510400.0} {"text": "oui", "appid": "813820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198434312089", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Najlepsza część i od groma DLC Polecam", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062368570", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Jogo muito bom... Um estilo bem diferente para quem, como eu, curte jogos de FPS e guerra. Mas é sensacional a busca pelo animal. Testa os sentidos da gente. Vale muito a pena jogar este jogo!!!!", "appid": "253710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198014225011", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588593600.0} {"text": "На часов 15 вполне хватит", "appid": "555440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117719597", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "haha heavy gun go brr", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198330917111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585051200.0} {"text": "Amazing game! 9,5/10 A fresh and an essential take on the old good Tomb Raider franchise. This game definitely guarantees that you will have the best Tomb Raider experience up to now. The game has so many features and implementations that make you feel like: \"Wow, this feels so natural, why wasn't this implemented before anyway?\" Taking Tomb Raider out of her \"sexualized objectification\" and giving her character a meaning is something this game has accomplished very well. So, our new fresh main character, Lara Croft is no longer just an Indiana Jones-with boobs, and this is how everyone should see her. Whether you are an old Tomb Raider fan, who wants to see more of Lara Croft or just a newcomer who has finally decided to meet Lara Croft (actually that's even better) this game is just for you! Btw. I like how it is called just Tomb Raider, and it deserves that name because they have really re-created the Tomb Raider and Lara Croft! Thanks Square Enix and Crystal Dynamics for this amazing game! Ok here is my review of Tomb Raider: Graphics 10/10 This games graphics look amazing! I have played it on maxed settings with TressFx on and everything looks just beautiful. The details of the environment and the atmosphere are stunning and it is very immersive. When you are hiding from enemies in the forest you really feel like you are in a forest. There really isn't much to say. Also dynamic hair is evolutionary! Sound 8/10 The sound effects were nicely done and the music was wonderful, maybe the ambient sounds could be worked on as I thought that the atmosphere of being in a forest lacked a little bit but that is very personal. Also why didn't they put subtitles without hearing impaired captions? I prefer having subtitles but with this game I had to turn them off. Story 9/10 Normally I never felt like the story was good in Tomb Raider games but this time it is really good. At first I thought it was a cliche; ship crashes, enemies on the island try to kill you and your friends but the game has pulled it off very well and the story was interesting, logical and thrilling. Characters were good. But what I found lacking was the given information about the characters in the game. And also because you don't really spend much time with any of your friends, it's hard to connect with any of them emotionally. The same goes for the enemies as well. Although it might be seen as you know only the things you see/find about them during the game; for me at least it wasn't enough. Gameplay 10/10 Gameplay is really where this game shines. Everything is so smooth and fun to play with. Gunplay is great, jumping around looks and feels great, finding your way on the island right after you have escaped from your enemies is great, animations are amazing; in short everything is great! At this point I want to point out a few features I loved about the game: - Animations: Animations in the game look just amazing! Whether you are exploring the island or shooting your enemies in a fight, they look great! Also, going through little cracks or auto-crouching animation or the way Lara holds the torch, they are all beautifully executed. - Weapon Upgrade System: You no longer find your new weapons somewhere in your Mansion or hidden in the world waiting for you. You upgrade your own weapons by finding \"salvage parts\" through out the island either by finding crates or by looting enemies. You also have skills that you can progress after gaining skill points. Both systems are working very well and you never really feel like you have to grind for your next weapon. It just plays out very natural. - Books: Books or diaries you find in the game are giving a lot of information both about the story and the characters. They help you to have a connection to the story and the characters. The extra beauty of them is that you don't have to read them or even find them, they are just optional; though I really recommend reading them as they enhance the story and the lore. - Relics: Relics are well relics scattered around the island that you can find. You can then see information about them and you can find small hidden clues on the relics that helps Lara to figure out more information about the relic, that's really interesting and fun. I wish more relics had those hidden clues. Additionally the information about the relics do not feel like a wikipedia article, instead they are short and interesting and you feel like Lara has just found a relic. - Tombs: Ironically this game has one of the best implementations of tombs in a Tomb Raider game. They are hidden and awating for you to explore them. After solving little puzzles, you find treasures and earn experience points. They are good breaks from the action-pace of the game while giving you some puzzles to solve and calm down :) - Immersion: This game is the most immersive and lore-friendly game I have played ever! All the implementations, characters and the story stay true to that! - Continue playing after it ends: Yes, I hate it when an amazing game is over and it doesn't let you continue playing the game with your developed character. This game lets you do that! Furthermore most of the areas are also clear from enemies which let you explore the island freely without a worry! Also I highly recommend going back to those places to see how beautiful all the environments are. - Lara Croft: Yes, Lara Croft. The modelling, animations and the voice acting are superb! And the fact that she has 'a soul' so to speak makes it all amazing! Also smaller boobs make her look more normal, natural and more beautiful, - in my opinion they could be even smaller ;) What I wish there was but there wasn't: - More time with friendly characters: You just play most of the time alone. I understand that it was meant to be that way but I wish there were times when you could at least see Lara Croft playing with other characters. - More hunting: I just wish the game had an optional hardcore survival mode that made you drink water, hunt animals for food etc. Afterall this was a survival game, right? - Romance? Overall 9,5/10 The game is amazing, period.", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044640686", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1386417600.0} {"text": "Najlepsza gra w historii", "appid": "639790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198354957664", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511870400.0} {"text": "fun", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198346646702", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603800000.0} {"text": "Наиграл я в эту замечательную игру считай 100 часов. Игра замечательная но многие её боятся якобы из-за её \"сложности\" по часте экономики. А так игра достаточно лёгкая играть в неё приятно хоть она и старая чего-нибудь подобного на рынке нету есть только жалкие подобия. Советую всем купить поиграйте насладитесь одной из лучших стратегий старого времени.", "appid": "282400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095664397", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1461153600.0} {"text": "Great platformer game, didnt play any mario platformer but my childhood was full of spyro and crash bandicoot and i just melted on this game, the music is also a big plus.", "appid": "253230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198059176600", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "coop d