, "tstamp_created": 1606305600.0} {"text": "Love it! Got my virginity card back and now I'm ready to waste away playing with virtual cards😎😎😎😎😎", "appid": "480650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198258643994", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581249600.0} {"text": "comi a loirinha e a irmã dela", "appid": "413150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198341217364", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "21", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605355200.0} {"text": "worst game i've ever seen <3", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048246113", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "Bought this game quite some time ago and had not even tried it out. Now I am hooked to daily playing it trying to fish up the achievements! Lots of fun, blood, burning and melee to keep you going for hours and the music is an extra bonus. I would suggest this game to anyone who enjoyed the Left 4 Dead franchise. Oh, I would suggest getting the community gun packs [cheaper online] as they have some really cool guns. Flair gun being one of the best to snag.", "appid": "1250", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998324734", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517313600.0} {"text": "---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- I once met a dude with a russian name fapping to hentai while playing Dm who had a totally kawaii overloaded profile. But than he started speaking and it turned out he was 8 years old. After 3 rounds his parents came in and started shouting. He left. #neverforget Also there are many friendly Slavs just waiting to shout cyka blyat when you're not rushing B with them. ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Overall it's a 8/10 because operations aren't