have. This game is literally a masterpiece, introducing art into the Videogames' world. This game is stunning and it has wonderful graphics. This makes you addicted to the game, losing your mind somewhere in The Blind Forest. Besides, you're not only going to explore \"the ground\". You'll have adventures in the underground or even in the sky, finding different creatures and enjoying lovely landscapes. : The story is going to last a couple of hours, being full of secrets that can hardly be discovered. Finding all secrets can be a little challenging because On the other hand, this is a great way to get used with the game for a higher difficulty. As the story goes by, Ori will find new abilities allowing the player to access previously inaccessible areas. Ori and The Blind Forest have an autosave feature BUT you can save your game by simply creating Soul Links with Energy Cells. Ori can gain Ability Points to buy various upgrades, such as increasing the damage of the spirit flame. is literally making you curious of what is going to happen. Also, the story is based mostly on nature-elements which are going to bring The Blind Forest back to life. You're going to explore special \"worlds\" which are hidden (at the beginning) on the map. The accent doesn't stand only on saving the forest. Ori is determined to leave because of its \"mother's\" death, Naru. A great thing is that Ori has a little partener (Sein) which is going to be there for him all the time. Another important thing is the soundtrack. The music literally fits every part of the story, making it even more heart-touching and makes the player to be even more focused on the gameplay. :", "appid": "387290", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119475498", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498910400.0} {"text": ":]", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198830257076", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595073600.0} {"text": "its okay i would say", "appid": "530700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198351653324", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511870400.0} {"text": "SOTTR: вы ищите хороший экшен-адвенчюрер, исследование и хорошую картинку, стелс и особую атмосферу с полуголыми индейцами? Их есть у меня! Из плюсов отмечу... да какие +/-? Я просто хочу поставить игре лайк:) это все так субъективно, например, жутко не нравится неудобный интерфейс карты и заданий. Но это не значит, что он плохой) Видя обычную палку, один скажет - плохое оружие, другой - классные дрова)) Это я к тому, что лучше вы ознакомьтесь-ка с игрой сами и получите свои собственные впечатления. Эта игра достойная внимания! Относительно моей любимой части серии ROTTR у Лары появились новые скилы, стало больше гробниц (с учетом dlc) и по впечатлению больше мир для исследования) Так же новые скилы, гробницы, одежку и новые вызовы добавляют в игру в т.ч. и неплохие dlc к игре В общем, вроде бы, всего стало больше, но не смотря на всё это игра все же, на мой взгляд, не смогла перепрыгнуть высокую планку поднятую ROTTR...", "appid": "750920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198261194104", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593777600.0} {"text": "Güzel bir yarış oyunu", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198433531692", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581854400.0} {"text": "Интересная игра", "appid": "1081510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068224236", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574769600.0} {"text": "Mein Fazit nachg über 50 Std Postiv: Eigene Char Erstellung Ne ganz andere Story Guter Schwierigkeits Grad Viele Spezial Attacken Viele Ausrüstung Netter Meisterschule(sag ich mal so) Viele Quest,auch Online machbar. Dauert bis man lv 80 ist Negativ: Zu viele abbrüche bei den Servern Zu wenig Charaktere (z.zt nur ca 47 ) Sehr Dumme KI bei kampf mitgliedern Zu wenig abwechslung bei den Quests Sehr komisches Loot System. LV Cap 80 (vllt wirds erhöht) Im Groben und ganzen das Beste DBZ Game aller Zeiten Leider wurden bis dato nur 3 dlc's angekündigt ..was leider schade wäre wenn dies so bleibt man kann mehr rausholen bei dem Game", "appid": "323470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198002022808", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1425556800.0} {"text": "buy.", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198028230943", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562155200.0} {"text": "Powróciłem 2 miesiące temu po ponad 8 miesiącach przerwy. Ta gra zawsze będzie się nudzić, a ja i tak do niej wracam po dłuższym czasie mając 100% radochy jak kiedyś. Cóż, czekam na kolejny bundle.", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198153797236", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1469275200.0} {"text": "nice game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196949341", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575806400.0} {"text": "Relax To Play", "appid": "562220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198334313564", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481976000.0} {"text": "Eight hours straight directly when I came home from work. This is a gem of a game allready in EA and I can't even start about how I look forward to play this as it grows both in content and quality. Runs amazingly good and loading times are not bad at least on my computer", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198023130923", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1585569600.0} {"text": "Imagine CIV5, but constant combat, less about the city building and tech advancing, more about the straight up combat", "appid": "489630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198027714922", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605528000.0} {"text": "Experience a game unlike anything else. This unique masterpiece is a perfect fit for people enjoying sarcastical and controversial views on (American) society. The story is about daily errands tasked by your \"lovely\" wife and the gameplay only gets as violent as you let to provoke yourself. You can finish the game with zero kills or nuke the whole town to Hell while pissing (!) on people until they puke. xD It's really not a game for fun killers taking it seriously and that's why it gets every rating from 0% to 100%. Even the developers are mucking about themselves by putting their studio ingame and using the restroom as an office. :D The \"missions\" have a great variety, from trivial stuff like getting milk from the supermarket or bringing back a book to the library up to pissing on your Dad's grave and running around with a Gimp Suit downtown. Other activities include visiting a Taliban terror camp or Uncle Dave's drug farm. Apart from the story you can also just run around and enjoy exploring the town like a free-roam sandbox game. The game was orginal released back in 2003 but thanks to Greenlight got a second spring on Steam, a new add-on called \"Lost Paradise\" and still (!!) receives regular updates from the developers - after more than 15 years. It's a true Labour of Love; it's proudly banned in Australia, New Zealand and Malaysia; it's funny and totally insane; it uses cats as silencer and counts the number of kicked in doors; it has 69 achievements (the number is NOT a coincidence, you get it, right?) and even featured in Black Eyed Peas \"Where's the Love?\" music video. As you can see the impact of this game is as unique as itself and worth a try!", "appid": "223470", "steamid": "profiles/76561197968240913", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "Польща може в Космос!! Я СДЕЛАЛ ЭТО))))))))", "appid": "512033", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993962137", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "14", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538395200.0} {"text": "Memes... It's just nature going it's own way.", "appid": "235460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110793727", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Sehr gutes Spiel am anfang kaum erfolgserlebnisse aber wenn man sich reingefunden hat macht es mega Spaß :) Edit: Stand 2016 und es ist immernoch extrem geil! :)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105130828", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434801600.0} {"text": "𝘎𝘳𝘦𝘢𝘵 𝘨𝘢𝘮𝘦", "appid": "960090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198449852486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578398400.0} {"text": "very good", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087658963", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1417780800.0} {"text": "What a bunch of entitled crybabies. Bad korean translation? So what? Is your \"thumbs down\" justified? Of course not. It's like not getting a PHD because you made a couple spelling mistakes. I am ashamed that this game had such a toxic korean fanbase. Not only koreans jumped on this bangwagon. This game is one of the best I've played IN YEARS, and many of you say the same. So why the thumbs down? You want developers to change translation by lowering rating below 50% DURING A SUMMBER SALE? This is one of the biggest opportunities for them to earn money to continue development! And their game is no longer being recomended because of its rating! You can ignore them, you can boycott them, but changing your review like that is such a bowel movement I would totally spit in your face if I met you in person.", "appid": "262060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013137662", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530014400.0} {"text": "สนุกมากกกก ยิ่งเล่นกับเพื่อนยิ่งสนุกกก หลอนดี เสียไปอย่างเกมนี้รอดยากก แลคค และ จอยลำบากมาก;w;", "appid": "251170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117148944", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496404800.0} {"text": "- 24 hours I don't know how to start. This game and 'Just Cause 3' were my very first steam purchases. This reminds me some nostalgic memories😍. I don't know why I underestimated this game. Whatever, THIEF (2014) is the reboot of the classic 'Thief' series. The game is set in 'The City', a dark fantasy world inspired by Victorian, Gothic, and steampunk aesthetics. You control Garrett, a master thief who has exceptional thieving skills...Ok let's get to the PROS and CONS>> - - I cannot remember another. If I find, I will add here. - Story - 7/10 Gameplay - 8/10 Level Design - 9-10 Overall - 8/10 Most of my friends have this their library..But if you don't have, buy this during a sale... Thanks for reading....Some information is collected from wikipedia", "appid": "239160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198394232524", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558353600.0} {"text": "After finished the mission solo, I must say, It's one of those cool missions on the series, There were several shortcut paths that I said to myself \"man, wish I had a chem kit\" while I chose to carried a wire cutter. Some of the shortcuts are really resourceful in this one. The map design is also remarkable, the lighting is great in many dark and dim areas. The fact that the area of the mission takes place in the nearby area of Hell or High Water giving you the nostalgic feeling and also making the world more believable. I finished it with heat level full in the first time and It felt like I john wicked the way through the mission (you know... a church and all) All in all a total fun episode to start a second season. It's not too hard to do it alone, and it's not too easy or short to make you feel lacking. I'll have to replay it again and again, cause it's that good!", "appid": "987170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063418879", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543492800.0} {"text": "Even more fun with Left 4 Dead characters. Better get it from sales or you will be left for dead.", "appid": "301640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198000460264", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1462622400.0} {"text": "Game is pretty solid, lots of variety with weapons, warframes, and the builds you put on them. Game is grindy and you can play this game for free and easily find a way to trade and obtain some valuable in game currency.", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042553093", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543233600.0} {"text": "Este juego va a poner tu ansiedad hasta el techo. Un juego de terror que me sorprendió gratamente, esperaba el típico juego indie que te mete el screamer en cuanto puede, el típico juego de terror que no trasmite nada. Y me terminé llevando una buena sorpresa, el sótano de Dios plantea un argumento muy interesante, una reflexión muy curiosa, da mucho que pensar. Y tiene una forma de transmitir terror muy inteligente, para empezar, no es el típico juego en el que tenés que rajar del monstruo, de hecho no podés morir, pero esto no hace que te sientas inmortal... En todo momento te sentís débil. También tengo que agregar que la idea que tiene el sótano de Dios como premisa es bastante interesante y llama la atención nada más empezar a jugar. Lo recomiendo muchísimo si quieren pasar miedo... el sótano de Dios los va a ser sentir muy incómodos.", "appid": "753930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198276140352", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589457600.0} {"text": "gg", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198815434175", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518868800.0} {"text": "I played this game for over 100+ hours and it was pretty fun. I played casual but, then it got boring. So i started playing csgo!", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308490265", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493467200.0} {"text": "Кодла ДАУНОВ! Но я ЛЮБЛЮ эту кодлу ДАУНОВ <3 <3 <3", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150056766", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574424000.0} {"text": "Anlatmaya gerek yok :D", "appid": "48700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134298727", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1559649600.0} {"text": "No Me Esperaba Para Nada Esto ._.", "appid": "698780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198248633414", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519646400.0} {"text": "Maneiro.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198061267453", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "Лучшее во что я мог бы играть в 2017 году", "appid": "238460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198200586946", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574510400.0} {"text": "Surpreendentemente maravilhoso. Este jogo é daqueles que você não quer que acabe de tão legal que é. A inteiração entre os personagens é impecável. Um enredo misterioso, com muitas reviravoltas, jogabilidade muito boa. Sistema de combate muito bem elaborado. Olha se falar mais estraga. Vale muito a pena ter este jogo em sua biblioteca. Recomendadíssimo. 10/10.", "appid": "752590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045150435", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "24", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574510400.0} {"text": "Ce jeu est une ode au voyage, entre rêves fantasmés et cruelle réalité. La direction artistique enchanteresse et la bande originale enivrante vous accompagneront dans un périple dont le dénouement ne pourra vous laisser indifférent. Avis à ceux voulant s'évader, sans prise de tête.", "appid": "493200", "steamid": "profiles/76561197969762126", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543147200.0} {"text": "Genre defining", "appid": "546560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198017384651", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585656000.0} {"text": "yes.", "appid": "782330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198152907574", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584705600.0} {"text": "TIMES'S TICKING!", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042234823", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1476100800.0} {"text": "Very Nice", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198827800043", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594468800.0} {"text": "tres bon jeux", "appid": "787860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141800895", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546430400.0} {"text": "This game is one of those games where you could sit in your chair all day and not get up up unless it's for food or the bathroom. It's a very entertaining game to keep you going and it can teach how to survive in a way. Not exactly, but bits and peices. Despite the fact that it is VERY laggy, it was worth playing even though it's free. I definetly recommend this game, if you don't mind the lag.", "appid": "346110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198166077508", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1469880000.0} {"text": "I can recommend OutDrive for what it is. An interactive 80s style music demo, featuring a very very easy never-ending driving theme. If you are looking for an actual driving game, this is not it. The music and visuals are awesome for as long as the soundtrack lasts. A good hour and a half. By that time you will have seen the 3 possible routs several times, and you probably want to stop playing. The driving is too easy to be challenging at any point, except fot the very first time, due to \"unexpected\" controller settings.. (which you need to setup every time you play). I don't think I'll play the game again, but for me, the 2 hours I spent driving in this \"Blood Dragon\" laser world with 80s electro-synth-pop in 2017 production quality, was well worth the 50c I paid on sale.", "appid": "441870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135792443", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "30", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509364800.0} {"text": "To be completely honest, this game is really fun and enjoyable, involves mental strategy and manipulation, Requires tons of mental facts between minimal things provided to you, if you think about it, its like the board game Clue mixed with Guess who, but all the characters are real life people, making it that much harder and more challenging, Social Deduction at its finest", "appid": "334230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198267223519", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572696000.0} {"text": "um jogo parecido com o ark convencional mas so que com mais animais e recurcursos", "appid": "593600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134979352", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1546776000.0} {"text": "Plus -Znovu-hratelnost -Náhodně generované -Nenáročné Minus -Z počátku obtížné (budete furt umírat)", "appid": "250900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198028369512", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "I like cats! My cat is called Sofus!", "appid": "219640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198040403959", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387627200.0} {"text": "Outlast is a very cinematic game that definitely includes scares. Outlast does include innapropriate things, but it is all worth it. Outlast makes you think and has puzzles with enemies that you have to sneak by. You do have to sneak a lot as you cannot fight enemies. I loved this game and love playing it. So excited for Outlast 2~!", "appid": "238320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198129300687", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "You can hug zombies with chainsaw", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198821043498", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601812800.0} {"text": "I am really enjoying Deadfall Adventures. First-person viewpoint games give me a headache, and this one does, too, but it's not a twitch-shooting FPS, so it's not that bad. For all the complaints you may read about Deadfall Adventures, I am really enjoying it. Ultimately, this is just a fun game that puts you in the shoes of an Indiana Jones or Lara Croft-like character, though more of an adventurer and less a knowledgeable archaeologist (like Indiana) and less of a bad-ass (like Lara) ... and now that I think about it, more like a Bard (from The Bard's Tale) in that he's a confident, sarcastic guy who just goes with the flow. Lots of exploration and different environments -- check the Guides section for the guide for Collectibles, and you'll see all the places you'll go just from the YouTube video headings. Puzzles are pretty easy (so far), so the focus is on fun and exploration and environment. Fighting is likewise pretty easy, at least on the Normal setting. You don't have to be spot on with your aim. This is good for me because I suck at aiming.", "appid": "231330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052935907", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574510400.0} {"text": "Ayo red actin kinda sus", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087614637", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602936000.0} {"text": "not bad", "appid": "292030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271696720", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509710400.0} {"text": "Bir oyun düşünün; atlıyorsun ve 2 vuruşta adamı öldürüyorsun. Rainbow Six Siege'yi düşünün birde. Taktikleri iyi olanın kazandığı,en çok vuranın değil,en iyi korunanın kazandığı bir oyundur R6. Akıcı oynanış. Aradığınız çoğu özellik bu oyunda.", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198228639752", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490443200.0} {"text": "Quebrei meu controle de tanto combar, muito bom o game, deveria estar na lista do GOTY ano passado", "appid": "601150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198100935500", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581422400.0} {"text": "Решил пройти игру в очередной раз, когда узнал что EA похерила студию создателя этого шедевра. Мне особенно понравилась тем, что помимо классики в виде второй части Чужих напомнила так же фильм \"Сквозь горизонт\". Dead Space это лучший космический хоррор.", "appid": "17470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198210006979", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "23", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509796800.0} {"text": "Buen juego, le faltaria alguna otra amenaza ademas de la falta de oxigeno.", "appid": "361420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075942025", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Игра Легенда!!!", "appid": "22330", "steamid": "profiles/76561197987516569", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1489665600.0} {"text": "pretty ♥♥♥♥ makes you salty", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198285841850", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1510315200.0} {"text": "单次部分收集通关游戏本体与DLC耗时4.7小时，自诩不擅长解谜类恐怖游戏，如果抱着和笔者一样单纯的想体验单周目剧情而不追求收集要素的话，诸位玩家的通关速度应该会更快，总体而言流程偏短，但如果再长一些的话，可能这篇评测都不会存在了，这在后文中会细说。 1.\t场景设计与艺术性 游戏将标题所言Layers的概念贯穿始终，加之大量精致的艺术性和暗示性的元素点缀，层层抽丝剥茧深入画家的记忆，设定的完整度和细致程度是令人惊艳的，如果对美术有研究或者有兴趣，在游戏过程中自行了解名画背后的故事也是别样的体验。正是受这点吸引而购入的笔者对此没什么可以抱怨的，十分满意。 2.\t游戏性 Layers of fear在流程中的互动基本限于三点：开门、开柜子、找东西。缺少操作性的电影式游戏有很多，但私以为Layers of fear最初的本意可能并非如此，虽然相对于游戏中收集道具的数量，可以探索的柜门数量多的可怕，我想如此设定的本质原因大抵是希望玩家多与这座古宅进行交互并增加代入感。然而如果将特定恐怖元素的组合称之为一个模式，在这样一个流程本就不长的游戏里，近乎完全相同的模式不断的出现，让后半段的游戏几乎完全丧失了所谓的恐怖性不谈，笔者也产生了一定的审美疲劳而根本懒得去一个个开箱子，大概是错过了许多细节和彩蛋。除此之外，在几乎没有游戏指引的情况下，让我个人寻找部分剧情道具的过程痛苦不已，特别是在获得最后一件遗物时的房间，至少我没有看到寻找在光线不足的房间里寻找棋子的乐趣和必要性，甚至有些强行延长游戏时间的嫌疑，如果游戏流程再这样复制性增长的话，可能笔者会失去通关的动力。 关于DLC，本质上是以主人公女儿的视角重返古宅，补足了主线剧情缺漏的细节并让男女主角的形象丰满了许多。较之主线，DLC的游戏流程更注重解谜，恐怖性反而较为薄弱，光线虽然依旧昏暗，但关键道具终于学会了闪烁，让发现他们轻松了许多。然而最后女主做出的决定颇有些突兀，加之随后的点题，一种微妙的中学生作文的秩序感油然而生。总而言之，该作DLC是对原作剧情的填补，如果喜欢原作剧情的话建议购入，但总体而言没有满足笔者的期待。 3.\t剧情 本作的剧情其实颇具含金量，叙事方式也很值得玩味，一步一步挖掘出事件背后的真相以及对玩家所操纵角色身份的探究都很让人满意，也正是剧情激励着笔者继续着不那么让我满意的游戏过程，希望购买游戏的玩家不要为了追求刺激而忽略了这一点。 4.\t总结 亮点：令人惊叹的美术水准，相当漂亮的场景和画面，看起来很厉害的故事，较为完整的设定。 缺点：首次通关可能根本无法了解其实可圈可点的剧情，重复度较高的模式，十分无趣的找东西环节，部分场景太特么黑了连灯都难找。 推荐给：喜欢精致富有匠心作品的玩家，对剧情有要求的玩家，想尝试恐怖游戏但不敢尝试的玩家，对该作美术设计有兴趣的玩家。 不推荐给：解谜爱好者，核心向恐怖游戏玩家，对流程长度有要求的玩家，和笔者一样不擅长找东西的小龙虾们。", "appid": "391720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168796916", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "35", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479124800.0} {"text": "govno redkoe", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198124225471", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1423828800.0} {"text": "1. Spawn on beach 2. Die to ak kids screaming at you 3. Spawn again 4. Grind for a nice base 5. Get more loot 6. Log off with some nice loot 7. Log on next day being raided 10/10 I would play this game again Rust trailer:", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198319492303", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544616000.0} {"text": "喏递钞票_(:зゝ∠)_ 给我奶子谢谢(๑˙ー˙๑)", "appid": "711990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198383929305", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521028800.0} {"text": "Punai Punaiiiiiiiiiiiiii", "appid": "774171", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075042549", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594814400.0} {"text": "Sehr schön anzusehen und brutal. Man merkt es steckt eine Menge Arbeit dahinter. Ich bin begeistert. 11/10", "appid": "351570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198019575123", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1427025600.0} {"text": "Good game to play with Friends Laughing so hard while playing this game and now im arrested", "appid": "285900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189895407", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1547121600.0} {"text": "fps version of 'god of war'. lol", "appid": "379720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198241513206", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501243200.0} {"text": "Simulador 