ile. But they don't want to live like their mothers. They don't want fear to rule their lives. They don't want to live like their fathers, who worked so hard that they broke down. They don't want to give up while they are alive. They will never accept the shackles they try to put on. All they have is themselves. They have always been together and always will be. Someday they will create their own paradise.", "appid": "554620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198112895265", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602504000.0} {"text": "Крутая!", "appid": "368230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198233771612", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1513684800.0} {"text": "gud gaem but FPS: 10", "appid": "755790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201328702", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Daha iyisi gelene kadar en iyisi bu !!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198186400991", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "23", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1463313600.0} {"text": "\"Paladins\"-игра, которая вызывает кучу споров и горение пукичей фанатов \"Blizzard\", но тем не менее несущаяся с горы, будто снежный ком, наращивая темп и своё комьюнити.", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198104919873", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1495281600.0} {"text": "Games featured: Get chips every day:", "appid": "436150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263092255", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1570708800.0} {"text": "+++ Besser als Pubg, keine Lags, leichtes Spraycontroll, bessere Funktionen (3 Waffen, automatisches Anlegen von Equip), interessante Fortbewegungsmöglichkeiten +++ - zu wenige Maps aktiv", "appid": "755790", "steamid": "profiles