ho have been here since '14 are still commenting, people seem to like it. Feel free to correct me if I'm wrong.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198323102405", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "19", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539864000.0} {"text": "Игра супер советую поиграть!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049445881", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1408363200.0} {"text": "Keşke devamı gelse.", "appid": "330840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198181681013", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595332800.0} {"text": "It's..... okay I guess", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198194070477", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Oka these game is one of those Isometric turnbased CRPGs which is new comer friendly. Also this isn't final game devs gona make these game more polished and better because they are those few devs who communicate with their consumers and try to make their game better by taking feedback seriously. pros: 1. Beautiful graphics 2. World is small but beautiful 3. I have enjoyed the combat ,they are indie devs I didn't expect Divinity Original sins type awesome and engaging combat 4. Also got some achievements for a demo is also really good. 5. Sounds are nice ,I loved it. 6. But most important thing is that game is so much addicting ,I can't stop playing I want more of these game. 7. Decent story 8. The whole game gave me perfectly balanced challenge except the final boss Guardian one who one shoted my party, which feels unbalanced because I hot 1 level 9 and three level 8 companion .But I have managed to defeat him but it was brutally tough so manay deaths I have to face ,I hope they will fix that. Cons: 1. When you equip the Armors the companion physical appearance doesn't change which l