"votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591272000.0} {"text": "准确地说，这不是一款——最起码不是一款你所认知的“刺客信条”，装备、技能、游戏细节、AI智力都和大大弱化了“刺客”体验，但是就是打着很爽啊，玩着很带感啊，没别的啊，就是好玩啊!", "appid": "812140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042277599", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543233600.0} {"text": "Хоть фон и черный, но сюжет офигенный) Спасибо!", "appid": "48000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198267596499", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1467374400.0} {"text": "awesome", "appid": "11280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198097742086", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515758400.0} {"text": "立直！ 融（qu)了！！！", "appid": "1329410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198364590099", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595332800.0} {"text": "Отличный стимулятор творческого потенциала. После 0,1 часа потянуло писать хайку (не аниме-тёлка). Первый опыт, не судите строго: P.S. Разработчики! Сделайте поддержку геймпада Xbox 360. Куплю ещё пять игр серии.", "appid": "666940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198214779185", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1537358400.0} {"text": "游戏性很一般，但是从视觉和听觉上可以称得上良心，刚入手的时候没有中文，有点艰涩，正当我准备好字典开啃了，中文已出（聊胜于无），三下五除二通关，但是已经忘了以前的故事剧情了，要不要再来一周目呢……总的来说是一款不会浪费你时间的轻优秀游戏。", "appid": "237990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198257493870", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538308800.0} {"text": "Я помню, как всё начиналось, Как первая игра искалась, Как всё казалось интересным, Заманчивым и неизвестным Как в первый раз мы загружалсь, Как впятером на мид сбежались, Как мы носили море хиллок, Не знали вражеских абилок, Как шли мы под чужие вышки, Как скиллы тыкали мы мышкой, Как умирали в первых драках, Били крипов автоатакой, Как собирали дезолятор В каждой игре на всех подряд мы, Как сделали годлайк впервые, Ни в чём тиммейтов не винили. Как рики имбой мы считали, Как сами мы под хук вставали, И в поисках секретной лавки Носились мы по всей той карте, Про роли ничего не знали, Что нравилось, то покупали, Как в ммр мы заскочили, Тысячу рейтинга набили... Но стали лучше разбираться, Куда идти, как закупаться, Как ганкать, как крипов ластхитить, Стали тиммейтов ненавидеть, И за любые недочёты С их мамками мы сводим счеты, Мы из-за каждой смерти злимся, Лишь рейтинг мы поднять стремимся, И на игру мы тратим нервы, Ведь круто быть по цифрам первым, Мы удовольствия лишились, Но мало мы чего добились, Мы в каждой катке полыхаем, Со зла всё больше игр сливаем, Хотим победу за победой, Хотим винрейт мы стопроцентный, Но всё не можем мы понять: Нельзя всё время побеждать", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198145269030", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480248000.0} {"text": "Just a masterpiece! Nothing to add.", "appid": "883710", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998823994", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549454400.0} {"text": "Вечный победитель в номинации «Любимое дитя»", "appid": "250900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198017424365", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "41", "votes_funny": "9", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "Im Krieg gibt es niemals Gewinner oder Verlierer...nur Tote und Überlebende. Die Überlebenden sind meist kaputte Menschen, die vom Krieg dazu getrieben wurden. Aber wozu kämpfen? Für den Frieden, dem man mit Waffen sichert? Wenn man im alleingang tötet ist man ein Mörder, wenn man für die Regierung tötet ist es heldenhaft? Was andere Spiele des Settings noch als \"Spaß\" darstellen, brettert Spec Ops volle Breitseite ins Gesicht. Ob es die Moral und Schattenseiten sind, die es meist nur gibt. Sollte man gespielt haben, es lohnt sich in jeglicher Hinsicht! Ich hoffe die alten Teile kommen mal auf Steam, sowie ein neuer Ableger der Reihe. Diese Serie ist großartig.", "appid": "50300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081691855", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598011200.0} {"text": "This game good.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198867895213", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1568808000.0} {"text": "Los sucesos del juego toman lugar en 1912. El jugador asume la identidad de Booker DeWitt, un ex agente de la Agencia Nacional de Detectives Pinkerton que fue despedido de la misma por un comportamiento inaceptable. Es contratado por unos personajes misteriosos, dándole a conocer la ubicación de Columbia, una ciudad suspendida en el aire en la cual se le da la tarea de encontrar a una mujer llamada Elizabeth. Al llegar a Columbia, Booker se entera de que tras la fachada de distopía en realidad es una ciudad racista, xenófoba y extremadamente patriota a niveles religiosos controlada por el Padre Comstock. BioShock Infinite es un FPS con diversos elementos de juego de rol, aunque si debo mencionar que la mecánica de Shooter es mucho mayor en este título que en los pasados, olvidando un poco el tema de la estrategia y siendo mucho más vertiginoso. Para balancear esto, en esta ocasión solo podremos llevar dos armas a la vez y se le da más énfasis al uso de “Vigorizadores” que vienen a sustituir a los “Plásmidos” de la entrega pasada. Estas son pociones que nos darán habilidades especiales como utilizar fuego, manejar una parvada de cuervos o poder lanzar rayos a los enemigos, entre otros. Nada ejemplifica mejor este sistema de combate vertiginoso que el uso de Skylines que es un sistema de rieles al más puro estilo Ratchet & Clank en las cuales puedes colgarte y te da una mayor libertad durante las balaceras y la facilidad de cambiar de posición para emplear una nueva estrategia durante el combate. Una queja a los Vigorizadores es que a diferencia de los Plásmidos que se usaban para completar un aspecto narrativo en la trama de los primeros juegos, en esa ocasión están ahí porque si no fuera de esta forma el juego no podría llamarse BioShock. La desconexión a esto es tanto que los enemigos normales como la policía y los ciudadanos de Columbia ni los usan ni nada. Solamente los enemigos especiales, ósea los Handyman que vienen siendo los Big Daddys en esta ocasión y una especie de George Washington Mecanizado utilizan dichos Vigorizadores. Elizabeth es de lejos lo mejor de este juego. El equipo de desarrollo logro hacer que una acompañante controlada por la IA no se sintiera como una carga sino como algo viva. Elizabeth se siente genuinamente como una compañera y no como “la damisela en apuros” ya que ella no se queda de brazos cruzados mientras tú haces todo el trabajo y es que durante el combate y el gameplay en general te estará brindando apoyo. Durante tu partida ella te otorgara munición, vida y sales, sin mencionar que te dará pistas sobre varios secretos en el mapa además de que si le das el número adecuado de ganzúas te abrirá ciertas puertas en las cuales podrás encontrar “Voxafonos” que son grabaciones de voz que nos cuenta más del Lore del juego y “Kinescopios” los cuales reproducen una película muda y narran más de la historia del lugar. A estos dos se le suma las distintas vestimentas aleatorias que podemos usar y que nos brindan beneficios varios como una onda de choque al aterrizar de un Skyline o incendiar a los enemigos cuando los golpeas. Todo esto gracias a Eliabeth (como no amarla). Ya en combate es donde nuestra querida acompañante muestra todo su potencial y es que podemos usar sus poderes como una especie de “control de zona” al crear agujeros en la realidad e invocar distintos artilugios que nos darán ventaja durante el combate como una barricada que nos protege de las balas, charcos de agua para conducir electricidad, torretas e incluso tu propio George Washington Mecanizado. A diferencia del primer BioShock donde nos adentrábamos en una ciudad submarina llena de oscuridad y un ambiente algo gótico, en esta ocasión nos topamos con un ambiente más abierto coloreado por un cielo color vainilla y rojizo que incita al jugador a querer explorar todo el lugar. La estética retro de estirpe Americana te da la sensación de visitar un lugar que existe en la vida real y eso sumado al Soundtrack es una verdadera gozada. El sonido ambiente te da la sensación de que Columbia esta viva. Las primeras horas de juego donde puedes turistear la ciudad a tu gusto y visitar cada puesto, tienda y la feria la verdad si te llega a dar la sensación de que estas celebrando el 4 de Julio. En el apartado técnico el juego corre de maravilla y durante mi partida no tuve ningún bug o error. Mencionar que el juego me corrió con FPS estables en todo momento y con la configuración gráfica a tope. BioShock Infinite sucede antes de los acontecimientos del primer BioShock y no esta confirmado si sucede en el mismo universo, por ende el juego es accesible a todo público. BioShock es sinónimo de calidad, de narrativa bien construida y de Gameplay pulido. El juego como todo no se salva de pequeños detalles pero son eso, pequeños. La experiencia completa es tan satisfactoria que vas a rejugar este juego incontables veces y llevarla en tu memoria para siempre. Califico a BioShock Infinite con un 9.3/10 EXTREMADAMENTE RECOMENDABLE.", "appid": "8870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198367517986", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599220800.0} {"text": "Норм игруля для 2009 года,хотя кого я обманываю она будет играбельна даже в 2к17", "appid": "40300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198335616651", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511352000.0} {"text": "This is really fun! It's like a mix between puzzle and tactics, since it's not only about just destroying the enemies, but also board control in different ways (positioning, moving the opponent's pieces etc.) It's a really fresh and creative approach on TBS. It's very smooth, relatively fast-paced, minimalistic, yet surprisingly deep. It's not as unforgiving or even unfair as FTL sometimes, but can still be very challenging (I wouldn't compare these two anyway). And there are lots of customization options to your squad, adding replayability. And one thing I really have to note: The UI is outstanding! Everything is neatly arranged, plain and comprehensible. A lot of AAA productions can take a leaf from this book! To me this is a nice game for in between, when you don't want to play any more time consuming games. Maybe it's not worth the 15 bux to everyone, but should it be on sale in the future and you like TBS, this is a must buy IMO. P.S.: I haven't encountered a single bug so far. Seems very polished to me.", "appid": "590380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006507699", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520769600.0} {"text": "pretty chill and strange", "appid": "532210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198213158112", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569326400.0} {"text": "Медитативная игрушка. Было интересно пособирать разные штучки из деталей!", "appid": "1304910", "steamid": "profiles/76561197980057479", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591617600.0} {"text": "Looks amazing ;D", "appid": "391220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076554917", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511870400.0} {"text": "第一人稱恐怖遊戲，《返校》團隊的新作品。 與返校相比內容略短且為單一結局，但因為改為第一人稱的關係，讓製作團隊可以作出更細緻的場景美術、更有渲染的光影、更有臨場感的音效等等，驚嚇度也因此而高出返校不少。 劇情方面故事雖然簡單，但利用了時序和視角的切換、各種精心製作的文本讓玩家慢慢拼湊出始末，雖然有許多意識流的表現手法但也不會太抽象。 整體來說本作玩法上雖然只是個不錯的「步行模擬」，但卻是國產遊戲在製作技術與品質上有大幅提升的證明。對恐怖遊戲免疫的玩家不妨見識一下。", "appid": "1006510", "steamid": "profiles/76561197979617501", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550577600.0} {"text": "<3", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561197975073517", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572955200.0} {"text": "The story in Code Vein is very cool and the lore and history is shown through memories of the past, all 3 endings are very unique and the gameplay is fun, it's anime souls, what more could I say?", "appid": "678960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271757928", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569758400.0} {"text": "Raft is just pure joy with your friends. Apart from playing the main story which is short at the moment, there's plenty of things to do and plenty more shenanigans to be had with your friends. They also have a creative mode with no restrictions which is great. As it's in Early Access, the Devs have promised new updates so look forward to these!", "appid": "648800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138207102", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1598184000.0} {"text": "Total War: Rome II - Caesar in Gaul DLC It goes without saying that you like history if you're playing a Total war game. But if you're particularly intrigued by Roman history, the Caesar in Gaul DLC concentrates on a very specific period of time, 58-51 BC. You can command hordes of barbarians to bring the Roman Empire to its knees, or conquer the savages yourself for Rome's glory. There's also some nordic factions to play as if you desire a different approach. The map is zoomed in to Western Europe, including all of Germany, France, England, Italy and Scandinavia, so it has a tight focus. Each turn is two weeks, to account for the short time span of the DLC. + There are different buildings and units for each faction in this DLC which is nice. Weather now plays a crucial role in combat, with freezing conditions causing the deaths of thousands during winter months if they are sieging or traversing the wilderness. Dry summers can affect food production negatively. In addition, there are minor changes to the map of Western Europe, with more regions and greater complexity. + Some changes have been made to how battle commanders function. In Caesar in Gaul, you control legendary leaders from history who will take up the mantle against your foes - Vercingetorix for Gaul or Julius Caesar for Rome, among others. Each have unique traits which impact their ability to influence soldiers and win engagements. - While Caesar in Gaul kept my attention and made some revitalising alterations, none of these should have been left out of the base game in the first place. Seasonal weather effects weren't included in Total War: Rome II (we had this in Total War: Shogun 2) so this is lazy game design. The commander modifications could and should have been part of the base game too. Most of the new features didn't take much effort for Creative Assembly to produce. Still, it's a good DLC and fun. Overall Score: 8/10", "appid": "261050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007211313", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "19", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501070400.0} {"text": "Güzel oyun hayatımın çoğunu bu oyuna ayırdım oynamaya değer bir oyun tavsiye ederim", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135187446", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480420800.0} {"text": "найс игра", "appid": "307780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198181829599", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562241600.0} {"text": "DISCLAIMER: English is not my first language, so sorry for any grammatical errors. I played all of the Dead Island games that Techland made. I completed Original Dead Island 2 times, I finished Ryder White's DLC, I finished Riptide and I even played Dead Island Epidemic. But this game, is the best thing Techland ever made. It is fun, it is addictive, it is awesome. I tried to play this game all kind of ways, I played it alone, I played it with my new friend, and I tried to play it with Zombie invasions on. And even if it is super fun to play with your friend, or just some random person that connected to your game, and even if zombie invasions are really cool to, I will highly recommend you to play it offline, without players able to connect to you and without zombie invasions. It is the best way to play this game in order to feel it, how developers wanted you to feel it. If dead island franchise was build for 4 players to play together, and it is pretty boring to play alone, Dying Light was meant to be the game you suppose to play alone. Because there are a lot of moments when the game maybe not scary, but creppy and nervous for sure, and when you play with someone, game stops to be scary and nervouse. And play it on a Hard difficulty, because thats the best difficulty to play at, because this game is meant to be hardcore.", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198188762847", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1507809600.0} {"text": "Отпиздил черепаху", "appid": "346110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198186356473", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "+", "appid": "307780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198238953886", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "I have loved what I have played so far, I am very excited about the full release of the game! Extremely happy that there is going to be a cross over with Star Shift. Both games compliment each well in terms of their mechanics and the dev for this game is very approachable and lets me know when there are new updates available. Play this game and let the small studios that do this have some of the limelight! Amazing effort from all involved. Keep up the hard work, I appreciate it. The empress ;)", "appid": "1164480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074310743", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1601640000.0} {"text": "Jeśli lubisz strzelaniu to ta jest najlepsza", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198275955482", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1460548800.0} {"text": "Good Game.", "appid": "9930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198001609347", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403870400.0} {"text": "존나 빨라도 리듬이있어서 대충눌르면 안돼는 게임 그래서 꿀잼", "appid": "977950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163536895", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575892800.0} {"text": "pra quem veio de cs 1.6 e meio dificel de se acostumar mas ta valendo! game good!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198058476815", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1425038400.0} {"text": "meow meow, feed me please. im so hungry /ᐠ｡ퟑ｡ᐟ\\", "appid": "1117630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120151386", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1565524800.0} {"text": "Where multiplayer? Where everyweek update? Don't sleep \"Beam Team Games\".", "appid": "313120", "steamid": "profiles/76561197974554198", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1442318400.0} {"text": "Muy buen juego , lo cagan los camperos que se quedan enfrente del gancho pero me ha dado buenas risas y sustos con amigos", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198310102058", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525176000.0} {"text": "Super addictive. Makes you think a lot about your next steps while playing the game so if you have a lazy brain definitely check it out!", "appid": "329110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198302893482", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495022400.0} {"text": "十五分鐘的流程，劇情方面我是半懂不懂的就不瞎談什么，但是偶爾帶海聲的BGM聽着倒是挺舒服的。 原價入手不值，畢竟流程真的是太短了就算多一個小時也是國產6元的程度，喜加一的話推薦進去感受一下寧靜。", "appid": "363410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198020939446", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1524916800.0} {"text": "One of the best, if not even the best, MX vs ATV Game so far. Dont listen to the people who say who say there are bad graphics, Maybe these people should look for some glasses. Graphics are pretty good, Sounds are also ok and the Soundtrack is awesome.", "appid": "520940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006884123", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522152000.0} {"text": "arkadaşlar tavsiye ederim hemde ♥♥♥ ucuz benim pc daha iyi olsa just cause 3 alırdım ama buda kotu degil arkadaslar tavsiye ederim bence iyi bi oyun iste alin aga ucuz bide", "appid": "8190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198404958266", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501243200.0} {"text": "For a free game :))) it's ok :))", "appid": "513650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198421697735", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523620800.0} {"text": "настоящая конкуренция коунтер струйку", "appid": "706990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198836856441", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574769600.0} {"text": "Tja was soll ich dazu schon sagen. Es ist ein wunderschönes Spiel, der Zeichenstil (Grafik) gefällt mir sehr und die Handlung ist ebenfalls sehr schön. Die Musik ist einfach passend zu dem Spielumfeld. Einfach Top. :3", "appid": "472680", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126353691", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1469448000.0} {"text": "very goten tag", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198355641970", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601294400.0} {"text": "Ótimo passatempo. Jogo e música relaxante!", "appid": "521280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198162080422", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571918400.0} {"text": "Polecam :)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198354233074", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483531200.0} {"text": "Pros about the game: +Awesome gameplay, you will love the mechanics the game works on. +Bo Duke'em! Press Shift+E (Default buttons) while near the car and hop in, Dukes style! +Excellent storyline, despite Saints Row IV, this has WAY less futuristic stuff in it and it maintains the Gangsta feeling that was on Saints Row II also. +Fixed car handlings, we all hated the car handling back in Saints Row II. +Multiple weapon customizations, Upgradable weapons that will keep even the most gun-specialist happy. +O U T S T A N D I N G Car customization! From front bumpers, to rims and even interior coloring! A NFSU2 fan would love it, :steammocking: +No fly/swim/drive limit. You can go flying for like 3 hours straight and it still wont pop you close to the world, no limits gentlemen! +Shaundi's HD ♥♥♥, lol. +Can run on a Low Spec PC with 30 fps stable. (Tested on a Celeron 2.51 GHz, 2gigs of RAM and Intel HD Graphics.) Cons about the Game: -There are some really wierd scenes in-game (Won't spoil it for you, will see if you actually buy the game). -There (Might) be some random frame drops, even while in combat and this may be a little disturbing.", "appid": "55230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198017952272", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485345600.0} {"text": "muitos cheaters mm, não jogue essa desgraça que nas primeiras horas vai ser divertido depois disso é só tristeza, descendo de patente por causa de cheatado. Alem da comunidade toxica pra krl, só pega logo essa porra e vai jogando que vai ser amor a primeira vista", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198265170125", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601985600.0} {"text": "A lot of people recommended this game to me but this game has the same issue every \"anime\" game has. Toxic, disrespectful and somehow people who has no boundaries whatsoever. Game looks good and effects are off the charts i feel like. When slaying a boss if someone ults the guy time slows down*if im not wrong\" which makes sense. If you have friend, some tolerance level and a nice gpu this game will make you good :)", "appid": "844870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198164927483", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1564228800.0} {"text": "这游戏对我的印象就是 游戏难度高 游戏画面好 游戏打斗一般 防火女小姐姐漂亮 推荐喜欢追求高难度游戏的玩家游玩。", "appid": "374320", "steamid": "profiles/76561199074841776", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599393600.0} {"text": "Increíble juego, te quedas picado hasta que pases el nivel. En lo personal no me presioné a cumplir las misiones, sólo a pasar los niveles, y aún así disfruté muchísimo del juego. Totalmente recomendado.", "appid": "353640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119413091", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "Ослы", "appid": "349700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198170626011", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1444392000.0} {"text": "güzel bir oyun", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198927008725", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "Бляяяя, Фэйс, вот ты флексишь...", "appid": "67370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168083577", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525521600.0} {"text": "Laggy, but it is early access... That's all I have to say *floats away*", "appid": "394690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074261742", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1460721600.0} {"text": "Ну и дерьмо", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031327735", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "Grind base game, its rich in both story and contents. There's lore to this game and that is Dark Sector. Its more like space ninja kinda feel with futuristic weapons and tech. Graphic is great and still improving,", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071517825", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535544000.0} {"text": "FAJNE !", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198181272881", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "çok güzel oyun almayanın crackli indiren delikanlı değildir", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198336343642", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1585742400.0} {"text": "♥", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198381772626", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "pretty good for free", "appid": "208090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030381554", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1399118400.0} {"text": "good game really it's fun اللعبة رهيب وممتعه خصيصا طور اللي تبني فيه ملاهي خاصه فيك وكذا", "appid": "493340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044721952", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480075200.0} {"text": "Искал я значит игру на свободное время... А тут смотрю - Джаст Коуз по скидке. И внезапно друзья решили меня позвать в Коуз поиграть. Ну я понял что это мой самолет. В общем: Плюсы: +игра ооочень большая, только сюжетные миссии займут у вас по крайней мере часов 100 +просто дофига дополнительных квестов, их можно выполнять вечно +у игры еть очень классный мультиплеер, можно и с друзяшками поиграть +огромны выбор транспорта. И вы можете в самом начале игры просто взять и спереть вертолет или самолет. Это очень круто! Минусы: -ebanaya озвучка. Постоянно или спешит или опаздывает... -заданий много, но они очень однообразные. Очень бысто надоедает -3,14зда какие дыры в сюжете. Я вообще не понимаю че там Скорпион остался, ведь его задача была выполнена давно... -этим kalichnым самолетом нереально управлять. Серезно, так трудно было сделать управление чуть проще?! На этом вроде все. Игра крутая, но со своими минусами. Мне понравилась. 10 хаоса из 10", "appid": "8190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198905375477", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1583841600.0} {"text": "กลับมาอย่างยิ่งใหญ่", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086613510", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Spooderman + Cod AW + Gta 5 = Just Cause 2", "appid": "8190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143448653", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1434801600.0} {"text": "Яркий пример неизвестного шедевра игровой индустрии. Прекрасная графика, неповоторивый, захватывающий сюжет, интересные, зачастую очень сложные и ставящие в тупик логические задания. Эта игра для тех, кто любит проверять все возможности своего логического мышления. Это лучшее произведение подобного жанра, черт возьми, которое я проходил за последнее время, однозначно большой плюс разработчикам!", "appid": "11370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076857794", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "44", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1391688000.0} {"text": "I love mayonese... 20/10 Would click again", "appid": "434260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052869867", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1467547200.0} {"text": "THIS GAME IS SUPER FUN. I NEED MORE PEOPLE TO PLAY WITH IT. BEST $2.99 SPENT.", "appid": "104900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011711098", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1393675200.0} {"text": "Güzel Oyun Ama Tır Almak İçin Para Biriktirmek Gerekiyor Ve Parayı Biriktirecez Diye Götümüzü Yırtıyoz", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198443259817", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538654400.0} {"text": "Rogue-diablike. Has curious progression options. Nails 'one more room' feeling. Overall, one of the best titles in Early Access in 2019. It's totally playable now, I don't even know what might be missing there.", "appid": "1145360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198027938810", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1577966400.0} {"text": "I woke up in a grassy meadow dotted by petite, fragrant daisies. Their sunshiny centers grinned at me while a soft breeze ruffled the white petals. Suddenly, an insane man came out of nowhere and beat me to death with a rock. Best game ever!", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198107139388", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1404475200.0} {"text": "op", "appid": "346900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198846819725", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553774400.0} {"text": "Why not??", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039274636", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1483963200.0} {"text": "nice cool mmorpg", "appid": "836620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198122176530", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580299200.0} {"text": "best puzzle game ever!", "appid": "795100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198428514984", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543320000.0} {"text": "Good Anticheat!", "appid": "282660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198169404231", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Ща буит мясо =)", "appid": "379720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198055023876", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1482580800.0} {"text": "Disclaimer: I got this game for free because I bought Stock Car Extreme before this game existed. One of the most enjoyable hardcore racing games to date. No online fees, Minmal DLC releases. Stock, V8 Super, and Go karts... F3, juniors, F1's, and many older ones to boot. The Classic F1 and 86 Opala Chevy I6 Stock Car being my favourite cars to run. The game uses an upgraded Rfactor engine with great physics and more livly graphics and textures. Clearity @High FPS and any resoloution is always awesome. The modeling is pretty great. If you can't play anyone online, then why not just get together with a friend and race the Ai Together, it works for me. This is so much better then all those other games that pass them selves off as simulation, such as Asetto Corsa, and Project DLC. All super cars, no soul. The server system finally works, the Hud is pretty good for such an old game engine, and the controls are solid, just make sure you spend enough time tuning the wheel outside and inside the game and make sure the steering feels just right.", "appid": "431600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050045314", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480593600.0} {"text": "io ke ze no zoi jueko", "appid": "335300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087111557", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458734400.0} {"text": "Many game modes very fun", "appid": "240", "steamid": "profiles/76561197996523120", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521979200.0} {"text": "Very fun with friends! The QoL changes make Monster Hunter feel fresh and fluid", "appid": "582010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048504421", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575201600.0} {"text": "Просто научись играть и не сливать игры.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198166517116", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "good but hard", "appid": "248570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198235819668", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "screm :)", "appid": "773920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198131493690", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1544097600.0} {"text": "Kinda fun , even in non prime matchmaking , keep your good work valve , and improve the VAC system to make this game better and better :)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198876146770", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1551441600.0} {"text": "Not a big fan of Tomb raider series still after playing for like 4-5 hours or so here are some pros and cons :) • Absolutely gorgeous world to explore especially in wide-open areas, dense beautiful environments and hub areas with impressive designs. • Puzzles and Challenge Tombs in particular are fantastic, amazingly designed and satisfying to solve. • Character moments resonate, gets deep into Lara’s character and continues to be a strong well acted heroin. • Optimization is Average as long there is no ray tracing. • Great music which matches the ambient of the game. • Photographer mode which has quite a few features but still far from perfect. • Pretty much bug and glitch free expect some texture pop up in some scenes. • Story-line isn’t really told that well fails to capitalize on past game’s characters and story much of the story feels contrived, or full of holes. • Narrative is weak, disjointed and throwaway, noticeably sub-par voice acting in some scenes. • Platforming sometime feels imprecise which is frustrating. • Stealth feels inconsistent and unsophisticated. • Combat isn’t that great, mechanics feel clumsy and unsuited to most encounters. Game is set to release after few hours today. I would recommend waiting for sale. Running unstable 50-60fps@High Gtx 970.", "appid": "750920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198244372940", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1536926400.0} {"text": "Old but g old", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561199042306251", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593345600.0} {"text": "Пожалуй лучшее, что есть из драк на PC. Только бокс, без лишних движений. Любителям жанра брать полюбому.", "appid": "296770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050878312", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508414400.0} {"text": "Another Masterpiece!!", "appid": "20920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198954994345", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Pretty good game, specially cheap on sales. Worth every buck.", "appid": "282800", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961539417", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Mejoro bastante", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148818445", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1474545600.0} {"text": "Игра хороша,не знаю почему ее хают.", "appid": "368500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039568970", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "A Very cool game of trucks, good to play and chill, also can be played with mods/online. Aproved. If you played eurotruck simulator or eurotruck simulator 2 is the same way of game, you need to drive trucks and deliver cargos, buy more trucks and build your company, basically is the same game with other trucks and in other continent.", "appid": "270880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198215022083", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594209600.0} {"text": "Сыграв 100 часов я понял что она стала уже обыденым делом, дальше остаётся только задроцтво, так как Топ-1 я занимал очень часто начинает надоедать, а могут найтись и те кто сравнятся с вашим набитым скилом и это раздражает, система донейшона никак не влияет на скил в игре, разве что если у вас очень редкая вещь которая даётся за 50 уровень в сезонном испытании можно понять что с вами лучше не связываться, и почти все из-за этого дают драпу от вас... В общем если вам некуда деть бесполезные часы своей жизни советую в неё поиграть, потратить пару сотен тысяч нервных клеток ^_^", "appid": "813820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198363730278", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1576670400.0} {"text": "AWSOMEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! :D", "appid": "22350", "steamid": "profiles/76561197989680477", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1325073600.0} {"text": "FlatOut 2 - это отличная игра от хороших разработчиков.В этой игре достаточно режимов,чтобы повеселится,посмеяться или же просто поездить как псих и поразрушать всё нахрен и разбить в дребезги свою машину и в итоге БУМ!)В игре хорошая анимация и отличная графика для 2006 года. + Много интересных режимов + Просто шикарные саунтреки (бывает не выходишь из гонки потому что играет твоя любимая песня) + Хорошая физика Скрежет железа и рёв моторов под музыку жанра металл- это круто! 10/10", "appid": "2990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036131793", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "47", "votes_funny": "16", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1445947200.0} {"text": "Заебок игруля но нужно соло режим доделатьб а то не в кайф соло против 2их играть", "appid": "813820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047423841", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1528459200.0} {"text": "Guacamelee! Gold Edition, pero que genial! es un juego que se ve tan simple, tan facil, tan simplista, pero al jugarlo te sorprende con divertidos escenarios y personajes, chistes muy graciosos y peleas epicas contra enemigos que nunca te hubieras imaginado. posee una atmosfera tan divertida, tan colorida que te atrapa en un vicio tremendo, le tire 21 horas (incluyendo un epic speed run en hard mode de 3 horas y media seguidas) a este juego para poder terminarlo al 100% y finalmentete lo logre! un juego epico, maravilloso y que vale totalmente el dinero. si lo quieres aprovecha el HB que lo estan regalando por un dolar. no lo pienses y compraloooooooooooooooooooo!!", "appid": "214770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045541947", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1393675200.0} {"text": "OYUN ASLINDA ÇOK GÜZEL BİR OYUN AMA BİLGİSAYARLARA GÖRE KASMA MEVZUSU DEĞİŞİYOR BENİM BİLGİSAYARIMDA BİRAZ KASIYOR YİNEDE OYNAMAYA ÇALIŞIYORUM BU OYUN BENCE DAHA İYİ OLABİLİR MESELA PUBG LITE GİBİ HER BİLGİSAYARIN KALDIRABİLDİĞİ VE KASMADAN PİNG ÇIKMADAN OYNANILABİLEN BİR OYUN OLABİLİR", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198842821445", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561032000.0} {"text": "I recently played it again and i remembered why i damn love(d) this. Great maps, guns and no double jumping is whats making it so good and worth to play. The multiplayer is actually pretty active for a game, which came out 7(!!) years ago, especially for a Call of Duty. If you're planning to play the zombiemode with other ones- forget it. Every map, kinda except Kino Der Toten, is dead and abandoned. So if you're owning a patato PC, which cannot handle the newer games, COD BO1 is a great choice. Tip: Steam price's too high , buy it cheaper somewhere else.", "appid": "42700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196909675", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470657600.0} {"text": "ridiculamente op sknis <3", "appid": "417461", "steamid": "profiles/76561198160725852", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1455969600.0} {"text": "一款十分惊艳的游戏，偷偷抱走卡珊德拉~", "appid": "812140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198396031227", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "39", "votes_funny": "13", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1557576000.0} {"text": "a good game", "appid": "1120690", "steamid": "profiles/76561199034052114", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584619200.0} {"text": "BONK", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198237290880", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514376000.0} {"text": "dark souls: o jogo q vc morre mais no caminho do boss q para o boss, e um jogo maravilhoso pra caralho pqp q jogo foda so e triste ele ter o problema de fps q o faz pra mim rodar a 15 fps mas isso e so detalhes historia maravilhosa realmente faz vc se sentir no jogo, unica parte ilegal e vc ter q matar o sif ;-;;-;-; pq nos obrigam a isso ? :c mas o jogo e foda <3 um dos melhores jogos q ja joguei com certeza se nao o melhor <3 recomendo mto msm q a 15/30 fps so audhuihaush É pra ruder cu de creusa", "appid": "211420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141441705", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1469966400.0} {"text": "Блины решают всё и в этом мире, и в аду.", "appid": "1289310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198280260320", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592827200.0} {"text": "Meh/11", "appid": "218230", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981185897", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582545600.0} {"text": "Pros: -Replayable because of the variety in cards and relics -Looks good -easy to get into the controls -thousands of combinations of card sets -low requirements -awesome animations of the different moves of the cards Cons: -hard game, especially for beginners to the genre Definetely a buying recommendation", "appid": "445980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198151656674", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Sorry for the late review.. But Ubisoft is finally on pace with its Assassin's Creed Franchise.. TBH, both Unity and Syndicate was a huge let down for this franchise, but with Origins, they regained their position.. Performance on lower end rigs is a bit bad, but overall optimization is definitely a +1.. Well Done Ubisoft.. Expectations have been met <3", "appid": "582160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189994186", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517227200.0} {"text": "Si te gusta ir a las favelas de brasil a matar marginales, este es tu juego.", "appid": "204100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198365994995", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587384000.0} {"text": "When a game that was released 7 years ago, is still among the top co-op games, you know that this game is well done. Out of all thee nowadays co-op games, this is still the most played....after 7 long years. ● Pimp ass characters ● Usually when a co-op games have a lot of game modes, only few are played. However with this game every mode is played all the time. Want to play scavenge, you got it! Want to play survival, you got it! That's beacuse the modes are so well done, balanced and really enjoyable, especially with friends! ● Price, of course you would expect a game that old to be priced low, but still you know, this attracts many players. ● Workshop, that still gets updated daily, with new game modes, funny skins and weapons. Probably the most fun thing is to play campaigns with friends. I still cannot get over it, how fun Heavy Rain is with friends, it's just such a joy and frustration to play that campaign on expert and realism mode. So much laughter while trying to sneak through a small area infested with 5 witches, so many memories created.", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198288957886", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481112000.0} {"text": "Боже...Ремейк просто замечательный. Спасибо разработчиков, что сделали замечательную игру", "appid": "1030840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198131420242", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "14", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601035200.0} {"text": "Some games you never forget.", "appid": "22000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198187857337", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586520000.0} {"text": "good game but too many russian my friend", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086358767", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520683200.0} {"text": "Muazzam", "appid": "414340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198156076629", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Нормальная игрушка! Как раз подойдёт для \"убивания\" времени на время \"самоизоляции\"... :)) P.S. Только испытания надо отслеживать и выполнять как можно раньше, на зачищенной территории это стало проблемой... :)))", "appid": "234140", "steamid": "profiles/76561197988517196", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586001600.0} {"text": "really sad to see this shutting down. It was fun as hell to watch the first Falcon 9 landing in VR with a ton of other people, but I guess that's just how indy dev teams roll...", "appid": "407060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198054141946", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501243200.0} {"text": "Moba excepcional! Não só favorece o TeamPlay como é o que as vezes o torna um problema pois os cinco membros da equipe precisam trabalhar de forma sincronizada para obter a vitória. Exige muita estratégia e reflexão antes da tomada de atitude, pois , então morrer no Dota não é só ruim para você, mas para", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198029941471", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387368000.0} {"text": "Build Your Demon 10/10", "appid": "987050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066391127", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580299200.0} {"text": "Great addictive game.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198826473354", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590753600.0} {"text": "Me encantó. La historia es super lineal pero igual resulta muy divertido para jugar entre amigxs.", "appid": "42910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198392674447", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517918400.0} {"text": "Brawlhalla is an amazing way to spend your time with friends or even alone. Playing Alone, you feel rushed to win in online matches, but with friends, you get to gauge how good at playing you really are, brawlhalla is a great way to have casual fun with your friends while having an amazing competitive time.", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198149004985", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1497009600.0} {"text": "I haven't given this game a thumbs up? Yes, this is absolutely worth it.", "appid": "374320", "steamid": "profiles/76561197978607315", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592913600.0} {"text": "Franquia excelente! Kalipso esta de parabens!", "appid": "492720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026993517", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553947200.0} {"text": "Un juego bastante divertido pa dejarte sin pelo", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198914958770", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603108800.0} {"text": "tomanocu essa porra não roda nem com 1050 se fuderrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr", "appid": "349040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198407454327", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519560000.0} {"text": "good slasher to kill time.", "appid": "232090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063245041", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602244800.0} {"text": "This game unlike many others nowadays is actually really fun to play. Its feels like a refreshed version of Rebellion's \"Zombie Army Trilogy\" game combined with puzzles like in tomb raider. A 1930's adventure game taking place in Egypt, seeking treasure and solving puzzles all while you battle your way through hoards of dead mummies and interesting bosses. The level design and map detail in this game is outstanding. The gameplay is fun and satisfying, the puzzles are cute, the guns, customization and gamemodes are also pretty decent. Overall this a casual game but an exceptionally fun one to play. A must play in coop with friends. The game is a bit pricey so that might be the biggest reason affecting your decision to buy.. In my opinion, if your looking for something new and actually fun to play among the heap of questionable games out there right now, I reccomend picking this up. Bravo! 8/10", "appid": "312670", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993310177", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "41", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535457600.0} {"text": "Confesso, depois de algumas atualizações minha curiosidade foi maior e visitei o jogo sim, mas já não estava com paciência de grindar tudo denovo, na minha percepção, iriam ser as mesma coisa que já foi citado acima. Baixei o jogo novamente (Por insistência de amigos próximos) quando chegou o verdadeiro Multiplayer prometido, foi ai percebi que já não estava familiar, o jogo tinha quests, estava com outra pegada, tinha até uma história parecendo um filme da Sessão da Tarde, mas era algo novo e animador, fui lendo os patchs passados e percebi que o conteúdo estava vasto e que o mesmo estava indo para o rumo certo e também estava cumprindo sua proposta de início. Tá, mas por que você está RECOMENDANDO ele ? Pois bem, vamos lá. Depois de anos de atualizações, o jogo ficou totalmente novo, quests infinitas, mineração mais complexa, craft foi retrabalhado, construção de bases, veículos, robôs, naves cargueiras (que ainda por cima tem mais quests), lugares abandonados com muita carga histórica e por entre outros que estou ainda por explorar. Os gráficos são bonitos, porém a vários glitch de textura deixa isso a desejar, trilha sonora é maravilhosa e a dificuldade é bem equilibrada para sua jornada ser tranquila e bem rentável e por esses motivos tive que recomendar só agora. Bom, para torná breve essa minha experiência vou ser direto. , o jogo está bom, não digo que está ótimo pois ainda tem muitos problemas técnicos que atrapalham a imersão (bugs, crashes, bug’s e mais bug’s), é um jogo procedural:” ” - (às vezes nem isso sei fazer direito). Ele não é um jogo feito para todos, não se engane só por que tu jogou minecraft, você não pode ter a mesma experiência em No Man’s Sky, ele é um jogo que você precisa entrar com objetivo e grindar por horas por aquilo. Tentei ser o mais direto possível nessa minha bosta de análise, com o objetivo impossível de querer voltar no passado e me dar um por ter comprado ele na pré-venda, mas no final fico feliz pelo jogo atingir as expectativas e me fazer jogá-lo por mais horas.", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086969794", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "42", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596110400.0} {"text": "Рекомендую ли ее я? да тут без сомнения да конечно,тут каждый наидет что хочет,хочешь воевать играешь в саму арму,хочешь выживать играешь в оринальный дэиз мод(который прилагается),хочешь воевать и выживать играешь в эпоху и кучу других модов,мой выбор Arma 2: Operation Arrowhead", "appid": "33930", "steamid": "profiles/76561197973986885", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1422446400.0} {"text": "Terraria. Viele denken wenn sie das Spiel sehen, warum sollte ich das kaufen es gibt doch Minecraft.... aber wenn ihr das denkt, habt ihr falsch gedacht. Es hat zwar ein ähnliches System wie Minecraft (Crafting, Blöcke abbauen, Tiere/Monster töten usw..) aber es hat auch noch einiges mehr zu bieten. Es gibt mehr verschiedene Blöcke, Waffen, Rüstungen usw. auch eine viellfältige Monsterschar ist abends aufzutreffen. Es ist nicht in einer 2D Sicht, was aber den spielspaß um keinen falls verringert. Nein im gegenteil es ist auch mal wieder eine abwechslung. Es gibt auch mehrere verschiedene Maps und auch ein Multiplayer Modus ist vorhanden. Terarria ist ein simple gestricktes Game das aber, die stärken der anderen ähnlichen Spiele übernimmt eingene Ideen hinzufügt und ihre Fehler ausgebessert hat. Es ist also auf jeden Fall mal einen Blick wert. Und 10€ sind ja auch nicht zu viel verlangt.", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091083158", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1394971200.0} {"text": "Es un juego bastante entretenido aunque se nota que aun esta en acceso anticipado, una de las cosas que mas me gustaron de este juego es el gran trabajo que hacen los desarrolladores que actualizan constantemente el juego, no me refiero a que le metan contenido a cada rato si no que arreglan las imperfecciones que este tiene incluso hasta dos veces al día, tal cariño por su producto a veces ni las empresas triple a lo demuestran.", "appid": "994220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201672123", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1560340800.0} {"text": "love this", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198206113737", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511524800.0} {"text": "Great, great, great, I love it! 10/10", "appid": "207610", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255776936", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1462017600.0} {"text": "非常经典总之很棒！", "appid": "379720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198301397113", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496664000.0} {"text": "Очень интересная игра, есть свои плюшки например:можно нацепить на дробаш прицел от снайперской винтовки это ли не круто , Есть в своем роде модинг все что вздумаеться, игра прикольная но меня затянуло на 30 ч впринципе норм. 8/10", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561199000870119", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592481600.0} {"text": "The best game for relax", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198962142853", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1567252800.0} {"text": "Has Nagato. Nothing will change my mind.", "appid": "1150080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121924585", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581768000.0} {"text": "Nice game, funny game !", "appid": "212480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084715332", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1386504000.0} {"text": ": вы любитель онлайн шутеров, но КС уже надоела? (или другая причина) Берите, не пожалеете своих кровных) Здравствуй, читатель (-ница)! Если ты действительно заинтересован в покупке Rainbow Six Siege, то ты пришёл по адресу! Я всё тебе расскажу. Сам того не осозновая, я купил Сидж. Это произошло быстро: увидел, что игру стали часто поддерживать разрабы, посмотрел на цену в 500 руб. (У меня стартовое издание) поднакопил, купил, PROFIT!1! После пару часов в игре я понял, что это прекрасно. Хочется сказать, что я и раньше играл в Сидж, на купленном аккаунте, и что я увидел год спустя, меня шокировало! Огромное кол-во оперов, отличные карты (кроме Яхты и Луна-Парка, фуу ненавижу их), неплохой неткод, прекрасная стрельба и многое другое... И, наиграв на данный момент 53 часа, я пишу этот обзор и рекомендую эту игру, по причинам: Их в игре очень много и большинством приятно играть, но никто не отменял криворуких д@унов с большим количеством реальных денег, которые способны купить себе всех оперов и руинить другим катки из-за неумения обращения со \"спецспособностями\" РИАЛ ЛАЙФ СТОРИ: Как было выше написанно в обзоре у меня Starter Edition (после недавнего времени там дают целых 6 оперативников), с которым более чем приятно играть, т.к.: разрабатываются свои тактики для разных персонажей, вы обдумываете покупку любого опера и т.д. Так вот: купил себе Пульса, славного малого... и пожалел. Я абсолютно не умею им играть, но он очень меня выручает на мною ненавистных картах, такие дела (вывод таков: все оперативники имеют свои \"карты\" и полезны только в определённых ситуациях) Надеюсь, что мой обзор дал вам понять, что игра стоит своих денег и времени, лучше уж это, чем неподдерживаемая КС, которая дико потеряла онлайн.", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198146656813", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1524830400.0} {"text": "Un Clasico, muy bueno!!!", "appid": "252350", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998263938", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "Good Game, better than DBD in my Opinion, every Round feels Different and the Sides between Survivor and Killer are pretty even out", "appid": "1195460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044535269", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576411200.0} {"text": "Tahle hra je prostě skvělá a za tu cenu myslím že luxus. Rozhodně doporučuji a větší zábava s více lidma. Sranda