player user.", "appid": "424370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042311658", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598702400.0} {"text": "Sus", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198190918489", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604404800.0} {"text": "Its a very good game. but too mutch hackers", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198210426680", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1427112000.0} {"text": "If you support child slavery than yeah you should play this game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263019489", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "よくできたシングルFPSでもあり、 『零 -Fatal Frame-』シリーズに影響を受けたホラーゲームでもある。 謎の黒髪の少女 絹を裂くようなカナ切り音 \"なにか\"がいそうなドア向こう、近づくごとに高まるノイズ 死者からの無線 説明が付かぬ心霊現象 点々と続いていく血痕 というジャパニーズホラー的な恐怖演出があるが、 いわく付きの廃屋ではなく、現代的なビル 古来より伝承された呪われし儀式ではなく、倫理的タブーとされる科学実験 敵は物理攻撃が通用しない幽霊ではなく、武装した兵士 なので、結局は重火器ドンパチゲーになってしまう。 ホラー要素はあくまでフレーバーであり、主要素は良質なアクションゲームだ。 ポルターガイストが起きてる中、マシンガンをぶっ放しながら突撃する脳筋プレイも爽快だ。 日本語には対応しているが、一部シーンでは日本語オフにしないとフリーズする。 そうそう、『零』と一番の違いを言うのを忘れていた。 主人公が華奢で儚い美少女でなく、マッチョな男性軍人", "appid": "21090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013638663", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1512734400.0} {"text": "Zum Spiel; Grundsätzlich gut umgesetzt, und in ner 5 Mann Truppe auch sehr spielenswert, leider ist CSGO auch bisschen wie Roulette.. es macht solange spaß, bis es russisch wird... und leider treffen wir unsere \"Freunde\" ausm Osten sehr oft in \"Wettkampf\" an...", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050191109", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1447502400.0} {"text": "Best game ever! :D", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198152054757", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1429185600.0} {"text": "Играбельно", "appid": "489520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198058737458", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562241600.0} {"text": "Risk of Rain 2 - рогалик, как было описано выше. Сейчас он находится в раннем доступе и я вообще никогда не обращаю внимания на ранний доступ, но наслышан о \"дело в раннем доступе\" и эта игра, к этому определению не подходит. Многие писали раньше и даже делали руководства о плохой оптимизации и поднятии фпс - сейчас такой проблемы нет. Игра работает на абсолютно максимальных настройках в 60 фпс, разве что антизатропная фильтрация, или какая она там стоит в 4x - ну это дело в моей конфигурации. 2 часть отличается от первой многим, конечно же дело в том, что первая часть была платформером с пиксельной графикой - а здесь шутер от третьего лица в трехмерном измерении. Очень сильно люблю эту игру и первую часть, в которую я и поиграл лишь 30 минут вроде, но думаю после второй части куплю как-нибудь снова и поиграю больше, ну так вот - я люблю эту игру и первую часть за их авторов и вообще за многое, чего я просто не могу назвать, что-то тут есть. Название Risk of Rain - переводится как возможность или опасность дождя, наверное. И становится понятно, что-то связанное с дождём в названии есть, когда вы будете выбирать уровень сложности - \"Дождик\", \"Ливень\", \"Сезон дождей\". Мне приятно становится на душе от этих названий, а что же было в первой части с этой мрачноватой пиксельной графикой и задним фоном на котором не было ровным счётом ничего, но это всё создавало вместе с музыкой, автор которой очень талантлив, создавали ощущение того, что погода в игре была пасмурной - здесь такого нет. Потому что игра трёхмерная и по карте вы бегаете не в зад и вперёд а как вам угодно. Кроме того, естественно графика больше не пиксельная. Я если честно не хочу говорить о том, что эта часть стала лучше или хуже по отношению к первой, так как у этих двух частей есть, такая атмосфера, благодаря которой они обе становятся уютными. Хочу лишь сказать, как эта игра сильно продвинулась в перёд во всём. Как сильно разработчики любят свою игру. Самое важное, что музыка в первой части, как я говори до этого, вместе с цветовой гаммой и контрастом создавали шикарную атмосферу, однако во второй части нету такой графики, но она стала шутером от третьего лица, с очень хорошо сделанными механиками и так же с очень приятно сделанными, опять же механиками, еще в раннем доступе. Авторы понимали, что игра теперь от третьего лица в трёхмерном мире и та атмосфера, что была в первой части может пропасть и пропадёт, потому что нету того уюта, что создавался тогда, ахринеть, вот чисто минуточку, я просто только что понял, что уже 7 лет назад, не будет того уюта, что создавался 7 лет назад. Но он пропадёт, если они решат сделать игру такой же какой она и была, только уже в трёхмерном измерении - не получится сделать такие же платформы, механики, нет. Поэтому они сделали всё правильно сделав новые механики и карты, которые к слову не шипко то и мрачные, особенно начиная со второго этапа - там вообще микс из всех цветов радуги и больше. Но как же тогда быть? Как сохранить атмосферу игры? Ответ под носом, сказал бы Шерлок - музыка и баланс в цветовой гамме и графикой. Баланс между гаммой цветов и графикой - я имею ввиду, что графика игры позволяет сделать игру либо слишком разнообразную на цвета при этом не выжигая глаза таким колоритом, либо же, что и есть на деле - сделать в игре карты, которые имею от одного до наверное 5 разных цветов и несколько их оттенков(мобы не в счёт). Это очень важно, ведь тот же зелёный цвет, в сочетании с темно-серым, так и ещё в месте, куда не попадает свет - то есть тут есть тени создаёт приятное сочетание цветов и света(это, если что описание одной из карт первого этапа, что означает первый этап, второй и так далее, вы поймёте когда будете играть в это, если ещё не играли в первую часть), Что я имел ввиду, когда говорил про музыку - конечно же очевидно, однако, так же я писал ранее, что автор музыки очень талантлив и я не соврал - музыка тут шикарна и атмосфера её вообще идеальна. Конечно же она могла бы и не создавать такой атмосферы будь у игры другие цвета и по другому сделаны карты - об этом я ещё кое-что скажу. Но все равно если бы вы слушали эту музыку просто в наушниках идя по улице сидя на диване дома, ну или лёжа и в других ситуациях, когда слушаете музыку - атмосферу вы бы всё равно чувствовали, потому что музыка способна действовать на разум человека воображая ему разные картины по своей атмосфере, изменять его настроение не обязательно по настроению самой музыки и так же действовать на разум психологически. Даже если бы были другие цвета и другой контраст и другие формы карт - музыка делала бы своё дело, но не так сильно вы бы его ощущали, потому у вас перед глазами было бы другое, просто логично, что всё в игре связано между собой, так и должно быть, потому что просто иначе никак, иначе ничего не делается и не происходит. Формы карт и сами карты - это тоже один из важных пунктов атмосферы игры. Очень важно, чтобы на тектонических равнинах в туман, куда нельзя попасть уходили пустые и живописные поля с обломками. А на горных вершина были толстые каменные столбы созданные природой и чтобы столбы эти держали такую толстую и каменную платформу, до которой вам не добраться, но так же важно чтобы платформа эта закрывала небо и создавала теневую поверхность, а из этого места можно было и в тоннель войти и выйти из него уже на открытой поверхности и наоборот, помните, что я писал выше? Так же не плохо было бы, чтобы такая карта была окружена водой и в ней были места с которых можно было бы спрыгнуть и у вас закружилась бы голова и начали бы порхать бабочки в животе, если вы достаточно погрузились в игру. Карт в игре к слову много, не для раннего доступа, а для игры, конечно в какой-то момент возможно вы поймёте, что не так много как кажется, но я за это ручаться не могу, мой рекорд 3 этап, на котором меня убили, но карты довольно сильно друг от друга отличались и как я говорил до этого соблюдали не большое количество цветов и лишь их оттенков было много. Карты большие и разнообразные, не только в отличие друг от друга, как я говорил ранее, а в целом сами по себе - по ним интересно бегать, пусть пока вы и наиграетесь на ней вы успеете обежать её по кругу несколько раз, но всё таки размеры карт действительно большие - вы всё время можете перемещаться и большего чем есть вам не нужно. Когда я поиграл в первую часть и решил вернуть за неё деньги, я спустился к обзорам на неё - мне было интересно сколько часов в такой игре могли наиграть другие люди, я увидел в \"похожих играх\" или в \"других продуктах от этих разработчиков\" не помню уже, Risk of Rain 2 и я естественно перешёл на страницу этой игры с мыслями \"о хох, первую часть купил и тут уже вторая скоро выйдет\" я действительно удивился и не много офигел, потому что я поиграл в игру платформер с пиксельной графикой, а тут я увидел 3д игру от третьего лица в трёхмерном измерении, которая мне даже показалась игрой с открытым миром, где надо будет исследовать планеты и убивать по мере исследования боссов, в одиночку или по сети, я сразу подумал, что когда игра выйдет я её куплю, не сразу, а когда будут деньги и другие факторы, которые будут соответствовать желанию(не считая цены). И вот я купил эту игру только 31 января 2020 года с хорошей выдержкой так сказать с момента выхода этой игры, я думаю хорошо, что так вышло, очень хорошо. Игра сейчас отделана так, что остаётся лишь добавлять и добавлять новый контент, пока творческие способности позволяют, ведь больше тут нечего фиксить, багов нет, графических багов тоже нет, графика устраивает, оптимизация тоже отличная, какие ещё у игр есть основные факторы успеха - всё хорошо. Это всё тоже приятное приключение по планетам, но отличающееся от первой части лишь тем, что теперь это трехмерное измерение. В итоге Risk of Rain 2 - это игра в которую очень интересно играть и можно не отвлекаться не на что, да вас и не отвлекают - вы и игра наедине, вдвоём и вы погружены в игру и вам действительно интересно и приятно играть в неё. Всё, ухожу в закат...", "appid": "632360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198442952493", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "24", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1580644800.0} {"text": "Fun! Wow! 10/10", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198041224247", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "instakill.pl Tyle w temacie.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141150010", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518868800.0} {"text": "+!", "appid": "570940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003982637", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "Um jogo desafiador, que no qual você se diverte bastante com os amigos.", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198272720144", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "20", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515758400.0} {"text": "Good.It has a goal to make you play the game.Shortly there are ranks and you want to climb the rank ladder.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198108720632", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454673600.0} {"text": "This game is amazing just see for yourself. The only real complaint is the bad mouse and keyboard controls in the menu which is not game breaking just annoying. Pick up a game pad to ignore all that, and enjoy this masterpiece.", "appid": "288470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087465927", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516622400.0} {"text": "Don't just press e... Press q! You will not regret buying this game! And now modding was made very easy since June 21 2020 when Mod workshop support and Mod tag support was added!", "appid": "1118200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032133949", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594468800.0} {"text": "Did u like FC3? Yes? Good, u'll love FC4.", "appid": "298110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132824593", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "Приятная игрушка, красивые значки, несколько неплохих фонов для профиля. Собственно и все :)", "appid": "539720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084008866", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585310400.0} {"text": "I love this game", "appid": "550650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198347426907", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1511784000.0} {"text": "Nice Anticheat", "appid": "282660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198963101435", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597924800.0} {"text": "The game is not like most zombie games. It feels more realistic and dependent. I'm a fan of the walking dead (If you like TWD get this game now) and I like the fact that shots to the head to the trick. Unlike L4D2 when your just spraying into the body. And when someone gets scratched there screen begins to fade as they can no longer control it and just die as the friends have to put them down as a zombie. This game is pretty awesome with a nice soundtrack, interesting maps and a preferably large variety of weapons to choose from and a strong and high FPS running rate. Game is really worth it I would really recommend trying this out!", "appid": "238430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198083934388", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1448625600.0} {"text": "south park: the stick of truth e um jogo de rpg em turnos inspirado no desenho animado criado por trey parker e matstone.e eu vou começar essa analise pelo enredo \"genial\" dessa bagaça.quando o voce iniciar vai assistir uma cutscene narrada pelo cartman que conta uma parte da historia.durante mil anos os humanos do kastelo koopa(com k mesmo) e os elfos ♥♥♥♥♥♥ de larnion travam uma guerra pela posse do cajado da verdade(stick of truth)pois aquele que controlar o cajado controla o universo,as profecias falam sobre um \"novato\" e para salvar a raça humana o grande mago tem que encontrar o novato antes que os elfos manipulem a mente dele e o usem para roubar o cajado.e ai acaba a cutscene e voce precisa criar seu personagem.e ai esta o primeiro ponto positivo do jogo.voce pode customizar o seu personagem e deixar ele do jeito que quiser.mudando a cor do cabelo,roupa,cor da pele,marcas no rosto entre outras coisas.porem infelizmente voce nao pode escolher se vai ser menino ou menina.voce vai ser menino e nao tem como mudar isso e se eu revelasse o porque disso eu estaria dando um spoiler.porem mesmo assim esse sistema funciona perfeitamente bem e varias pessoas criam seus personagems parecidos consigo mesmo.ou voce pode ser retardado como eu e criar uma bosta de personagem tosco.depois de criar seu personagem voce se ve dentro da sua nova casa,sua familia acabou de se mudar.saindo para fazer novos amigos voce encontra o butters e como sempre ele esta apanhando de alguem e voce precisa ajuda-lo e como recompensa ele vai te levar para conhecer cartman(se bem que conhecer o pau no c* do cartman e mais um castigo do que uma recompensa mas enfim) e ai voce descobre que tudo e uma brincadeira de rpg.lembra da historia epica sobre cavaleiros e elfos ♥♥♥♥♥♥ lutando durante mil anos? pois bem os cavaleiro,magos,elfos e etc sao crianças fantasiadas.os palacios,tabernas,e casas sao simples cabanas que eles montaram no quintal de casa.o tal grande mago e o cartman com manto chapeu e um pau na mao(ui) e o cajado da verdade e um galho que foi encontrado por ai.ta mas ai voce pensa \"a entao a historia do jogo e uma bosta certo?\" nao.pode nao ser uma historia seria e mega epica com a qual voce vai se emocionar mas acredite e MUITO criativa.voce vai dar muita risada com esse enredo hilario cheio de personagems carismaticos e piadas sujas a cada 2 minutos e vai se esquecer de que e uma brincadeira de criança.no inicio do jogo voce conhece cartman,butter,kenny e clyde.a e o scott malkinson.exato! aquele que ninguem liga.e as outras criancas aparecem depois.quando eu cheguei nessa parte eu ja estava fascinado com a quantidade de referencias que eu ja tinha visto.e ainda tinha muito mais! o jogo e repleto de referencias a varios episodiose ao filme se voce e fa de south park vai notar essas referencias tambem.eu aposto um braço que pelo menos 90% dos cenarios no jogo tem referencias e nao so o cenario,varias missoes sao puras referencias.como uma missao que nao posso falar como e pra nao dar spoier mas que e referencia aquele episodio sobre o campo de concentracao da intolerancia e um rato.isso sem contar algumas musicas que fazem referencia ao filme de south park que possui varias musicas.e por falar em musica,elas sao otimas.a maioria sao temas medievais ou musicas que como eu ja disse fazem referencia ao filme ou a algum episodio mas quando voce entra em combate toca um tema mais animado.um outro ponto super positivo no jogo e o sistema de combate.nao e aquele tipo de rpg onde voce escolhe o poder que seu personagem vai usar e em seguida assiste ele executar o golpe sem precisar que voce faça nada.aqui e como em paper mario onde para o golpe ter eficiencia maxima voce precisa apertar algum botao na hora certa,por exemplo o golpe mais basico do jogo e um onde voce simplesmente ataca o seu inimigo com a sua arma branca que pode ser uma espada, um bastao,um vibrador,uma muleta,um galho,ou outra arma bizarra que o jogo te deixa usar.mas enfim se voce simplesmente selecionar o golpe e ficar assisindo se personagem vai chegar perto do inimigo e causar 1 de dano.porem se voce apertar o botao certo na hora certa vai causar tipo,80 de dano.enfim,voce nao vai simplesmente apertar 1 botao e ver seu personagem matar todo mundo.e sobre a dificuldade?e relativa.se voce nunca jogou um rpg na vida ou jogou muito pouco,voce vai ter certa dificuldade no começo mas em 5 horas no maximo voce entende muito bem como esse jogo funciona.garanto que antes do final do jogo voce ja vai entender muito bem todas ou quase todas as mecanicas desse jogo.agora,voce ja tem ampla experiencia em rpg?voce e do tipo que zerou todos os jogos da serie final fantasy?voce ja fez todos os finais em chrono trigger ? entao ai vai uma dica: assim que o jogo começar coloque na dificuldade maxima ou voce nao vai ter desafio algum! e isso nao e exagero,o jogo e muito façil e simples de entender principalmente se comparado a outros jogos de rpg.mas esse NAO E o principal defeito do jogo.o principal defeito e que apesar de ser um rpg ele e 100% linear.fala serio,99,99% dos rpgs sao nada lineares.ate os primeiros rpgs la do nintendinho tinham varias alternativas diferentes e missoes que se voce realizasse em uma ordem ou em outra alterava a missao seguinte ou ate o resto do jogo inteiro.ai chega em 2014 e encontra um rpg totalmente linear? a vai pra fruta que caiu.alem disso o jogo tem apenas um final.nao importa qual classe voce escolher nao importa qual caminho voce escolher nao importa qual missao voce vai ou nao fazer nao importa qual parceiro voce escolhe e nao importa se voce faz ou nao as missoes secundarias,o final e o mesmo e a historia se desenrola do mesmo jeito.chrono trigger foi lançado quase 2 decadas antes de south park: the stick of truth e tinha mais de 10 finais e era nada linear.so tem uma coisa nesse jogo que muda: as piadas que o cartman faz com voce.dependendo da cor da sua pele,do seu cabelo ou da sua classe esse feira da fruta do baralho faz piadas diferentes com voce.por exemplo se voce criar um personagem branco e escolher a classe ladrao o cartman vai dizer: \"um ladrao branco? nunca ouvi falar mas parece bom\" e isso combina com a personalidade racista que o cartman tem no desenho.visto que ao dizer isso ele esta insinuando que os ladroes sao todos ou em sua maioria ♥♥♥♥♥♥,outro exemplo e se voce escolher a classe judeu(sim judeu por algum motivo e uma classe nesse jogo.) se voce que escolher qualquer outra classe cartman vai dizer \"entao bem vindo babaca,o mago\" ou \"entao bem vindo babaca o guerreiro\" porem se voce escolher judeu ele vai dizer \"entao bem vindo babaca o judeu que provavelmente vai tomar conta do nosso ouro\" ou alguma coisa assim.e nao eu nao escolhi o nome \"babaca\" porem nao importa qual nome voce escolha vao te chamar assim.e outra critica:apesar do jogo possuir 4 classes,mago guerreiro,ladrao e judeu voce vai poder usar qualquer arma do jogo.entao se voce e mago e seu amigo e ladrao voces vao usar as mesmas armas e equipamentos durante o jogo.a unica diferenca entre as classes e que as magias sao diferentes e algumas tem mais hp e outras mais mp.e os graficos?sao horriveis porem ao mesmo tempo sao os melhores possiveis.vou explicar.esse jogo nao tem graficos de ultima geraçao,pelo contrario,sao super-simples e o play 2 roda isso tranquilo,porem os graficos e a animaçao sao identicos ao desenho e voce realmente sente que esta em um episodio e nao em um jogo o que nao aconteceria se o jogo tivesse graficon melhores.enfim eu recomendo esse jogo sim.porem tenha em mente que esse jogo foi feito para os fas de south park e se voce nao gosta de south park,mas gosta muito de rpg provavelmente dara nota 6/10 enquanto um fa daria nota 11/10.se voce e fa da serie compra,sao risadas garantidas e varias horas de diversao porem se voce procura um bom rpg recomendo outros titulos ou entao espere uma promoçao mas minha nota como fa de south park e de rpg e de 8.5/10", "appid": "213670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198206025700", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1453291200.0} {"text": "喵 喵 喵 meow meow meow", "appid": "552200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092985202", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "I love this game", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198852212155", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593259200.0} {"text": "Best Games", "appid": "397900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086042680", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "I love the game WOULD PLAY ALL DAY IF I COULD", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198185565923", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521201600.0} {"text": "Симулятор избиения младенцев.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561197965816861", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593691200.0} {"text": "decent coop zombies game ~", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198813980971", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601035200.0} {"text": "1", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198332251835", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493985600.0} {"text": "10/10", "appid": "200510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018302142", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1459339200.0} {"text": "10/10 would get for free again", "appid": "224420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198083829696", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1405944000.0} {"text": "If you like crafting, survival, gathering, exploration and sandbox games, then you should enjoy Darkout. Graphics are pretty decent for this sort of game, and the atmosphere has a special feel, its not redundant or boring. Some areas are pretty and colourful while other areas are dark and creepy. You start off simple, gathering and crafting things, trying to survive shelter, weapons etc.. Soon your little shed may end up being a huge complex mining base or a well fortified outpost. So there is a sense of progression and satisfaction which I love very much. If you are still hesitant about the game, wait for a sale :]", "appid": "257050", "steamid": "profiles/76561197995162325", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "43", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1418904000.0} {"text": "Fajna napierdalanka", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198307231586", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511784000.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "1099440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198113973571", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1577966400.0} {"text": "Muito TOP", "appid": "287450", "steamid": "profiles/76561198388441125", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496318400.0} {"text": "nixe", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198823312381", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576411200.0} {"text": "A really good FPS computer game with a very large community that grows everyday. The way valve has incorperated skins and cases into the game have really made the game alot better", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077958857", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1447934400.0} {"text": "2 nice 2 be tru ma ♥♥♥♥♥", "appid": "40800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198843917655", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530360000.0} {"text": "Good game!", "appid": "500", "steamid": "profiles/76561197972899969", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1394193600.0} {"text": "Program jest przyjemny i łatwy w obsłudze a przy tym dobry.Polecam!", "appid": "1840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198156647646", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "24", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1447848000.0} {"text": ";)", "appid": "658560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198818384990", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1527508800.0} {"text": "Kanka 35 saatimi verdim valla bak temiz deli olursun oyun çok güzel, herkese öneriyorum bol bol olmasada herkesin oynaması gereken bir oyun olduğunu düşünüyorum dikkat edinde kafayı çizmeyin sakın", "appid": "698780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198367426592", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595160000.0} {"text": "Blood Money is simply the best Game of the whole Hitman Series, this is what should have set the path for all following releases, \"Hitman: Absolution\" wasn't a bad game but it certainly did not come close to the real Hitman experience since it was more of a action game and the two other ones that followed are packed with DLC's etc. that easily cost you 70-200 and they still lack the experience of this game. I wish they would have released a follow up to Blood Money with the exact same gameplay and new contracts. If you want the full Hitman experience, I recommend to get Blood Money. Each contract can be done the way you want to (of course the more of a ghost you are the better) and there are a ton of ways to complete a contract in a clean way. The contracts and the environments give a realistic vibe. Once you get into it you'll notice how your stealth skills improve try after try. The soundtrack delivers an incredible atmosphere. There are many details that the other Hitman games lack. This is also one of the best stealth games ever made. I spent a ♥♥♥♥ load of hours playing this game before it was on steam back in the days, probably my most played game and I still come back to this one on here since no other Hitman gives me these kind of vibes.", "appid": "6860", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977159343", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584360000.0} {"text": "<3", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036967097", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387713600.0} {"text": "Good game but short content ps: crafting stupid", "appid": "250400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119908558", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403784000.0} {"text": "Pra quem é fã de Star Wars, nada menos do que comprar este jogo, cenarios incriveis, trilha sonora nem se fala, é um pouco curto mas vale cada momento nele, desde a primeira vez que voce liga o sabre ate o ultimo momento voce se sente em Star Wars e quer ver mais sobre o Cal.", "appid": "1172380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096339566", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584360000.0} {"text": "Игра оставляет неоднозначные ощущения. Кажется, что перед нами идеальный кандидат в те игры, которые не заслуживают негативной оценки, но и до \"пальца вверх\" таким играм как пешком до Луны. Самой подходящей оценкой был бы сдержанный нейтральный отзыв. Из недостатков игры в глаза бросаются бедность уровней, интерьеров помещений, очень средняя графика, весьма отсталая анимация лиц и анимация персонажей в целом - в мире, где существуют анимации героев в Witcher 3 или новеньких Resident Evil - подобные невыразительные движения и мимика героев просто недопустимы. Постановочные сцены на фоне кинематографичных сцен из CoD - даже образца десятилетней давности - тоже вызывают смех и недоумение: солдаты сопротивления, приговорённые триггерами разработчиков к смерти в активных сценках падают как манекены практически даже не попадая под обстрелы, если наблюдать это всё со стороны. Практически все механики взаимодействия с миром не доведены до конца и даже если проходить на высшей сложности - не составит труда обойтись полностью без шумовых приманок, термальных ножей, да даже торговли, т.к. если заглядывать под каждый угол, как можно раньше вкачав \"навык\" получения большего опыта, то в определённый момент времени даже раньше середины прохождения в инвентаре скапливается настолько огромный арсенал и количество боеприпасов переваливает за тысячи патронов и зарядов, что совершенно пропадает смысл играть с противником в прятки - проще и быстрее их расстрелять. К тому же игра никак не поощряет скрытные обходы противников без вступления в бой. С учетом кривости искусственного интеллекта, который спустя пять - десять секунд преследования теряет к вам интерес - выживание превращается в обычный проходной \"шутан\". Хотя, казалось бы, нам противостоит противник с \"разумом Роя\" и подвергнувшийся нападанию даже самый последний дрон должен призвать на поддержку весь уровень, но нет. Зачищаем локацию оттаскивая роботов по одному по углам и закоулкам. Самое смешное, что в ходе сюжета нам рассказывают о том, что Skynet предугадывает действия Сопротивления, а в ходе непосредственной игры мы разделываем жестянок как самых тупых рядовых солдат из какой-нибудь stealth-игры, вроде Sniper Elite или Splinter Cell. -Ты накатал такое полотно недостатков, но поставил положительную рекомендацию, почему? Разработчики с душой и с добрым рвением отнеслись к своему творению. Если не воспринимать игру всецело как самостоятельный шутер с элементами stealth и rpg, а понимать, что перед нами игра по вселенной фильмов Terminator, причем именно каноничных и наиболее качественных двух первых частей - то рука не подымается ругать игру. Игра на ночных локациях выдержана в стильной серо-голубой гамме, благодаря которой зрители T2: Judgement Day тут же вспомнят первые минуты фильма, это сцена очень сильно впечатывается в сознание и разработчик очень умело играет на ностальгии по тому краткому фрагменту. Качественный саундтрек практически идентичен музыкальному сопровождению из фильмов и пробирает до мурашек, особенно в первые моменты встречи с T-800. И конечно нет-нет да встречаются отсылки к фильмам. Узнаваемые кабины фур, тело человека, лицом очень сильно напоминающего актёра Роберта Патрика и, конечно, сцена с командиром сопротивления, которая практически полностью идентична сцене из второго фильма - настолько сильно радуют глаз, что прощаешь игре очень многое. В такие моменты понимаешь, что представленная игра, по-хорошему, должна была быть фильмом - окончанием трилогии о борьбе человечества с вышедшим из-под контроля ИИ. И это было бы очень логичное и, по субьективному мнению, правильное решение. Но, увы, достойные фильмы по этой франшизе закончились ещё на втором фильме, всё, что вышло после - паразитирование на имени. Спасибо разработчикам за подаренные положительные эмоции. P.S. Подытоживая, если убрать из игры всё элементы, характерные для франшизы, перерисовать роботов, по-другому назвать, заменить на другой саундтрек, убрать узнаваемые звуки плазменного оружия и в таком виде продать - однозначно не рекомендуется к покупке. Для всех тех, кому близки первые два фильма, кто помнит многие сцены из них, смотрел документальные фильмы о создании этих фильмов - игра подарит очень много положительных ощущений. Но надо понимать, что игра очень линейная и совсем не подлежит отыгрышу во второй раз. За одно прохождение можно легко получить все достижения и получить хорошую концовку. Что уж, у нашего героя в эпоху апокалипсиса секса оказывается больше, чем у игрока в относительно беззаботное и сытное нынешнее время, так что для любителей \"по-горячее\" перед непосредственным прохождением есть возможность ознакомиться с руководствами сообщества и поставить соответствующие фиксы, чтобы увидеть, что разработчики не поленились нарисовать действительно обнажённых персонажей. Мелочь, а приятно.", "appid": "954740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049226015", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594900800.0} {"text": "╔════ ೋღ☃ღೋ ════╗ ||---------------------------|| || ~~~~~~ Here lies ~~~~~~|| || ~~~~~~ my R Key~~~~~~|| ||---------------------------|| || ~~~~~ 2015 - 2016~~~~|| ||---------------------------|| ╚════ ೋღ☃ღೋ ════╝ Rest In Peace﻿", "appid": "274170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118789339", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": "28", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1464868800.0} {"text": "Я поддерживаю Я", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198247739780", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1585569600.0} {"text": "this game is awesome you are bored play this game you are tired play this are you angry pffft play this masterpiece youll be just fine AND THE MvM is AWESOME <3 <3 :3", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198286166121", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544702400.0} {"text": "good game", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198805649552", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572004800.0} {"text": "POG CHAMP", "appid": "732690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198247807280", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581595200.0} {"text": "一天11小时三线通关。先说一下总体感觉吧。我也好久没认真写评测了。同样本评测不含有任何剧透成分，放心阅读。 故事写得非常棒。一个好的剧本可以使一部作品从开始就成功了一大半。如果近年来国产谍战电视剧和抗日电视剧能做到这个剧本一半的水平都不至于让我三年没看过电视。故事铺垫，反转，伏笔，回收做的很足，让人充满欣喜与惊讶并代入其中。 全篇故事主要结局一共有三大个，分别是红色芳华，美丽新世界，东瀛扶桑。 也是全篇大结局最快最短的结局，很是让人难受。但剧情设计也过于仓促，让人通关后感觉不是很舒服。 不知道为什么我竟然很喜欢这个结局路线的故事，觉得特别真实，真实的让人心疼又不得不认同的感觉。孤独凄凉又无可奈何，我们都没有回头的路了。不知道为什么，看到男主在官场沉沦，在桌子上被一瓶瓶劝酒的时候，我比看任何一条线的都想哭。 和众多分线游戏一样，要想达到这个结局也需要你在整个故事里做出非常多的选择前提，非常不容易的得到这个结局故事。在这个结局故事里所有的人都有了归宿，当然也包括你自己，尤其是最后三线伏笔的回收，让人在最后终章有一种又畅快，酣畅淋漓又倍感欣慰的感觉。从序章开始到芳华结尾，是真正一个荡气回肠的故事，连贯稳定，让人喜欢。 --------------------------------------------- 游戏机制方面上。整个游戏宣传的是互动电影模式，但我心目中的互动电影其实是像《夜班》那种感觉的纯播片演绎。本作其实运用的是大量定帧来串联剧情，总播片数也就在十以内吧，不过画面清晰度还是很高的。再加上三线故事线的设计，所以我觉得这个作品倒是可以定义为“比较新颖的谍战题材Galgame” 游戏本地是没有任何视频内容的，你下载下来就是一个纯粹的播放器，所有内容都要联机实时播放。我不知道这是纯粹为了防盗版还是什么原因，总觉得是个画蛇添足没有意义的行为。因为官方提供的服务器实在是太烂了，500M的带宽速度只要在线人数超过一万绝对要卡。玩到最后1.5W人在线的时候几乎三秒一卡，更狗血的是因为游戏本身内容是定格镜头，所以多数的时候我竟然不知道自己卡了没卡，只能靠字幕动没动去分辨，实在是太影响游戏体验了。 再说一点就是也许制作者想特别凸显潜伏任务的不容易与危险，所以游戏过程中有相当相当多的选择会让你直接Game Over。我不知道设计这样过多的死亡路线是不是好事，但实际体验下来是会有明显拆散剧情的表现。你会经历大量的失败与死亡，然后拉出故事线，重新再选，再拉，再选。这样的过程在紧张的剧情氛围里实在是太破坏玩家的感情调动了。不过这也是双刃剑吧，因为在最后达成大团圆结局后，我还的确因为这一路自己参与其中的艰苦感觉到了革命潜伏的不容易和坚信啊，哈哈。我到是希望制作组能做一个机制，可以让玩家通关后自己一口气完成所有选择再连续的把播片放一遍，让我连贯的重新体验一下剧情 另外对于之前wegame和steam版本闹得那个事我到没觉得有什么，我也不是玻璃心，优秀品质够，自己选的平台自己认了呗。 最后通关了说点俏皮和题外话的吧。 1，\t男主演技全程在线，很棒！超棒！这个一定要单独拉出来夸一下。 2，\t庄晓曼妆画得真的好看！衣服搭配的也棒！不愧是成为了一票玩家心目中的正宫啊。 3，\t如果啊，真的有那么一天你不小心穿越了，成为了潜伏的卧底，我就告诫你一句话。NPC给你的道具，千万到通关前都一个别扔。一个刀片从头用到尾，我是服气的。 4，\t我一直坚定的认为。牺牲，一定要是当局者的觉悟，而不是局外人的悲命。 5，可能一开始被送上延安的火车，去边区教书才是最好的结局吧。但若不是这样的沉沦，挣扎，妥协，反抗，我又怎么能够遇见如此多彩的你们呢。 最后嘛。用我才买的，印象超深的。英雄联盟中蕾欧娜日冕皮肤里的一句特殊语音结尾吧。", "appid": "998940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263267436", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1552046400.0} {"text": "有繁中 就給讚", "appid": "1250650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198373307080", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585483200.0} {"text": "I've been playing this games for years now and despite some balance issues wich get fixed here and there the game is just great ! It's an action filled 2D Moba where the team effort and strategy gets you the win, you can only play as a team of 3 people and against a team of 3 but the many maps, characters and playstyles each of them can have makes each team and match unique ! The game has only one large flaw... there's no one playing it ! The devs had to choose between a bad matchmaking (you get to play against way better player then you because no one else with your level is playing at the moment) or make you wait up to 6 minutes to launch the game... I don't care about waiting because I get to do a lot of stuff I wouldn't be doing if there was no restriction but many people do care about that and stop playing because of this issue... People leave because of this matchmaking but there can not be any good matchmaking if no one is playing ! It's a loophole the game has been struggling in since years ! The game is free so please do me a favor, if you like the game just talk about it to friends so we get more players to play !", "appid": "204300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198188732518", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530532800.0} {"text": "Don't worry about the virus. Life is temporary, DooM is ETERNAL!", "appid": "782330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198287807449", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584705600.0} {"text": "Wow! Simply delightful. Back in the 80s when people started talking about games as a story I was like, 'What story? Aliens march down screen, I shoot them, End of story.' 1/3 game, 1/3 story, 1/3 experience. All good.", "appid": "378610", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010657809", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508155200.0} {"text": "this is better than vodka", "appid": "38410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198277086199", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "14", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485086400.0} {"text": "Это классика, и добавить тут нечего.", "appid": "289070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036363731", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543147200.0} {"text": "Nic dodać,nic ująć poprostu zajebista gra!", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198283051221", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1478952000.0} {"text": "Çok güzel", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198362017974", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498651200.0} {"text": "pc kasiy ama", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198211087319", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574510400.0} {"text": "Fajna wyścigowa gierka idzie sie pośmiać ze znajomymi.", "appid": "44350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198244933314", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553342400.0} {"text": "Класс", "appid": "17520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198230030460", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1534852800.0} {"text": "Similasyoncuyum moruq", "appid": "258760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198328365151", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1547899200.0} {"text": "𝒀𝒆𝒔, 𝒉𝒐𝒏𝒆𝒚.", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143530292", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501156800.0} {"text": "SimCity and all the other city building games can go suck it because this game sets a whole new standard", "appid": "242920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198059181038", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1392724800.0} {"text": "Самобытная, с туговатым порогом вхождения, но весьма годная!", "appid": "582010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080093695", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575288000.0} {"text": "It's great to be back on Aincrad. Get your NerveGear on and let's hop into this great adventure ♥ I love the game, it's fun to feel like you are inside SAO. The Boss fights are badass, the dialogues are funny and the gameplay on the xbox controller is great. But get ready to spend a lot of time on this game. This is the kind of game that sucks you in for hours and you look out your window and it's nightime already. Haha. It's also great to be able to get Kirito and Asuna together. Best couple ever! The only weird part is Leafa and Sinnon being in the game. The rest is just amazing.", "appid": "638650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198028934604", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585656000.0} {"text": "Muito bom o Game!!! Geralmente n gosto muito de sthelf mais esse eu gostei de mais... boa ação, bons gráficos, jogabilidade e dublagem, embora a história seja meio despeça e meio ruim no meu gosto ainda sim da para se divertir muito... único ponto ruim mesmo é q tem pouca gente no coop e online por enquanto mais ainda acha... recomendo muito!!", "appid": "235600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198127017914", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1420113600.0} {"text": "Guns don't kill people. 47 does.", "appid": "236870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013579069", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603281600.0} {"text": "Это действительно хорошая игра, но таки она довольно сложная.", "appid": "979160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198391057982", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563451200.0} {"text": "goood play", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198840123639", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529064000.0} {"text": "its fun to play even if your not a furry", "appid": "778700", "steamid": "profiles/76561199052215326", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590235200.0} {"text": "Before Mass Effect, there was KOTOR. Definitely a great purchase even by todays standards.", "appid": "32370", "steamid": "profiles/76561197960270969", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1342094400.0} {"text": "kesinlikle oynamanız gereken bir oyun 10/10", "appid": "620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047800827", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446120000.0} {"text": "I don't quite understand why this game gets so much hate; sure it's not a \"game\" in the traditional sense and there's not much actual \"gameplay\" involved, but have people forgotten the FMV games back in 90s? If anything, FMV adventures come as close as it gets to classic old-school games because the earliest adventure games actually used to be like this. So basically, the entire game consists of full-motion videos (a.k.a. movies) with real actors in them and you're given a few choices on how to advance the plot. Let me start by pointing out that most of the wrong choices are pure comedy gold. Sure, it's cringy and weird but it's one of those cases that \"it's so bad it's almost good\". I just couldn't stop laughing after watching some of the scenes play out after making the blatant wrong choice. There's also a commentary on every choice after the scene is over which actually does a pretty decent job of explaining what you did right or wrong. Sure, you can't just learn how to score dates in real life from playing a scripted video game but that's not the point. At least, that wasn't the point for me. If you go into this expecting to become a dating guru, you'd probably be disappointed but if you treat it as a comedy, you could have a great time laughing at the situations and dialog. Another criticism that I often see is that this game provides false information about dating, that is not true at all. I mean, there aren't any super secret mystical magic words that will instantly get you any girl in this game or any other game (because no such thing exists in the real world) but it does give you some basic understanding of how things work. For example, it does tell you that you should always treat women with respect even if they're rude to you. Again, expect comedy not a tutorial... - Cute girls - Some useful dating advice - Decent production quality - Hilarious dialog, very funny - Good environment and scene variety - The only gameplay element is dialog choices - Cringy presentation - Somewhat weak acting - Rather poor soundtrack - The scenes occasionally cut off abruptly - There's a small delay before you can skip a scene 6.75/10 - Decent Super Seducer is a genuinely hilarious work of comedy which does provide some very basic and trivial dating advice. It's a FMV adventure with the only gameplay element being dialog choices. Acting has room for improvement but some of the dialog is extremely funny. Overall, I'd recommend trying it out but expect a comedy movie (not an actual dating sim).", "appid": "695920", "steamid": "profiles/76561197963259080", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549972800.0} {"text": "Well after 145+ hours I guess it's time to write a review. I picked up this game on impulse for $7.99, thought it would be fun to mess around with a friend of mine in co-op. Somehow that turned into several months of addiction. The game has decent graphics for being an indi devoloped game (it runs on unreal engine 4), music is fitting and doesn't get annoying. One thing to note is the performance can be a bit jumpy, especially in online co-op, I can see 155 fps one second and 45 the next, but overall doesn't hurt playability in my opinion. The maps are procedurally generated each time you play and are random. The enemy spawns are dictated by your item pick ups which makes for some intense sitiuations. If you're low on ammo, do you grab that box of pistol ammo and risk some high level spawns or try to melee to save ammo? After each game you are awarded currency called \"karma\". You spend karm leveling up your gear, called \"trinkets\". The addiction comes from once you start being able to hunt for demon chests which have the random high level trinkets in them that make your character very powerful. It's a bit like Diablo in that regard. The game also has a small dedicated community that are awesome to play with and willing to help new players get into the game. After a while single player gets boring but co-op is where the fun is! Just be prepared to die a lot, the game is pretty unforgiving on the higher dfifficulties. The games creator, Blue actively reads the forums and continues to take suggestions on ways to improve the game with future updates. Overall, I highly recomend Unloved if you like fast paced FPS's. Special shout out to Zod, sobored3440, Moki, Linkowiezi, JIm, Godsdoomer, and tendersurrender. Playing with those guys is a blast, don't hesistate to jump into one of their games if you see them!", "appid": "321270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198175178995", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487246400.0} {"text": "В самолете датчиков меньше", "appid": "394360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198198525715", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582804800.0} {"text": "bom jogo", "appid": "113200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198332379920", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "ok", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198291650494", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "말해뭐해..", "appid": "333600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198361503004", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576929600.0} {"text": "Was REALLY surprised that they were giving this away for free. I would have been more than happy to pay full price for this, it still holds up even today.", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198962505943", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586088000.0} {"text": "Норм", "appid": "555440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198931641561", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Paradox tired of its niche status and wants to be major publisher specializing in strategies. All kind of strategies. They started with the powerful collaboration and then continue with destroying region prices on their games, like most of the big boys do. Yeah, let's make it about politics. It’s not like bullying the way through their loyal community is the new tactic for Paradox. Crazy DLC politic is the great example. But what’s more important is what let them do anything they want and it’s their card of uniqueness. You won’t find any alternatives to paradox games. But you won’t find anything like Eugene’s game either, that’s why SD might be so important to paradox. Eugene delivered solid gameplay with an uncanny similarity to their Wargame Series. The main feature is the frontline which moves with the units. Neat idea on the surface turns out to be more of a gimmick. Even so, Eugene says that’s the main part of gameplay, in the end, it didn’t really change it, but make it more noob-friendly. And this is the main theme of SD. Wargame series are well known for its total unfriendliness toward new players, the game doesn’t have a proper tutorial, it got 2000+ units you better learn (how they perform and even looks). So they decide to cut the corners. Now we got 400 units, fewer stats for each unit, \"autodeckcreator\", we lost few tactics; like helicopter rush (no one would miss it, but still helicopters gave more tactical choices), we cannot get around and strike opponent to the back (because frontline shows there we got units, except recon infantry). Tactical choices reduced to constant push-build defense line-push/retreat. Maps became wider and units became sooo much slower, which is make sense but still might be frustrating. People who wished the infantry would be the kings of the Steal division (spoiler alert it doesn’t) would find themselves disappointed. Roles didn’t switch, dynamic didn’t change drastically, artillery became more powerful than ever. Even new stress system feels just like a light touch. Paradox is… that game is still semi-realistic and really complex for the newcomers, while wargame veterans will get “less of the same”. I think I appreciate the gentle approach, no one want’s to learn everything from the scratch, but at the same time, I can’t find anything that justifies the transfer from Red Dragon to Steel Division. Surprisingly enough SD doesn’t look as good as you might expect, models look shabbier than their brothers from Wargame DLCs. But animation became smoother; infantry doesn’t slide through the hills like they used to do. Anyway, I doubt you would notice it during the game, cause all you need to see is pictograms of your units on the whole wide map. The best new thing is the circle which allows you see how much vision each point on the map will give to you units, that’s what Red Dragon surely missed. Steal division doesn’t feel like a step back, more like “confident mudding-through”.", "appid": "572410", "steamid": "profiles/76561197974517652", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495454400.0} {"text": "HYPERCHARGE: Unboxed, Digital Cybercherries ekibi tarafından geliştiren eğlenceli odaklı bir FPS oyunu. Oyunda oyuncak olarak oynuyor, diğer oyuncaklara karşı mücadele veriyoruz...", "appid": "523660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148654358", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1551355200.0} {"text": "AMAZING GAME, CUSTOMIZE WEAPONS, RIFLES, ROCKET LAUNCHERS, AND DESTROY, SIMILIAR TO TEAM FORTRESS 2 BUT WAY BETTER. GIVE IT A TRY ITS FREE!", "appid": "208090", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981243674", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1392033600.0} {"text": "Fun with friends.", "appid": "386940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198067494486", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "Bruh", "appid": "203770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198216564712", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571659200.0} {"text": "Awsome :3 Game :)", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198199983191", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1473508800.0} {"text": "You'd best be glad you're single(Jingle jangle), because this game will suck your time dry like other games suck your wallet dry. Wait for the ~3-5 times a year sale that brings all(except 4) Fallout games down to $2.50 in USD. That sale is one of the best deals you can make, even if you have [Barter 100]. YOu wiLL NOt REGREt buYINg thIs gaMe uNLEsS YoU ValUE fReE TimE fOr aNYTHinG BUt THIs (aLsO You gET shOT in the FaCE RIGHT AT the start, and IT'S PART OF THE STORY. Tell me another game that does that.)", "appid": "22380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198283982364", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1507032000.0} {"text": "Excelente juego , muy entretenido , la jugabilidad es muy buena y los graficos estan bien !! Esperando la proxima entrega", "appid": "391220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045762640", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1534420800.0} {"text": "atmosfer güzel build olayları güzel optimizasyon çöp şu anda inş düzelir *güncelliyorum* 25.04.19 oyun son güncelleme olan alpha 13 güncellemesinden sonra değişti -optimizasyon sıkıntıları çözülüyor fps artışı çok iyi -doğa zenginleşti hayvanlar arttı -yeni başlayanlar için kolaylıklar geldi ŞU ANDA BU OYUN ALINIR İNCELEMELERE BAKIYORSANIZ DA ALPHA 13 GÜNCELLEMESİNDEN SONRAKİ İNCELEMELERE BAKIN LIKE THIS.", "appid": "656240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198289280335", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "40", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1549022400.0} {"text": "Рейдят 24/7, убивают, а так игра топ)", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198280326332", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535371200.0} {"text": "Finaly!!!", "appid": "55230", "steamid": "profiles/76561197960410538", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1359115200.0} {"text": "Gr8 b8 m8 I r8 8/8", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198041614814", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458475200.0} {"text": "<3", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198431657407", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589630400.0} {"text": "Nice teaser for Life is Strange 2. Nice music and gameplay, but short.", "appid": "845070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198175633183", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530532800.0} {"text": "Что можно сказать о \"Resident Evil 2: Remake\"? Игра отличная, сюжет очень интересен. Раньше я не был знаком со вселенной RE в целом, но пройдя эту игру то понял что многое потерял, ведь сама история, повествование сделано на высшем уровне! Мне даже захотелось пройти все части этой франшизы, что собственно я и сделаю! Если вы вдруг задумываетесь над приобретением игры, то смело рекомендую к покупке! Не пожалеете явно! 10/10", "appid": "883710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198195447306", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584792000.0} {"text": "2007년의 GOTY 수상작인 바이오쇼크 이 게임은 과거 미국의 건물 디자인을 잘 살린 것 같다. 게임의 사운드트랙도 괜찮고 지도를 보면서 구석구석 탐색하도록 유도함. 아쉽다. 이름만 리마스터고 그래픽이 전체적으로 하향되어서 게임 플레이 내내 내 눈을 즐겁게 해준 리마스터가 출시되어서 판매를 중단했다니... 명작이라고 해서 단점이 없는 건 아닌데 특히 이 게임은 다른 게임에 비해서 멀미 유발이 심한 편임 참고: EAX 5.0을 사용하려면 EAX 5.0을 지원하는 Creative社 사운드 블라스터 계열의 사운드 카드가 필요함", "appid": "7670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198293223631", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603627200.0} {"text": "Best MK so far,yet not very different than MKX and I wish they had Shinnok,Quan chi and at least 1 robot(beside frost) but overall it's worth it", "appid": "976310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081230013", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586174400.0} {"text": "What I like of the game is that the game is utterly bonkerly massive and the great skill system What I don't like is how the story is written as you're the chosen one, but everyone is also the chosen one. Especially in main story quest with the epic cutscene played out and player are jumping like a madman around NPC. I wish you can just turn off seeing other player in this game, really break the immersion for me", "appid": "306130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075533241", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1560686400.0} {"text": "Отличная игра! Повествование сюжета просто супер:)", "appid": "493900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198015913670", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542628800.0} {"text": "Juegazo. lo unico que deberian reveer es la politica de Smurfs y lo horrible que es el matchmaking en cuanto a como elige contrincantes", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198328468857", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543924800.0} {"text": "Joguei por muito tempo porem tudo no jogo é pago e temporario, isso me deixa bem triste para um jogo mas joguei por mais de 150 hrs e nao me arrependo por isso Adorei jogabilidade Adorei as armas (principalmente)", "appid": "273110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198269119083", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1500379200.0} {"text": "Советую игра, почти готова.", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561197979882589", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1507204800.0} {"text": "Ne pas pouvoir se déguiser en femme est tellement dommage, toutefois c'est déjà très drôle ! Du génie !", "appid": "236870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198058520931", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Counter-Strike: Russian Offensive", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009245890", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1425816000.0} {"text": "wie beklommt man die neu map", "appid": "209650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009227547", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1429531200.0} {"text": "sanırsam türünün lideri", "appid": "227300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118605115", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "36", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "gigjghjgjg", "appid": "9480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198352250985", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498132800.0} {"text": "They are definitely on the right track here. I like the new combat system althought it needs improving. HITBOXES? WHAT ARE THOSE?! It invokes the old one with it's simplicity to learn but hard to master nature. The blocking system requires the player to be active in combat and not just swing at the enemy and hope for the best. I say keep it. The graphics need more work. Why is everything so... \"shiny\"? Why the text on the interface is so flurry? I have nothing against the music. It fits the tone and brings back memories of the first Gothic ^_^ Just one thing... make it so the music changes into a dynamic theme when the actual combat starts. It shouldn't change just because my character has his sword pulled out. Now let's talk about the writing... It needs more work. Especially for the Nameless Hero. The guy shouldn't be so chatty outside of the actual dialogues. He should be a man of action not words. Unless it's some critical info don't make him \"talk to himself\" it's pointless and annoying. \"Worst prison ever\" was one of the cringiest things I've heard this year -_- Diego sounded forced and artificial in his speeches. Like a father that explains life to his kid. Was that the intent? I don't think a guy like Diego should treat a rookie like a kid but like someone who has potencial. I didn't felt that when he spoke with the Nameless. Keep up the good work guys! ^_^ This teaser has a big potencial! Bring back the legend from my childhood! Good luck!", "appid": "950670", "steamid": "profiles/76561197991642616", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577275200.0} {"text": "Muito bom principalmente em servidores modificados ! Costumava jogar apenas em servidores normais, porém com indicação de amigos encontrei um servidor muito bom, modificado que comecei a jogar sempre, porém foi alterado toda a estrutura do servidor, não ficou do meu agrado e não estou mais jogando lá. Ótimo jogo, recomendado. :D", "appid": "1250", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085056521", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "23", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1433160000.0} {"text": "A pesara de solo haber jugado el episodio 1 he podido ver que es un juego apasionante, completamente original en su desarrollo y con una carga emocional poco habitual en los juegos actuales. MUY RECOMENDABLE!", "appid": "319630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093515602", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1451217600.0} {"text": "четка", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561197977974719", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543147200.0} {"text": "In this game you will encounter alot of crazy ♥♥♥♥ such as: Pedobear's Cousin A Street Fighter Character on steroids A otaku nerd Chihiro I'd still hit it. A Miles Edgeworth wishes he was Sasuke wannabe. A Forgotten Dragonball character. The girl you like You and many more! So if you like games like 999 and ace attorney and be like \"wtf is going on this entire game\"You will love this one.", "appid": "413410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087349666", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515412800.0} {"text": "Ich empfehle dieses Spiel eingeschränkt! Mein Kumpel und ich sind mit falschen Voraussetzungen an dieses Spiel ran gegangen. Wir dachten das der Fokus auf den Rätseln liegt, wir also gefordert werden. Außerdem das wir stark als Team arbeiten müssen. Wenn man vorab aber weiß das der Gedanke der Entwickler darauf gemünzt war, das Menschen die dieses Spiel zusammen erleben, einfach eine angenehme Zeit zusammen haben sollen, sieht das ganze schon wieder anders aus. (Natürlich soll zusammen zocken, IMMER eine angenehme Zeit sein :D ) Was gemeint ist, ist das die Rätsel mit Absicht einfach gehalten sind, die Atmosphäre eher eine Rolle spielen soll und die Geschichte gemeinsam zu erleben. Hält man sich das vorher vor Augen, dann wird man sicherlich nicht enttäuscht.", "appid": "790740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198029114530", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591531200.0} {"text": "Всем привет! Игра просто полный капец! Я игры такого вида не очень предпочитаю, но, у меня эмоции зашкаливают, решил поиграть чуток просто моментально затянуло!!! Всё меня устраивает : графика, интерфейс, озвучка. Плюсы игры : -Достижения Steam -Коллекционные карточки -Стоимость26 рублей(а сейчас скидка 15 рублей), просто берём и раскупаем! -Доступность на слабейшем ПК РЕКОМЕНДУЮ!!!!", "appid": "657740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198015860100", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1500465600.0} {"text": "good game", "appid": "700330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198336902624", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579003200.0} {"text": "Не советую играть людям со слабой психикой)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198369936535", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542974400.0} {"text": "ля", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198408448114", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593086400.0} {"text": "Aconselho sim a comprar este jogo , da muito vicio se jogarem com seus colegas , melhor jogo de Hunger Games", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198258392453", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1504785600.0} {"text": "GGEZ", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198282142302", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "it's good for an indie game.", "appid": "489520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168884671", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1484222400.0} {"text": "I do not know about you, but I like to play Cs: s. A year game. Cheaters are not few, but not many. Play and enjoy .", "appid": "240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198315253757", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "is a well designed puzzle game in the vein of Sokoban (or rather of Steam’s series), featuring 62 very enjoyable levels. With its charming graphics and easy mechanics, it’s pretty impossible not to love it. Sly is a little green slime that you need to slide around the map in order to collect the mushrooms that are located on specific tiles. While in Sokoban games you have to move the cubes to a certain target point, here the only movable element is the cute square-shaped slime: using the mouse you can make it slide in one of the 4 main directions so that it bounces off walls or off other cubes, until it reaches the mushroom. The innovation that adds to some of the levels is a multi-layered, three-dimensional structure: you can naturally descend from the current layer to the one blow and you can climb up one layer by using certain tiles that push you back up. Furthermore, there are also specific tiles that act like switches for these elevators and these tiles must be activated a certain number of times until they reach their correct position. These few simple mechanics combine slowly into increasingly complex levels, but the difficulty always remains pretty casual. You will surely need to try some levels multiple times until you figure out the correct order of movements and sliding directions, but it’s a given that you will not get frustrated by any of these levels. For a mere $2, I’d say that this little game is well worth the price, assuming that you don’t mind the fact that it’s quite short (around 1h, depending on your skills) and that it might leave you wanting for more levels. It comes with a very nice soundtrack and Steam achievements triggered for each level.", "appid": "1387030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063574735", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "19", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600776000.0} {"text": "Good DLC!", "appid": "1245150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198291103303", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598356800.0} {"text": "NICE GAME!", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198924939975", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558699200.0} {"text": "Рекомендую. Прям как в старые добрые времена, только в ТРИ ДЭ! Главное не стреляйте в бабаку, вы же не хабаровские живодёрки? Стоит своих денег.", "appid": "746510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010646448", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "50", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575547200.0} {"text": "This game is a legend.", "appid": "698780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198020628541", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514030400.0} {"text": "Why am I writing this,I could be playing 700 different games at this moment,all of them inside this game,and that's what makes it good. The game is still good but I had to update my review so here you go lmao returning to this review to update it one more year and it sounds cringy as ♥♥♥♥ lmao", "appid": "4000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198101966002", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "Good game. Make me spent half of my life hahaha", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095124286", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1387454400.0} {"text": "Bu oyunu oynuynca Cüneyt arkın Ve Kara murat oluyorsunuz .. 😊", "appid": "219640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198139131131", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1557230400.0} {"text": "This game is AWESOME! if you like this type of game its a hidden gem... best of all it cost me £0.39!!!!", "appid": "281920", "steamid": "profiles/76561199014303827", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579262400.0} {"text": "dgdf", "appid": "222880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198825576437", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535112000.0} {"text": "Human: Fall Flat é um jogo de puzzle onde você pode jogar sozinho ou com amigos! Os gráficos do jogo são bem bonitos, parecendo muito com os de Gang Beasts, mas não se engane, são dois jogos completamente diferentes. Esse é o tipo de jogo que é melhor se jogar com amigos. O jogo tem alguns bugs por não estar pronto ainda. (Pelomenos não está pronto no dia que estou fazendo essa análise). Os puzzles são bons e tiram algum tempo seu para serem resolvidos, as vezes por você não saber o que precisa fazer, mas acredite: O maior desafio do jogo são os controles. Não existe história em Human: Fall Flat, então não sabemos o porquê de estarmos fazendo tudo isso. Resumindo: HFF é um jogo bonito, desafiador, e muito engraçado, mas você so irá ter a experiência completa se jogar com amigos.", "appid": "477160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198078203289", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530273600.0} {"text": "it's ok i guess", "appid": "286940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198001124495", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "13", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1437048000.0} {"text": "nicw", "appid": "225260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198357514093", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514289600.0} {"text": "Bought a Vita just to play this and then used it as a paper weight. 10/10", "appid": "1113000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082055811", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594900800.0} {"text": "Loved it, abslutely loved it Pros: + Awesome Story with a lot of plot twists + Likeable Characters + Tons of areas and content + LOTS of weapons + A mouthful of references to other games/pop culture + Godly Co-oop Mode + Fairly balanced + Lots of playstyles + Around 6 characters, and they arent a copypaste of the other + Fun overall + Lots of variety in equipment Cons: - Annoying Leveling system - Enemy AI isn't the best at times - Enemy AI can screw you over , or getting some hits on you that'll make you doubt how the hell did he even got the accuracy - Some skills are completely broken and should get a fix - If you play with someone thats broken, its going to contrast a lot - Physics, although they are good, will sometimes make you think what the shaite were the devs thinking - After a long while it may get repetitive - NOT ALL THE DLC'S ARE AVAILABLE IN THE GOTY - Some characters are debaitably better than others -Some pieces of gear, although rare, quite broken 86/100 Loved the experience i had with this game", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198127123289", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "Underrated Games!", "appid": "265300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121220575", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600516800.0} {"text": "Really good, looking forward for more contents from the devs", "appid": "1122050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198397562804", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1572523200.0} {"text": "Fun game Really hard at times makes you rage when your players makes silly mistakes against friends but overall a really good game", "appid": "482730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196910907", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498824000.0} {"text": "WO FK", "appid": "391720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198302210440", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576929600.0} {"text": "Good simulator, lots of good games. It takes about an hour to figure out the interface, but when you know how to deal with it it works really well. Lots of great mods make it possible to play Arkham Horror, Uno, Mahjong or whatever you want, just check the workshop and see if your favorite board game is there (it probably is). Saves you the hassle of setting everything up and putting it back in the box, as well as playing with people that you can't meet in person. The bugs are manageable, some can be annoying but the same can be said about dropping a token or a die on the floor irl!", "appid": "286160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003950705", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1421064000.0} {"text": "Одна из самых активных игр, которую я запускаю поиграть часами. В основном играю за Маньяков, особенно за Аню) Что бы понять и научится играть, нужно потратить не мало десятков часов из своей жизни. Но это того стоит, что бы получать удовольствие от игры. Самое тяжелое что могу выделить по своему мнению, это то, что нужно выкачать на свой выбор разных Маньяков или Выживших для улучшения способностей. Так же, часто горит жопа из за группы выживших которые играют в месте. Иногда с трудом удается сделать -1. Ну а так, в целом всем рекомендую. Веселая игрушка)))", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198444480187", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566907200.0} {"text": "Jogo dos mucânicos do aço", "appid": "645630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095142454", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "Gioco della Madonaaa... Tutto Estremamente positivo!", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198089880980", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1430136000.0} {"text": "Nice Game", "appid": "4000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198283331168", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532174400.0} {"text": "Шедевр, не поспоришь. И RTX пригодился))", "appid": "1190460", "steamid": "profiles/76561197994800821", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594728000.0} {"text": "Great game runs well on low end pc", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198397693408", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "Kurczę pieczone", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010890686", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Counter Source: Global Office is a great video game to play on the internet. Personally, I like to play multiplayer more than single player. However, multiplayer is more difficult because the enemies shoot back. I think they should nerf the sniper because people can kill me in one shot even when i buy the helmet! This game is very tough but fun. I heard that the pros warm up before their matches by playing minecraft so that's what I do too.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065375533", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "34", "votes_funny": "27", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1407758400.0} {"text": "Nice.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198102514902", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Stupidly late to the party, but here we go Bought this game back when it released, got a good 55% through it, then just never picked it up again... until a few days ago, and I managed to finish it. ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥, what a game. By far the absolute best VR experience I've ever had (and possibly ever will get). It's incredible quite how immersed you manage to get in this - it's Story-wise, come on, let's not kid ourselves here, it's a fully fledged Half-Life game. The story isn't emotional at all, but it's incredibly riveting. Only a few amount of important characters, with no specific antagonist except for just \"The Combine\" TM, but the intricacy of the HL-universe is enough to get you hooked in. I'd never played another HL game before this, but that really doesn't matter. Gameplay is incredible. Puzzles are original and interesting; not so difficult that you have to be smart to solve them, but they're not total 'gimme's either. Most of them play off the same few mechanical tricks, but in interesting ways that require you to genuinely stop and think about what you're trying to accomplish. In terms of combat, they really hit the nail on the head here. Controls feel natural, even in the heat of battle, and the guns play super well into this. Perfect execution on the items like grenades or medkits. 10/10, best VR game ever", "appid": "546560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198100112667", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602417600.0} {"text": "great game much buy so play very greatness", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070177879", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1389268800.0} {"text": "This is the greatest comeback of gaming history. Other devs need to learn from HG's example. Hello Games is still updating this game. Look at the release date. If you are reluctant , visit", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198103396111", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "Russisch lernen leicht gemacht wusste ich garnicht das Valve jez auch spachkurse macht", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198002022808", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1418731200.0} {"text": "bruh", "appid": "496460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198368486822", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580126400.0} {"text": "It's cool", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198400403494", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586260800.0} {"text": "Piola", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198860344898", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599825600.0} {"text": "--------------------------------------------------------- --------------------------------------------------------- --------------------------------------------------------- Помоги двум братьям посеять бессмысленный хаос и добраться до Мексики... А в целом оценка игре 7 из 10..", "appid": "532210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150178517", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576497600.0} {"text": "Typa podrochit`", "appid": "927890", "steamid": "profiles/76561198873972570", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575028800.0} {"text": "Lara Croft. Namıdiğer Tomb Raider. Crystal Dynamics ve Square Enix tarafından başlatılan ''yeni'' Tomb Raider serisinin ilk oyunu. Peki ilk oyun olarak seriye heyecanlandıran bir yanı var mı? Tomb Raider, 2013 yapımı bir oyun ve oyunun kontrolleri ve grafiklerinin eskimediğini düşünüyorum. Hikayesi oyunun gerçekten çok iyi. Bazılarınıza klişe gibi gelebilir ama bunu takacağınızı zannetmiyorum. Tomb Raider sizi daha ilk dakikalardan itibaren içine çekmeyi beceriyor. Hikayenin gidişatını merak ediyorsunuz. Oynanış deseniz o da gayet iyi. Sahip olduğumuz silahların kullanımı gayet rahat ancak dümdüz yürürken bazen nedenini anlayamadığım bir şekilde kontroller sapıtıyor. Nadiren olsa da bu durum canınızı sıkabiliyor. Klavye ve mouse ile oynadığımı belirteyim. Tomb Raider'da keşfedebileceğiniz mezarlar, hikayeyi anlamaya yardımcı olan yazılar, eskiden kalma objeler dolu. Bir de ''challenge'' dediğimiz aktiviteler var. Oyunun ana hikayesini bitirdikten sonra bile bunları bulmak için oynanabilir. Ayrıca oyundaki upgrade sistemini de beğendiğimi rahatlıkla söyleyebilirim.Grafikler de 2013 yapımı bir oyuna göre çok iyi. Size müthiş manzaralar sunuyor. Tomb Raider'da bir de online mod bulunuyor ama bu kadar yıl sonra oyuncu bulabilir misiniz bilemem :) Kısacası oyunu indirimli/indirimsiz fark etmez(Tabi indirimde almanızı tavsiye ederim). Alın oynayın. Çünkü gerçekten çok güzel. Son olarak olsa daha iyi olurmuş diyeceğim bir şey var: Keşke mezar keşfetme mekaniği oyunda daha fazla yer bulsaymış kendine! ARTILAR -Merak uyandırıcı hikaye -Muazzam detaylar -Çıkış dönemine göre müthiş grafikler -Upgrade sistemleri EKSİLER -Bazı bug'lar -Kontroller arada sapıtıyor -Nadiren de olsa can sıkan optimizasyon problemi - Keşke mezar keşfetme mekaniği daha fazla yer alsaymış NOT 93/100", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198403236844", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544702400.0} {"text": "Muito bom", "appid": "389570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198218873075", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472644800.0} {"text": "Could someone help me? I have this game on my account but I don't find the ark: survival evolved. How come I don't have it in my library? Pleas help me.", "appid": "407530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198195379934", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1502971200.0} {"text": "Took 11 hours to complete the 1st season on normal difficulties so not worth the 50€ at the current state. Trying to complete all mission on higher difficulties is hard since cant find any players for them. Gameplay itself is pretty good and fun.", "appid": "717690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095183544", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542024000.0} {"text": "This is a strategy game, but also a free roam lone wolf type of game as well which is awesome. Very fun game. Very much recommend! :) :hunter0:", "appid": "594650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198180129645", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575288000.0} {"text": "Pretty average shooter but the AI can see you through solid objects.", "appid": "17300", "steamid": "profiles/76561197984297974", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591704000.0} {"text": "Лучший мультиплеер", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198078508695", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403265600.0} {"text": "é deiz barra deiz mermão História ótima, personagens bem feitos (Chumbucket will live forevah my friend), trilha sonora bem boa e os fazedores de fumo parecem ter vindo do intestino do satanas :)", "appid": "234140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093884714", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497182400.0} {"text": "100% fare and square", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118706041", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592913600.0} {"text": "Amazing game campaing feels like doom but just more epic story is good athmosphere is amazing theres lot of content in multiplayer and lot of customize fun vechiles and maps are fast paced and are like just better cod/bf maps and game has competive mod