_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1493380800.0} {"text": "ก็ดี", "appid": "1238810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073225460", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602590400.0} {"text": "\"Unstable connection with the Mastermind (room host)\" aka \"matchmaking-waiting-simulator\". Nice game beaten by crappy technical state...", "appid": "952070", "steamid": "profiles/76561197968357064", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586520000.0} {"text": "Das Spiel ist lagweilig hat sich nicht gelohnt zu kaufen.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096091934", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1423915200.0} {"text": "Cool and challenging game. It's like being in an apocalypse.", "appid": "251570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047932072", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1603022400.0} {"text": "El juego logra al fin unir a 2 generos completamente diferentes el rpg y los fps dando un juego mas divertido que los juegos anuales de cod y los rpg de sistemas aburridos de combate. En definitiva es buen juego.", "appid": "8980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198401400872", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577793600.0} {"text": "This is puzzle game in which you are the monster. As you unlock various abilities, you can go back and unlock puzzles that were previously unbreachable. I am not really a fan of puzzle games, but this one held my interest to completion. As I was able to complete everything on the first run within five hours, I would not call it a $20 game. If you enjoy horror and puzzles, I would recommend picking up when it goes on sale.", "appid": "953490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010707310", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595678400.0} {"text": "Зашел на сервак,один крутится,другой стреляет хедшоты сквозь стены,другой прыгает и напоследок тот кто попадает всегда в голову.10читеров из 10", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198815438597", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519128000.0} {"text": "very a good game but too much ♥♥♥♥ to do i forgot what to do", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198154473459", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "« De toute façon, il y a une chose que tu dois comprendre : ce n'est plus le pays où on a grandi. Ni celui que tu as quitté il y a 15 ans. Ce pays n'est plus ce qu'il était. Je t'assure. C'est un truc bizarre qui ne sait pas où il va. C'est vrai, c'est pas le paradis, mais on se débrouille et on survit. Je me plains pas. » ; Laurent Cantet, 2015.", "appid": "239030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198133744231", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1514462400.0} {"text": "Great", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198229823320", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1551182400.0} {"text": "Valve в 2004 году уже знали что будет происходить в россии. А мы не воспользовались шансом ещё тогда свергнуть нашего Брина и весь его альянс. Спасибо Valve что хотя бы пытались нам помочь.", "appid": "220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148796299", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543838400.0} {"text": "lol funniest game ever played", "appid": "1368430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198401682384", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602936000.0} {"text": "Атмосфера дикая, всегда хотел поиграть в что-то наподибие такого)", "appid": "648350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198147879854", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528804800.0} {"text": "Great puzzle game! Very challenging but gratifying. Worth buying and playing.", "appid": "893180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060845504", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606132800.0} {"text": "Здесь я узнал,что у меня рак и спид", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198305420513", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1565697600.0} {"text": "When you at office working and you felt bored. Play this game cause no matter how old your pc is or how bad is your office pc is this game will run on it and you play all day at your office when you too bored to do any works.", "appid": "38600", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997262912", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1460376000.0} {"text": "Belgium started a global conflict by invading The Netherlands, allowing France to take over the majority of the Northern Hemisphere.", "appid": "314980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198012196532", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": ":3", "appid": "322330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198104321540", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "Excelente Juegazo Lo jugue en sus origenes y tengo el gusto de volver a jugarmelo en su Remake. 100% Recomendado a todos, sin mas que decir que esperan para obtenerlo. XD", "appid": "952060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198099198079", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589803200.0} {"text": "good game just some information is wrong such as the clownfish it says it is a tro