This game have not glitched on me yet and I have played 40 hours so far. It is anoying though how fast you can die from one blow. But I guess thats why you have all the stealth powers and ability to be invisible lurking in the darkness. When I bought this game, I didn't look when it was published. I usually have a rule not to buy anything older than 2015 even if on sale. But this was very cheap, so I got it and I don't regret it to be honest. I reccomend it to everyone who loves Assassins, however wants to play fantasy instead. Who still has a bit of love for elves and goblins, likes cursing a lot and enjoys when a character can drop an \"f-bomb\" on you here and there. Styx is definately is one of my fav characters nowadays. And its hard to make that list for sure.", "appid": "242640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045682840", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545048000.0} {"text": "I had alot fun in this game :)", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013199771", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "Отлично, для любителей вселенной.", "appid": "214510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198287351760", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571486400.0} {"text": "good game", "appid": "222880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119350316", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1402315200.0} {"text": "first i play when for me no crash until end story. aaarrrgghhh really good game. Graphic 9/9 Story 9/9 Maybe i play again New Game +. Please give more Sony : Bloodborne, Uncharted, Last of us, God Of war, Ghost of Tsushima #JustDream wkwkwkwk", "appid": "1151640", "steamid": "profiles/76561199012297488", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599652800.0} {"text": "ЗАПУС