1198387600576", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594641600.0} {"text": "Каааарточкииии!!!!!!! Нужно больше карточек! ^^ 10 жадных евреев-бизнесменов из 10", "appid": "29800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198152119956", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1438516800.0} {"text": "Amazing, enchanting and immersive. 9/10 ♥ Don't buy this game expecting to have the most amazing gaming experience of your life, it's not Call of Duty, it's no stealth or fighting game. Plug in some earphones and dive into this beautiful, thought-provoking and beautiful world. The only issue I had at all was frames dropping slightly but that's to be expected in some of the high traffic areas when I'm running it on a relatively rubbish laptop. I particularly reccomend this game to anybody who has any sort of anxiety condition or similar, it really does help and at the very least it drags you in and makes quite the lovely distraction.", "appid": "384190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198254879478", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1510142400.0} {"text": "this game is so amazing. I have playeed this for over 3 hours in one sitting and loved every second of it. Even though it has a few glitches like going through the ground when i use the rewind option but apart from that a great solid game!!", "appid": "244930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198157248017", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1481803200.0} {"text": "LOGistICAL is a great, great game. It truly is, and the way it combines pure logical puzzles with fleet management is both unique and brilliant. LOGistICAL: British Isles is a huge stand-alone extension tot he game, giving you the entirety of the UK, plus Eire and the Channel Isles, to deliver to. The basic set up is this: Every town and borough is represented, and every town's citizens have their own needs. You start out with an old banger of a truck, and you order that truck to drive to town B to deliver what town A wants. When you complete the delivery, you get money, so you can buy bigger, better trucks and go about appeasing the population of the entire country, one town at a time. Here's the basic game flow as an example: Town A wants apples. Town B has an orchard, which means the town produces apples as a resource. Town C has fertilizer, which the orchard needs to produce apples. You take the fuel (fertilizer) to the industry (orchard) and wait for it to make the product (apples), at which point you can deliver the apples to town A. Your truck will automatically go back and forth, until the number of apples the town needs is met, at which point the town becomes 'completed', and it's icon on the map goes from black and white to coloured, to reflect that. From now on, the town will never need another delivery. So that's the puzzle side of things. The management side of the game comes from how and when you work on the towns. You see, until a town is completed it will consume the resources you provide it, and so you have to make sure you're assigning enough trucks and over not too great a distance to meet the demand, and finish the town. L: BI features over two-thousand towns to complete, and has dozens of industries like the one I give an example of above, and many require multiple ingredients to complete. To compound the difficulty, there are also roads which will need to be repaired to be able to be used, and quarantine roads which don't allow the transfer of restricted goods via them. And now the inevitable caveat: for everything the game does brilliantly, it obfuscates and behaves obtusely about something else. Even with the tutorial island included in the game (The Isle of Man), I remained mystified about changing game speed (which comes after completing capital cities) and unlocking industries to build manually (upgrade an existing industry to level three to get to these). The UI is absolutely awful. Even the old, original version of Transport Tycoon was more intuitive and friendly – here, everything is in hovering windows with nonsensical icons, with occasional other markers popping up now and then. Some things are just badly labelled: A truck action, 'skip', actually means set off now, even if it doesn't have a full hold of whatever it is it's going to deliver. Not, as I thought, skip the next destination in the chain. There is a small icon in the bottom right corner of the screen which give you instant tool-tips on everything, but it's still an obscure game to get into. I owned it for a couple of months, and it's only now I've really started to get the fabled 'one more town' feeling LOGistICAL fans crave. Regardless of the UI, once you've learned it, it sticks. The game also integrates seamlessly with the base game, which features the entirety of Australia and has very full, satisfying DLC to bolster it's longevity, into the hundreds of hours. You can currently deliver goods to the entirety of Australia, New Zealand, California, Germany, The Netherlands, Hawaii, Egypt... The end goal is for the whole Earth to be represented, and skipping from one country module to the next is as easy as clicking on the globe and clicking a different country. In summary, LOGistICAL is a fantastic puzzle game with a very addictive management mechanic, and if you spend two or three hours reading a guide and the manual and retrying the tutorial island, you'll end up loving the game and wanting to play it every spare second. ~M~", "appid": "684940", "steamid": "profiles/76561197994097437", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502280000.0} {"text": "Неплохо, сюжетка понравилась, файтинг сделан умело и красиво, музыка на высоте. Жду вторую главу)))", "appid": "574980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120836476", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588939200.0} {"text": "겨울 스포츠를 좋아하는 사람으로써 스키장을 갈 여유가 생기지 않아 구매한게임 유비소프트라 살짝 걱정은 됬지만 해보니 그래픽도 우수하고 마음껏 산맥에서 산맥을 활강할수있다 밤에 불끄고 하면 좀더 풍경이 멋있어보인다 스키 스노우보드뿐만 아니라 낙하산과 비행슈트가 있어 눈쌓인 멋진 풍경을 더 넓게 볼수있다 하지만 사양이 높아 같이할 친구가없어서 나는 혼자 즐길수밖에 없다", "appid": "460920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198335577474", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "Довольно таки динамичная и порой забавная игора с отличным саундом,которая затянет вас надолго,как минимум потому что постоянно выходят новые апдейты и ивенты.Сюжет конечно дыряв как Саша Грей,но я вангую что в длс все исправят.Моя оценка сие игре - 9.5 из 10.", "appid": "782330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198167381696", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584705600.0} {"text": "good game", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051523302", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1440504000.0} {"text": "Awesome game!!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198178443330", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1448107200.0} {"text": "Good game but was better when crytek boss it", "appid": "291480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085620259", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1527422400.0} {"text": "good", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198184843069", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1427198400.0} {"text": "Всех приветствую! Буду довольно краток. Эта игра получилась прекрасной! В ней удивительно все: интересный сюжет, увлекательный геймплей, отличная анимация, персонажи и мобы. Особенно хочу отметить сложность игры. Она - нереально сложная! Решил пройти сразу на сверхсложном уровне. Скажу сразу: если вам дороги ваши нервы, ваш стул и пукан, то советую играть на легком уровне, иначе спалите весь свой дом. Я никогда... Слышите, НИКОГДА ЕЩЕ ТАК НЕ МАТЕРИЛСЯ, с*ка... Это был просто еб*чий ад! Просто 9 пылающих пердаков из 10. Всем советую.", "appid": "428550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198137499122", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1504267200.0} {"text": "Oynanan en çok oyunlar arasındadır.Bir çok kişi oyunu tavsiye eder bende bu kişiler arasındayım.Gayet güzel bir oyun.Sadece 25 TL karşılığında oyunu alabilir ve oynayabilirsiniz...", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198866769282", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1540296000.0} {"text": "It's like Rust but smoother. Needs more content.", "appid": "393420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079234763", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1525003200.0} {"text": "Хм....ну мне кажется длс-ка не стоит своих денег. Она классная но я думал что за 360 рексов я получу побольше чем 40 минут бегатни с мага-скелетами. Может ожидания были завышены но я думал тут будут комментарии персонажа обо всем пиздеце что вокруг происходит, какие-нибудь ролики , персонажи, (может даже магия но на это похер по-большому). А получили просто ноль какой-то истории (кроме записок) и забивание скелетов в тишине, да ещё \"сокровищница\" в конце прям моё почтение. Вообщем купить со скидкой можно а так лучше не стоит, не дотянули до такого ценника.", "appid": "1300710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047663377", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597320000.0} {"text": "I have 2K hours in this game on another steam account. I love how there's something different for every league the devs really put all their sweat and tears into this game and it shows. Blizzard doesn't compare and probably never will have the s