arly_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1357214400.0} {"text": "스카웃 시발", "appid": "493520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198311348013", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1580126400.0} {"text": "I received the game for free thanks to the Humble Bundle Play Outlast is a game full of blood, violence and fear in the game he played for a journalist who wanted to reject the law of the abandoned Psichiatria but did not know that there were things that marked him for life. The game contains RPG elements of classical Horror, such as collecting documents, exploring the environment, and collecting the flashlight. It is true that the game has beautiful and breathtaking graphics with places with which man also freezes but such a player does not fear horror so do not expect anything from it because I was not afraid at all. The game is optimized with excellent texture, sound effects and NPC characters, and the Camera of the Hero is excellently crafted and can be seen from your character but forgot to give the mirror the heads and NPC reflections. PROS + Graphics + A breathtaking environment + Blood and other effects are processed in detail + The water is processed in detail and contains Physx (when water flows through it) + true horror atmosphere + Night vision is extremely effective + Camera is processed in detail + Models and textures are nice and done in high resolution to praise the Creators + beautiful sound effects and NPC sounds and spooky sounds + the story and its end CONS - Short but if you enjoy the game, it will last for 7,5 hours, which is the perfect length of the FPS shooter. - Smoother landscaping GAME 7/10", "appid": "238320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198335973146", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506772800.0} {"text": "a very fun game with ur friends", "appid": "571740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035170970", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1570017600.0} {"text": "yfqc cnhtkm,f", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076614451", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Play or die", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105642545", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1444564800.0} {"text": "I had low expectations for this game but Turned out to be very good I strongly recommend this game", "appid": "205230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198254053450", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1456056000.0} {"text": "Can't talk, going postal.", "appid": "707030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008587937", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1574769600.0} {"text": "粮，粮，粮，粮草征收人", "appid": "813780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198099567247", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574942400.0} {"text": "Overall not bad but Borderlands 2 still the best.", "appid": "397540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053321362", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "144", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586001600.0} {"text": "nice", "appid": "40970", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992551110", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558872000.0} {"text": "A very cute hidden object game with an art style reminiscent of old books. Starting off extremely easy, finding items becomes increasingly difficult as you progress through the levels. Even using interactive scenery to hide a few here and there. I absolutely love the direction taken with the art style and wish more hidden object games adopted this style, instead of the overly used cliché horror/realism approach. Overall, it's a fun game to dwindle away a few hours and one I could see being great fun for children too.", "appid": "1348920", "steamid": "profiles/76561197982273259", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "100", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "Highly polished and entertaining puzzle game.", "appid": "511470", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992967892", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "Задумка интересная, но всего один сервер и тот пустой. Введите ботов что ли..", "appid": "574080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052061115", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577448000.0} {"text": "Besides the Occasional Bug You'll encounter on your journey, the game is a blast. There's something satisfying about being able to slice zombies' heads clean off while doing parkour in Harran. The story is interesting at least, and keeps you hooked until the ending. A plethora of sidequests give you something to do even when you're done with the story. A personal favorite of mine is one in which you shoot up zombies in a zombie \"movie.\" Easter eggs like dancing zombies and EXPCaliber show the devs had a blast making this game. Check it out if you haven't already, its good. 8/10", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198350276277", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596542400.0} {"text": "Metro: Last Light Redux – самая лучшая и полная версия классической игры Metro: Last Light, обновленная с применением последней, самой совершенной версии графического ядра 4A Engine для игровых систем последнего поколения. Игроки, не знакомые с серией, получат один из лучших сюжетных шутеров за всю историю жанра – эпическое приключение, сочетающее в себе захватывающий «Сурвайвл-хоррор», исследование местности, тактические бои и стелс. В это издание входит также весь выпущенный ранее загружаемый контент, который добавляет дополнительные 10 часов к игре в одиночном режиме. Поклонники игры в ее исходном виде заметят, что механика улучшилась, и появилось новое –например, возможность в любой момент узнать время и боезапас, а бои и фигуры игровых персонажей заново анимированы. Те, кого привлекал знаменитый приквел Metro 2033 с его ориентацией на хоррор и выживание, смогут сыграть по-новому, поскольку теперь появились два способа игры – «Выживание» и «Спартанец». При первом способе Last light из игры с упором на сражения и скрытные действия превращается в тихую, но напряженную схватку за выживание.", "appid": "287390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119997652", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522152000.0} {"text": "NIce game", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198333746034", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515844800.0} {"text": "witch update have the cars :)", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198125139414", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1408276800.0} {"text": "SUPER JEU achetez le il vaut la peine", "appid": "24810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096841036", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1432814400.0} {"text": "Interesting for experiencing at least once, the graphics are beautifull, and it is a nice change of pace from mainstream games.", "appid": "334120", "steamid": "profiles/76561198043546629", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1512907200.0} {"text": "sehr gutes game", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134756372", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1505736000.0} {"text": "Higher Replay value than any Call of Duty game", "appid": "311340", "steamid": "profiles/76