story, the uncoordinated art style and generally predictable characters in 'By Moonlight' tainted the experience. You're given the illusion of choice whilst going through a linear story line, with an unsatisfying ending. The story attempts to present endearing characters, though is unable to present them as anything other than two dimensional . The choice system implemented results in no real consequence, and the 'bad endings' often took an odd thematic turn, leaving an unpleasant taste. However, the game shines with clever dialogue and an exciting premise, albeit dissapointingly never fully developed. When dedicated, the game presents a playful and fun vibe, genuinely enjoyable, though this is diluted through a weak story line and somewhat lazy art style. Considerable care has been clearly invested, yet this ultimately fails to pay off as a worthwhile experience.", "appid": "1014880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198281011881", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1551614400.0} {"text": "meh", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198432024223", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575201600.0} {"text": "dose not work", "appid": "1415530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039399510", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601467200.0} {"text": "El juego tiene el volumen de sonido bugueado y aparte no me deja hablar por el Voice Chat de la partida, estaba jugando y de la nada me morí (Estando en una Zona Segura) WTF. No recomiendo comprar este juego ya que es vendido como una ''Edición Definitiva'' pero éste tiene más bugs que el original y encima se ve peor jksjsk", "appid": "383150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082586199", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604664000.0} {"text": "If you can pay steam to remove some games i would definetly do it. And this one is first on my list. Take my money and please delete this game forever.", "appid": "247730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198067832191", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1438257600.0} {"text": "Un juego que al principio pintaba bien hasta que en nivel alto te das cuenta de la importancia que tiene el PAY TO WIN, intentaron solucionar el pay to win quitando del mercado la compraventa de items integrado en Steam, cosa que lo único que cambió es que los jugadores no podían seguir sacando beneficio de la venta de varios items, porque ingame la gente puede seguir comprando lo mismo solo que a Ubisoft \"que es lógico que quieran sacar más beneficio para ellos mismos\" pero las cosas claras, PAY TO WIN en toda regla", "appid": "239220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198137099693", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1461844800.0} {"text": "В ЭТУ ИГРУ НЕ УМЕЮТ ИГРАТЬ, +30 ФРАГОВ ДЛЯ ПОБЕДЫ НЕДОСТАТОЧНО, КАЖДУЮ ИГРУ 4 УEБAНА МЕШАЮТ ТЕБЕ ВЫИГРАТЬ", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198441732736", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521633600.0} {"text": "was exactly what I was expecting it to be but hoping it wouldn’t! Much like VTM:Bloodlines and Red Embrace: Hollywood (I haven’t played Coteries of New York), you play as a recently turned fledgling whose sire isn’t in the picture. This time you play as Julia, a former investigative journalist who is now the bottom of the barrel in vampire society. Self-loathing, outspoken and a chronic chain smoker. The future doesn’t look bright for this lost soul – well literally because you know, no sun. When a sudden murder needs investigating, Julia is thrown head first into a political game that she is not only unqualified for, but also no one is really willing to help her out. It’s clear she is a pawn and a disposable one but being the type of person she is, she soldiers on in the hopes of busting this case wide open. Needless to say, this shares a lot of common ground with other vampire games; newly turned. No sire to guide her. Shouldered with responsibilities far above her status and way too much politics; it’s not exactly original. This version also has a heavy side dose of religion. Nether are things I really enjoy reading. I do however, like being the underdog that no one really suspects. The one everyone takes for granted and doesn’t believe will ever succeed. Extra points for being sassy too. The artwork is beautifully dark and envisions children of the night quite nicely with it’s gritty, stylish and grungy design. Animated backgrounds and atmospheric sounds/music really push this to the next level as well. As someone who can appreciate the beauty in darkness, this was nice eye candy for my twisted little mind. The cast of eccentric characters was the cherry on the top to this delicious ice-cream Sunday! Considering Vampire: The Masquerade is in it’s own universe I was a little annoyed when there was mentions of a pandemic that originated from China in 2020 – I mean, really? REALLY? I don’t know about other people but I play games to get away from all that chaos outside. I don’t want it to needlessly show up in the thing I’m trying to use to escape mention of the damn virus and when I say “needlessly”, I do mean it. It literally had no effect on the story what so ever apart from a few lines here and there that could quite easily have been replaced with – oh I don’t know – anything else!! Something that really let me down was the sheer lack of clan traits. For example, I’m a huge fan of Malkavian’s. I adore the insanity that was displayed in VTM:B but there was no crazy to be found here. In fact, only Julia really displayed any clan traits and that was merely necessity to keep the relationship with her human friend for the ending decisions. Completely disappointed! The choice on how you get the good and bad ending was To get the good ending To get the bad ending Overall, not a fan of the visual novel version and I’d be very hard pressed to recommend this to anyone.", "appid": "1279630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044949801", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601553600.0} {"text": "Bok gibi bir optimizasyon gta 5 i ultarada açan bir pc bu oyunu en düşük ayarlarda 30 40 fps acıyor keske iade edebilsem :(", "appid": "438740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198311038793", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508241600.0} {"text": "유트 스페셜 트랜스포트보다 퇴화한 에스코트의 인공지능 1. 2차선에 사고현장 있으면 1차선으로 비켜서 지나가면 되는데 사고현장 앞에서 잠듬 (세이브와 로드로 해결해야) 2. 뻥 뚫린 고속도로에서 시속 40마일까지 올릴 수 있는데 가끔 일부러 늦게 감 3. 에스코트가 트럭하고 거리 유지를 충분히 해야 하는데 자꾸 박고 싶은지 급정거를 시전 (시비 거는 거냐) 4. 후방 에스코트가 다른 AI 때문에 길 막혀서 못 오는 경우가 있음 (세이브와 로드로 해결해야) 짜증 나서 결국은 일거리에서 특수화물을 거르게 되는 이상한 게임이 되어버렸다 유트 스페셜 트랜스포트가 인공지능이나 버그나 훨씬 낫습니다 구매를 비추천합니다", "appid": "962750", "steamid": "profiles/76561197966510042", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562932800.0} {"text": "Recomendo para jogar em 10 amigos. Agora para jogar solo ou com poucos amigos sera um simulador de randons em call te acusando para proteger o amiguinho, ou de hackers. Logo, não recomendo devido ao jogo não ter um filtro de banimento ou proteção anti cheat.", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051362773", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602417600.0} {"text": "-การที่คุณมีประสบการณ์จากเกม FPS มาแทบไม่ช่วยเหี้ยอะไรในเกมนี่เลย -คุณจะได้พบกับความ unbalance แบบสุดๆ เล่นแล้วประสาทแดก -ปืนจะฟาร์มเอาหรือใช้เงินจริงซื้อก็ได้ ที่เหี้ยคือถ้าจะฟาร์มใช้เวลาสิ้นเปลืองเกิดไป -ปินที่พอฟาร์มซื้อได้ต้นเกมมีแค่ smg กากๆแถมฟาร์มนานด้วย สุดท้ายสู้ใครไม่ได้อยู่ดีแม่งใช้ปืนAR LMG กันเกือบหมด -เป็นทหารที่ต้องไปรบในสงครามแต่ทุกอย่างส่วนตัว