nd $20 max as they'd get bored in 3~ hours", "appid": "1142100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069788250", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "At the first look , this game looks ok...but when you get to play it for a long time , you will get bored as i do...", "appid": "299360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198037589588", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1471608000.0} {"text": "Elég nehéz játék 1000/734", "appid": "43000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036704556", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1459684800.0} {"text": "Got banned ever tho i wasnt cheating", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198342013199", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575633600.0} {"text": "идиотизм слов нет конченная игра", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198422016654", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542715200.0} {"text": "çöp almayın iade etcem", "appid": "50147", "steamid": "profiles/76561198394187682", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584100800.0} {"text": "чет не очень", "appid": "239160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079023012", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588680000.0} {"text": "this game is a master thesis on international communications and the failures therein.", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075440596", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "A pesar de que no fue apoyado el juego, le quise dar una oportunidad, aunque ya despues de jugar varias horas te das cuenta que es como cualquier juego Movil que si queres avanzar rap