оторой стоит забить на кс и пойти играть в ваши любимые игрушки. 2. COMUNITY CS:GO - на самом деле есть адекватные тиммэйты, с этим спорить абсолютно бесполезно, но хороших тиммэйтов на самом деле очень мало, я даже могу их посчитать на пальцах. а большинство дебилов играет в эту игру потому что она теперь FREE-TO-PLAY. как то я играл в кс (это не мой основной, если что) в 2 на 2, и мы играли с рандом чуваком в тиме (я чаще всего играю в соло) и помню когда был последний раунд первой половины игры я сел в угол, и стал ждать, но мой тиммэйт - то еще животное. вместо прослушивания шагов и раздачи инфы, он слушал много матов в его адрес от меня, и раздавал инфу по мне. в итоге мы с этим конченным придурком так и не смогли взять. вообщем, игра - полное дерьмо, я никому не советую ее покупать, поскольку это абсолютно бесполезно. много читеров, много дебилов, много кого еще вам удастся увидать.ставлю этой игре 10 аимботов и триггеров из 10. желаю вам удачи, и играйте лучше в какой нибудь пабг, или тот же самый фортнайт. пока)", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070240620", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529323200.0} {"text": "Презираю упрощение и деградацию, поэтому презираю такого рода игры, а валв так вообще обленились", "appid": "1046930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134508857", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1564920000.0} {"text": "This game is very repetitive and boring...", "appid": "457440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006980881", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491134400.0} {"text": "Like legit one of the worst ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ games you could ever buy.... Its called a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ milsim game yet the developers them selves add in a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ go karts DLC.... What ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ type of military has ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ racing go karts... ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ ♥♥♥♥ ass ♥♥♥♥♥ game aint no milsim.", "appid": "107410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198149662939", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496059200.0} {"text": "If you ever need a demonstration of how there is absolutely no quality control done by Valve, and how every hack with Unity and a Youtube tutorial can piece together a game and publish it on Steam, you definitely should check this one out.", "appid": "581200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091696828", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589284800.0} {"text": "This geam needs soundtrack only version would pay pls", "appid": "616220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198244250934", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545480000.0} {"text": "Желаю вам всего плохого ............/´¯/)..........................................(\\¯`\\ .........../....//............................................\\\\...\\ ........../....//..............................................\\\\ ..\\ ...../´¯/..../´¯\\........................................./¯`\\....\\¯`\\ .././.. /..../..../. |_....DEEP SILVER.._.|..\\....\\....\\....\\.\\ (.(....(....(..../.) ..)....EPIC STORE...(...(.\\....).....)....).) .\\................\\/.../..............................\\...\\/.............../ ..\\.................../................................\\................../ ...\\.................(.................................)................", "appid": "287390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198257105042", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549972800.0} {"text": "Noooooo, I wanted to play God Simulator, not GOAT simulator :(", "appid": "265930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198017308898", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1488110400.0} {"text": "There are only a handful of maps. This is only just the locations you pick with their day and night cycles, but the actual tactical maps you’re on. It looks sort of detailed, but when you look past the first few layers of the tactical maps you’ll see the green non-detailed background and other blocky items. I understand that is nit-picking, but if you’re going to add a few maps then that should’ve never happened. The sounds were a bit off at times. Some of the guns sounded as if they were being fired out of a muzzled tin can and at times when you put the volume down the lightning would still be louder than rest of the game. Hey, I know its lightning and thunder, but shooting a gun near you ears also has that similar deafening sound. The progression of RPG elements is a nice touch, but every character lacks detail about who they are. I’m a police officer, or I’m a nurse. Okay? Were you the clerk, did you specialize in a certain field, were you the janitor? I mean, a lot of the characters lack a full fledge background, story, or more information about who they are. You try to see it based on the very limited dialogue, but compared to other RPGs, this is very concerning when you jump into a genre that is more story and knowledge than anything else. The survival aspect of the game was done well enough. You gather supplies by searching the same zones over and over and over again. You’ll get anything from cloth, to food, to gun components. You’ll take those back to your camp and make med-kits, guns, or clothing to help you further down the line. You’ll also have access to a shop to sell some of your findings to make a killing in materials (currency). What I found the hardest of anything was the lack of tools and most of it was through the quests you’d get (you get some via exploration as well – if RNG doesn’t hate you). The RPG attributes and skills were an iffy one with me. You’d get to choose between picking points into weapons/combat oriented or skills that benefit the camp. I found this to my dislike because it should have been separate. So everything I learned is either or? I see the point of it to prolong the ‘survival’ bit of it, but other survival games did fine as well keep it separate. Some of said skills help with guarding from raiders/zombies attacking in the night, hunting, or building items to be used. With the attributes none of it really added up either. I had someone who is level 3 Cunning and they still get hit like they’re a wet paper bag. So, if block is at 20 is that 20% to block, 20 less damage? I mean, a lot of the stats in here were not informative enough to know what is going on stat wise. There were no clear instructions on what or how it was used while in combat but did become more useful for jobs around the camp. I also didn’t like how far the gaps were between certain skills were to make a change. So what does selection 16, 18 (stat) do compared to selection 20 with a higher chance of block and level 3 guard selection? No idea, it was never explained. That’s a big issue when you add RPG elements into a game that one must detail what they do here, there, and up against enemies. Raises the chance of what? That is throughout a lot of this game. What chances is cunning at the third selection when guarding and with 6 block? No idea. Again, 6% chance of blocking, less damage, how does this affect the enemies in turn? This is where the combat becomes disappointing. Why is this particular zombie ineffective at everything! Melee, long range, traps. WHY is he ineffective? I look at the zombie and there is no stats, no buffs, no debuffs. Just in-effect-ive! Why did another zombie block all three of my party members attack with the same information? Is this vagrant a tank when he’s one of the first zombies you see? Is he even a tank? Do they have a random hidden stat that no one knows? And this is why stats are important in RPGs because so you can know how to counter things, but unfortunately there is so much RNG in here it wouldn’t make a difference. From blocking all your gunshots, to running low on AP. Even AP is odd at times. Wait for a round. The round you’re in against enemies, or when you start a new round? Does it restart if you go to the next zone? I mean, we’re missing out on a lot of the combat information and the descriptions are vague about it all. Now what pushed me over to deleting this game? When you fail you start completely over. Okay, I get that because it’s a survival game, but we’ll help you cheat in the next round – basically you’ll get perks so your guy doesn’t suck so much next round. But now you do everything over again, with the same repetitiveness, storyline, dialogue, limited events, same pictures; that you’ve seen all in the first few hours again – No. Also, the lack of character customization is a drag too. Why do I have to play this Jack guy? Yes, I can rename him, but playing Jack is boring. What if I want to spice up my own character? What if a female wants to play a female character? Those options don’t exist and with RPGs, you have the option on how you want to look (even if limited) and this was rather forced. I guess there were also romance options too, but I didn’t see this in the game. Between the lack of details, to RNG heavy, to lack of information on stats, boring combat, and limited RPG elements; I found this game to be boring and extremely repetitive. Now, since it’s an Indie Dev and I support such small companies and teams, I’ll say it’s a game worth its price, but I cannot continue on. If this game is something down your alley and want to try out a game knowing there are flaws, then I think you might enjoy this title.", "appid": "363930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003026615", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592222400.0} {"text": "The game is a good foundation but it still has a few major bugs and the interface needs improvment, for example I lost all troops in transit wich cost me ~5k reinforcment and a complete front didn't have any troops now. There is also a bug where you can't select anything. I wil come back to the game when the major bugs are patched out.", "appid": "603850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084595689", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "its literally just a worse nether... Its not worth the 9 dollars if you already own nether...", "appid": "1010270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198202196316", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1557921600.0} {"text": "Сын собачьего дерьма создал эту игру, не видел хуже оптимизированных игр более 10ти лет со времен модов на сталкер, и это по вашему уровень? Лучше быть геем и играть в фортнайт!", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198098097643", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579521600.0} {"text": "Arkadaşlar şöyle bir incelemede buluncam Şimdi amacınız balkondan aşagı bok fırlatmak ve insanların başını kirletmek özel gücünüzü kullanarakda bomba bok kusmuk bok ve havaifişek bok kulanabiliyorsunuz. Oyunda 3 tane harita var ve görevleri tamamlamaya çalışıyorsunuz kesinlikle 2 liraya degmicek bir oyun mini oyun gibi canınız sıkıldıgında girip oynucagınız zaman öldürebileciginiz bir oyun ama ben tavsiye etmiyorum", "appid": "449540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198192604070", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458043200.0} {"text": "\" \" (С. Э. Кинг, ) Новое интересное , новый крутой ... и очередной платный контент-пак в придачу. Не пойми неправильно, , получилось оригинальное, но к хорошему быстро привыкаешь. Увы. Кто-то скажет, мол, грех жаловаться: ребята и без того стараются радовать нас бесплатными обновлениями и стыдно не поддержать любимого разработчика покупкой нового . Тем более такого! А в нём и впрямь есть на что посмотреть... Тематика , на сей раз затронутая , как нельзя лучше вписалась в стиль игры и так крепко с ней сплелась, что без неё уже сложно воспринимать и без того эклектичный и бурлескный мир \"Killing Floor\". Персонажи для первого (да, за ним последовал ) набора выбраны недурно. Взять хотя бы (ближайшего родственника ) - стильного пиромана и мечту любого ! Отличный прикид дополняет грамотное отображение предплечий и митенок от первого лица (впрочем, судя по данному , это уже становится правилом). Слишком экстравагантно и анонимно? Не вопрос - к вашим услугам (или ) , готовый десантироваться в гущу кровавой сечи. А взгляните-ка на ! После такого захватывающего образа даже не верится, что эти люди когда-то создали модель , которая при виде от первого лица опускала несуществующие рукава и меняла стерильные медицинские перчатки на чёрные кожаные! и достался собрат из : запаянный в самодельную броню уличный рыцарь . Если не самая оригинальная, то уж точно, самая забавная модель в . И, кажется, вот же оно - счастье: отличные персонажи, залихватские биографии, масса веселья в сетевой игре и... и... И всё же это стагнация. Не поймите неправильно, в сравнении со - это адекватное . Но вечно держаться за косметические подачки нельзя. Надеюсь, что в это тоже понимают и рано или поздно дадут зелёный свет полноценному контенту, расширяющему игровые механики.", "appid": "35425", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003512990", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586001600.0} {"text": "Refunded. Full of bugs. Well what id expect?", "appid": "22370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198311860400", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "21", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530792000.0} {"text": "Разработчики от души постарались чтобы убить рыночный потенциал этой игры. Это крутая возможность потестить минимальный функционал за цену полноценной игры, но спасибо, пожалуй не нужно. *обновлю отзыв, когда игру доработают и можно будет пометать молот не только в плохо работающий ИИ", "appid": "908740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081111924", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1603972800.0} {"text": "this game is broken and wont work on most computers", "appid": "22300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198094942146", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1448020800.0} {"text": "Heu ! comment dire !? C'est juste un truc bourrin comme bien d'autre, sans stratégie aucune, avec des 'coéquipiers' qui preferent se ruer sur les coffres pendant que tu te fais les packs de rats qui le protégeaient. Moi qui pensais que la tendance \"zombies à toutes les sauces\" était passées, ils les ont juste déguisés en rats de toute taille. Gardes plutot ta thune et ton temps pour un bon Mordheim ou encore un Total War: WARHAMMER si tu veux rester dans le thème sans etre déçu ....", "appid": "235540", "steamid": "profiles/76561197968261726", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1464350400.0} {"text": "J'ai terminé le monde 4 mais j'ai pas assez d'étoiles pour débloquer le 5, il faut que je me refasse les niveaux d'avant en 3 étoiles... Non merci, je m'amuse plus du tout dessus (depuis le monde 1 en fait), c'est trop compliqué et trop répétitif à mon goût.", "appid": "252130", "steamid": "profiles/76561197962923398", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604750400.0} {"text": "Didn't like the game, graphics were horrible, gameplay not unique...", "appid": "444200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198112870822", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "Très bon jeux et l'histoire est bonne mais rendu au niveau de l'hélicoptère, asti on peut même pas descendre pour passer dans le tunnel, criss de jeux mal coder", "appid": "55100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049471741", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502020800.0} {"text": "terrible game, wtf is the mouse accel, fix this sht", "appid": "281920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198288147454", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "16", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535284800.0} {"text": "performance เเย่มากๆ", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198238730016", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1512820800.0} {"text": "Игра честно скажу мне не понравилась. 1. дибильные квесты, на каждой карте ты должен добежать из пункта А в пункт Б, сфотографировать, места или цветы, поиск мусора и т.д. От всей этой беготни через час игры начинает раздражать. 2. Одна и та же дибильная музыка в сопровождении игры начинает раздражать уже с первых минут игры. 3. Неживой мир, звуки животных (через чур настойчиво звучащие) есть, зверья нет. 4. Сильно простой геймплей и поиск предметов. Бежишь себе по лесу, жопой почуял тут, ну и собственно поводил металлоискат елем и выкопал. Игра не оправдала оджиданий, как было написано в одном из отзывов можно было добавить поиск сокровишь по картам, доп оборудование, кастомизацию перса в конце концов, тайники, секреты. пока всего этого нет игра выглядит неплохо, но очень уныло.", "appid": "748300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141599601", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544270400.0} {"text": "Its not a free game, you start with some cash that is granted to you for a start just to get the feel of the game. Welll, I started with poker and had some hands played, but when I went back in to play, idiots forced players to go \"all in\" and cheat. Instead of just playing a good hand of cards, and once you run out of the cash given, uninstall the game or you will need money to continue real money to buy fake money!", "appid": "436150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198013872060", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584532800.0} {"text": "Such a shame about Open IV. Needs to be sorted as im not playing another rocksatr game till this gets fixed", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198208913503", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497787200.0} {"text": "8 years... Buying this game was automatic. What does this game feel like? Honestly? A Warband remaster with improved graphics. Early Access I'm sure some things will improve and be added, but do I think the end product will be worth the wait and hopes and dreams? No... No I do not. EDIT: Later in game, as of patch 3, the crashes are so frequent doing sieges it's almost impossible to play atm. But they are patching consistantly. EDIT: Patch 5, I crash every time I try to save lol. EDIT: Patch 8 fixed my siege crash, and is playable now. More random crashes but I have advanced quite a bit. Stable enough to have some fun now. EDIT: Patch 10: Well, I can play, I guess that's a plus. But these lords come back, even from long defunct kingdoms. You can never vanquish anyone... I started executing them... and more come under different names. I give up. EDIT: Patch 1.1: Game was steadily improving, to the point you could play without very frequent crashes, but I lost all sound in the game. Sigh. EDIT: Patch 1.1.1: Have sound again. Things seem stable. They are patching at a good rate and have a good alpha/beta/release system. They are going in the right direction.", "appid": "261550", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961038549", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1585656000.0} {"text": "-", "appid": "1085660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198292970798", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575201600.0} {"text": "Overall, this game is underwhelming. I came into it expecting a decent JPOG successor, as they've been advertising for years. Instead, I got a buggy mess with terrible animation and models. Overall it's a 2/10. I'd not put money into this game, just wait 2 months for a good dinosaur park sim, or go check out Prehistoric Kingdom Edit: Now that I'm coming back after the announcement that Development has stopped on this ♥♥♥♥♥♥ excuse for a tech demo I'd like to point out that a close friend of mine still hasn't been paid for her work on the game and neither have several other Devs. It's a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ scam, don't waste your money.", "appid": "719590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198144454684", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1525435200.0} {"text": "Sürüş keyfi berbat, ultra da bile grafikleri pek iç açıcı değil. Bunu başka bir oyuna kıyasla söylemiyorum, hikaye modu eğlenceli onun dışında serbest takılmada pek birşey yapılmıyor (Araba sürmek ve etrafa saldırmak dışında) öyle işte tarzım değil oyuncuyu kendisine bağlaması lazım. Okuduğunuz için teşekkür ederim", "appid": "243470", "steamid": "profiles/76561198445656379", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553342400.0} {"text": "首先使用加速器还是经常断线断开连接，第二节奏太慢，地图太大，适合养生玩家。 想增加游戏玩家，品质和网络都重要，国内这么多玩家，不开个香港服务器，让大家裸连，怎么可能提高在线人数", "appid": "1174180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198164671069", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585742400.0} {"text": "очешь проебать нервы тебе сюда. Ты нажимаешь \"Начать игру\" а далее \"Принять\" а потом сильно об этом жалеешь! Хотите узнать насколько ваши друзья действительно дегенераты? Эта игра идеально подходит для вас. Немного вырезок: *Сразу после старта команда берет 4 керри* -Эй ты, бери саппорта. -А почему вы не взяли саппортов? -Ахахах тупой чтоль? Сапа бери бл*дь. *берет керри* -♥♥♥♥ репорт тебе! Сказали сапа бери! Мр*зь еб*ная! ГГ ФФ в тиме 5 керри! Тупой русский паб! - Мидер где ганги??? -А где варды? Саппорты поставьте варды, чтобы я видел руны, я тут же гангать начну. -А ж*пу тебе не полизать? Оху*вший, надо сам поставь. И репорт за то что гангов нет. -Антимаг тупой му*ак, фарм отдай! - Говорит Некр. -Ты саппорт вообще-то.. -Нет я в керри! Ну все иду фидить! Скажите антимагу спасибо! *Фидит*", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163368058", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1449835200.0} {"text": "Optimalization sucks (sory i don't know how to wrote optimalization)", "appid": "823130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308021508", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528459200.0} {"text": "Allen vorran, ich bin Achievment Hunter, nicht, dass ich auf die Menge scharf bin, sondern auf die Vervollständigung. Kann das Spiel so NICHT empfehlen. Es gibt vom Start Level 1 bis Level 51 genau 2 neue Gegnertypen unterwegs, die Nightstalker und Hasen in weiß ? Etwas sehr mau, ja die Krokodille, aber im Ernst, zähle ich nicht. Das Game selbst lässt sich nicht zu 100% erfüllen, da 2 Achievments buggy sind. Ab Level 30 verkommt es zudem zu einem sinnlosem gegrinde. Es kommen quasi keine \"neuen\" Missionen mehr, man sucht also eine Quest die man schnell erledigen kann und wiederholt diese bis zum erbrechen. Die Ernüchterung, wenn man dann feststellt, dass man um alle Skills zu erreichen noch 100x iwelche Level rennen muss ist argh groß. Zudem man erst am Ende fest stellt, dass man wenigstens 2 Errungenschaften nicht erreichen kann. Das Spiel könnte richtig gut sein, leider nur könnte.. - zu wenig Abwechslung in den Leveln - zu wenig Abwechslung bei den Gegner - ab Level 30 einfach nur noch sinnfreies gegrinde, Game wurde künstlich in die Länge gezogen - 100% nicht möglich, den Entwickler stört es scheinbar nicht - Solo absolut einschläfernd auf Dauer - spielt man jede Mission genau 1x endet man ca. bei Level 30-35, falls überhaupt ?! - diverse Bugs im Spiel, wie unsichtbare Gegner in den Verteidigungs Missionen - Base Ausbau ebenfalls sehr Grindlastig, wenn man überleben möchte - Schwierigkeit richtig sich nach eigenem Zeitaufwand, je mehr man grindet, desto einfacher ist es eben.. Schade.. denn der Ansatz ist nicht schlecht ;)", "appid": "360170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198303526516", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517054400.0} {"text": "A very fun game if you enjoy ground, air and naval combat and have a lot of patience and interest for world war and post war vehicles. The game is very realistic with a ton of iconic vehicles to choose from. If you like a certain tank like a T-34 or a Tiger or even an Abrams you will have a fun time grinding and finally getting the vehicle you want. What I must stress though is that grinding is the biggest part of the game and getting the higher tier tanks or planes will definitely take years to get if you don't spend money within the game, even if you do it will still take about a year depending on what you buy. For example buying a premium tier IV tank is only good for researching tanks around that tier and once you get to tier VII you will struggle and will probably lose a lot of silver lions because of your stock tanks. The biggest problems I personally have are: - having to play against post war tanks that one shot you almost every game when you yourself are playing a late world war 2 era tank - this game has pay to win aspects such as bushes and camos that can only be bought with real money - Once you have the tanks or planes you wanted from the start you start to lose interest in the game and in the end you stop playing. Once a new vehicle comes out you get it and lose interest in the game once again, this cycle keeps on repeating. - camping is probably one of the best strategies in the game and if you don't have the patience to stand still and watch a point for 10 minutes then you should play arcade, which in itself is fun but makes grinding take quite a lot longer. - In the higher tiers there is always powercreep meaning that they will release a tank or plane for one nation with something far superior to the others which then makes that one nation extremely op UNTIL other nations finally get the equivalent some patches later, furthermore there will always be wallet warriors that will instantly get the OP vehicle on the first day and just keep killing you without you being able to do anything as your nation hasn't gotten an update yet. Conclusion: If you are one of those people that like a particular vehicle like the Challenger or a MiG then sure you can get this game, but if your vehicle isn't a top tier one than you will most likely get annihilated by vehicles that your tank or plane would have never met pretty often, also getting higher tier vehicles will take a LOT of time. If you are willing to spend some months to experience your favorite vehicle then sure get this game why not, but if you aren't ready to play a game where grinding is everything and the only way to make it faster is by spending money, then I dunno, go play other games where there is a ranked system and everyone is matched equally and skill is the main part of the game.", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198151327588", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594987200.0} {"text": "Игра однозначно стоит внимания для любителей ТД . Не рекомендую лиш потому что те кто играют на телефонах/планшетах имеют кучу бонусов из-за рекламы а в Steam данных бонусов нет ибо мы не можем смотреть ее . В нормальных моб играх в Steam просто ставят таймер и можно забрать бонус без рекламмы . Это ничто иное как проявление рассизма к PC геймерам , пока существует данная несправедливость обзор будет отрыцательным .", "appid": "429540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068377377", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578657600.0} {"text": "Neovladatelná srajda", "appid": "378860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049281531", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601380800.0} {"text": "Juego de Habilidad, en el que de forma muy simple debes de acertar la bola en los lugares en dónde aparecen las dos barras verdes. La música és interesante. Son 3 pistas de música electrónica, bastante diferentes entre sí. Están bien creadas. En el juego existen dos modos de juego, pero resulta que los dos modos funcionan exactamente igual. 1- Classic Theme. Tienes dos barras verdes, y dos barras rojas, formando un cuadrado. En el centro de ese cuadrado, tienes una aguja de reloj moviéndose cada vez más rápido dependiendo de los puntos que ya tengas. También, dentro de ese cuadrado.. hay otros dos cuadrados mucho más pequeños, y clickando en uno de esos cuadrados podrás lanzar la bola, para ganar uno, o dos puntos (o perder una vida si fallas el lanzamiento). 2- Epilepsy Theme. Todo igual que el Classic Theme, pero con un fondo más extraño, y con colores más vivos, intentando ser molesto como para aumentar la dificultad. Para jugar al juego, tienes que hacer click en uno de los dos cuadrados pequeños que hay en las esquinas arriba-izquierda, y abajo-derecha. - Si aciertas al lanzar la bola, y ésta acaba en una barra verde.. ganarás un punto. - Si aciertas al lanzar la bola, en una cosa pequeña que hay parecido a una mariposa, y la bola acaba en una barra verde.. ganarás dos puntos en lugar de uno. - Si aciertas al lanzar la bola, en un corazón pequeño, y la bola acaba en una barra verde.. ganarás una vida extra (puedes acumular hasta 5 vidas extra a la vez). Llegar lo más lejos posible, en la puntuación de cada modo de juego. El Juego muestra solamente a los 20 mejores del juego en puntuación, en su pantalla principal. Así que si no llegas a ese nivel altísimo de puntuación, no sabrás en qué lugar del ranking estás. Juego de Habilidad, más o menos fácil. Una interfaz minimalista. Pocos elementos, pocos colores, y un fondo casi siempre igual en el modo Epilepsy. Sólo 3 pistas de música. Éstas pistas electrónicas son interesantes, y están bien.. pero no ayudan a alargar la experiencia del juego. \\\\-------// És demasiado simple... . Le faltan más opciones en su jugabilidad. //-------\\\\ //~·-.. ..-·~\\\\", "appid": "487220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011831460", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535803200.0} {"text": "*一个很像Rust的游戏，背景貌似是暴风雨已把你带到了一个陌生的岛屿上生存。 完全没感觉到岛上有求生难度， 。 *画面说实在并不好，比起同类游戏逊色不少， 。 *再来说说服务器，0/75 1/50这都是什么鬼，官方添加一半的道具都是给多人娱♂乐的吧， 难到我还要用弩炮射动物？", "appid": "327090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198273753228", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1486728000.0} {"text": "absolute ♥♥♥♥ p2w dont install unless you want to suffer", "appid": "291480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271829366", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562932800.0} {"text": "首先，没中文就算了，我打个补丁，但是补丁打上了各种闪退，根本没法玩，这虽然看似是补丁的问题，但是其根本之原因还是你世嘉没出中文的锅，本来想着4快出了买个1代补补，这下被搞的性质全无，如果4没中文我是不会给你们捧场的我受够了补丁！！！先给差评，这是原则问题，更是一个态度！希望世嘉重视中国玩家，庞大的市场不会让你没钱赚，想通了你就能赚到钱，好了就这些~！", "appid": "294860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121496986", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "12", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530705600.0} {"text": "2일차 낮에 승리 팀 정해지는 쓰12레ㅐ기 게임 트럭팟이나 킬 먹으면서 찢고 다녀야 겜이 굴러감 3~4루트 무기 다 쓰레기 되고 적폐 캐릭들 다 너프 먹고 황벨 될 때 1년 묵히고 꺼내 먹으셈", "appid": "1049590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198159211894", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1605614400.0} {"text": "Great game. Too bad it crashes every time I try to load a save. I spent more time troubleshooting the issue than I got in gameplay and that's saying a lot. 