ка. + Добавили семейное дерево и повысили роль политики в игре. + Самые сложные компании в серии. + Хороший сеттинг. А теперь о самом главном. Это тот же Rome II. Тютелька в тютельку. За 1300 рублей (старт продаж), мы снова получили \"самую лучшую оптимизацию\", мы снова получили тонну DLC, опять новые фракции, кровь, и всё то д*рьмо под названием DLC, которым SEGA и разработчики пичкают нас каждую игру. Нет, вы не поймите меня неправильно - игра хороша, но именно таким должен был быть Rome II. А данная игра больше на аддон походит, чем на полноценную часть. Подитожим. Если бы это было полноценным DLC для Rome II, было бы довольно неплохо. Но продавать это под видом совершенно новой игры, революции в жанре - плевок в лицо всем фанатам серии Total War. Брать данную игру только со скидкой. Если не купите - ничего не потеряете. Ждём Вархаммер. Может его хоть не испоганят. 7/10", "appid": "325610", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126926759", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "712", "votes_funny": "80", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1444305600.0} {"text": "氪了金还要肝时间 棒子想圈钱圈时间也是绞尽脑汁了 我一万多软妹B的装备跌到2000，一如既往的差评。", "appid": "888770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198315268806", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529668800.0} {"text": "Smite is a fun game to play and I really wanted to like it however the community is quite toxic and unwelcoming to new players. You get a small selection of gods to choose from if you don't purchase the dlc packs to unlock them all. Not to mention all of the ingame microtransactions. For those reasons I can't recommend.", "appid": "386360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198364534971", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "is lag game thanks wwe for nothing -.-", "appid": "664430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198228274852", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544616000.0} {"text": "The campaign is uninteresting and boring. You're never told why you need to save this guy or kill that guy or whatever. After almost every mission, this generic soldier dude appears, says \"train go boom\" like he's the coolest guy ever and then vanishes. Then you are blinded by a bright light (or something like that) and you're back at the hub, preparing for another mission. You don't even have a name. Your name is literally 'player'. What!? If they wanted to give players the opportunity to create their own characters, they should have given us more options. You can only choose from a selection of faces for the protagonist (or 'your' character) and you don't even have the option to choose a black man's face. They're all white. What!? That's racist! As if the player base wasn't low enough on pc, the 4 dlc packs as well as the season pass has divided the player base even further. There is literally NO ONE in the 'No DLC' playlists. So I guess screw me 'cause I decided get the standard edition rather than the deluxe edition. And no, I don't have anything to say about the actual multiplayer gameplay because I haven't had the pleasure to play it at all. I've searched all the (active) playlists for several minutes but I guess I have to spend another 50 bucks (or 25 on sale) to actually get to play the multiplayer. And there ain't no way in hell am I gonna do that. Ahh, the zombies mode. I got the game for 3 reasons: 1) split screen for all modes on pc. 2) multiplayer (which doesn't even work for me). and 3) zombies. I wanted to play the zombies mode in split screen as I don't really enjoy playing it alone. But the split screen doesn't work! :D the game freezes every time I try to play zombies in split screen mode!!! YAYY :D. And now even if I manage to run it and it turns out to be great, my opinion about this game ain't never gonna change unless the multiplayer miraculously gets populated. DON'T GET THIS GAME if you intend to get the standard edition or for the campaign. As for the zombies, I really can't say, as I wasn't fortunate enough to get it to work.", "appid": "311210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072276670", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497441600.0} {"text": "If you want to go to a psych ward institution then this is the game for you. If you want pay for the game to run a server then round up a group of friends just for them to draw retarded photos of a frog or something and then makes you guess it for you only to get it wrong. You can load up a better game in seconds through a browswer. This game is so trash you would probally want to walk into a dumpster and shoot yourself so your remains get crushed because of this ♥♥♥ game. ♥♥♥♥ drawful this peice of garbage.", "appid": "442070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196763523", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588680000.0} {"text": "Loved this game a couple years ago, but since then they have added dinos that have totally destroyed the simplicitiy that made this game so great. Griefing is a huge issue now, and its dev supported, do not reccomend unless you ONLY play with friends on a private server. EDIT: Apparently it is an issue, and has been for several years, that clients will crash constantly while on a non dedicated server.", "appid": "346110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036216584", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1531051200.0} {"text": "Honnêtement, vous pouvez jouer à csgo, votre skill sera beaucoup plus récompensé qu'ici. Les jeux rivaux de celui-ci tel que S.K.I.L.L , Zula Europe, etc... sont tellement mieux. C'est plus votre arme qui compte que votre skill, même les joueurs les plus à chier peuvent faire une tuerie. Imaginez ce jeu, avec vous en train d'utiliser un nerf, contre des gosses hyperactifs avec des vraies armes, ben c'est à peu près le