text": "If you already own, and have completed, the original - there was nothing that made me want to replay this version, unfortunately. The controls do not seem any more improved from the original - so the same issues from before are still here just wrapped up in slightly higher detailed textures.", "appid": "667720", "steamid": "profiles/76561197962245406", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "В игре очень бесячая музыка на один мотив (та самая, которая играет в видеоролике на странице игры). И ее нельзя отключить - в игре вообще отсутствует раздел Настройки! Поиграв несколько минут эта музыка с колокольчиками засядет в вашей голове надолго.", "appid": "292620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035171115", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587124800.0} {"text": "Esse jogo na Steam não ficou boa, até no Ps2 o jogo roda melhor e liso, não é o meu pc que é ruim, é o jogo que está dessincronizado. Tomara que não tenha gado da EA para comentar, não perca tempo hateando essa análise, vai juntar o teu precioso tempo e juntar 2.000 reais para comprar todo o pacote do The Sims 4 vai, bicho tá foda ultimamente viu.", "appid": "17430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198876535513", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595851200.0} {"text": "结论： 谁买谁傻逼！ 去爱心分享大胸鸟的版本吧！ ———————————————————— 刚趁着史低买的358超级无敌威力完全版， 感觉毕竟出了两年了，bug估计修的差不多了， 结果呵呵，bug真的是一点没修，updata全在加dlc上了， 开局就遇到了不支持宽屏， 我还觉得无所谓，分辨率设置成1920*1080直接进去了， 把分辨率强行拉成矮肥圆了，算了也不重要能玩就行，结果....... 出bug了！！！ 不论鼠标还是键盘按什么都不好使， 退了重进选完英雄游戏直接崩溃， 行，你暗耻牛逼，", "appid": "730310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198116611530", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588334400.0} {"text": "Que pedo con este juego alv :v", "appid": "788880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198169545644", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521547200.0} {"text": "Recent changes to trading are disgraceful", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198186349158", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522411200.0} {"text": "waste", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198269491986", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "Melhorar o anticheat e balancear as patentes. Assim ficará mais agradável este jogo", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198129926522", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "Rogue Party 2 is an indie, 3D third person rogue-lite dungeon crawler. While it is not the worst thing i played, it is mediocre at best. Art approach is low-poly and sound effects are mishmash of low and decent quality of nonsense. While UI does its' job, it is really ugly. It seems like developer of this game tried to avoid some artwork usage (like icons, images etc) and i couldn't understand the reason of that. Only thing you can see in-game as image is mana and health icons which reminds me of my old attempts to create something decent on mspaint. Ah, there is also the parchment image (clip art) you see when you unlock an achievement or an item. Gameplay-wise, combat is dull. There is no melee combat since you throw your weapons. AI is poor. There is no free look and trajectory logic is same as most of FPS games of 90's. Inventory system is basic. When you grab an armor, weapon or magic item from a chest, it immediately replaces your equipment with the one you got. There is no way to reverse this process since your previous equipment vanish. Also, you can't compare your equipment to the item you found in chest before you change it. While you can learn the quality of items throughout your play time, there is no way to really know if your currently equipped and upgraded item is inferior or superior to item you found in a chest. Maybe inventory screen will help. I don't know why the developer made a so-called sequel to first Rogue Party. It seemed to me that he could improve the first one without releasing the second. If you compare Rogue Party to Rogue Party 2, you can see that they are identical. I didn't try to play the game co-op so i can't comment on that. TL;DR: There are far better alternatives to this game. First thing comes to my mind is Barony.", "appid": "1274980", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981055338", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592827200.0} {"text": "гов не покупайте никогда", "appid": "673770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198447364495", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1512043200.0} {"text": "I am sad to say that this game is a tragedy. fun for a while, yes. but 22cans promised us something that they havent, and porbably never will live up to. i have seen the reviews go from mostly positive to mostly negative in less than half a year, and the fact that this game failed is saddening.", "appid": "232810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084113748", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1428408000.0} {"text": "O jogo é foda. Um dos melhores da franquia. Mas vai levar o meu negativo pq deveria ter saído assim e não te obrigarem a pagar pra arrumarem o jogo. E a inda a palhaçada de excluir a versão antiga obrigando quem não tinha o jogo que já é antigo a pagar o preço de um lançamento. Mancada da produtora!", "appid": "570940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071460592", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "174", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562241600.0} {"text": "Cancer Community", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198167391121", "voted_up": false, "votes_u