lse, "tstamp_created": 1427803200.0} {"text": "ÇÖP", "appid": "592580", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201481087", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "23", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529496000.0} {"text": "broken af", "appid": "527760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198235125160", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566129600.0} {"text": "When do card games crash?", "appid": "470220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045673356", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1565352000.0} {"text": "寒蝉当他们哭是一个健全的小说。 音乐，背景和人物共同创造一个世界，这是用户阅读的小说的舞台。 他们大笑，哭泣，生气。 用户以主角的角度来体验故事。 这个故事也是一个久违的老动漫系列故事......甚至不想去购买它： - 安静的叙述 - 没有新东西", "appid": "577480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198165413614", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529150400.0} {"text": "До выхода GTA 5 на PC, можно было поугарать и по\"PvP\"шиться. Но е*учий донат и выход GTA 5 на PC ставит большой и толстый крест на этой игре. Народ, вместо донатов на эту шнягу, лучше покопите баблинского и купите GTA 5. Там всё в разы лучше и интересней. Пис ;)", "appid": "113400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057938588", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1486036800.0} {"text": "Would be fun back when i was 8-12", "appid": "218330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070937929", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1473595200.0} {"text": "Used to love the game...This one thing I bought in a hurry since the game came out and regretted later... This is by far the most regret 729 baht that i ever spent on.", "appid": "438740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198182201003", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525867200.0} {"text": "本地双人二号位没法确定，想加个官方群问一下还拒绝通过。我好评nm呢", "appid": "650780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198157311072", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589544000.0} {"text": "Why is this game so hyped ?", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561199059344401", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590235200.0} {"text": "긴박하고 박진감넘치는 배틀로얄게임의 나쁜 예시 반면교사와도 같은 배울점이 많은 게임이지만 나처럼 구매를통해 배우진 말자", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060688289", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1523448000.0} {"text": "My recommendation is a big Meh. I liked the arcade mode and airplane battle. But the game is \"junk\", hard to understand. Not really polished. And the main problem for me is in a 15vs15 battle, you are 2 real players and 28 bots... Also maybe you will like it, maybe not, better to try it, it's free with a lot of micro transactions. Maybe I played too much World of Tanks to enjoy this game.", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198022532442", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587297600.0} {"text": "It was fun while it lasted, but nothing new is brought to this game, and I highly prefer insurgency source because of the bigger player base and AMBUSH is the best game mode, this game is just unbalanced as ♥♥♥♥. When it came out 7/10 Where it is now 5.5/10", "appid": "581320", "steamid": "profiles/76561197982629543", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573646400.0} {"text": "Отличный симулятор поездки в метро. Ехал дольше чем играл. Игруля неплохая, но оптимизации 0. По сравнению с прошлыми частями игра, мягко говоря, вышла корявой. 5\\10 Потому что не выдержал бесконечных загрузок, частых фризов (Причем не важно какая конфигурация графики. Для сравнения Ведьмак, FF15 и CoD на ультрах идут ровно без лагов.) и непонятной стрельбы.", "appid": "337000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198894896225", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599566400.0} {"text": "tolol", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198377527404", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533729600.0} {"text": "i play for 50 hours now i come back to the game and it has deleted my account ;-;", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198067799041", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584360000.0} {"text": "Не рекомендую.Игра на движке юнити,созданая бомжами студентами, дабы заработать27 рублей на бич пакет. Сюжет ох.уительный.Мы идем в психушку(ну как всегда)искать свою дочь Проститутку наркоманку,в итогде попадаем в какойто дет.сад,ясли.Подбирая книгу нас накрывает,и мы переносимся в больничку 50 десятых годов в россии. И тут поняслась.Подбираем фонарь,и на нас вылетает обосаная шл.юха которая пропадает от света божего,далее на нас вылетает Боярский в своей шляпе и убивает нас.Конец 3 обосаных бомжа со спидом из 10. Купить можно только из-за карточек. Р.s в игре нет сохранений.если вас убивают все сначала", "appid": "291010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198158731845", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1484395200.0} {"text": "this dose not load at all", "appid": "1133330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198152217686", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1605614400.0} {"text": "Не затянуло(((", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053882021", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480161600.0} {"text": "bad", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561197990243703", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1476014400.0} {"text": "Nach einem relativ kurzen, aber stimmigen, Einstieg gehts auch schon ab in die grafisch hübschen Wildlands. Man läuft durch die bolivianische Pampa und sammelt Materialien und Orden zum Freischalten von Fähigkeiten, räuchert den ein oder anderen Kartellunterschlupf oder eine Armeebasis aus und zwischendurch werden noch die Storymissionen mit ein paar gezielten Schüssen abgehakt - Open World a la Dragon Age Inquisition. Im vierer Gespann macht das alles vermutlich mehr Spaß. Alleine mit den KI-Gesellen jedoch nicht wirklich und verkommt recht schnell zum stupiden Minimapsymbole-abgeklappere. Vielleicht kann die umfangreich wirkende Story das noch rausreißen. Im Moment jedoch keine Empfehlung. Als ich das Spiel beendete, befand sich mein Ghost gerade unglücklich in einer Felsspalte - hoffentlich komm ich da wieder raus um die Review upzudaten... Update: Nach zwei weiteren Stunden, die fast auschließlich in Storymissionen investiert wurden, haben sich meine Vorurteile eigentlich nur noch bestätigt. Langweiliges Open World Gameplay in hübscher Kulisse. Auch scheint mir die KI nicht sonderlich gut zu sein. Es gibt zwar immer wieder Ansätze eines Flankenangriffes, meistens verkriecht sie sich jedoch in der Deckung und wartet darauf ausgeschaltet zu werden. Auch höhere Schwierigkeitsgrade resultieren nur in mehr Leben bzw. Schaden. Da ich keine wirkliche Lust habe weiter zu spielen, bleibt meine vorherige Aussage bestehen. Die Story mag später vielleicht besser werden, das auszutestet ist mir aber keine 60 Euro wert.", "appid": "584210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030904437", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487851200.0} {"text": "Не понравилось. Подсказки ужасные, радиус объектов больше, чем спрайт, поэтому кисть сбрасывается, достижения стрёмные. Я прошёл все 100 уровней - это было худшее, что я делал за последний месяц. Не рекомендую покупать.", "appid": "956100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198252964029", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587124800.0} {"text": "never again", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198291878955", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589112000.0} {"text": "Я любил Total War Rome 2, и то что авторы подстелились под толерастов это нож в спину, от них я такого не ожидал", "appid": "214950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198104301890", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1537790400.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "109600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198369132940", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544356800.0} {"text": "KURŞUNU OLAN HERKES ADAM VURABİLİR SİLAHIN NE OLDUĞUNU ÖNEMİ YOK", "appid": "714210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198816320040", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Chujowa", "appid": "364270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120130713", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454068800.0} {"text": "I love you Gabe Newell <3", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134371384", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1475928000.0} {"text": "not responsive controls", "appid": "509960", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971576301", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472299200.0} {"text": "THe reviews are true this game is not like the csgo bunny hoppinh wasted my money 1/10", "appid": "429780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198162272308", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1480075200.0} {"text": "O servidor dedicado em parte acho que é uma das coisas que eles poderiam voltar atrás pois simplesmente acontecem hits impossíveis, prefiro o modo de antes P2P só jogava quem tinha internet boa. Rank desbalanceado, sou sobrevivente rank 1 e na maioria das partidas os sobreviventes que estão comigo são rank baixos e isso desanima tanto o sobrevivente quanto o assassino. E aproveitando a questão anterior não consigo jogar de sobrevivente por que o jogo no meio da partida cai e eu levo banimento e isso não acontece apenas comigo. SWF extremamente forte contra o assassino, eu jogo mais de assassino mas sempre que pego SWF na maioria das vezes sou obrigado a camperar, algo que fica chato tanto pro sobrevivente enganchado quanto pro assassino pois os 2 não pipam e fazem poucos pontos, a BHV deveria colocar um modo de comunicação mas que seja possível ter um counter. Sobre os pontos positivos boa ambientação, uma grande variação de assassinos, mapas, sobreviventes, perks, boa jogabilidade e os assassinos/sobreviventes feitos pela própria desenvolvedora você pode obter de forma gratuita com fragmentos. Dead By Daylight não deixa de ser um jogo bom, mas precisa melhorar e até lá recomendo comprar com alguma promoção.", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198207130307", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487160000.0} {"text": "Tbh this game was trash the first time I started it. 20 min for a game just for 1 player to dc.", "appid": "273350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004293381", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549108800.0} {"text": "Do not buy this video-game if you hate the following: - Star Wars Disney Canon™ - Basic Dark Souls-esc movement & combat mechanics - Puzzle-solving The music is the best part of the whole game. Save yourself the $60 and just listen here:", "appid": "1172380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057628986", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595419200.0} {"text": "В общем,ничего необычного,два часа качал при скорости 9мб\\сек. Запустил,прошел кучу диалогов с соглашениями. Пропустил всратое обучение. Потом игра обновилась и запросила перезапуска. Перезапустил,пошло нескончаемое наставление и объяснение каждой ссаной функции как будто я дебил. После 5 минут пропуска прошлого пункта,пришло время для присвоения ID. После 10 минут отказа в каждом из моих никнеймов или словосочетаний игра - удалена. Итог - зря потраченые 3ч жизни. CAPCOM - ARE U ♥♥♥♥ ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥? WHY A U BULLN ME? JUST STOP IT. GET SOME HELP.", "appid": "310950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198161443373", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1564833600.0} {"text": "Cancer. Spray and Run. Bad Netcode. And Fire Spit-Shotgun.", "appid": "696790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026488283", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506686400.0} {"text": "Do not buy this game at it's current state. Wait for the developers to fix the problems with stuttering during cutscenes AND gameplay along with the constant crashes. My game crashed within the first 15 seconds into the gameplay. This game is a real masterpiece, and deserves all the praise that it's gotten. Unfortunately, the PC port that we've gotten is not on par with the game itself. Buy it later, please!", "appid": "1151640", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981363722", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596801600.0} {"text": "repetitive, hackers, not fully working physics, small amount of modes to play with Other than that, I recommend buying it ON SALE.", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198280537494", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599307200.0} {"text": "\"После неудачного запуска For Honor из Ubisoft ушёл Джейсон Вандерберг\" (16.07.2017) Старт, как раз, был относительно не так уж и плох. Но их дальнейшее безразличие к отзывам и просьбам фанатов, сделало своей дело. Если бы они ИЗНАЧАЛЬНО отказались от P2P, то все (возможно) было бы куда лучше. И что они продолжают делать? Да, они все так же продолжают делать еженедельные анимации/мифические доспехи/таунты. Вот, недавно выпустили патч, который значительно чинит сетевую составлющую игры. А нет, показалось. Патч чинит проблемы с яростью персонажей....", "appid": "304390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069618766", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1488628800.0} {"text": "Всем привет. Чтобы понять что за игра - мне хватило поиграть 30 минут, и сказать этой игре \"Вон с Двора\". Купил эту игру в надежде что это будет неплохой survival, хоть и отзывы были самые разные - решил попробывать, но в ней всё плохо.... И почему же всё так? Плюсы: -Оптимизация (вот так вот).После захода в игру, меньше минуты лагов(видимо прогрузка), и игра стабильно идёт 30-40 фпс, без проседаний. -Лут. Всё как и должно в игре про выживание, вроде есть , но мало и немного. -Техника и фракции. -Мир. Большая карта (не Dayz конечно) + Бункера, есть где походить. И теперь что выбешивает в игре: -Стрельба. Оружие хз пойми куда стреляет, хоть и стреляешь после того как отдышишся. Да и урон наносит как с водяного стреляешь пистолета. -Анимация. Это вообще хоть глаз выколи. Играю как будто не человеком, а гибким гомункулом. Даже при ударах кулаком бывает руки в обратку загибаются. Анимация взаимодействиия смешна. Из колодца даже ведро не подымается, наливаешь и пьёшь из пустоты. -Боты. Глюченые и глупые. Стоят как вкопаные, в большинстве случаев, подходишь к ним за препятствием - дёргуются и орут, но не стреляют и не идут к тебе, да и на дальних дистанциях также. Оружие вытащат - стрельнут, и обратно в рюкзак и снова.. А когда в рукопашку дерёшься ,ммм, никогда не видел чтоб кто-то от удара прикладом улетал на 5 метров. +Когда лежишь на спине стреляют между ног просто - встаёшь, убивают сразу.. (либо колокола из железа у персонажа либо слепять врагов что те попасть не могут) -Пвп. Кто в броне тот и папа. Хоть запором дави игроков кто в хорошей защите, т.к. от оружия мало толку. -И по мелочи: Текстуры выпирают из других текстур. Проблемы со звуками. Вывод: Эту игру делать и делать. Можно было понять разработчиков если игру выпустили в ранний доступ месяца 2-3 назад, но выпускать из РАннего доступа настолько сырой и не доделанный продукт - это плевок в лица игроков. Лучше пока повременить с покупкой сего продукта, т.к. он не стоит своих денег ибо это больше похоже на какую-то бета версию игры чем на полноценный продукт.", "appid": "519190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026947980", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526990400.0} {"text": "Weird horror game, I thought I was playing as The Slasher, but I was actually a survivor trying to escape from 5 bloodthirsty high-school teenagers...", "appid": "1195460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069717461", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581854400.0} {"text": "Yeah", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086079342", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1442145600.0} {"text": "Heheh, this game has changed since i played it last. Its \"awesome\" now. Thats if you get to play it. I install the game from steam, the install was done in the morning, about 87gb....I push play happy that im gonna try it again....but oh what a surprise, the ESO's own launcher wants me to install another 87gb. of data. Searched the forums about it - it turns out its a known problem from last year. There people said its probably just patches and that they may be less than whats stated. Well thats cool and all, but it doesnt let you neglect the warning unless you have more than 87gb. So all in all....a very strange situation, which unfortunately will make me have to put a negative review on that one. At least fix your installers people. Thats like the first thing your customers see when getting acquainted with your games. Edit: 4.11.2020, two and a half years later - still the same. (facepalm)", "appid": "306130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008772998", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521720000.0} {"text": "This is one of the games should stay in miniclip. I don't want to play that game for free, 300Mb Of pure Scam.", "appid": "385200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198154341517", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490529600.0} {"text": "Lol! Po tak licznych pozytywnych recenzjach liczyłem na to, że w grze spędzę chociaż dwie godziny, a nie wyjdę tuż po pierwszych dwóch questach! Gra ma taki ohydny, nieintuicyjny i przeładowany interfejs, że aż nie chce się na to patrzeć. Zlewające się informacje, nudne ściany tekstu z wyjaśnieniami mechaniki, niepłynne poruszanie się postaci, totalnie żenujący poziom dialogów, historia banał... A co do grafiki, grałem na niskich; być może to dlatego gra nie miała mi nic więcej do zaoferowania, jako że twórcy najwyraźniej cały swój wysiłek wpakowali jedynie w zaawansowany edytor tworzenia lasek fantasy i widoczki :)", "appid": "582660", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997082432", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516968000.0} {"text": "This game is dead. Officially. Honestly, there should be some kind of a punishment for devs/publishers, who try to pull off stuff like this. First they cry for support on every corner, then they are grarbbing as much cash as the possibly can, then they run and never actually update the game. Why am I talking about such devs? Cause this is the exact case. It's safe to say that the game is actually unplayable, cause it simply won't let you change any settings (try changing sound effects or music volume, and you'll crash the game). Games like this is why people don't pre-order or buy Early Access, and for a good reason.", "appid": "611770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198005271335", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1582113600.0} {"text": "игра говно оптимизаци 0 кругом макросы и читеры", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198165320480", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515844800.0} {"text": "Конкретно к игре претензий не имею - можно сказать родоначальник жанра и моей любимой серии. Не без косяков, конечно, но их все можно считать частью ВЕСЬМА удачного эксперимента, чего не скажешь о Remastered версии: мало того, что самих изменений не так уж и много, так игра еще умудряется выдавать стабильные ошибки при запуске и лаги по части оптимизации. Еще здесь можно застрять в текстурах ( ) По части графики изменения можно увидеть лишь в детальных сравнениях на Ютубе: где-то подкрутили теней, где-то добавили световых эффектов. Впрочем, ничего нового Завезли мини-карту, наконец-таки, но где другие геймплейные возможности!? Почему до сих пор нельзя выбирать квест-задачи находясь непосредственно в транспорте? Почему бег постоянно прерывается стоит сдвинуть стик в сторону? Все это сугубо мелочи, но на протяжении местного, и так монотонного скучного геймплея (благодаря безыдейным сайд-квестам и странному сюжету) начинает бесить Владельцам оригинала обновленная версия досталась бесплатно, и на том спасибо.", "appid": "729040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198265230268", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569672000.0} {"text": "😢", "appid": "1266560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198159211894", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605355200.0} {"text": "looks like a 2008 flash game and plays like one too edit: good game insufferable players", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198149828258", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599739200.0} {"text": "Hilelerden oyun oynanmıyor.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198354669308", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490443200.0} {"text": "Il gioco mi ha annoiato, gli scontri frequenti e ripetitivi interrompono troppo spesso il ritmo, la storia non mi ha trasmesso grandi emozioni, i personaggi sono carini anche se l'umorismo è molto bambinesco, per non parlare del fandom dietro, a cui manco interessa la storia ma addirittura la sessualità dei personaggi.", "appid": "391540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198236668022", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1531224000.0} {"text": "sziasztokgyelekik", "appid": "440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198160686262", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491393600.0} {"text": "Just buy Dead By Daylight, it's damned 2.0 baiscly.", "appid": "251170", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997082784", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1467979200.0} {"text": "A game that is bad and I wasted my time and money on it...", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198344545174", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525694400.0} {"text": "Хоть игра и отвлекается отлично на нажати клавишь, но это не значит, что её стоит покупать... Ачивки только для количества, не более... Спасибо хоть карточки есть))) К покупке не рекомендую однозначно.", "appid": "581670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120235688", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530878400.0} {"text": "Do you remember that old pal you never really liked from back in the day? The one who always had to get the laser gun from the original game and yet kept complaining about how he disliked the smallest bubbles because he just didn't have the skills to do so? Of course, at least he did hit the platforms with it, wich drove him even more agitated as in the original you had to stay with your grapling hook to shoot them down. Wanna know what he does today? Well ... looks like he f*'n made this game, because he hates about everything from the original concept! Even the timeless piece of art that is the music tune playing throughout the levels got shoved out. There is just no reason at all to play this very reincarnation, apart from what looks like if you do so, you could unlock the original game as a bonus after completion of the overly stretched out tour mode. Avoid, if you love the original!", "appid": "415150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052707118", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590667200.0} {"text": "The screenshots and trailer no longer represent the game. MANY of the skins and some of the models have since been removed. The community is toxic now and anything other than complete and utter praise for this game and its devs will result in a horde of sycophantic fan boys descending on you. The devs are incredibly arrogant and insulting, frequently attacking or insulting their paying customers or their computer hardware. That being said... If I'd written this review a few months ago it would have been so different... Sadly, I can no longer recommend this game. I bought this game a few months back, from what I read and what I'd seen it seemed like a really cool game. There aren't many where you actually get to play as a dinosaur and that really appealed to me. On many occasions I would turn on The Isle and run around the sandbox like, open world servers. Sometimes I'd be a herbivore, a Stegosaurus or Ankylosaurus, and run around trying to ward off predators, find a herd and eat and drink my fill. Sometimes I'd be a carnivore, A T-Rex or an Allosaurus, and find a pack to hunt with, then hunt down some herbivores while trying to avoid being attacked myself. None of this is possible anymore... Not only have they implemented a \"progression system\" Where, each and every time you log in, die or the server crashes, you have to start out as the smallest dinosaur possible and wait a full 60 minutes to get enough points to be a slightly bigger dinosaur. This means that if you wanted to play one of the big carnivores or herbivores it would take , that is of course assuming you don't die and the server doesn't crash. If you are killed, die somehow, get stuck or the server crashes then you have to start It doesn't matter if you are 5 points into your first dinosaur or only need 5 more points to get the biggest, you go right back to the start. There is no \"save\" feature, no checkpoints, nothing. If, for whatever reason you die or are removed from the game your 3-4 hours of waiting around become meaningless. Some people may like this type of meaningless waiting around, this waiting to play the game. Personally I do not. The thing that annoys me is the fact that this is not the game I bought. I would not buy the game in its current state, not because it is early access, but because I don't like this type of game. I don't want to have to wait around for 3 hours in order to play it! If you haven't bought The Isle yet, I would strongly advise you to look at and decide whether you like the direction the game has gone in. If you do, then you can make an informed decision whether you would like to play it or not. For those of us that bought this game for what it was, we're basically screwed...", "appid": "376210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042871443", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "191", "votes_funny": "9", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1470312000.0} {"text": "526 horas en mi otra cuenta y debo decir que no recomiendo el juego. Con la salida de Zexal mejoró un poco, y la banlist hizo un buen trabajo pero hacia falta. El juego no ha mejorado lo suficiente como para atraer nuevos jugadores (nuevos en conocimiento de YGO), el meta sigue casi parecido, ahora es un poco más sencillo subir pero no para decks F2P. Algunos decks cuestan muchísimo, y que decir de un deck META. Toma el ejemplo de los nuevos SatellarKnight, son 5 a 6 monstruos UR de una misma caja, pero eso no es tan caro, lo caro es que si quieres jugar a casi cualquier deck necesitas Staples, en el deck mencionado se usa ballista (no siempre) es UR y necesitas 2 copias, es de otra caja, puedes reemplazarlo por enemy controller, pero no es lo mismo. Mi opinión es: Si quieres jugar, debes tener 3 cosas a mano, las cuales son, tiempo, paciencia, y dinero; la última pareciera broma pero es cierto. Creo que el juego debe mejorar en muchos aspectos, pero de Konami no espero mucho. Si quieres divertirte unas 100h adelante.", "appid": "601510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255751473", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591185600.0} {"text": "very fun to lose cus of your crewmates (SHAUNIS!!!)", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271922163", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603972800.0} {"text": "-много часов жизни", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198877124063", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582804800.0} {"text": "游戏饭圈化是大势所趋", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198275616581", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598270400.0} {"text": "Optimisation is dead.", "appid": "644830", "steamid": "profiles/76561198133570470", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569326400.0} {"text": "This game has become disgraceful. First 17 pieces of pay2win dlc, now pay2win microtransactions.", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198078930346", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1445083200.0} {"text": "No esta mal para pasar el rato, fue lo mejor en su momento. Pero ya es muy irrealista y demasiado arcade. No puede ser que UN TIGER TENGA QUE DISPARAR 50 VECES PARA MATAR A UN SHERMAN. En fin, no me quejo de que es divertido pero solo es para cuando estas aburrido.", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198176864319", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594987200.0} {"text": "помойка не оптимизированная, не советую", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198322649999", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575806400.0} {"text": "Miért...? Ez a játék egy böngáészőből megnyitható és bármikor játszható játékkal ér fel, csak fizetős... Még szerencse hogy ingyen megszerezhető volt... Egyébként mielőtt bárki pszichopatának gondol csak achivmentekért játszottam...", "appid": "554530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198343312525", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555934400.0} {"text": "Brian Hicks has destoryed the name Dayz. This game is boring nothing like the dayz mod which made you play for hours. Hopefuly soon they add modding support to save this dying ship of a game", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065442252", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1387195200.0} {"text": "Пустая трада денег,самый обычный обман пользователей эта игра и 150руб не стоит 1.Лута нигде нету, а если и есть то он совершенно бесполезный (за 2 часа нашел топор и одно яблоко) 2.Багов море:Летающие камыши,слепые зомби,провалы в текстуры,баги с лестницей и тд. 3.В игре дико скучно в отличии от модификации (там всегда движуха) Максимум за 1 час встретите другого бедолагу который будет пытаться убить вас за еду (которой катострофически не хватает) 4.Отвратительный интерфейс начиная с перезарядки винтовок (для этого нужно открыть инвентарь) это значит что если в перестрелке закончились патроны в обойме ты уже труп,также не понятен уровень еды, воды и крови Вывод: Отличный симулятор бомжа (ибо лутаться вы будете 24/7) \"\"4.5 бутылок боярышника из 10\"\" (За баги и низкий уровень оптимизации)", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105629374", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1493553600.0} {"text": "*Bot simulator *problemas de desempenho,ta precario jogar, já se passaram anos des do seu lançamento e o game continua sem fluides. add passe,add skins lança logo uma atualização pra arrumar tudo! outra coisa que deixou a desejar foi que não da pra selecionar o mapa que voce deseja jogar,tudo aleatório! Pubg pé na cova", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118588601", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588334400.0} {"text": "steaming pile of garbage just get pavlov", "appid": "957790", "steamid": "profiles/76561197989688466", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589976000.0} {"text": "49% читеров, 49% аутистов, детей, недоразвитых и других маргиналов, непонимающих что надо делать и как надо взаимодействовать с другими игроками. Если у тебя есть ДЕНЬГИ, ты можешь убивать всех имбами, типа БТР, разрывных патронов, миниганов и прочего дерьма. И тут есть еще одна проблема. Половина игроков читеры (наглухо отбитые и тупоголовые дегенераты) => они имеют кучу ДЕНЕГ, и, соответственно, имеют честных игроков, которые после обновления копят на эти плюхи как минимум неделю-полторы. Исходя из этого, играть в общественной сессии не доставляет никакого удовольствия, в принципе как и взаимодействие с другими игроками вообще.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057766651", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499601600.0} {"text": "horrible if your looking for horror games do NOT and i repeat DO NOT play this game its a beautiful mess", "appid": "241640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095044862", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1427544000.0} {"text": "Nah", "appid": "1174180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050038390", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578571200.0} {"text": "游戏是好游戏，是真的好游戏。 声优有的配音有些出戏，但是我相信会越来越好 我给差评，是因为模型抄袭，也许作者一个人没有多余的精力和资金，也许作者没有意识到这个问题的严重性，但是不管怎么洗，抄袭就是抄袭了。 但即便这样我依然是充满期待的，我期待中国游戏的发展和希望，他让我看到了中国制作人的未来，路一步一步走，饭一口一口吃，也许这个款游戏是抄袭了模型，但是技能系统，打击感以及画面可以算不错了不是吗。我等得起，因为我看到了这条路 我听闻作者已经在慢慢的修改模型，我是期待的，如果当游戏里抄袭的模型全部修改完，如果当正式版出来不会再有抄袭的问题。我会修改评价并且将这款游戏赠送给我身边游戏圈的朋友 祝国产游戏越来越好", "appid": "955050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198099414690", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "237", "votes_funny": "43", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1551096000.0} {"text": "Me sacaron mi juego!", "appid": "753650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047104900", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1603800000.0} {"text": "Mejor te hubieras quedado muerto: Es duro cuando un juego no alcanza siquiera tus expectativas y este es el caso: Kane & Lynch: Dead Men es una bazofia, de esas que poco o nada pueden rescatar y que, de no ser por su secuela de aparente mejoría, seria una saga para desecharla en el olvido. Gracias a Dios jugar a este videojuego en su tiempo no supuso ningún gasto para mí (porque lo jugué en la consola de un familiar). Somos Kane quien, por motivos que nunca se llegan a explicar, es traicionado por su propia organización / mafia / lo que sea, llamada Los7, y que deberá hacer todo lo posible para salvar a su mujer y a su hija. Durante toda la aventura nos acompañará Lynch, personaje jugable en cooperativo. El guión, que parece digno de un film de Hollywood, en realidad está muy mal relatado en el juego. Las 4 horas que durará la campaña son básicamente incomprensibles, ya sea porque de un lugar pasamos instantáneamente a otro sin mas que una simple explicación en voz en off, o porque existen \"lagunas\" que presentan los hechos antes de tiempo y, en consecuencia, nos perdemos completamente en el hilo argumental. Pero eso no es lo peor, sino que en ese muy corto tiempo no podremos realizar un lazo de empatía con alguno de los protagonistas: Uno que quiere hacer todo bien, y otro que siempre lo caga todo. Tal vez esto sea por la poca emotividad con la que se trata a estos 2 carismáticos personajes a lo largo del juego. Pero en resumen, es un apartado totalmente irrelevante y olvidable. Seré breve: Todas las mecánicas están rotas. Apuntar es impreciso, las coberturas o son muy rígidas a la hora de permitirnos usarlas, o son tan simples que no cumplen su función, y el movimiento de nuestro personaje es tosco. Cuando perdemos toda nuestra salud, estaremos incapacitados mientras tanto escucharemos voces con eco (en una decisión ciertamente agradable), y tendremos que esperar a que un compañero nos reviva. Si nos incapacitan de nuevo, entonces no podremos ser revividos, o sufriremos una \"sobredosis\" que da fin a la partida. 2007 no era precisamente el año de los efectos más impactantes, pero esto es el colmo. Las explosiones son planas, la iluminación es pobre, las cinemáticas son muy básicas, y la I.A triunfa solamente por la poca salud que tenemos, rivalizando incluso con Turok. Mientras que del apartado gráfico no hay mucho que decir. La costumbre de los juegos es que los protagonistas sean los que mejor modelado y texturas posean, pero aquí ambos factores son meramente correctos. Dicho esto, ya te podes imaginar como se ven los escenarios y los enemigos. El doblaje está bastante bueno y da con el personaje al igual que la banda sonora. Mientras que el sonido de las armas me resultó bastante simplón. He leído a muchas personas comparando a este juego con el primer Army of Two y nada que ver. También se puede acusar a los personajes de ser estereotipos, si, y que la historia es algo básica, pero el conjunto final no se ve muy a menudo. Es fácil darse cuenta porque este juego tuvo criticas mixtas. Esta muy roto, y da la sensación de que con controles mas fluidos, una campaña mas trabajada y un guión más llamativo, estaríamos hablando de un gran juego. Más solo me queda comentarte esto: Tienes una parte 2, así que aléjate de estos \"Hombres Muertos\". Mi nota: 4/10", "appid": "8080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198961683445", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590667200.0} {"text": "THIS GAME SUCKS DON'T BUY IT. THE HIT REG IS PURE ♥♥♥♥", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093502837", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1512216000.0} {"text": "oyun kötü almayın bence", "appid": "300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198324014426", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498996800.0} {"text": "Valve, bring back to us old gifting system", "appid": "50", "steamid": "profiles/76561198015399334", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502884800.0} {"text": "The game concept is AWESOME. Enough crafting for the moment, enough minerals, the game is awesome. Positive points : 1/ Simple but efficient graphics 2/ Improved gameplay, with simple building 3/ Amazing ambiants ,agriculture implemented with success. BUT many negative points : 1/ No multiplayer. Imagine the fact to play with friends to build a base and survive together underwater? It would ROCK. But it wont exist, as the developpers doesnt seem to want to implementate it. 2/ The game story is extremely short ( i finished it in 2h20 ) and could be improuved. 3/ The game seems abandonned. And THATS a tragedy. I would not recommand this game for these reasons, i'm totally disapointed by the fact the game has no multiplayer gamemode, an extremely short story, compared to the rich gameplay and environnements/crafting thats it contains.", "appid": "286340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084022012", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1440676800.0} {"text": "Игра мне не понравилась. У нее плохая оптимизация , мрачная и не красивая атмосфера , про графику я нечего не буду говорить , потому что игрушка старенькая и смысл судить про графику, плохое управление транспортом(кроме вертолётов), чтобы проходить сюжетную линию нужно получать очки авторитета для этого нужно выполнять дополнительные миссии , это бывает скучно. Из плюсов можно подчеркнуть отличную музыку, музыка как придуманая авторами так и знаменитые песни старых годов, много видов транспорта. Моя оценка Ужано.", "appid": "9480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198806659373", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "Проект достаточно специфичный, рассказывающий о кофейне, куда приходят только что умершие люди. Вцелом, подача сюжета через эдакие замороженные во времени 3Д сцены представляет интерес. Если вам сильно интересно следить за рассуждающими о смысле жизни и смерти людьми - можно посмотреть. НО! 1) Готовьтесь к тому, что звуков здесь очень мало и преимущественно слушаешь музыку на фоне. 2) Никаких развилок сюжетных тут нет. 3) Какой-никакой геймплей есть, но скорее \"никакой\". Надо угадывать к какой \"теме\" относятся конкретные слова, но их хрен угадаешь. Вобщем, игра на любителя, но, к сожалению, я этим любителем не оказался. Более подробно рассказываю здесь (не бойтесь, не летсплей :)) :", "appid": "725270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035366861", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600516800.0} {"text": "Играть норма. Я просто спрашиваю что как сделать мы значит мм понимаю. Я но неважно старый года давно быть кто играть понравлюсь понял и отлично Место что не понимаю почему не видел обратно теперешний мда Ну память сохрани RESIDENT EVIL 2 / BIOHAZARD RECELATIONS 2 (", "appid": "287290", "steamid": "profiles/76561198155230008", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590926400.0} {"text": "The game was ok at start and followed a logic of checkpoints in case of a fail which it followed until the very end in which the checkpoint was right next to the gate instead of outside where the snow was, forcing me to end it without wanting to and explore that hall more. So because it didn't follow the safety logic until the end and made you force end the game without your volition I wanted to give it a 8/10 but won't, I give it a 6/10, that was something that ruined my experience of it and got me extremely annoyed by it doing that. In order to go back and do it you need to redo the whole game, no, I am uninstalling it right now and I hope the programmers fix such stupid rookies mistakes in the future. I mean come on, the real exit was like 20 meters ahead of you but you put the script to end the game and not allowing even a checkpoint in case the player wanted to explore more, now that's stupid and you should learn from that. An easy fix would be a confirmation to end the game too. That gate ending right as soon as you step out angered me extremely because I was returning back towards the hall too, just came around it to see if there is something on the other side. Won't be trying the second game because of that, unless it gets fixed, only then will I even consider it.", "appid": "582500", "steamid": "profiles/76561197975294582", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549108800.0} {"text": "Interesting approach to an NSFW game; normally it would just be 'virtual fun' if you catch my meaning; however the real points go to the artistic design of the game. It is no joke when the game is inspired by Lovecraft and H.R. Giger because you can see & hear it everywhere in this prologue alone. HOWEVER; while i give points to the artistic design -- i give negative points to the gameplay; it's essentially fetch quests \"go do this\" \"do a puzzle\" etc, etc. You know how it goes. Depending on the price point in the full game is the huge factor; overall i say if you are curious then try it! However, do not be surprised how very little this prologue has to offer; obviously the full release is going to be different; but this does not warrant a full download P.S. NO there is no NSFW option once completing the demo", "appid": "1170820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068329619", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602936000.0} {"text": "F Battlerite, SLS u s^ck!", "appid": "879160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048425649", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562155200.0} {"text": "Its pretty meh", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198031313244", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1500033600.0} {"text": "Makes no sense especially near the end, some characters basically have no reason to be there and you dont understand what theyre doing and kreia is dumb and makes no sense. you teleport to the end planet with no cutscene and all your party is dead and all the sith etc are cookie cutter not actual bosses and one of the \"sith lords\" doesnt even have any dialogue but your character pretends to understand it or something. terrible game not finished and whatever kreia tries to tell you makes absolutely no sense. and this is WITH the restored content mod", "appid": "208580", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132960019", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1547812800.0} {"text": "Игра для обезьян, обожаю :3", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198023937472", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511524800.0} {"text": "no", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198847213186", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "80", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544097600.0} {"text": "Short story", "appid": "417860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198867427613", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588334400.0} {"text": "Definitely not what I was expecting from this game. Many people appearantly find it a lot of fun, but I find it boring and repetitive.", "appid": "245490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050185655", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1402142400.0} {"text": "Oyunu direksiyon seti olmayan almasın. Oynanışı çok zor. Ayrıca simülatör mantıklı bir oyun.", "appid": "244210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198047265254", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511784000.0} {"text": "Dota 2 R.I.P.", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198208297113", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "В эту часть стоит играть только купив подписку, своей полной цены она не стоит. В игре достаточно много багов: проходы сквозь текстуры, топорные нпс, кривые анимации. Уровень интеллекта у нпс тоже оставляет желать лучшего, на сложности ветеран играется так же как на новичке. В принципе неплохой сюжет, не отличный, но не плохой. Понравился геймплей, в частности возможность арестовать преступника, ты здесь все-таки за копа играешь е**ный сыр. Большой выбор оружия и кастомизация, вариативность прохождения игры можешь пройти по стелсу арестовав всех или убив(оглушив) или ворваться и раз**бать все на*й. В целом 5/10 это не тот Battlefield который все так любят. P.s онлайн мертвый не берите ради мультиплеера.", "appid": "1238880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198274148725", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603195200.0} {"text": "Another Hyped Bullsh!t Early Access Survival game with broken promises. Back to DayZ (which is actually becoming real good finally). They made jokes about dayZ .... now Scum is the joke", "appid": "513710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063898155", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "oynuyorum ama siz OYNAMAYIN aq oyununu", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198312645899", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589889600.0} {"text": "游戏总的来说还是挺好的，但是！ 一堆bug，还有一些反人类设计，游戏体验极差，不是东方厨不建议入！", "appid": "776490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085594514", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516708800.0} {"text": "Not the same anymore. Played it for about 2 years and the game just gets worse. They even cut their developers. Was fun for a while, I even got this game back when it was worth money, would love to get my money back. But hey, if you want this game go for it. You'll just run into the same people every game. Good luck, thanks Daybreak for ruining this once amazing game. :)", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198161461907", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1484222400.0} {"text": "Joguei achando que iria ganhar uma medalha de honra mas não ganhei nada, não cumpriu com o nome do jogo.", "appid": "47790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198408326248", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600948800.0} {"text": "Playing through Temple of Sun alone as sorcerer. Game balance is so bad that I cannot recommend this game to anyone. Enemies have way too much HP and bosses are just pure pain. I am struggling with the end game boss and it is not fun at all. Not even challenging fun. Just awful design. Here are its abilities: * Lots of HP. I guess in range of thousands. My regular attack does 12 points of damage. * It keeps spawning endless amount of ranged unit. * Every enemy in the level does fire damage so even if you get hit only once, it keeps burning you. * In each phase, boss gets new ability. In third phase, it gets tracking fire pillars. In fourth and last phase, it gets tracking fireballs. One hit from either pillar or ball will kill you because of extended fire damage. Unless you use potion but you only have one. So you have at maximum one hit before you die. * Best part: boss regenerates if you are outside of combat area. And it regens fast. If you die, it has gained all the damaged health back and likely even more. So extra lives are useless because you have to kill it without dying. I have over 25k gold that I cannot use because there are no upgrades left for sorcerer. Another messed up gameplay design flaw! Got through third phase by just kiting the boss in circular motion. This is the only way I found to survive. Unfortunately, each round only nets you couple hits so this took me perhaps 30 mins of kiting. Who finds this kind of gameplay fun or engaging? Did the dev even play the game and boss? Feels more like just hammering as much difficulty as one can without thinking.", "appid": "239070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004748172", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595246400.0} {"text": "Developers are tryhards to milk the money cow to the very last drop", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198088357458", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511352000.0} {"text": "Singleplayer is very meh, but that's not the reason you bought/want to buy this game. Multiplayer loading is long, there are modders.... lots of modders in almost every lobby. Some drop you money, some explode everyone, or grief in different game. You have lots of things to do, but you can't do them, because recently missions cannot be started/completed. I highly don't recommend this game. Just go buy something else or wait for GTA 6.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198188059271", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602072000.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "287390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121188476", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1548763200.0} {"text": "it had potential its fun to play however u might consider the modding community dead coz of the constant updates that ruins all the mods that are recently updated poor modders gotta re code everything to scratch just to keep the mod alive but the devs dosent kinda give a ♥♥♥♥ about the modders hardwork since the content that devs have been making is juicing all the money out of it i really had fun playing it but its not worth the price if it isnt sale", "appid": "302670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198213717747", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578139200.0} {"text": "filled with child predators and e-daters do not recommend", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198034874619", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "12", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1461412800.0} {"text": "Bought GTAV in 2017 on sale excited to pla