nu - Camera movement feels like ♥♥♥♥ and mess up controls - Enemy AI is broken (they will get stuck in mostly of times) - There are no settings, nor pause menu - This is an \"Achievement\" spam based game too, but the dev can't even do that good, achievements stop unlocking after some time and it's necessary restart the game (and cross your fingers) to make achievements work again This game is meant to be , the dev really wants to make you play it but you can jump on a car (enemies won't hit you) so you can do something else on 3 hours 🌟☆☆☆☆", "appid": "589390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091959655", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1502280000.0} {"text": "The game is fun, had fun playing it,but is virtually incompatible with Steam. Unless you have a really LARGE storage disk and a FAST ISP you will have to suffer 6-8 hour update download every 3-ish weeks. They like to blame steam, yet they knew how steam worked prior to coming here. I believe they only did it to then make you go download and use their own client to span their other games to you? Either way, as I said, I like the game a lot, but their mostly trivial (Silly events) updates to so many of their files causes steam to slap you with a 4-6 gb \"Update\" every 3-4 weeks before you can play again. Hence, I uninstalled and no, I won't be getting their client just for this game.", "appid": "552990", "steamid": "profiles/76561198194801761", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572609600.0} {"text": "Нахуя я потратил целых 2 бакса а точнее 120 р и купил эту игру 20 дней назад ?) Игра оказалось говном особенно система крафта бронежилета! и спрея у оружия! Полное дерьмоЁ", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198317531292", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520510400.0} {"text": "clunky and laggy gameplay.", "appid":