his game is honestly God awful. Props having an option in the menu settings where you can mute it. Secondly, the graphics are painful to look at, and are even buggy too. How are you even supposed to play this game if you and your opponent's cards are appearing as pink textures? It's an unplayable mess. I didn't even pay for this game (received a free code for it), but it's definitely not worth the price it currently is. I don't think this is even worth over a quid, now that I think about it.", "appid": "343180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198207044979", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515067200.0} {"text": "Un juego totalmente injugable para Laptops/Pcs de gama media y baja, las specs estan desactualizadas y el juego va muy mal, basicamente el juego está muy pero que muy mal optimizado, me corre mejor el rust.", "appid": "251570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198250998194", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1594123200.0} {"text": "日，卡死了，我不玩了", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073197154", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "24", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1507377600.0} {"text": "Wasted a few minutes of my life for a free hat. Sent this game spiralling back to the trash bin where it belongs.", "appid": "99900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198174282142", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "21", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549886400.0} {"text": "говно", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060603844", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561982400.0} {"text": "good game, BUT -> We need to solve the problem with the over populated server I was waiting in a quee with 3301 people waiting along side me", "appid": "761890", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051464035", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555848000.0} {"text": "Купил игру со скидкой, долго ждал хорошей цены на эту игру. Думал, сейчас поиграю, но как говорится не получилось. Полчаса я пытался принять код для регистрации, причем он приходил, но лаунчер его не принимал. Потом заработала и я попал в абсолютно не дружественный интерфейс, нет нормального туториала, не понятно даже как взлететь. Крайне не рекомндую.", "appid": "359320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198105145253", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1475582400.0} {"text": "Интересная задумка, очень атмосферно. Но весьма скучно. Поиграла в бету, через время купила игру в раннем доступе и поиграла с друзьями. В основном были тупняки во время прохождения, вследствие чего мы умирали и начинали заново. Продвигались помаленьку. Да, прикольно начать заново раз, два, три, пять, но потом уже все матчи превратились в невероятное уныние и скуку. Звуки и музыка в игре хорошие. Влюбилась в оформление интерфейса, ну и монстры средненькие, неплохие. На этом всё. Вернула обратно, так как больше нет желания в неё играть. Не затягивает вообще. Очень интересует лор этой игры, хотелось бы почитать про вселенную, про действующих лиц, про монстров, лабораторию и обо всем, что в игре собстна происходит.", "appid": "493520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069304119", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1603627200.0} {"text": "toxic", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198277944245", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586692800.0} {"text": "!", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198038511857", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1559217600.0} {"text": "el juego es exelente pero sus servidores son muy malos no puede ser que tenga 200ms en todo momento y eso que el servidor esta en brasil pero no es como en otros juegos que en brasil tenes 60ms, en fin el juego es bueno pero sus servidores no", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120294104", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508500800.0} {"text": "I really wish I could pick between a thumbs up and down, because this game has potenial, constant updates, and passionate devs, but there are just so many bugs, systems, and components that if you are a new player and you don't have a friend to guide you, you will struggle, you will fail, and you will hate this game. The fact that rather than fix issues with texture collision, the devs descided to add an \"/unstuck\" command speaks for itself and I have yet to play a single game session without running into a bug. The tutorials are severally out of date, new features added are rarely explained propperly, and there almost seems to be a requirement to fail at least once before the game decides you might need an explaination that is still not comprehensive enough. I would have quit this game a long time ago if it were not for people guiding me through the many confusing bits, but honestly, if you are starting this game solo, good luck, because you are going to get overwhelmed as soon as you start. The worst part is the addition of the open worlds, which is usually something I would like since I love open worlds but the implementation of a host-based system means that if the host disconnects, you lose all of your progress. Imagine that in any other game: you spend hours doing activities and then the host decides to leave and thus you lose everything. at the very least, the devs could follow the method of gta online but with all of the bugs in this game I cannot recommend this game.", "appid": "230410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198059095828", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541937600.0} {"text": "Играл я в подобные игры в ВК и на мобилках. В основном это были клоны клонов от Plarium Games. Правила Войны, Корсары, Спарта, Кофликт и прочие подобные. Каждый раз я играл в них два дня, потом удалял. Решил глянуть чем отличается Warhammer: Chaos And Conquest. Да практически ничем, разве что рынка нет с чертежами. Потому что какой в пекло может быть у хаоситов рынок с мать его чертежами. Прокачка ппц какая долгая, геймплей унылый, на хайлэвэле может поинтересней, но без доната там туго. Не стоит она потраченного времени. Но если вы всё же ищете ММО стратегию, то советую обратить внимания на Stronghold Kingdoms, она поглубже будет.", "appid": "1144170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050171135", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603195200.0} {"text": "쓰레기 폰게임류 뭐 하려고 하면 무조건 캐시 질러서 가속해야함", "appid": "378760", "steamid": "profiles/76561197965243451", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1588420800.0} {"text": "gay.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198823305326", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577793600.0} {"text": "Awesome game, ruined by a patch that installs kernel level anticheat in a primarily singleplayer game. Gross invasion of privacy, one that you as a consumer should not tolerate in 2020.", "appid": "782330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096587097", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "32", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589803200.0} {"text": "Useless", "appid": "1046930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198372979773", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1574856000.0} {"text": "Update, after 3 more Hours of Gameplay: The Pixel-Problems (Characters \"Cut in half\") are clearly most impactful on Feena. What's really positive is the Gamespeed when you're leveling, menuing, fighting or exploring - it makes the Game feel more enjoyable. Still, no thumbs up because of the graphical issues - will be a thumbs up if they at least TRY to fix it on a regular basis. Grandia is my favourite Game ever, but it has a lot to do with Nostalgia. I really looked forward to play it in the HD-Version, the Screenshots and Gameplay looked awesome. After the first 3.5 Hours of Gameplay i'm really disappointed...the Game itself is great, the Battle System and the Story is just as good as it was nearly 22 Years ago. BUT: In every little Cutscene there are Pixel-Bugs at the Character-Models (Characters seem \"Cut-in-half\"), Sound-Glitches still happen in some places (Battlestarts, strange Loops, etc.) and in some Scenes the Camera glitches out or the Scene isn't made for Widescreen (Opening Scene especially, Models staying on Screen when they shouldn't, etc.). Seriously, wasn't there any Playthroughs of the Game by Testgamers? I can't believe this. There are so many obvious flaws its ridicoulus. I'm very sad GungHo launched this Game in such a State. I'm no Fan of using Emulators, so i was more than willing to pay Money to get a new Version of this Masterpiece. In this State, especially if you're not as Nostalgic about the Game as the most of us - don't buy it.", "appid": "1034860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026348154", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "81", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571227200.0} {"text": "everything was very nice since I started playing solo company But ur multiplayer is literally ♥♥♥♥. it's always crashing after like 5-2 minutes I tryed to fix it by ur guide, but it still crashing The only reason why I'm posting such a bad review is based on this crash. Solo gameplay 9/10 Multiplayer 3/100", "appid": "813780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198292471091", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586347200.0} {"text": "dis game is bad", "appid": "304930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011266350", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1463659200.0} {"text": "Lo malo de este juego no se puede jugar live hay que tener una cuenta de windows live y activar la clave del producto pero el modo historia se puede jugar offline pero es algo corto juego y un final muy malo del Resident Evil: Operation Raccoon City", "appid": "209100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148732270", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1466251200.0} {"text": "Возможно......когда нибудь........в эту игру можно будет нормально играть , а может быть даже и пройти...... но не сейчас . ПРОСТО ТОТАААААААААААААЛЬНЕЙШИЙ ДИСБАЛАНС!!! Даже не подходите к этой куче кода.", "appid": "691630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032924730", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541246400.0} {"text": "C'est devenu un gros P2P pour farmer chinois. Bien sûr vous pouvez toujours y jouer en F2P, seule la première map est gratuite. Pour pouvoir accéder aux autres map, soit vous grindez comme un vieux porc tous les calicobas afin de vous payer un voyage sur la seconde map, une license obligatoire pour pouvoir viander celle-ci ainsi qu'un peu de stuff qui sera rapidement useless pour les maps suivantes. Soit vous allez postuler au mcdo, avec votre première paye vous aurez peut-être assez d'argent pour passer par le cash shop et enfin voyager sur une ou deux map suivantes avec license et stuff adapté... mais je vous promets rien. Quoiqu'il en soit, la deuxième solution est probablement la plus rapide. Enfin, après 3000 congélos remplis de fish et une fois lvl max, vous n'êtes pas à l'abri d'une maj qui va faire flamber les prix des voyages/licenses/stuff... etc. C'est bien ce qu'il s'est passé messieurs les déveloparnaqueurs? Et vous vous retrouverez sur la première map gratuite comme pakpak à devoir faire la manch... heu, à devoir sortir des trillions de calicoba pour pouvoir vous payer une réparation de stuff. Grâce à ce nouveau stuff flambant presque neuf, si votre volonté est toujours intact, vous pourrez commencer à pêcher les 300 trillions de perche soleil supplémentaires nécessaire au paiement de votre futur voyage sur une autre carte. Oui ça sent le vécu, mais j'ai arrêté au premier poisson. Bref si vous avez 5 min (sans compter le temps de dl) de votre vie à perdre, pourquoi pas.", "appid": "380600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198021841581", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528545600.0} {"text": "This game is ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥. I'm glad I got it free and so happy I did not buy it. My goodness the maximum resolution is 1280 x 1024 which made the everything seem awkward looking. This is a first person platforming game and you control a character wherein in order for you finish a level you must try to avoid different bear traps, lasers and what not blocking your way. However, the jump control does not respond when you press it and it just based on pure luck. Jumping is very essential to the game and why is it broken and unresponsive WTF? That is plain stupidity on the part of the developers. This game made me curse a lot and I just probably might go to hell for it. This game cost Php70.00 in my country which is rather cheap but after playing this awful game the developers should add Php70.00 on my Steam Wallet. If there was a Top Worst Games List on Steam this would be in the upper-echelon. Putik-ng-inang game ito.", "appid": "443940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189605322", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "44", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1461585600.0} {"text": "-rep girls have no nipples or vaginas", "appid": "981910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198173250889", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1559736000.0} {"text": "THIS IS STUPID I CANNOT LOAD INTO LOBBY SERVER K