n bazen buga giriyor,kamera açısı bozuluyor kullanıcılarda çok fazla ping var vs. -------------------- DİĞER 【♡】 Multiplayer Multiplayer tabanlı bir oyun. -------------------- 2/10", "appid": "527450", "steamid": "profiles/76561198121805618", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538740800.0} {"text": "this game is lag-inducing, unbalanced, pay-to-win, unofficial trash. it makes me want to hide in a corner and cry every time i see it in my library. it has a toxic community that won't even help you if you say you have a problem on the topic discussion. it's not even fair that you have to constantly grind to be on the level of the PTW'ers. the people who upvoted this are just happy they get to dominate people who don't throw money at everything they play, and they want more people to play it so they can dominate them forever. TL;DR: don't get this game. you'll cry if you do.", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163990101", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1465646400.0} {"text": "Bad game to start with I couldn't find the keys I needed and then I had to use a code for the keypad which I think I found but the code doesn't work and the frost is the problem when I can't find the yellow potions anymore.", "appid": "890880", "steamid": "profiles/76561197972300511", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580126400.0} {"text": "игра скатилась в ямуу :с зачем играть в это дерьмо ? -что бы получить удовольствие и поднять ранг а ху* ты это сделаешь с кучей читеров и бустеров теперь скажу как работает вак вот есть 10 читеров забанят токо того у кторого бл* был бесплатный софт я сожелею что потратил деньги на эту игру (она ещё и подешевела ведь валве надо что бы она преносила доход, а раз она подешевела читеры тратят меньше денег на новые аккаунты) вопщем не кому не советую покупать а темболее донатить в это дерьмо вот когда игра станет бесплатно(а она станет бесплатной) то тогда можете смело качать софты и еб*шить по рейджу.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198385484761", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518004800.0} {"text": "Сижу зачищаю карту, не помню имен персонажей вообще. Уже начинает подташнивать от мелких однообразных заданий. Здесь есть крутые места, да и в целом красота и окружение это плюс игры, один из факторов, который может завлечь на прохождение. Однако, я играю после Одиссеи, поэтому все локации не такие уж и эксклюзивные. Я снова захожу и вижу ретекстур одних и тех же камней, заборов, зданий, природы, и так далее. Дыры в заборе в том же месте, под тем же углом. Это нормально (может быть? я не знаю?). Все сливается в размазанное пятно после нескольких часов скаканий по карте, так что внимание на отдельные города уже не обращаешь в любом случае. Что это там? Это деревья, на которых обычно требуется синхронизироваться, те самые, которые почему-то торчат абсолютно идентично из одних и тех же скал по всей территории Египта и Греции. Да. Это сиамские деревья, почему нет. Неудивительно, что игры успевают пилить по одной, а то и две в год. Точно понятно то, что брать их каждый год абсолютно не стоит. Сюжет не совсем дно, но на пару сантиметров выше разве что. Зачем я в это играю? В итоге все, что я запомню - гринд. Позабавил момент, где надо было в одном месте зачистить очередной сундук. Подхожу, а там пятнадцать мать их змей. Пятнадцать. Просто рядом друг с другом, кроме шуток, в полуметре друг от друга. Им там нормально вообще такое делать в игре? В тот момент помимо этого вопроса проскочила тупая мысль по поводу атмосферной части. Разве местных не смущает, что у них там такая популяция ползающих тварей буквально возле дороги? А с другой стороны, почему это вообще должно кого-то волновать? Мир мертв. Ведь все нпс тупо слоняются по городу щебещут про себя какую-то хрень, а вооруженные ждут пока я приду зачистить очередную хату или блокпост, чтобы снова там заспавниться (я еду крышей?). Просто все контрл-с-контрл-в. Это не разбавляют вообще никакие квесты, какие тут могут быть эмоции, кроме желания поскорее закончить и больше не притрагиваться к подобным вещам. Надо было слушать маму, ведь она говорила: \"Часики то тикают!\". И правда, какой в этом смысл в итоге? А время уже не вернешь. После таких открытых миров нужна как минимум долгая реабилитация. Учитывая то, что Одиссея вышла уже после, то что-то глобально изменить не получилось, если и там под конец закрытия контента было ощущение полной за*банности. В душе пустота. Зато скриншоты будут красивые. Все это - мое мнение (такое же перемешанное и жидкое, как мозг в моей голове) по поводу тех моментов в игре, которые реально даже такого как человека как я заставили изосрaться, это совсем не значит, что вся игра состоит только из этого. GG.", "appid": "582160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168539853", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "79", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582545600.0} {"text": "trash", "appid": "397900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198248896802", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592481600.0} {"text": "Ну что, довольно скучненькая игра с однообразным геймплеем. Все монстры убиваются почти одинаково, а даётся для этого пара пукалок и дедова трость. Конечно, сложность с уровнями возрастает, но ничего особенно сложного для людей, хоть раз игравших в игры, тут не найти. Итого 9 уровней, унылый сюжет и кучи квадратных человечков. Жаль потраченное время, хотя уже в начале хотелось свернуть, забыть и дождаться заветных карточек за игру, которая стоит 3р. В общем,", "appid": "303390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198011585139", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1419249600.0} {"text": "yo pre-ordene el juego. mi experiencia fue mala. los servidores tardan muchisimo tiempo en encontrarme una partida (estamos hablando de 20-45 minutos). lo peor que puede orurrir es que a los 3 minutos de jugar se te desconecte de la partida. que pasa? no volves a la partida en la que estabas y tenes que esperar unos 40 minutos mas hasta encontrar una partida. te pone a pelear con compañeros bots totalmente faciles y poco cooperativos lo cual si se te desconecta un compañero y te coloca un bot fuiste... otra cosa es el desbalance que tiene el juego. hay ciertos PJ que son muy OP y que uses quien uses no tenes chances. realmente confie en ubisoft. cai bajo la trampoa de los graficos y youtube. nunca mas caigo en tus trampas Ubisoft!", "appid": "304390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198125602200", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491220800.0} {"text": "ПОЛНЯ ХУЙНЯ КАК В ТАКУЮ ПАРАШУ ИГРАТЬ Я ДУМАЛ ЭТО РЕАЛЬНАЧ ЖИЗНЬ А ЭТО РЕАЛЬНАЯ ХУЙНЯ ПИЗДЕЦ ШО ЭТО КАК В ЭТО ИГРАТЬ ЕБ ВАШУ МАТЬ АААААААА. КАЧАТЬ СОВЕТУЮ ЕСЛИ ВЫ ДОЛБОЕБ. ГРЯЗНАЯ АНАЛЬНАЯ ДЫРКА ИЗ 10", "appid": "313630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198210249888", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538568000.0} {"text": "When I first bought the vanilla version the game ran up till a certain point in the game until a bug broke my game file and made it unplayable. I bought the \"REDUX\" version and encountered a different yet gamebreaking bug. The greedy publisher would not offer a discount to those that already owned the game already.", "appid": "287390", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967605168", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517140800.0} {"text": "I'm not quite sure if there's more than one version of this game but the one I have is awful. The game is very small, not that difficult since the solutions to the puzzles are presented to you. The only thing that made it a bit harder for me was the poor quality of the images of the hidden-object challenges but nothing that I couldn't overcome. The game isn't worth the money, at least I got it in a bundle with way better games of the same genre so my loss wasn't that significant.", "appid": "294390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080001787", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1441454400.0} {"text": "闪退，各种方法试了依旧不好使。最受不了的是steam EA会员只能 在steam用和EA烂橘子平台不共通！买个会员就图玩个fifa年货和非EA的独立游戏，fifa锁区，EA上的playlist还玩不到，还算期待的和睦小镇玩不了，我还买了年会员，我是大傻逼！！！", "appid": "1262240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198364590099", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599134400.0} {"text": "Испортили игру", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263500848", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572868800.0} {"text": "dsodupy mGRA ZZJEBANA CHUJ W DUPE TEJ GEEERXZEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198404209646", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598356800.0} {"text": "lo scopo di questo gioco è stare fermi, prendere delle chiavi che ti appariranno davanti e metterle nei rispettivi lucchetti che ti appariranno davanti... fine. cagata assoluta 10 euro buttati nel cesso", "appid": "680780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198083177078", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506254400.0} {"text": "Fu", "appid": "1140440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198981054882", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605009600.0} {"text": "This review is my personal opinion if you dont like it or do not agree with some points nothing cant be done there :) So game was having a free weekend and i gave it a try. I have been simracing for almost 3 years now. Big fan of AC and ACC and FFB in those games. Positives + F1 cars are looking great + Campaign in the game is well made (did not play it but i did watch gameplay) +Little details on track and cars ( monitors around tracks, warning lights, tires wear?) Negatives - menu controls swaping in between the wheel buttons controls and keyboard button controls. No mouse :/ not a fan of that.( just as an example in ACC i can use my keyboard and mouse to control the menu and all options and then when i am on track i can also use wheel and keyboard in the same time widouth controls scheme swaping around) - BIG BIG Negative in this game are tracks. Some tracks have such weird look and weird corners that are nothing like IRL. For licenced game this is big no from me.. for a big company like Codemasters that they can not deliver laserscaned track is big dissapointment -FFB is horrible imho car and ffb feels weird driving on the wheel. I tried fiddling with the ffb settings improved it a bit but still feels weird. -Physics I just could not get it.. car starts loosing back you cant feel it on wheel. In the corner letting the car cruise feels like its getting artificialy slowed down turning in corners -watched graphics comparison videos from f1 2018 and 2019 only improvement was lighting and it looks good but all other textures in game are reduced quality. So with these couple of hours spent on the game over free weekend, doing some laps and as a huge fan of F1 i am glad i got to try this game out. But as a sim racer i would not buy it.", "appid": "928600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063570798", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": "9", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572782400.0} {"text": "The game is really fun and visually not that bad considering its from 2009, but can't really suggest getting it specially if you use a newer system constantly keeps crashing after I try to load a save file,did try to find solutions but cant really find anything helpful.", "appid": "10150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198379490128", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530100800.0} {"text": "what can i say is Pay to Win and so Old", "appid": "781030", "steamid": "profiles/76561198190282910", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1551355200.0} {"text": "Csgo 0800 ? Hack simulator by valve.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051362773", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544875200.0} {"text": "As Much as I love Tomb Raider, and knowing this was a rushed game... either I get Controller support that works, CONTROLLS THAT WORK, Im sorry... this game honestly is just not tomb raider", "appid": "225020", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081010969", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1420977600.0} {"text": "trash", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198287946977", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498824000.0} {"text": ": :", "appid": "888800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163677213", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596628800.0} {"text": "Great! Rockstar simply deleted my character that I played 1,500 ♥♥♥♥♥♥ hours (and permanent BAN). Thanks...", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198276040712", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "728", "votes_funny": "114", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1482321600.0} {"text": "看到steam好評才買的，玩了之後才發現是中國人洗好評出來的，被騙了很不爽。 對白 super 生硬又尷尬，就好像是硬湊上去的，正常人根本不會這樣對話， 你是300年沒跟女生講過話嗎，只會幻想出這種語句，就不能潤一下嗎？ 劇情也是他媽的不合理。 音效、配樂做得很粗糙，你是不懂得留白嗎？無關緊要的場景也要放上背景樂， 像是填空一樣，發現哪邊沒聲音就不爽，硬是要把它填滿，而且太罐頭了。 語音也不能控制速度。 遊戲性、過場、UI控制都需要再加強。", "appid": "1377360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198103936574", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "32", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601899200.0} {"text": "não rodou eu uma rtx 2070 mas rodava antes quando eu tinha grafico integrado ???????????????????", "appid": "10150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198243624274", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Минусы игры: Наши любимые минусы: 1)Графа плохая (хотя меня это не сильно задело). 2)Плохое звуковое сопровождение. 3)Имеется сюжет, но он очень плохо продуман. 4)Плохо проработанный инвентарь. 5)Имеются баги - Можно пройти через текстурку замка, прыжком поднять целую корету и запихнуть в любую текстуру. Очень сложно взять вещи, нашёл меч, но вруки взять так и не смог. 6)Игра Однообразна - 1 вид еды (Яблоки), врагов (Они похожи на Shao Kahn из Mortal Kombat, только с мечом), крестьян, а вот стражи будет чуть больше. 7)Очень плохо продуманна смена погоды. Плюсы: 1)Можно построить свой Замок. 2)Можно нанимать собственное войско. Это всё, игра находится в Ранним доступе, так что всё может изменится. Я буду накидывать ещё на этот обзор, чтобы не было дезинфы. Спасибо за внимание!", "appid": "382240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198142411119", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1444132800.0} {"text": "Скучная", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201610493", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541937600.0} {"text": "The worst game I ever played. The controls are way too sensitive, tons of random obstacles visible and invisible, you crash into something in less than 5 seconds. Then it's game over and you have to restart. Not fun, impossible difficulty, even free would be too expensive.", "appid": "834420", "steamid": "profiles/76561197960560399", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553774400.0} {"text": "игра норм настоящий classic, нет скинов ,есть модельки но комьюнити... играю на паблике поставил хедшот [я не читер софты не использую и использовать не буду] похоже админу ииииии бан причина aim detected ,бан на 1 год. -хороший сервак. не дай бог vac прилетит.", "appid": "10", "steamid": "profiles/76561198386041335", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532174400.0} {"text": "100500 разрывов соединения из 100", "appid": "304390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198022827288", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487505600.0} {"text": "Worst game ever. GG Steam.", "appid": "448620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077156429", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1573387200.0} {"text": "Pros or cons ? 1. A lot of champion with similar ability. 2. You can get everything (not cosmetics) with gold/essence which is hard to get. 3. A lot of bugs which wont be fixed in a short time. 4. Very hard to get crystals,so as a f2p player it wont be easy to get cosmetics (very low chance in loot boxes). 5.\"Paladins is played from a first-person perspective\" its wrong now,you can change camera mode.", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126810269", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1511611200.0} {"text": "The development team have a mindset that \"If we make it like PUBG, we will get more players\" but what's the point when I can just play PUBG instead. This was my favourite game and I used to be excited to play it... This game has come so far downhill which is just sad.", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062858425", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1507896000.0} {"text": "Сама игра не плохая, но ультра дроп игры из за детской кроватки в домике 4 уровня, которую нельзя никак убрать!!!! Сцука зачем это сделали???", "appid": "413150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198107827952", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572955200.0} {"text": "Wasted 425 hours of my life. Not worth it.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086980642", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1459684800.0} {"text": "Que no se mal entienda mi reseña , en si el juego comparada con SGW 2 mejoro \"bastante\" digamoslo tanto como en fisicas, graficas y varios de esos efectos al impactar la bala del rifle, hasta ahi tenia mi voto positvo, puedes jugar con muchos rifles y pensar bien como abarcar cada mision y/o campamento enemigo, donde se gano mi voto negativo (ESTOY DISPUESTO A CAMBIARLO A POSITIVO SI ES QUE HAY ALGUNA MEJORA) es en la historia en la cual empezo bien y de ahi fue de mas a menos , conoce a varios personajes , a su ex , etc ,pero cual es el problema?, solo se podia interactuar con los personajes cuando activavas la mision y solo leer lo que te decian y cuando se terminaba, para un juego de que empieza con una historia en la que tu dices \"mira se puso buena la cosa\" fue una ofensa para todos , la poca compenetracion con estos mismos , hay personajes en los que incluso los ves en imagenes pero jamas en el juego, ya con eso tu dices espero que el final sea bueno pero les digo (ALERTA DE SPOILER) no esperen un climax decente , es mas deja muchas cosas en el aire lo cual resulta decepcionante y la 2 cosa que me paso demasiado a menudo fueron esos malditos BUGS , derepente disparaba y la Bala atravesaba y no mataba a los enemigos , caminaba y me topaba la pared invisible y varias cosas mas ( Si crearan un DLC mejorando algo la historia , un final alternativo , ahi que los desarrolladores usen su imaginacion y arreglen esos malditos BUGS) . Un pequeño consejo para los desarrolladores \"SI VAN A VENDER UN JUEGO TOMENSE LA MOLESTIA DE HACER UN JUEGO CON UNA HISTORIA DECENTE Y BIEN REALIZADA AL IGUAL QUE LA COMPENETRACION CON ESTOS MISMOS Y EL ARREGLO DE ERRORES, SI BIEN ES UN JUEGO DE FRANCOTIRADORES NO JUSTIFICA QUE CAREZCA DE UN CONTEXTO , HISTORIA , RELACION CON OTROS PERSONAJES . HAGAN ESO EN VEZ DE LANZAR JUEGOS SGW CADA CIERTO TIEMPO LO CUAL LLEGA A PARECER ALGO \"GENERICO\" SOLO CON ALGUNAS MEJORAS Y LES ASEGURO QUE SERIA UN JUEGO ALABADO Y SE GANARIAN A UNA CANTIDAD DE JUGADORES LEALES Y ADEMAS POR LA CALIDAD DEL MISMO JUEGO Y TODO LO DEMAS PODRIAN DESPUES CON ESO MISMO HACER JUEGO QUE COMPITA CONTRA LOS GRANDES", "appid": "368070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090321265", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577275200.0} {"text": "dieses game ist schon so lange released aber es fühlt sich immer noch an als wäre es im early access", "appid": "346110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198259685797", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525262400.0} {"text": "Во времена OutDrive, которая вышла 4 года назад, подобное вызывало интерес, а теперь, даже не смотря на то, что мне нравится синт-тематике, данный продукт остаётся всего лишь лёгким способом срубить бабла и ничем больше. Не спасает даже наличие разных машин и возможность лёгкой кастомизации, ехать в закат здесь просто не интересно, чему способствует деревянная механика управляемого тобой \"утюга\". Я проехался на четырёх (включая Шаху), все управляются одинаково, только звук разный. Из плюсов можно отметить внешнее разнообразие машин (пока их 10 штук); есть несколько трасс, все довольно красивые (естественно, если вы любите такую стилистику; синт неплохой (около 20-30? трэков в списке), хотя вот в том же OutDrive мне трэки больше понравились (возможно здесь самые крутые я не услышал). Если любите такое - вам зайдёт. Просто держите в голове, что это та же самая поездка в закат, что и у игр-клонов, только с другой музыкой. А я пойду запущу Forz'у, сяду в Ламбо, включу синт и помяну Retrowave. P.S. Контроллером от Коробки можно только рулить, а управлять в меню - нет. А ещё я не понял смысл сложности masterpeace (или как там её): просто едешь вперёд, машин нет, проиграть нельзя, получить очки тоже - и в чём прикол? Или это какой то баг? upd: я нашёл ещё один плюс этой игры - она мне напомнила про OutDrive, я её запустил, а там ачивки добавили и новые трэки, все туда, ребята, там хотя бы поворачивать можно, а музыка лучше в разы!", "appid": "1239690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066914428", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1588507200.0} {"text": "Pior jogo q ja joguei da STEAM ou pela STEAM, os controles são extremamente bugados tanto no controle quanto no teclado....Primeiro q msm vc invertendo e mudando as coisas do controle ele n muda pq o analogico q vira a camera tds estão acostumados c o direito, ja nesse game n, é o contrario, e no teclado algumas ações n funcionam...Me desculpe, mas na minha umilde opinião, este jogo é uma merda em relação ha controles, passei 1 hora apenas no tutorial devido ha ao problema nos controles do game, além do jogo ser de 2009, pelo menos os graficos são bons... Resumindo jogo completamente BUGADO e CAGADO com Controles (Keyboard e Joystick), N COMPRE!!!", "appid": "17410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198342445374", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530619200.0} {"text": "This is a bad DLC, pure and simple which is a real shame because the previous one was quite good. Here are some of the reasons why I think it was sub-par: - Writing is just plain boring and it reminds me of the BL3 main campaign story which also sucked. I thought they were on the right track with previous DLC which actually had a pretty decent story but it's one step forwards and two steps back with these devs. - Levels are pretty average, there are a couple with cool visual design but the rest are mediocre. - Boring loot, having completed all side-quests, I have all the unique loot and it's meh at best, the legendaries specific to DLC are also sub-par and I won't be using them in my builds. - Really boring side mission design, it's just more \"kill enemies in designated circle\" and \"fetch this\" crap, out of all side missions only stood out. - Extremely poor endgame content, previous DLC had a number of areas that can be farmed for specific drops, world drops and XP, there is very little of that here. The story bosses are all multi-stage crap design that can't be farmed efficiently and all chests I opened just had garbage in them, not a single legendary. - It is short and lacking in content compared to previous DLC and BL2 DLC. - Extremely annoying achievements that add nothing of value to the game.", "appid": "1232257", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006217347", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "34", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585310400.0} {"text": "更新了驱动还502，各种玩不了", "appid": "1097840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198100600500", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569067200.0} {"text": "Probably most flawed of all quests designed by Tim Schaefer. Main story criplled by extremely shortiness, which leads to transformation of potentially great characters to unremarkable and blank sidekicks. The sole exception here is Ben Throttle, who had a lot of capacity to stand on par with Guybrush Threepwood and Manny Calavera, as another great hero of quest genre, but only affirms a fact, that such characters need a stong secondary support cast to uphold them. Aside from Ben, only garage rock music by The Gone Jackals (exceptionally fitting for blasting through apocalyptic road scenery) remains untouched by corrosion of time, and deserves listening on its own. Buy The Monkey Island or Grim Fandango instead.", "appid": "228360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081897286", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516536000.0} {"text": "Tek ruined the Game. Dino Survival with Transformers isnt fun. Game full of Dupers. Heavy Lag Issues since Alpha which will never be fixed. No DX12 Mode for Windows 10 for years.", "appid": "887380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066556018", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541592000.0} {"text": "wuu", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198873418448", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545480000.0} {"text": "Sin dudas hoy en dia uno de los killers mas aburridos del juego, tanto como jugar con el o contra el. Yo se que la gran mayoria opina lo mismo", "appid": "971790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198217561141", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591358400.0} {"text": "Eine Warnung an alle Spieler. Drückt auf keinen Fall ESC. Ich habe mir das Intro gerade 10x angeschaut.", "appid": "234940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042858126", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597060800.0} {"text": "car epic games", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198151278798", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1557576000.0} {"text": "Probably The worst Total War game I have played out of them all, too basic and if you want more \"Gore\" They ask for money, what a joke", "appid": "779340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035548313", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Pains me to give a bad review to the sequel of such a good game, but I don't enjoy Dishonored 2. The level design is too open, making it hard to stealth as I enjoyed in 1, leading to having to restart from checkpoint every few minutes. Also, its easy to get lost as it lacks linearity. Go get Dishonored 1 if you haven't already.", "appid": "403640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051039079", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498392000.0} {"text": "Don't make the same mistake I did, do not get this game on PC. Console is fine but this multiplayer is borderline unplayable and not fun at all. The story and zombies for PC is somewhat ok but multiplayer is difficult to even find anyone and its not fun at all.", "appid": "292730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091551521", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1478433600.0} {"text": "A história e os gráficos são pontos positivos, porem os bugs e todos os problemas que tiveram desde o lançamento tiraram todo o brilho do que poderia ser o game do ano se a Ubisoft tivesse feito do jeito que deveria...", "appid": "289650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075109940", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1417521600.0} {"text": "Everything is good from combat to skins. The only ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ problem is the damn launcher !! For ♥♥♥♥ sake fix that launcher, i can barely enter the game because the stupid launcher keeps closing itself and the play button keeps showing grey for hours,", "appid": "323370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198164556443", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1500120000.0} {"text": "Tja was soll ich sagen... CSGO halt Ich gab CSGO: -Liebe -Geld -Zeit CSGO gab mir: -hass gegen Russen, Polen, Franzosen und Russen -ein Kaputte Tastatur -eine kaputte Maus -einen Wütenden Nachbarn -Smurfs -Trolls Im Wesentlichen - CS ist eine gierige Frau, aber ich liebe sie <3 EDIT: Free 2 Play und ein schlechter BR Modus? statt einem ordentlichen Anticheat System? Danke aber nein Danke...", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060723813", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1450785600.0} {"text": "Bad animations (who thought it would be a good idea to make this look like a 20th century game?) rehashed maps, annoying NPCs, bugs, zero skill combat, just spam AOE on trash mobs then get tired of being 1 shotted all the time (not even going to mention the bosses here), absolutely ridiculous, i wanted to like this but couldnt even finish the entire game as it just felt like a chore towards the end. It also has the worst MTs ive ever seen in a game, want your character to look nice, get ready to spend £100! 6/10", "appid": "238960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079913445", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577275200.0} {"text": "#FIXCSGO", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198092598353", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487851200.0} {"text": "A game that gives you the satisfactory of leveling up and clicking, thats it. One of the most time wasteful games on steam that comes with the full package of carpal tunnel. 0/10 would not click again.....", "appid": "363970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086364827", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1439640000.0} {"text": "My most favourite game back in the days. This version of course graphic beautiful, but glitch after glitch what was not so common in old version. Crash after crash... Bots are worse than in old game, they get stuck in technology and not building more than 100 population after you set limits higher. Paying for that £16 - no thanks...", "appid": "1017900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198103284618", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577448000.0} {"text": "DZIEKI ZA KARTY!!!", "appid": "416270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198392435429", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1504785600.0} {"text": "Pubg > H1z1", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119175534", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1498651200.0} {"text": "too repetitive too much grind overall bad", "appid": "335190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198251700618", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579176000.0} {"text": "Free pre-order bonus Separate items to DLC Visual novel game not action No CG, only moving left, right, up, down and shaking PNGs Boring battles, just spamming skills, even 3 years old can play this game Camera and game controlling f***ed Only good things is voiced dialogues This is just free mobile game in PC, not worth paying", "appid": "1150080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074015106", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581681600.0} {"text": "For a $1 game the achievement is worth", "appid": "545580", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051081333", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516968000.0} {"text": "i love this game , but when you play online ,punkbuster does not conform to this , which is a big problem and because of this i would not recommed .", "appid": "10090", "steamid": "profiles/76561197994381144", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1408795200.0} {"text": "May as well just remove single player at this point and rename it to GTA Online - we'd like to ♥♥♥♥ you up the arse, along with your wallet", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198001644928", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497700800.0} {"text": "Bland and uninspired. One of the weaker solitaire games available.", "appid": "395890", "steamid": "profiles/76561197994239917", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1452772800.0} {"text": "hackers... too many.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119636670", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530360000.0} {"text": "Vaya puta mierda de juego literalmente es injugable cuando entras en el launcher salta un problema de inmediato y aunque intentes arreglarlo con una guia de internet o algo asi igual sigue sin funcionar se bloquea y se sale de inmedianto vaya perdida de dinero y tiempo doy gracias a que se puedan reembolsar los juegos", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198145866238", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1492862400.0} {"text": "\"First Time Loading Up\" olayının vız gelip vız geçtiği bir oyun olan World War 3, teoride muhteşem, pratikte berbat sıfatını kesinlikle hak ediyor. Peki bunu teşkil eden neden nedir? Son zamanlarda erken erişim oyunlarına karşı bir nefret içerisindeyim. Özellikle bitmiş gibi sunulan ancak aslında oynanamayacak düzeyde olan erken erişim oyunlarından. World War 3, medyanın deyimi ile \"Loading Screen Simulator\" bir oyun değil. En azından benim için. Kayıtlarda 42 saatlik bir oynama söz konusu ancak bunun tek bir saniyesinde dahi eli silah tutan bir kimseyi kontrol edemedim. Bu 42 saatin yarısı Idle programlarının marifeti, yarısı da açık bırakıp da \"Belki gelince girmiş olur\" diyip evden çıkmamın sonucu. Maalesef ki oyuna giremiyorsunuz. Ebediyete uzanan bir yükleme ekranı ve beraberinde size içten içe sırıtan bir oyun. Ne zaman oyunu açıp evden çıksam ve aradan 2-3 saat geçtiğinde eve dönsem ekranda bir hata ile karşılaşıyorum. İşsiz, güçsüzmüşcesine ekran başında bekliyorum ve yarım saat gibi bir sürede ecel terleri döktükten sonra tam açılır gibi olup, sonrasında hata veren bir oyunla karşılaşıyorum. Olumlu yorum yapanlar var gördüğüm kadarıyla. Ancak benim gibi oyuna erişemeyenler de çoğunlukta. Belki de dönemsel bir sorundur, şuan bakım tarzında bir olay gerçekleşiyordur, o kadarını bilemem ancak söyleyebileceğim tek şey oyunu en azından şuanlık edinmemeniz. Ben şahsi olarak oyunu oynayamadığım için oyun hakkında belirli etkenleri eleştiremeyeceğim. O nedenle bu incelemeyi \"Tavsiye etmiyorum\" diye işaretlerken sadece o cep yakan fiyatı zerre hak etmemesine dayanıyorum. Şuanlık World War 3 benim gözümde No Man's Sky'dan farksız. İleride görüşümün değişmesi ve bu alanın uzunca bir eleştiri satırına dönmesi dileğiyle... Oyun incelemeleri yaptığımız küratörümüzü ziyaret edebilirsiniz.", "appid": "674020", "steamid": "profiles/76561198273392977", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1544011200.0} {"text": "后期内容重复度过高，除了简单难度之外，不内购的话非常难 不是喜欢的类型", "appid": "812140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198342515375", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "I didn't liked this game. I just can't stop playing it.", "appid": "582010", "steamid": "profiles/76561198059997149", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539259200.0} {"text": "give me back my money", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198214167663", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518782400.0} {"text": "This game runs like crap even on good hardware. It's riddled with bugs like enemies shooting through walls, bullets not going where they should, and invincible enemies. Do not buy, you can't get a refund.", "appid": "365590", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992747290", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458302400.0} {"text": "НУ КАРОЧ, Я НАЧАЛ ОБНОВЛЯТЬ ДОТУ 2 И ПО КАКИМ-ТО ПРИЧИНАМ У МЕНЯ СИНИЙ ЭКРАН И ТУТ Я ОБОСРАЛСЯ И ДУМАЛ Я УЖЕ НЕ ПОИГРАЮ ДОТУ, НО НЕ ВСЕ ТАК ПРОСТО Я ЖЕ ДУМАЛ СЧА ОПЯТЬ ОБНОВЛЮ И ПОИГРАЮ И ЧТО ЖЕ ВЫ ДУМАЕТЕ? У МЕНЯ УДАЛИЛАСЬ ДОТА 2 #ПЛАК #ХНЫК #ГРУСТЬ #БЕДА #ПЕЧАЛЬ", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060793377", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1491480000.0} {"text": "A worse version of Conan Exiles. As a fan of sandbox survival genre, I wouldn't recommend this game at this stage. Early Access experience: For more information, visit the forum to see more posts about the unacceptable bugs. I'd hold off and wait for the full release.", "appid": "903950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198099986382", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1585224000.0} {"text": "...", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198250943906", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522238400.0} {"text": "Can't even play half of the time.", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198221316748", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605441600.0} {"text": "Takes forever to join an online session. The community management is so bad. People are spamming noise, chats and links. So often disconnected from online session or getting errors.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079787805", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589025600.0} {"text": "Crash just deleted my save game twice, i lost around 2 hours progress. The fun fact is: This bug happened 3years ago and the dev didnt fix it", "appid": "409710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076368396", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587384000.0} {"text": "The unimpressive (by today's standards) graphics aside, it is the camera that ruined it for me. None of the angles seemed quite right, it responds slowly to player's movement and doesn't allow to rotate around at all. Maybe it would've benefited from some kind of \"spring mechanic\" where you change the angle with the joystick for a brief moment, then it returns to the default angle when you let go. Also the possibility to accurately choose the distance to the player model would've been nice.", "appid": "681280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060266670", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582891200.0} {"text": "Por lo general me gusta recomendar o no un juego al pasarme por lo menos su campaña principal pero hay veces en que un juego me resulta demasiado monótono y repetitivo, que termina por desesperarme y aburrirme demasiado que simplemente no puedo seguir jugándolo y justamente eso consigue luego de un par de horas Tears of Avia. Siempre estoy pendiente de algunos rpg y juegos de estrategia que están por salir, y este juego llamo mi atención, obviamente no esperaba que me sorprendiera pero si algo decente al menos, pero por desgracia este titulo es realmente malo en varios aspectos sobre todo en el combate. Para empezar al comenzar el juego podremos elegir el personaje con el cual comenzar la aventura y luego tendremos un roster con otros 5 personajes para un total de 6 , aunque solo podremos llevar 5 a cada misión pero cada uno cada uno con un gran árbol de habilidades para desbloquear, y aquí es donde empiezan los problemas ya que tendremos 5 habilidades activas de nuestros personajes y otras 3 que nos proporciona el arma que se reducen a ataques, pero las habilidades básicas de un juego por turnos como ser el overwatch o la postura defensiva no las tendremos, una decisión de diseño que en lo personal no me gusta para nada. Siguiendo con la parte del combate para resumirla en una palabra seria tosco, esto debido a unas pobres animaciones en todos los personajes en los movimientos y las habilidades especiales, y que por desgracia solo las animaciones de las habilidades permite saltar, además sumándole que la mayoría de los personajes tienen poca movilidad por el mapa en cada turno y con unos controles igual de malos sumado a su cámara que es demasiado lenta. También que el diseño de los escenarios en las bases creo que esta bien pero esto cambia mucho en los combate ya que se empiezan a repetir mucho, así como los enemigos que en un principio son bastante malos, para que luego el juego comience a amontonar muchos enemigos en el mapa para así tener algo de desafío, y para sumar al combo esta su banda sonora que en cada combate nos pone una melodía lenta y nunca alguno que nos haga sentir una emoción en el combate. Otra cosa que pienso que esta muy mal planteado es el tema de la dificultad en el cual solo tendremos 2, una que es la estándar y otra la hardcore, la primera sinceramente es completamente aburrida sin nada de desafío y que con que se avanza rápido en la historia, pero la segunda también esta muy mal planteada ya que los enemigos obviamente aumentaran sus stats pero también el escenario nos hará un daño progresivo en cada turno a todos los personajes y que al final es ese daño es el que plantea el desafío porque los enemigos son igual de malos que en la normal. Sumando otra cosa mas a los malos diseños que tiene son los menús que tiene, sobre todo el del inventario y las habilidades, muy mal organizados los 2 a la hora de ir cambiando los ítems no muestra de forma correcta las estadísticas, el de las habilidades es muy poco intuitiva y no da una opción para organizar de manera rápida las mismas. Para terminar de describir este pésimo juego tenemos su historia que la verdad no es la gran cosa y con unos personajes que resultan un poco carismáticos, pero el problema es que para avanzar algo hay que realizar muchas misiones consecutivas y cuando por fin aparece algo, esta se desarrolla demasiado rápido y que nos hará perder el interés demasiado rápido. Aunque a simple vista Tears of Avia puede resultar interesante, la realidad es que es un juego que corrió con muchas decisiones de diseño que terminan por convertirlo en un juego bastante mediocre, sobre todo en el combate y que termina por parecer un early acces a medio hacer. Un juego de estrategia muy malo y no se lo recomiendo a nadie.", "appid": "461510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198129076118", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602849600.0} {"text": "muy malo, no tiene cloud, no hay ranking, se cuelga, no te deja abrirlo generalmente, no te reconoces los saves guardados, y no sacan una triste update casi nunca. sigan en el clicker heroes 1.", "appid": "629910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198062865770", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1554897600.0} {"text": "Good game but full of cheater..", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198884140890", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563710400.0} {"text": "M I C R O T R A N S A C T I O N S", "appid": "841370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198033100962", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "51", "votes_funny": "17", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550318400.0} {"text": "To be honest, it's a good game... only if you cut-out the \"Assassin's Creed\" part from it. Because this is sure as hell ain't an Assassin's Creed game. You want to make an open-world RPG with fantasy stuff on it? Great, go ahead and do it but for the love of all that is holy, A lot of stuff doesn't add up. Spoilers ahead, skip to Pros / Cons for a basic review. The Animus show you different stories / endings - it's just impossible. And there's a simulation inside a simulation which can also show you different stories based on your choices, you just can't do that with the Animus. Ubisoft should've just made a separate RPG game & kept the \"Assassin's Creed\" title far from it but let's poop on that logic, it's gonna generate money! Abstergo is already selling Animus to everyone - so any idiot with a little brain can discover whatever they want, all you need is the DNA of someone. New Animuses / Animi can use the DNA of anyone and is no longer limited to the user's DNA only. So, why the rest of the World doesn't know about The Hidden Ones / Assassins and Templars / Order of the Ancients / Cult of Kosmos / ? That broken spear of Leonidas only contained two blood samples? Pretty sure I've killed thousands of enemies with that spear. The protagonist only cuts herself / himself once, there's no way that blood is still on that spear after all this time. From the previous games, we know how powerful and resourceful the modern-day Templars are. Yet once they knew all about freaking they only sent 3 common soldiers without guns to investigate? Otso Berg killed Layla's best friend in the previous game. Layla has killed several people in the previous game, 3 soldiers in this game and her doctor as well. Yet she let Otso Berg live? Are you serious? He's one of the biggest leaders of the Templar order. And why did he came to Layla alone is beyond me, why is he fighting with a sword? Why not just shoot her and be done with it? Layla's last hit to Otso Berg looks extremely fatal, how on earth did he survive that? Mythical creatures, revisiting realms of afterlife at will, Isu machines speaking in English, enemies performing godly moves and you have godly abilities. Remember when Assassin's Creed used to be historically accurate? The goals of the modern day Assassins and Templars made sense? That franchise died with Desmond Miles. Since when and why are we calling \"Those who came before\" by the name \"Isu\"? The World was saved by Desmond's sacrifice, what's the point of using the Animus now? They're clearly not searching for any artifacts of Eden. The protagonist in the Animus confirms that their power can drain over time, so no point in going through all that trouble with the Animus to find some ancient piece of Eden that may or may not work. The reason why I'm focused more on the modern-day story is because you have to have a good enough reason to be in the Animus in the first place and I don't see any good reason to do that. The modern-day story is a complete mess and it's not going anywhere. Absolutely nothing happens when we finish the main story of the protagonist inside the Animus. We don't discover any artifacts that would help the Assassin in the ongoing battle against the Templars. It has become clear that Ubisoft has no idea what to do with the modern-day story-line and they don't seem to care enough to tie up loose ends. Instead, they're adding more characters to the story that we know nothing about and honestly I don't care about them. I didn't feel anything when Layla's best friend died in the previous game and her doctor's death in this game and one injured character - that's because I don't know much about them to care. Yet when Rebecca was shot a few titles back, I was desperate to see what happens next. I'm interested in finding out what happened to the previous characters such as Rebecca Crane, Shaun Hastings and William Miles. Those characters seemed to have been abandoned. Apart from the stinky poop that is the new modern-day and Isu stuff, the world of Greece is massive and beautiful, though most of the assets are from the previous game. But bigger doesn't always mean better. Maybe some people will like it, maybe some won't have the time to 100% everything. It took me a lot of time to finish up everything in the game but I encountered a bug with an engraving challenge, so I didn't get that satisfying feeling of completing everything because even though all quests, locations have been completed, there's one engraving challenge that's now impossible to complete. Maybe some completionists would know how annoying this can be. I pre-ordered the Ultimate Edition but I was shocked to see the number of premium content that are available for purchase using more money. Micro transactions in a single-player game is awful. I feel like I'm missing out. What's the point of purchasing the most expensive edition if I still have to buy more stuff to get everything the game has to offer? There is a way to get premium items for free but the process is worse than loot-boxes. + Gorgeous graphics and good soundtrack which fits various atmospheres. + Greece is really huge, there's a lot of things you can find that might surprise you. + Land adventures on foot or horse or even mythical creatures (act as cosmetics). + Sea and underwater adventure with customizable ship, its lieutenants and crew. + Tons of customization are available for your character and your preferred play-style. + Very realistic facial expressions, conversations feel natural. + So many quests! So many choices! So many outcomes! So many save slots! + You can bang quite a lot of NPCs without getting any ancient STDs. ! Requires a lot of time to complete everything, then there's the New Game+. ! Assassin's Creed game(?). ! Radiant quests for a never-ending adventure. ! Mythical mounts, ship items, crew can be obtained (they are cosmetics). ! Requires a lot of grinding before moving on to the next story related mission. - Poor modern-day story from the very beginning to the very end. - Uses about half of the game's assets from the previous game. - Isu story-line doesn't make much sense. - So many repetitive quests, even the dialogues of some quests are the same. - Very limited number of sea shanties compared to the previous titles which gets boring. - Mythical armor sets and ship lieutenants that can be purchased are not just cosmetics. - Lacks logic in most situations and basic common sense in some situations. - Micro-transactions in a single-player game. Question: How many Assassin's Creed games will you release before ending the series? Ubisoft: You have to visit Ubisoft's game booth at every gaming event and play all the games there. What's that? You live in the other side of the World? Well then.. no rewards for you! You have to participate in their Closed Alpha Tests, Open Alpha Tests, Closed Beta Tests, Open Beta Tests of their games. What's that? You weren't selected by them to be a tester? Well then... no rewards for you! You have to own several other Ubisoft games on the same account. What's that? You don't have the money and not interested in those other games? Well then... no rewards for you!", "appid": "812140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198063115240", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "60", "votes_funny": "37", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538740800.0} {"text": "This game is bad.", "appid": "204300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198524398906", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1515758400.0} {"text": "I love point and click adventure games but what the heck did I just play? I admit I read some of the reviews and thought people were just making up everything that was said but nope now I understand. - Very short game over in like 10 minutes if that - Naked lizard people - Human kissing and tickling naked lizard woman and her child, yes AND her child! - Strange naked lizard doctor who is clearly stuck in the 70's. I wouldn't bother playing this game unless you got it for free and is into disturbing behavior.", "appid": "463110", "steamid": "profiles/76561197984373540", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1473768000.0} {"text": "half baked anime dark souls", "appid": "678960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117160265", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1570276800.0} {"text": "HİLE DOLU adaletsiz aptal bie oyun", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198262682500", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1494763200.0} {"text": "Всем доброго времени суток. На момент релиза поиграв несколько часов я накатал быстро положительный отзыв, сейчас же, спустя десятки часов я переобуваюсь. Начну сразу с минусов, некоторые из них мое личное мнение: - Очень хреновая локализация. Были патчи, но даже не смотря на них, локализация как была кривая, так и осталась. - Скелет. На данный момент игра представляет из себя просто скелет, без мяса, органов и т.д. Я это понял в момент, когда сидел в CK3, и пока крутилось время в игре, я открыл планшет и листал ленту ВК, читал новости и даже играл. Если выскакивали случайные события, то я их уже видел десятки, если не сотни раз, они скорее раздражают. - Ветки прокачки, перки. Единственная ветка, которая реально принесет хорошие плюшки - ветка ученого, это имба. Остальные нах не нужны по сути. По крайней мере в одиночной игре. - Где должности? Как во второй было. Регент, придворный шут, подчаший и т.д.? У меня ребенок становится правителем без регента, сразу на престол, не дожидаясь зрелого возраста. Класс, че. - Фишки с наследованием, мое любимое. Привязка законов к технологиям и времени. Угу, идите ка вы на**й, разрабы. Законы о единственном наследнике, примогенитура (первородство) и закон, когда младший ребенок наследует титулы, появятся у вас только к концу игры. И это если повезет. Все остальное время, 90% времени, вы будете еба**ся с конфедеративным наследованием, потому что остальные две доступные на**й не нужны будут, зачем их вообще добавили? И ваше гос-во будет разваливаться раз за разом. На**й мне тогда вообще потеть и собирать земли под собой, если я знаю, что они развалятся, а повлиять я на это едва ли могу. Я знаю, что есть фишка с лишением наследства, но это БРЕД ПОЛНЫЙ, это тупо недоработка механики, я каждый раз вынужден портить отношения со своими детьми, лишаться очков династии, просто потому что по другому никак не могу повлиять на целостность гос-ва. Почему то во второй части с этим всё было гораздо проще. Последняя партия, я играл за балтийскую культуру, я дошел до примогенитуры и мне оставалось чуть больше 50-ти лет до конца игры. То есть, если я захочу играть за племя, и начинать с низов, то вероятность того, что я приму нормальный закон наследования стремится к нулю. Я тупо не успею изучить всё до конца игры. Во второй такой зал**ы не было. Получается в игре нет вариативности развития, как было во второй, игра задает тебе направление, и ты не имеешь права с него свернуть, нет такой возможности. - Сражения, битвы, солдаты. Я честно не понимаю как мне повысить качество армии, как бегали двести лет назад бомжи в лохмотьях, так и бегают. На релизе у меня было всё. Потом случился судя по всему патч, и качество армии у меня теперь не поднимается вообще. Как и у других гос-в тоже, такие же бомжи скачут. Во второй части сражения были интереснее, три полководца, на левом фланге, правом, и центровой. Были ивенты во время сражений, события. Это всё где? - При переходе из племени в феодализм на**й рушатся все постройки. А зачем я их строил, вкладывался и т.д.? А деньги то в минус идут стремительно. Теперь я такой же бомж, что и те, которые в моей армии скачут. Хоть и феодал. Феодал бомжей. - ИИ. Он просто тупой. Вот и всё. - Крестовые походы. Их так много, что это словно поход за хлебом в магаз. Хотя участие в них очень выгодно. Это лично доеб от меня. Теперь немного плюсов: - Модельки, это то, что мне понравилось, выглядят неплохо. Приятное нововведение. Правда и тут есть минусы, дети допустим азиата и европейца выглядят супер нелепо. - Развитие династии. Ветки прокачки династии тоже интересная новая фишка, с полезными бонусами. - Очень удобно стало с наемниками, во второй приходилось слюнявить им деньги каждый месяц, если ничего не путаю, из чего мог попасть в просак, потому что плохо посчитал расходы. в CK3 теперь ты раз им платишь, и у вас заключен контракт на три года. И никакой е**и. В конце можно просто продлить, заплатив им ту же цену. В прочем игра та же CK, что и вторая часть, только пустая. Если вдруг что еще вспомню, то напишу. Короче, я поменяю отзыв, когда игра обрастет мясом. Сейчас в ней делать особой нечего, даже ачивки выбивать не очень хочется, они не сильно трудные, но их просто не интересно выбивать. Ждем сотни DLC. Что бы поиграть в игру, её мало купить, нужно сначала её собрать, как как конструктор лего и т.д.", "appid": "1158310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198067163245", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598961600.0} {"text": "heavily biased towards rus. no real balance. devs ignore players while interesting at first, get realy boring after first few tiers. unles you play tovarisch ♥♥♥♥♥, then its easy mode all the way", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004676771", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1439294400.0} {"text": "Save yourself trouble and don't play this.", "appid": "289090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069611135", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485345600.0} {"text": "Samaya xydwaya igra v mire, prosoto rassadnik citerov i idiotov, igrat ne vozmojno, s nei pokonceno!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198094368556", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "ЧЁРТ ДА ЭТО ЛУЧШАЯ ИГРА НА ПЛАНЕТЕ. ВСЕГДА ЖДАЛ ЕЁ В СТИМЕ И ЕЩЁ ПО ЦЕНЕ 249 РУБЛЕЙ. ЭТО БОЖЕСТВЕННО.Я ТАЩУСЬ ОТ НЕЁ. ВСЕМ СОВЕТУЮ.(ГРАФИКА НА ВЫСШЕМ УРОВНЕ, СОЦИАЛЬНАЯ СОСТАВЛЯЮЩАЯ ПРОСТО СУПЕР, А ПРО ГЕМПЛЕЙ И ГОВОРИТЬ НЕЧЕВО-НЕРЕАЛЬНО)!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!", "appid": "278970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068957137", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435060800.0} {"text": "This game makes me rage a l