ии, и наконец мое любимое, бан трейда мой хлеб и не только мой.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143850649", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525694400.0} {"text": "this game suck nice remove story fk dead game with autistic game developer from elsword and grand chase nice p2w trash game", "appid": "844870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198144767409", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "Ни в коем случае не покупайте эту игру! 20 минут пытался с другом поиграть, в итоге ничего не вышло. Если я подключаюсь к другу в лобби, то он меня не видит, а если он ко мне, то соответственно я его. Ну, в принципе от Юбисофт чего-то другого и не стоило ожидать.", "appid": "470220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163153734", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589889600.0} {"text": "0% Anfängerfreundlich Ausgewaschene Grafik selbst auf hoch (man kann so gut wie nichts in der Ferne erkennen (verpixelt)) Oft Laggs und die Musik/Sound hört manchmal einfach auf Gespielt mit einer GTX 1060 (Full HD)", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198153705767", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1493208000.0} {"text": "Cтоило мне зайти в игру, как у меня бомбануло, никогда не думал, что могу в дезмаче закончить со счётом 1 32...", "appid": "219640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008204482", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1415361600.0} {"text": "Bad game", "appid": "314700", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143314012", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1448625600.0} {"text": "Bought this game before it went free to play.. Feel Like I got ripped off because there was nothing to really set it apart from any free to play fps out currently. Besides the GitS theme, theres not much to offer. Especially now that it's shown its true form as a f2p fps game that was marketed as a paid full game. Could be way better.", "appid": "369200", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970343469", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470571200.0} {"text": "At first glance a nice game with nice elements. However, there is no catchy storyline and everything is the same from start to finish. Stupid shooting seems like the only goal, but finding hidden rooms and items is challenging! For those who like that and make no further demands, this might be a great game. Since everything is the same, it gets very boring halfway through so I no longer enjoy the gameplay. As a result, you simply sit down and shoot to finish the game as quickly as possible. The gameplay also offers a number of options to improve your performance and skins, but given the monotonous nature of the game and the boredom that it causes, it is not a challenge for me to work on it any longer. In short, for me a game that you play once and then never again.", "appid": "782330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198292029498", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "8", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597579200.0} {"text": "I would avoid purchasing this game as it has very bare-bones gameplay at the moment. ==Pros == + Graphics are nice and colorful + The noises that the Mooj make when you pick them up remind me of Chao from Sonic Adventure. + The ability to skip directly to night time. + A variety of different features to enhance the garden including milking stations, farm areas and cooking pots. + Mooj' appearance is based on their evolution from eating various food. == Cons == - First few days are very boring and hard to get into. - More emphasis is put on tower defense than simulation - you HAVE to fight monsters every night and defend the Mooj statue. - No music at all until random occasions such as an egg being produced or it switches to night. - Also, the music choice is very odd - it sounds like swing and big band music from the 40s and 50s that Dean Martin and Frank Sinatra would sing to. Very uncharacteristic. - The UI and text are difficult to read sometimes. Note: I didn't test what would happen if the Mooj statue lost all it's HP. I assume it's game over? I wish I waited to purchase this game and spent it on something else, but eh, you live and learn.", "appid": "1044760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090141267", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561550400.0} {"text": "Игра дерьмо, город не живой вообще, а когда тебя машины сбивают это вообще пушка, это как будто 2003 год. Вернул деньги, это уже не мафия, даже во второй физика и графика была получше.", "appid": "360430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198029327317", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "15", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1475841600.0} {"text": "3/10", "appid": "544920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198382933066", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1559044800.0} {"text": "Social club sucks ass. Won't start even when i press play offline. This was a waste of money gonna get a refund. Iha paska", "appid": "12220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198107907649", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479643200.0} {"text": "This used to be one of the best games I got but to be completly honest ever since they changed the shooting physics and everything it's one of the worst games out there. Would never buy again.", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198167579660", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "First, the caveats: (1) I've spent just over two hours with the title, and (2) I definitely paid too much for it. I bought it for $35.99 when the hype machine was turned up all the way and lots of people were praising the title. The reviews are all still very positive I see, so I'm going to try to give you a balanced viewpoint despite the aforementioned caveats. Here's the crux of it: if you're seeking a mindless bug shooter with some interesting flexibility in classes, weapons, and equipment, and you don't mind an overwrought story and what seems like shaky translations and porting choices, then this is a game you're probably going to like. To be fair, I like it for what it is; I just didn't really understand going into it and probably should have tried it sooner and requested a refund. It's just not my thing. I like casual brain-dead shooting sometimes, but this one puts the dead in brain-dead. I don't think I've even had to try on any of the missions. I run around shooting virtually everything that moves, running over pickups, and it's like its an enemy invasion of loot pinatas. I can't take the bugs seriously when I'm not sure I've ever been hit by anything in the first twelve missions. Candy Crush would provide more of a challenge. And again, I'm not all about the challenge, I've played games like this before, but my suggestion for you is that the title is really worth more like $20. You'll spend a few hours shooting stuff, maybe relaxing with your beverage of choice, and then you'll be bored, at least if you're like me. My suggestion is that unless you absolutely love the hokey sci-fi invasion B-movies from the 1950s and simply can't get enough, your money and your time are likely better spent elsewhere.", "appid": "1007040", "steamid": "profiles/76561197965466830", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579608000.0} {"text": "Great and entertaining at the start,but it gets boring when you level up.", "appid": "436150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198262523879", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519473600.0} {"text": "Oyuna gerçekten bir şans vermek için ve cidden bu türü sevdiğim için de hevesle girdim. Ama sonuç maalesef hüsran oldu. Hadi dedim onca olumsuz yoruma rağmen yapımcı bedava olarak sunmuş ne kadar kötü olabilir ki dedim. Emeğe saygımız olsun diyerekten oyunamaya başladım. Ama, şunu gönül rahatlığıyla söyleyebilirim \"hay demez olaydım\" ve bu oyundan KESİNLİKLE UZAK DURUN! Ha bu oyun Meteor simulatörü ya da, uzayda ki bir Kamikaze dalış simulatörü olsaymış o zaman 10 numara oyun olurmuş valla. Oyunda ki geminiz resmen daima ileri gazı var. Hiç geri vitesmiş, frenmiş yok. Oyunda dur iki dakka Jüpiter havası alayım bir çay içelim deseniz bile böyle bir imkânınız yok maalesef. Çünkü oyunda duramıyorsunuz. Tek şansınız bodoslama gelişi güzel bir meteora çarptığınızda durmak. Ha oldu ki canınız sağa sola savrulmaktan sıkıldı ve düşmana saldırmak istediniz. Hay hay saldırın tabi diyor oyun. Ama düşmana atış mesafesine kadar yaklaşmak için hareket etmeniz gerek. E hareket ettiğinizde de freni patlamış gibi gittiğinizden yanından hışımla geçtiğiniz için , ne düşman size ne de siz düşmana vuramıyorsunuz. İnat edip vurmak isterseniz bu sefer farklı yöne gaza basıyorsunuz ama bu seferde yine aynı şey. Bildiğin kısır döngü yani. Sonuç olarak vaktinizi bile harcadığınıza değmeyen bir oyun olmuş. Meteorculuk oynamak isteyen biri varsa balıklama dalsın bak, işte bu oyun tam size göre, iyi oyunlar.", "appid": "342980", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035407533", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1467720000.0} {"text": "Нет игра полна багав и вообще бред а не сюжет! P.S. ещькере", "appid": "338180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198259887059", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526126400.0} {"text": "Баны за мышку? RLY?", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053530619", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576152000.0} {"text": "Don't get me wrong. I think this could be a great game. The reason why I don't recomend it is because not only I think it should have achievements, but I think it should have like 200 of them... The mechanic of the game is to survive, you can't \"beat\" the game. And, in the end, is a game about \"doing things\". I think that the idea is great, but I also think that it would be nice to have some goals, and some way to know what you've managed to achieve... I know it has been asked many times, and developers said the reason why the game doesn't have achievements is mainly because they don't want to. I respect that, but they use to give some reasons that, to me, sounds more like excuses (I don't really know how hard is to add this to a game, programming and so...). But that is the reason I don't recomend this game. After a few hours, I'd rather be playing something else. If, unlike me, you don't care about that (Achievements, leaderboards...) then you might like the game. It is original, well designed and you can have fun playing it to kill some time.", "appid": "219740", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998124191", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1389096000.0} {"text": "Congratulations to Zombie Zoeds for being the first game on Steam in 11 years to inspire me to write a negative review. As you can see I've put in a few hours trying to figure out the objective of this game. 100 hours later and I'm still not sure. What I do know is this: * The only redeeming value the game has is that if you can find it on sale for $0.15 like I did you can idle it to earn your trading cards and then sell them for at $0.07 each for a total profit of $0.03.", "appid": "366890", "steamid": "profiles/76561197965179840", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1452686400.0} {"text": "матчмакинг выебан в рот, кривее игру сложно найти ты просыпаешься и думаешь дайка катану за сурва ща как вытащу красиво помаесую, итог спустя 4 минуты тебя ловит маньяк тупо потому что задрочил тайминги и карту за 4 тысячи часов игры а у тебя 2 каткка на ней, сурвы бегают хз пойми чо делать. Аналогично думаешь ты пойду за маньяка, а вот тут ты не угадал друг там целая команда с дискордом на связи и будут вводить тебя хоть пол часа вокруг машины и нечего ты не сделаешь, заведут генераторы за 3 минуты . Всем любви", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198070701169", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576584000.0} {"text": "it's a great musou game and all with my favorite characters from DOA and deception series but all the furry ♥♥♥♥ ruins it for me.", "appid": "610190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039875201", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1504958400.0} {"text": "First of all.. Yes. I had a lot of fun during most of the time I played the game. And yes, it was some weeks ago when I played it the last time. Second... The game did not change at all. It was the decisions of the Developers that made me quit playing this game. Reasons: --> No patches (there was no patch since I played the game the last time). --> Unannounced perknerfs (you grind a long time for the Counselorperks and the Devs decide to stealthnerf everything). --> Members of the Community were banned and told openly in the Internet that they are pedophiles (the ♥♥♥♥?!), because of some Kids that knows the Developers. --> The game is only playable in full private Lobbies. There are less people per day that play this game and the ones left are either not the ones you want to play with and the others play private Matches. --> (Not even talking about the \"content\" that is in the game right now, there are enough Reviews for it) <-- Update: Better add a paid DLC for this ♥♥♥♥ already. Wow.", "appid": "438740", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997263876", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495886400.0} {"text": "refunded, wait till the price goes down not worth the $30 , maybe 10 to 15. Mostly because there are problems when you save. I could play for 1 hour and get all this stuff done and i cant even open the menu to save it.", "appid": "719590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198170936262", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1515067200.0} {"text": "Why the ♥♥♥♥ are you looking for a reason not to buy this game? It's ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ amazing! Buy it for ♥♥♥♥ sakes!", "appid": "620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198310121061", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": "46", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1489838400.0} {"text": "Buy some good servers instead of keeping that money", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198414658682", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562414400.0} {"text": "Тупая игра!Даже кол!Бесит то,что всегда респаунишься на краю карты ,где бл ты никого не обгонишь со своей калымагой,бесит то,что все машина прокаченнне тебя!", "appid": "12360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198261251447", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470916800.0} {"text": "Скриншотов успела наделать много - игра очень понравилась с визуальной точки зрения. Мелодии приятные. Не понравилась скорость ходьбы в сочетании с оптимизацией игры, это отбивает желание поисследовать, да покрутить со всех сторон (из-за чего не собрала все рисунки), довелось идти исключительно по тропе повествования. Озвучка главного героя оставляет желать лучшего, совершенно не подходящие эмоции демонстрируются, кажется актер не знал ни кто его персонаж, ни что с ним происходит, философскую атмосферу (которую, видимо, хотели создать разработчики) это развеивает в прах. Ну и о сюжете, аллегоричность мне понравилась, но все уж слишком однобоко показано и в мрачных тонах. На этом фоне удивляет наличие выбора между новой жизнью и забвением, тут герой по умолчанию должен выбирать забвение. Хотелось бы чтоб персонажи игры больше включались в обсуждение темы и каждый представлял свое виденье, возможно девушка-мечта могла бы поделиться более позитивным взглядом.", "appid": "629840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143766109", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604577600.0} {"text": "Первая часть знаменитой-трилогии! Но тут нет Русского языка, хотя -это не проблема..! Для меня стало проблемой-то, что не работает сохранение... Кто мож в курсе??", "appid": "6800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198334694363", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1481112000.0} {"text": "ХРЕНЬ НЕ ЗАПУСКАЕТЬСЯ ТАК КАК ОНА Вероятно, игра Need for Speed™ Deluxe Edition не установлена. Установите или перезапустите игру.", "appid": "1262540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198143352525", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596024000.0} {"text": "Someone challenged me to play it for 90 minutes. It was extremely painful and the most boring thing in the world... I wouldn't get this game for free.", "appid": "975240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198110107228", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550923200.0} {"text": "Не понравилась", "appid": "776960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198055392964", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "the game is fun at the first 1 or 2 hours then it becomes repetative and boring and one thing that i desagree alot with the game format is the pay 2 win system that it has like tf2 i wont say that it is a bad game tho", "appid": "273110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198185869163", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516536000.0} {"text": "Собственно пробежал я эту игру за 99 минут (а мог бы и за 70, если бы управление не было таким гумозным) и хочется сказать несколько слов про нее. DreamBreak это 99 минут недоразумения. Как вы думаете, за такое количество времени возможно раскрыть персонажей, сюжет, вселенную? Конечно же нет. Банальнейший сюжет про антиутопию и ополченцев, несколько персонажей которые произносят в игре всего пару фраз, и три абсолютно невразумительные концовки, две из которых фактически одинаковы. Быть может геймплей спасет ситуацию? Нет - это абсолютно линейный и скучный квест с элементами экшна (ох уж эти убогие перестрелки). По поводу атмосферы - это очевидный закос под FlashBack, только теперь события развиваются в футуристичном СССР. Почему СССР? А не знаю, просто потому что. Никаких отличительных особенностей СССР здесь не прослеживается, кроме разве что \"генсека\" - замени его на \"президента\" и приставочку СССР можно смело убирать. В остальном - анимация, структура некоторых уровней, перестрелки содраны с FlashBack, только в более обрезанном варианте. Черт да даже название созвучно и как бэ намекает... Возможно это просто дань уважения классике, но увы, этого я в игре не заметил. В итоге хочется сказать что я не рекомендую к покупке эту игру, но если вы все же хотите попробовать, то дождитесь скидки хотя бы 80%.", "appid": "443570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198089629590", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "88", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1469361600.0} {"text": "Absolutes Drecks spiel sooo ein scheiß system was die da eingebaut haben und von Bugs reden wir mal garnicht aber wichtig neue DLCs und Skins bringen um mehr Geld zu schaufel haha", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198246101706", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530619200.0} {"text": "Terrible concept.", "appid": "797470", "steamid": "profiles/76561197969290651", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518955200.0} {"text": "Нормальные игроки в сделку не входили", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198190123322", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490270400.0} {"text": "dead game", "appid": "295110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069865966", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566734400.0} {"text": "Боже такое гавно, не советую с ней проблем просто п-е-з-д-а и графон убогий , а главное ОПТИМИЗАЦИЯ уёбещная. БОЛЬШУЩИЙ МИНУС СТАВЛЮ ЭТОЙ ИГРЕ !", "appid": "360430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074715240", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1476014400.0} {"text": "kamery w kamapni powinny byc kazde nawet na zaawansowanym bo nie widac jak jedziesz z tylu sprawdzalem ... na czuja nie bd robil dlatego taka opinia", "appid": "493490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198165292908", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578744000.0} {"text": "Egy érdekes kis játék ahol a vikingek és a trollok harcolnak a levegőbe ilyen zeppelin féleségekkel amiken vannak ágyúk de sajnos ez olyan játék hogy vagy társakkal játszol és valaki vezeti a zeppelint te meg lősz az ágyúkkal vagy mindent neked kell csinálnod... A földön nem lehet rusholni az enemy térfelére mert a víz is toxic és valami mutáns húsevő gombák követnek ha megpróbálod elhagyni a bázisod... Nekem nem tetszett a játék úgy öszintén megmondjam, de lehet valakinek tetszeni fog!", "appid": "223630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198054927784", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529496000.0} {"text": "Игра нормальная. Но система калибровки это ппц и из-за того что она стала бесплатной в игру пришло много читеров! Читеры эть ГЛАВНАЯ ГЛАААААВНАЯ проблема игры! Сраззу покупайте прайм что-бы было лучше хотя на прайме тоже есть читеры но ситуация на нём всяко лудше и меньше. НО читеры всегда были и будут учтите.....", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561199069485728", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595678400.0} {"text": "A fun game with a great potential that is sadly absolutely hindered by some major issues (and I'm not even gonna bother with the high amount of interface and physics bugs): -The netcode is complete garbage, most often than not you get killed while running behind a wall or a door, thinking that you're safe, while in reality the bullet reaches you even as far as a couple of seconds after hiding; -Game is ravaged by hackers: from wallhacks to aimhacks and even no recoil, you name it. Most of them are coming from China, but for some reason ($$$), Bluehole still refuses to region lock it; -Certain features, such as vaulting or opening doors/picking up loot are slow and unresponsive, and in a battle royale scenario the speed of such actions can make the difference between life and death; The developers sadly seem more keen on adding unecessary features such as gun skins, emotes or more lootcrates than fixing major problems that ruin what could be an engaging experience. I played this game for a considerable amount of time so far and I would love to really like it, but Bluehole doesn't seem to care about a good playing experience as much as they seem to care about making a profit, so I can't commend them for that.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130030967", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523620800.0} {"text": "Халтура !!", "appid": "438740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198033808107", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498305600.0} {"text": "bad game", "appid": "296050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138563857", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496750400.0} {"text": "bb", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198129561290", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1531310400.0} {"text": "В игре дахера багов не ракамендую пакупать", "appid": "241540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198108097167", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1403784000.0} {"text": "♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ got banned for no reason", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263382305", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1510142400.0} {"text": "Игра полная хуета и донат решает", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198884188563", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580385600.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198196757702", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554897600.0} {"text": "I'm really torn about this game. This game has a very interesting little story at its heart which will grab you if you give it the chance, but the overall game might not be worth your purchase (at least at full price). So lets break this down: The game starts with a relatively well animated intro with good music. The soundtrack is really good, at some points almost too good for the barebone nature of the gameplay. I like the artstyle of the game. The very cleanly drawn characters contrast well with the water-color painted backgrounds, altough on some screens this clashes a little too much. There are quite a few caveats though: This is a point and click adventure with puzzles so there are no suprises here. The puzzles are very reasonable and everything is very solvable by reading the text presented in the game. I enjoyed the puzzles because they were not frustrating but challenging enough to justify their existence. The point and click mechanics however, are disapointing. It is not very apparent where you character can move and it can be very frustrating to get your character from point A to B. The cursor will change to tell you where you can go, but sometimes the places where you can go are so needlessly small that it is hard to click them which results in some frustration. clicking on items from your inventory doesn't feel good and there is literally no feedback if you try to combine or use something, that you are not supposed to. There is actually still a bug in the game which freezes the game and the only way to procceed is to press the \"Skip\" button. So long after release you would've thought they might have fixed this. And even though I did not encounter a \"game breaking\" bug, there were quite a few instances of items just vanishing from the inventory (glad they were just invisible) or puzzles getting into undefined states. This game clearly lacks polish and I am surprised any decent game tester could overloock such obvious flaws. The story is what keeps this game afloat. It is a shame then, that this game is very short and the real plot is not revealed until 60~ minutes into the game, which is at about half of the play-time. Relating to the characters is hard when faced with not enough screen-time, but the themes the story is dealing with are heavy enough to make up for that. The Translations feels very clunky. I feel like there was a lot of missed opportunity to make the interaction between the cat and the heroine a lot more funny, which would've made the game a lot more enjoyable, especially in the beginning. I was also very disapointed about some key scenes in the story where I felt like I didn't quite get what was going on. All in all I'd say this game feels rushed. I really like the concept of the story and would like to see more of it, but the lack of polish, bugs, a slow start and the overall shortness of the game makes it hard to recommend this at full price. This game has a lot of unrealized potential.", "appid": "463460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053670536", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1482667200.0} {"text": "Antes de señalar las cosas malas de este juego quiero aclarar que aprecio que haya sido hecho con las mejores intenciones, este fue el primer juego de estos desarrolladores y ellos mismos admitieron que no fue bueno y bromeaban sobre ello, y usaron las críticas para crear un nuevo juego lllamado OLDTV y según los análisis de Steam es muy buen juego, otra cosa que disfrute fue el trabajo puesto en las voces, se nota que pusieron mucho esfuerzo en eso. Pero desgraciadamente todo eso no elimina el hecho de este juego es terrible. Primero que nada, entiendo que no este en español, pero que no hayan subtitulos ni siquiera en inglés complicó mucho las cosas, se bastante inglés pero aún así hay partes que no podía entender lo que decían por mucho que intentara. Y en cuanto a los niveles y rompecabezas en si, muchas veces busque guías sobre como pasar ciertas partes que aunque las pasara aún no tenian sentido alguno. La historia en si es cualquier cosa, un chico llamado Antony va a una fiesta y despierta solo en una casa con un maníaco que según él cree secuestro a su amiga Sam (La anfitriona de la fiesta), el maníaco llamado Vinny te jode y grita todo el tiempo y tienes que escapar de él, por lo que entendi Vinny era un vendedor de drogas y Antony y Sam son hermanos y terminaron teniendo setzo en la fiesta y de eso se trata basicamente, sobre una fiesta que termino en incesto xddd. Una advertencia importante es tener cuidado al jugar este juego pues este juego me dio fuertes mareos y un dolor de cabeza jodido pues hay partes donde hay que escalar paredes y cosas así, muchisimas personas se quejaron de esto también en los foros. Así que bueno no lo recomiendo a menos que uses guías para pasarlo, es un juego hecho de manera sana y gratis, con logros fáciles de conseguir y no dura mas de 2-3 horas, pero si no tienes paciencia puede ser un dolor de huevos.", "appid": "298260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198155496080", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518696000.0} {"text": "Bad", "appid": "244210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068094987", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1408622400.0} {"text": "waste of time", "appid": "619310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042628027", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519473600.0} {"text": "No idea why I purchased the game if it's just going to become F2P anway. Wish they would actually make a new game if they want to implement royale, or at least make a seperate copy thats free which is only royale, but just making the whole game free is absurd...", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091242786", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544616000.0} {"text": "Bad peformance inside game after use latest patch made this game lag unplayable.....", "appid": "73220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198366856739", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1516795200.0} {"text": "При входе на сервер вылетает не высвещивая какой либа ошибки", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120990381", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1447675200.0} {"text": "Симулятор доната -10/10", "appid": "253710", "steamid": "profiles/76561198128724799", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "175", "votes_funny": "60", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1447848000.0} {"text": "Разглядывая еле заметные объекты на экране, которые в представлены самим игроком и десятками прущих напролом врагов, цель у которых задавить вас не силой, а численным превосходством и обычным тараном, создаётся впечатление, что главное в shoot'em up играх - это иметь острое зрение и реакцию хотя бы выше уровня черепахи. И если вы пришли сюда, как и полагается, за хорошей данмаку-игрой, то забудьте об этом. Перед вами очередной продукт весьма посредственного уровня. Тут важно отметить, что не плоха именно из-за своего внешнего вида (ибо тогда в разряд провалов отошла бы львинная доля всех додзинси игр), проблема заключается в том, что продукту просто нечего предложить. И всё бы ничего, но даже исполнение уже имеющихся идей и наработок здесь хромает, а то и вовсе отторгает. Уже упомянутые подслеповатые враги, неохотно прущие на игрока, словно делают это с явной неохотой. Даже боссы не требуют к себе особого подхода и сдаются после очередного мощного залпа. Кочнено, такое происходит не всегда, но львинная доля геймплея с лёгкостью заставит вас скучать, пока вы не доберётесь до следующих уровней. Но даже если так, то еле слышимый саундтрек, перебиваемых средненького качества спецэффектами и серая графика (2008-го года), вам всё равно не дадут общего представления о том, какими на самом деле должны быть данмаку игры и качественные shoot'em up'ы. Ценник игры явно задран (на Desura игра и вовсе стоит втридорога). Платить тут ровным счётом не за что. Слабые спецэффекты, серый визуальный стиль, управление, которому явно далеко до отзывчивости, а так же тонны однообразного гемплея. Брать игру в коллекцию и рекомендовать её изголодавшимся по жанру - то ещё преступление. Ничего хорошего в нет и не появится. А между тем, хороших игр по этой тематике и так достаточно.", "appid": "284220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065950489", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1454500800.0} {"text": "The game is a pain in the a**. I dont like forced missions. Im probably done with the game for now, as it forced me into a mission while I was tabbed out, and I cant quit it or walk away. I have unistalled it and am unsure as to if ill bother with it again.", "appid": "552520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048014684", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1548417600.0} {"text": "this game is pretty much paladins, came out good , bad after updates hi rez", "appid": "813820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198264049214", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1529064000.0} {"text": "\"Spent 80% of the time playing by testing mods rather than actually playing the game. 10/10\" WAS used to be my review for skyrim. But now that Valve added a paywall and make many mods need to be purchased before using is a blatant attack on a free modding community that is driven by the community. This is turning the modding community much more of a bussiness rather than a big community who creates content that makes a game experience better and more variable. The modding community run smoothly for years until Valve got involved and decided to do this.", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117923928", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1421496000.0} {"text": "Скучный сюжет.Скучный мультеплеер.Бесполезная прокача перса.В общеем если фанат серии то норм а так не айс(.", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007723127", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1463140800.0} {"text": "Любите копаться в мусоре? Добро пожаловать в ММ! p.s Скины??! Вы рофлите?!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198848964593", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "t