 el internet explorer esta mejor optimizado que este metro.", "appid": "412020", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074912263", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": "33", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550232000.0} {"text": "What we have here is a permanent upgrade system like in titles such as or , mixed with some vanilla aRPG dungeon crawling. And it's all just a bit too slow for my tastes. It felt like the runs were watered down by being far too easy until you hit a wall. I would prefer a more potent experience where I die sooner and earn more gold in the meantime. Tighter loops; shorter runs. Now I'm sure this is a labor-of-love project with modest ambition - and I appreciate and applaud that. I just don't find it compelling and therefore can't recommend my friends run out and put down their money. You grind to get permanent upgrades and buffs, in turn to grind to get further in the dungeon. It can work, but in general this is my least favorite way to manage upgrades. The upgrades are all standard, too. We have stereotypical upgrades like damage buffs, and classic playable classes. This is an easy and free opportunity to make this title stand out from the sea of dungeon crawlers out there. Sure, it's an Early Access campaign. I get that. Controller support is pretty wonky right now. Many of the enemy sprites are muddy and really hard to tell what they are. The enemy AI is quite bad (they get stuck on corners and walls). Building your fortress sounds great, but it really just boils down to a tech/skill tree. Level design is nothing special. Again, I'm not trying to hate on a pet project, but all these things add up to something I can live without. +I can't argue with the price +I do like the idea of a bite-size aRPG rogue-ish game -There is nothing fresh here -Overly standard dungeon crawler -The enemy artwork is muddy -Controller support needs a good bit of work -The dungeon crawling is a bit too slow, and runs too long for my tastes I do wish the developer the best with this and any future projects - but this gets a hard pass from me.", "appid": "946610", "steamid": "profiles/76561198040884867", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "34", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1549972800.0} {"text": "各种问题，cpu、gpu占用高，希望改进", "appid": "616720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198208700869", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1542715200.0} {"text": "um coco", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068834178", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1419595200.0} {"text": "...", "appid": "554530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198393685579", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546603200.0} {"text": "When running Discord voice is lagging", "appid": "431960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198186907071", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546084800.0} {"text": "na minha opnião o jogo tem mt q melhorar ainda. hitbox bugada, interações \"bugadas\". o jogo n tem fluidez!", "appid": "893520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198321330685", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1541764800.0} {"text": "Не удобная в управлении глючная параша,короткая.", "appid": "968820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084555170", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580904000.0} {"text": "mucho texto", "appid": "626690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198152349704", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592308800.0} {"text": "unplayable on newer operation systems", "appid": "12130", "steamid": "profiles/76561198292175836", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "23", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1534507200.0} {"t