АЛО. В общем, я психанула и удалила эту суперпуперкласснуювсемсоветую игру. Зато мои нервы помог сгладить хотлайн майами. спасибо. 0/10", "appid": "391540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198285772647", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483531200.0} {"text": "Terrible shooting.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085246837", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603454400.0} {"text": "Крик души: Игра недоделанный кусок говна (я не говорю что игра плохая, она заебисъ, но не доделана и не будет скорее всего) невидимые текстуры за которые ты цепляешься при уворотах и ловишь по лицу, враг в 3 метрах от тебя машет своей вилкой ну он не должен достать до тебя, но не тут то было, он просто подъезжаете к тебе, и что? ловишь по лицу, индикатор тут просто \"шикарен\" не показывает нормально что удар слева быстрее чем с право прилетит и получаешь по лицу, показывает что удар будет слева а он с права и по лицу снова, покажет что щас ты по лицу с права получишь но не тут то было лови по лицу сверху. Персонажи: Раньше они были кто то более кто то менее сбалансированы но щас же, делают сраные спам машины для максимально простой игры (для слабоумных наверно) используй 1-2 приема убивай, новых персов добавляют опять же что? правильно, сраные спам машины, зачем? почему? что у них в голове?, добавляют сраные \"ивенты\", никому не нужные отвратительные доспехи и прочую хрень, месяца два по центру карты была невидимая текстура и кое как они её убрали, разработчикам видимо максимально пофиг на игру.", "appid": "304390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198141874578", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589371200.0} {"text": "SAKIN ALMAYIN!!! YARATIK KESME SİMULATOR Mmorpg oyunlara middle earth havalarına kısaca büyü kılıç ok vs olaylarını acayip severim 2010 yılından beri oyunlarını oynarım shayia olsun vb. Oyunda sohbette herkes sövüyor boş boş yaratık kesip duruyorlar Zevk alınmıyor 38 Saat boyunda orda ki yaratığı kes level atla şurda ki yaratığı kes level atla boss kes (2 dakika kesilen boss) insanlarla tanışmaya git hiç kimse umursamasın falan yani acayip boş ve gereksiz bir oyun verdiğim para ve saat sonuna kadar boşuna gitti. Hikaye desen acayip boktan uyanıyorsun bi köyde hafızanı kaybediyon bi ruh var diyo onu kes bunu kes onu yapıyon başka bir bok yok. Oyunda çok şey düşünülmüş vs ama amaç yok amaç onu kes bunu kes yani kafama sıçsınlar bir daha mmorpg oynarsam fragman ve incelemelerde acayip övmüşler dedim kesin alıyorum fiyatta uygundu yani mal mal iş mk", "appid": "836620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198204130853", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533038400.0} {"text": "My heart beats for The Elder Scrolls series but... Bethesda, c'mon? The Creation Club is a lack of respect for us, the players. There were mods better than the few in Creation Club, for the vanilla Skyrim. Besides, you are trying to make more money on a 6 year old game instead of working on an Elder Scolls VII?? Give us something other than pay-to-play, please. Elder Scrolls Online was a complete fiasco for the people who have always loved the good old Oblivion, Morrowind and Daggerfall games (some like every single one - from Arena to Skyrim [me]). I have over 20.000 hours in all Elder Scrolls games together (PC+Consoles) and as I watched Bethesda get bigger and bigger - they started caring less and less. And it shows in their games and pay-to-play spirit. This isn't, sorry for the philosophical way this will sound, in the spirit of The Elder Scrolls. This is all money-making business, sadly. And we're not stupid - we can tell that THAT is what counts now. Money. A young Cristopher Weaver once said \"the dream of gamers\" because Bethesda chased our dream - but... I don't know about you but paying 40 quid for a remake of a 6 year old game with paid mods to it - isn't my dream. Neither is a giant online game where it is clearly pay-to-play/ win. Don't buy The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim Special Edition - it has nothing new or extraordinary to offer. You might as well buy the vanilla game and download free and amazing mods from Nexus. Edit: And now they keep updating so the good old SKSE will not work for more than a few months at a time. It's sad seeing as how some of the newer Elder Scrolls games players/ modders brought on the foundation of most of the long-time players. No one would put so many hours into a game, without mods! Get your head out of your arse, Bethesda. The modders have been the ones keeping this dead ass game alive!", "appid": "489830", "steamid": "profiles/76561198111028550", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1507464000.0} {"text": "its a decent game", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198418527394", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "5 Palabras....Ostias que mierda de juego. Bug de trofeos,ESC,Space+G y saltan los trofeos de golpe.", "appid": "496680", "steamid": "profiles/76561198346951291", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511784000.0} {"text": "I Prefer the old game Insurgency. The old one looks better and plays better. This game feels like a mobile copy from the original Insurgency. Graphics are sh** (Even when putting everything on MAX and its badly optimal for PC's. I give this 2.5 / 10 ( Just going to refund the game )", "appid": "581320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198186339717", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546344000.0} {"text": "Bought season pass for more rpg, got a bad mod instead. At least you can tame a deathclaw which make this less bad then Contraptions Workshop.", "appid": "435880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072821096", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1466596800.0} {"text": "♥♥♥♥ update", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198334764789", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544356800.0} {"text": "worst", "appid": "375180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198103019515", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "This is ensentially a slender game, a very buggy version I have to say. There tons of bugs but this is a free indie horror game so I can't hate. For example jump from a table down to the ground: \"You fell to your death\". Uh huh, killed my brained celss that's what happened. Same rules get pages, run away from Slenderman. So, you're probably wondering where's the cool looking monsters in the trailer, hmmm... yeah there's none. It never came out, saying it did but no, no it didn't. Another thing I dislike is the map, not saying it's big, but the fact that you can get lost in the game. The forest is dark and the flashlight the game gives you doesn't give enough light to see where you're going. There's one part where you have to climb this big a** tower just to save the game. Like seriously, I'd rather die from Slendy than climb that tower. This game had potential but just never met the expectations of all gamers. All in all, if you want a scare you can get it, get it if you still fear the Slenderman. I give this game a 5.5/10", "appid": "241640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198147237442", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1420200000.0} {"text": "Спасибо за игру.Если меня спросят,когда меня тошнило в последний раз,я смело смогу называть этот день.", "appid": "517630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198238137498", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "5", "early_acce