 as another character. Moving on to the plot. The story so far , atleast in the first episode was top notch and I got to say I was pretty skeptical about the game after seeing how Polygon gave it a 6.5. But just for now the story has been great. The way it shows how major effects of the book/show affect minor houses is brilliantly executed. The decisions are playing a major role like they've played in the previous Telltale games. But this time around like Totalbiscuit said, it's solely not emphasizing on dialogues and etc, but rather small ones like \"taking this\" or \"not taking this\". The weight of your decisions are felt by your own playable characters as they have to go through them. This game thus far have been the best Telltale game with hard decisions for me. It's not only that, they manage completely to nail the grim nature of of GoT. This game isn't rated R, it doen't certainly have boobies, but holy cow it's violent. In a good way which is what Game of Thrones is all about. Moving on the the gameplay, the devs have used the same gameplay elements they have used in previous games, if you are looking for a button smashing, sword blazing GoT, THIS ISN'T THE GAME FOR YOU. Point and click mechanics and quick times events have been in the game so far with nothing new gameplay wise. The voice acting was excellent, especially since they were done by some of the original cast. Not to mention some of the scores from the original series. However the only thing I have against this game is the new graphics they have used. It doesn't look bad, but it seems a bit muddy and unpolished in a way. At times you can see some of the textures blur for no reason, that's something Telltale should work on. And the weird animations of characters can get clunky at times. Improvement from these two departments would have made this game a much better experience for consumers. But then again no one plays Telltale games for graphics. Overall this game is pretty damn good. You should note, if you haven't seen the TV show nor read the books, be sure to do either of them. Because this game is heavily based on the what has already happened in the series so far. Hopefully Telltale would release other episodes rather quickly than what they did with TWUA but for now if you already have the game, you'll be playing it a multiple times to see what could have been if you had taken another choice. I'd give it a solid 9/10. However this may change with the coming episodes. For now it's an excellent game. A MUST BUY FOR GAME OF THRONES AND TELLTALE FANS!", "appid": "330840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068882850", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1417608000.0} {"text": "This game is pure trash .... its a broken boring mess , its ♥♥♥♥ dont play it simple", "appid": "1092660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198156421532", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578744000.0} {"text": "Забанили ни за что, а отыграл 150 часов. Найс игра парни а читеров не банят конечно...", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032906174", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563451200.0} {"text": "ээээээ ыыыыыы эээээээ, помогите превращаюсь в аутиста", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198867551108", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "Игра как Кот Шрёдингера . Вроде играбельна , а вроде бы нет.", "appid": "318100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198118865656", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582372800.0} {"text": "wonky controls", "appid": "331600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096132190", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496404800.0} {"text": "Ich rate von einem kauf ab. Games for windos live 