It stupid nanos weapon damage. Optimization is very bad,but I wouldn't advise to play it,play better in FortNite(not is) the same,only for free,and for H1Z1 to pay still need. The game story.", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561197994454741", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1513512000.0} {"text": "В первой части можно было на все арты потеребонькать,а здесь только на парочку,бракую ((((", "appid": "963690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198163677213", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "нхуй", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130544930", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1464523200.0} {"text": "в анчале игры ты думаешь что тебя посадили в комнату с 9 даунами, но потом оказывается что в комнате даунов 10", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198148657613", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572004800.0} {"text": "I played like 30 rounds. First I would like to say the good things. Then the not so good things. + I really like the voice-chat feature. + The graphics are very good for a game like this. + I really like the themeing, because I watched all the Friday movies + Big map with 8 players - First bad thing I don't like is that Killer-choose-system... I was NEVER the Killer! Never in that 30 rounds. - Second thing, that it's almost impossible to escape from the Killer if he sees you one time... Stamina is empty in seconds. And if your lucky and have one item to stunn him, your able to walk 10 meters and he grabs you again. - Third thing is, that its too expensive for this much content... I would pay 20€-25€... Not 37€.... The game is based on luck. If he don't finds you, your free. But if you will be seen one time... YOUR DEAD. Besides all that I would recommend it, BUT the price is to high, so I will not recommend it for this price.", "appid": "438740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198160068608", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1496145600.0} {"text": "Враги на таком расстоянии, что я их даже в зуме разглядеть не могу. А они меня на полном ходу ловят с одной плюхи, и это в реалистичном режиме. Что там за киборги играют, я не знаю.", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198155142981", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1457265600.0} {"text": "0 context on the story, it feels like jumping in the middle of a bad science fiction space thriller movie. The creators had no idea about a concept called contrast. The bit sized enemy planes are very similar in colour to the background and you dont see them unless they fire you on your ship or go full kamikaze!", "appid": "473560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198268316075", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535803200.0} {"text": "Öncelikle Türkçe dil desteği için teşekkürler. Anime tarzı oyunları seviyorsanız bu oyunu da çok seveceğinize eminim. Grafikleri gayet tatlı ve hoş. Müzikleriyse insanı sıkmıyor. Bazı oyunlarda sinir eden bir müzik döngüsü olur bunda onu görmedim.Özellikle arkadaş ortamında iyi olacağını düşünüyorum. İyi oyunlar. 12.04.2020 Güzel bir oyundu. Bir şekilde türlü türlü işlerle oyunun içine etmişiniz ya valla helal olsun. Hangi oyunda ana hikâyeyi kaldırıldığını gördünüz? Size bu şahane (!) zekâ fışkıran fikri kim verdi çok merak ediyorum. Valla tebrik ederim eşine zor rastlanan bir politika izlemişiniz bravo valla resmen oyunun en güzel özelliğini kaldırmışsınız. Geriye de sadece içi boş , ruhsuz bir oyun kalmış. Başlayacak olanlara kesinlikle tavsiye etmiyorum zamanınızı boşa harcamayın.", "appid": "844870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035407533", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1575374400.0} {"text": "Leider ein reinfall. Ich hab es ein paar mal versucht aber bin nie wirklich warm gewurden mit diesem spiel. Fand ich eigendlich sehr schade da ich das Spiel Prinzig sehr gut fand und wenn es besser umgesetzt wäre hätte es wahrscheinlich auch gut spaß gemacht.", "appid": "24240", "steamid": "profiles/76561197991648071", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1419940800.0} {"text": "i was stuck in loading screens and game crashing errors for a whole hour dont buy this game", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198355351910", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "Игра для детей не больше 6-ти лет , играть в неё почти не возможно , только одно понравилось - НИ-ЧЕ-ГО !", "appid": "743580", "steamid": "profiles/76561198355216544", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596196800.0} {"text": "Если решитесь поиграть в это, то берегите свою пятую точку, ибо она либо сгорит, либо потеряет невинность.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198155495633", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "52", "votes_funny": "28", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558526400.0} {"text": "空荡的世界除了突突突还能做什么呢", "appid": "548570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198014849276", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569153600.0} {"text": "bad", "appid": "363440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076368396", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543233600.0} {"text": "buggy as hell, frastrating at times, can't recommend developers need to do a better job", "appid": "504720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072062771", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533816000.0} {"text": "is a 2D fighting game made by the same creators of . The game takes place in a dangerous city called Neo Seoul,filled with criminals,terrorists and corruption.You have to pick your side because not all characters are good guys,you can also choose the criminals to destroy the city! Every character (they are 8) have his little story behind.They are short and nothing special but for a fighting indie game they aren't that bad.But there are few problems,for example,every character have almost one antagonist,friend,rival, that looks the same as the protagonist.It was like fighting against a doppelganger,same moves,same celebration but different details like the haircut or a different color.Some stories are decent,some stories a bit stupid but it's just an addition for a fighting game,the really important thing is the gameplay! The movements feels really slow and mechanical,not unplayable but it i didn't liked them.It was hard hiting a special move because the character is really slow so you dont't have enough time to make it.Talking about special moves and combos,there are just 3 special moves for each characters,really easy to make but they are still very few for a fighting game.Also there is only one combo x character,with the rusty movements it's almost impossible to make a combo. Talking about the difficulty,the cpu IA is terrible,the enemies are super easy to beat,you can stay still,tapping just one button and win,at least until the final boss.I don't know why but the boss is unbalanced and overpowered,he can kill you with 3 moves,his punches destroys your energy bar in seconds.He is so unbalanced compared to all the enemies before him. There are 5 game modes in the game,we have.. Well,it isn't a Training,there is no tutorial,you have to fight an opponent and after you kill him you'll return in the main menu.He doesn't have invincibility like most fighting games to let you pratice,so pratically nothing useful. About the story mode,it's like the arcade (beat all the enemies until the last boss) but you don't have a game over and there is a background story in each fight..I didn't liked the random fights during the story.They broke the storyline just to fill a bit the short my opinion they should have done like this:have some fights without dialogue and then,when you fight an important character, you put the background story.Instead they put a dialogue with every opponent,and sometimes their reason to fight are nosense. You have to complete also some objects for each fight or you won't be able to win.For example using only your pistol,or you won't be able to damage your opponent.That's a bad thing too because they put a limit in your fight,you can't do what you want and you have to spam just a move like an idioti,otherwise you can't damage the opponente and you will lose. With a 16bit style,the graphic was cool and perfect for the theme of the game.The mix between crime drama and this blue filter was a perfect choice,accompanied by this 16bit awesome soundtracks made by .I liked also the characters drawings,my favourite one was Gyeong,with his broken detective attire.What about the stages?Nice job also here,there are lot of stages all differents from each other with unique details and animated backgrounds.Very nice job with the graphics and the soundtracks,that's the main reason why i was fascinated about this game months ago! With his 90's style caught me,fascinated by his blue filter,crime drama theme and the nice soudtracks.But the gameplay in my opinion was bad,rusty and slow for a fighting game.Performing a combo or just a simple move was hard.Also the cpu was terrible,really easy except for the unbalanced boss.Another bad thing were the objects in the story mode that limited a lot the gameplay and the antagonist that looked like the same as the protagonists,just with different colors palette or haircut.Lot of potential for a 3 dollars game,wasted by some bad choice and a bad gameplay.It was hard to choose if i liked the game or not,would love a neutral vote but there are more cons then pros so it's a sad no. Feel free to read my full review here with more details if you want! I'm not a professional reviewer but Thank you very much for reading,sorry again for the delay and thanks for all the followers,the good comments and EVERYTHING.And hope to see in future a game by this awesome developers with more features and a better gameplay.", "appid": "449210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075645628", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "50", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1472558400.0} {"text": "Tahle hra je dobrá ale co. Když nemáte DLC tak si moc nezahrajete a když si nějaké koupite a hrajete PAYDAY2 s tím nebo bez DLC víc než 2h Tak jí nemůžete vrátit. Bez DLC je hra moc prázdná a k výběru zbraní taky nic moc takže proto palec dolů. 5/10", "appid": "218620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198258556478", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1492171200.0} {"text": "Nie polecam , zabiła mnie żaba", "appid": "488440", "steamid": "profiles/76561198051729854", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1479556800.0} {"text": "BrokenGameOfTheDecade :)", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119581724", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Well, it's a good game, but support sucks. I played this once for almost 2 hours, then it just couldnt open again. I re-installed verified and everything. Aeria Games Login is white blank.Support is ignorant. Well If you want a good MMO pray to be of the few who have no problems with it e.e", "appid": "290140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198194555875", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1484049600.0} {"text": "Чет не зацепила", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/765