зация 2.5/10", "appid": "311210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198129896655", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1456574400.0} {"text": "The game is fun for about 10 minutes. Then it you will get bored and you will feel that you are unnecessarily paying 0.90€", "appid": "394870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134580826", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1486036800.0} {"text": "Самая ублдюдочная игра на всем белом свете, физики нет, баги на которые всем похуй, лаги на любых компах... Никогда не берите эту парашу.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198158641835", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "26", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1505649600.0} {"text": "I want to love this game, but the controls just feel, so unintuitive. It's like learning a new language. maybe if I could control just the tilt and going up seperately this would be more pleasant/easier. Alternatively if I controlled it with my phone tilt sensor. But as it is I cannot recommend this game due to steep learning curve in the controls department.", "appid": "457890", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992163205", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509883200.0} {"text": "♥♥♥♥. Go back to ARMA.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198060303696", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520078400.0} {"text": "this game is the badest game ever", "appid": "295110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198325682432", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1493121600.0} {"text": "I'm helping with getting the overall rating down to \"mixed\" or lower. :) ♥♥♥♥ you Take Two. The best thing about this game is modding.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198058710136", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497700800.0} {"text": "Aq öyle bir güncelleme getiriyorlarki 100tl bayılıp aldığın karakter 2 günceleme sonra gazi oluyo sikerim böyle oyunu", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198169421645", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1537185600.0} {"text": "Простите, но онлайн скатился в выкачивание денег, так как фармить крайне долго, отчего в игре уклон на донат. Еще и читеры в каждой сессии и баны ни за что (поулчил бан в том числе и я) Печально, что разрабы забили на сингл, ведь лучше сделать еще одно DLC для онлайна и получить с него денежку.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198091974751", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497787200.0} {"text": "Донат, донат и ещё раз донат!!!", "appid": "291480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198429386330", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606046400.0} {"text": "NO", "appid": "945360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198257191105", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599048000.0} {"text": "As a concept, the game is good... Now lets just actually discuss the game shall we? Softlocks the game is a first person Horror game with a plot that is somewhat so-so (Its understandable, but predictable), letting you explore a forest full of collision problems. If you buy this game, follow the paths, don't try to explore, weird right? you'd like trying to explore would help you find some hidden secrets? Or... Risk long sections of gameplay you've done just to get stuck on that Rock, Log, Small slope that looks traverseable and having to force a reset of the game, LOSING that progress (where most of my hours come from) Now, length, don't expect a long time if you avoided the dastardly hazards which are softlocks, because this game can span (In a long play session) roughly 3.5 - 4.0 hours, so if you think £24.99 (or whatever currency you use) is worth 4 hours of gameplay? then this would be the game for you. As of writing this i'm currently trying to get a refund, knowing my luck they will say \"No, you should have known this game was incomplete when buying\".", "appid": "1092660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048533035", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1567252800.0} {"text": "кал", "appid": "113400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198314112846", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "many hack", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198192823363", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530014400.0} {"text": "Its the funniest game of my life i have ever seen .The game was awful .", "appid": "844870", "steamid": "profiles/76561199022409765", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1580558400.0} {"text": "bad poopy game", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198168192711", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525521600.0} {"text": "If this Store Page was honest! Primal: $extinction is a class-based online roleplay featuring humans & dinosaurs A class-based online multiplayer shooter unlike any other, oh yeah we're so focused on other things besides that, we forgot it was suppose to be a shooter to begin with. We'll get on to the other things in a bit, but let's talk about the near non-existant PVP. Primal: $extinction features awkward paced aimless movie bad guys versus over-sized chickens moving around with their heads cut off, combat! <- yes, we and our fans consider this \"Fun & Balanced\" combat! Will you hunt down human prey as a variety of legendary prehistoric creatures? yes, because trying to play the humans is the equivalent of trying to shoot a cheetah while your drunk & dizzy while riding a pogo stick. Yet our Dinosaur features aren't much better. Unleash your inner rage as you try to take control of dinosaurs stiffer than a guy who worked out at the gym for 3 hours yesterday when he hasn't exercised in months. Choose from 10 unique dinosaur classes, only to end up playing 3 (Nova/Dilo/Ovi) cause the other 7 can't do jack s**t. Survive the island as one of the 5 distinct human classes, each with thier own special abilities to help the te- sorry we couldn't keep a straight face there. Take on your scaley foes with an aresenal of devastating wea- okay we're done here. *A Wasteland filled with trolls & horny kids/teens that have almost taken over the whole game, Roleplay. *A Broken Dino v. Dino mode that's more duable than our Human v. Dino PVP. *A Survival that isn't needed right now and makes Orion look good. *And everyones favorite, Search & Find! scroll through a bottomless list of servers where you desperately try to find a populated TDM or GTTC server with fair ping! Honestly, we tried adding more maps, but everyone wants Docks & Contingency. Aw yes, the real gem of our game, since Early Access we put most of our time & effort into an economy that people still whine about to this day. This is how we often forget about the shooting elements as we still continue to improve the economy and flesh it out with content that isn't really needed right now, but our fans still love it, heck even they forget the shooting elements as well! We have big plans for how to evolve Primal: $extinction, except areas which we were suppose to improve upon from the original since Early Access, but we've since then dropped that goal and wish to please our current fans. To see our roadmap of upcoming content and progress of fixing and adding bugs, check out our Trello organization! don't forget to buy those skins, it's really whats keeping our game alive right now rather than actual game sales and gameplay appeal. Wait wasn't this suppose to be called Primal Carnage: Extinction? oh right, cause we put so little focus on improving what made the original game so good, there's barely any Carnage to enjoy!! we might not be too far off from extinction though ...", "appid": "321360", "steamid": "profiles/76561198037249537", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "133", "votes_funny": "102", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1436875200.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "1034200", "steamid": "profiles/76561198161000134", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553342400.0} {"text": "değmez", "appid": "577800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198284345893", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533211200.0} {"text": "#IWantMyGems", "appid": "601510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198215428207", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1531742400.0} {"text": "This game is fully of bugs!!!!! - When i trove a Grenade i die...... - this game is ♥♥♥♥♥♥, i play zombie when i die and this is ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ dumm -.- ♥♥♥♥ THIS GAME", "appid": "238430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198140460872", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480852800.0} {"text": "Поиграл 30 мин... Думал, что прикольная реализация градостроения, все такое, но нет. Худ просто убогий, такой и я могу нарисовать за пару часов. Игра по типу построй это, просто то. В случае выполнения приходят новые бомжи даешь им работу и так и развиваешься. Играл как я уже сказал 30 мин и ушел тупо в минус, потому что содержания здесь не сбалансированное. Чтобы начать уходить в плюс нужно поставить рынок, чтобы его поставить надо 5 зданий построить и неделю собирать ресурсы. За это время твое поселение уходит в жуткий минус. В итоге психанул и вышел. Пока она в раннем доступе крайне не рекомендую ее покупать.", "appid": "690830", "steamid": "profiles/76561198065707788", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1551355200.0} {"text": "Yahu oyunun zekasını biraz değiştirseydiniz yav. FM 2019'da gümbür gümbür oynayan taktik, 2020'de de gümbür gümbür oynuyor.", "appid": "1100600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052467002", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572868800.0} {"text": "I hate", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198225039708", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1564920000.0} {"text": "It has many bugs but it's an awesome and very funny game with a lot to explore and a lot to do. Definitively better with friends to play and enjoy. It also supports mods :) Totally recommended, but again, be aware of the bugs. EDIT: Had to change my review because the bugs have overtaken the fun of the game. It has been several times they released a patch and a couple of days later they had to release a hot fix because the ♥♥♥♥ EVERYTHING. This time, they ♥♥♥♥♥♥ mods up so much, that I can't add and/or remove any mod without my game crashing. I'm literally stuck. Btw, the game is not finished yet, the final boss still doesn't exist, you can't leave the exile and restart the game. The story itself is unfinished, but hey, they have released several 10$ seasson pass/DLC for you to dress and have new weapons and ♥♥♥♥ if you want. I'm at the point where this ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ games is robbing me enough GBs to install a GREAT game, and honestly, I think that, instead of waiting for years for the devs to do their job and finish the game, I will just uninstall it and leave it as it is. The greed of the devs ruined the game, thy don't deserve my time anymore, and they deserve this review so MAYBE they realise what they are doing.", "appid": "440900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039516329", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542888000.0} {"text": "Extremely easy tile puzzle game. The artwork is decently cute, reminding me of more old-school H games. My main problem is that moving the tiles isn't particularly smooth, and every so often a tile will get \"stuck\" out of position, meaning you have to close the game and restart the puzzle from the beginning. This game is cheap, but still not worth wasting your money on. It even has a cheat button to auto-complete the puzzles - you're better off just browsing Deviantart for free. EDIT// It doesn't seem to have the problem with the tiles getting stuck now, and I think this might have been an issue with my own operating environment!", "appid": "984750", "steamid": "profiles/76561198025566272", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1547985600.0} {"text": "its a fun game no doubt about that but after a while it gets ultra repetitive and a little bit boring as theres nothing new , the content is so so minimal and items in shops are the same almost every day , idk why a season should last all that long time just to struggle the same maps over and over again worst thing in the game is team games it seriously should be removed", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198300071758", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "Jeżel jesteś fanem titan's quest'a, to jest to pozycja zdecydowanie dla Ciebie, w epoce Path of Exile jednak rozwój postaci ala TQ wypada blado a zbieranie ekwipunku jest przyjemniejsze choćby w diablo.", "appid": "219990", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961924647", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1565265600.0} {"text": "Hi. Pros: - This game is great, is ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ perfect, after the patchs run very well. - The single player mode is funny, not as the MK9 history but is great. - Fight with friends is funny, i recommend it. - Predator and Jason character are awesome, but i miss something i can't remember right now. - Nice combo and fatalities. Cons: - This is important, Warner Bros ended his support to this game with less than 1 years from the game release, no more content(as DLC:Kombat Pack 2, only PS4 and One), no fixes for online(Yes for PS4 and Xbox one), no Goty edition(yes for PS4 and One). - Bad port on his release. - The online mode is dead. - Missed content as the characters of Rain and Sindel, in the game files exist their movements, only added as NPC. I like this game, but the developers left him die, thanks Warner Bros, and thanks netherrealm studios, you know how to deal with the PC community, for that reason i put a negative review.", "appid": "307780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004856661", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "28", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1453291200.0} {"text": "The game is good but i won't recommend this game because the multiplayer ruins everything", "appid": "203160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198340732514", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586520000.0} {"text": "Intérêt global : ★★☆☆☆ PlatONIR est un jeu de plateforme 2D solo basique. On notera des graphismes corrects pour ce jeu Indie à récupérer en bundle. Graphismes : ★★☆☆☆ Pas mauvais pour ce type de jeu. Rien d'extraordinaire non plus. Musique / Son : ★☆☆☆☆ Musique chiante en boucle... Jouabilité : ★★☆☆☆ Basique basique, droite, gauche saut.... Durée de vie : ★☆☆☆☆ 10 niveaux, jeu fini en 8 minutes...", "appid": "882070", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967718083", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532952000.0} {"text": "This is a minor patch to Mafia 2, there's no reason for this to exist as a separate game.", "appid": "1030830", "steamid": "profiles/76561197972494985", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590148800.0} {"text": "Поделка ребенка на юнити, мир пустой, хп нету, ждем обновлений.", "appid": "447940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080647816", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1474113600.0} {"text": "Il gioco è bello MA è OTTIMIZZATO COL CULO! UN PORTING PESSIMO DAVVERO INGIOCABILE, E NON DICO CAZZATE PERCHè SONO PIGNOLO ECC. I N G I O C A B I L E Lo consiglio solo su console comunque", "appid": "9480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198122061258", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1435838400.0} {"text": "Ta gra to jest jakaś porażka. Matchmaking ssie pałe, community to jest dramat, serwery to jest totalne gó*no mam tu na myśli tickrate 64 co jest totalnym absurdem a system rang to jest jakieś ku*wa nieporozumienie. Antycheat...Szkoda ku*wa gadać wykryje co najwyżej stare hacki można powiedzieć że overwatch to jest jakaś iskra nadziei dla tej gry. Powiem tak, ta gra nie jest godna nawet 5€ nie wiem jakim prawem to ścierwo jest jeszcze popularne, przy takich developerach ta gra nie ma przyszłości.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198285454135", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1466251200.0} {"text": "Ortalama bir oyun. Artı ve eksileri bana kalırsa şunlar: Artılar: +Güzel grafikler +Akıcı oynanış +Güzel optimizasyon +Parkur mekanikleri +Yeterli ve sade crafting sistemi +Gece vakti oluşan o müthiş gerilim kalbinizin küt küt atmasına sebep oluyor Eksiler: -Tek düze ve ifadesiz karakter modellemeleri -Merak uyandırmayan silik bir hikaye -Ana karakterin hiçbir ağırlığı yok keza yan karakterlerin de aynı şekilde. -Karakter derinliği sağlanmaya çalışılmış fakat bunu oyuncuya aktarmakta çok sıkıntılı. -Bir süre sonra sıkmaya başlayan yan görevler -Kötü diyaloglar Eğer oynanıştan çok veya en az oynanış kadar hikayeye de önem veriyorsanız tavsiye etmiyorum. Hikaye sizin için arka plandaysa \"indirimdeyken\" alın. Her iki şekilde de asıl fiyatını BANA GÖRE haketmeyen bir oyun", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198210007307", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1507464000.0} {"text": "Донатное говно!", "appid": "397900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198136964564", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579867200.0} {"text": "Good Christ I hate this game. I wasn't expecting much out of a more modern shooter, but I had some hope given that it was done by the same developers of the legendary Aliens versus Predator PC game from 1999 (listed on Steam as Aliens versus Predator Classic 2000). How foolish I was. Starting off with the Marine campaign, I'm given a taste of what to expect: slow and stiff movement, sub-par shooting mechanics, poor damage feedback (both to the enemy and to the player) - just everything of a first person shooter that tells me I should quit and go play something else. But I hate myself and want to die so I was determined to play through it all. Everything about the Marine campaign pales to the 1999 classic. Hard. No tense atmosphere brought about by excellent lighting and level layout, and quick and deadly enemies. No breakneck movement speed with lethal weaponry. Just section after section of one tedious chore after another. Next up is the Predator campaign, which I think is the order they want you to play it in? It went Marine -> Alien -> Predator in the '99 game, but whatever. Again, the game is not as fluid and free as it was in AvP1999. The targeting mechanism for both fighting and moving feels so restrictive. It's almost a good idea, with the jumping ability of the Predator, but is hampered by requiring a pseudo lock-on system. They also turned combat against the Aliens into some kind of first person brawler, with a light/heavy/block method. Seriously. Now, they can take the tense Marine campaign and make it slow and tedious, and they can make the interesting and calculating Predator campaign and make it annoying and boring. Surely they won't take the fun and clever Alien campaign and make it annoying and pointless, right? Why did I doubt this? Instead of moving around at lighting speed, preying on terrified humans as you hide in the shadows lining up a head bite, you... well, just like the other two campaigns, are moving slow as can be, are much less lethal, and have to engage in a combat system so boring it feels like it's all designed busywork - which I guess it is. Easier than taking the time to design something that's actually fun. I mean ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥, there's a canned animation for entering vents! For the ALIEN! You have to press a button to enter a vent and there's an inescapable canned animation! Oh crap, I just realized I forgot to mention the grab system. So the Predator and Alien have a grab mechanic for instant kills. Except it's not instant. It's very, very slow. And you're completely vulnerable during it. Hey, that's good balancing, right? Instant kill mechanic with a drawback? Well, it makes them essentially pointless as you'd only do it when the target is alone, given how long it locks you into the canned animation each time. Why even have this mechanic, then? I guess to get around the game's other design fault of weaponry and attacks not being very lethal. No more charge-up Predator blade lobbing off Marine's heads here. I'll skip talking about the boss fights across all three species as they're just annoying chores. The whole game was just a dull slog. I guess if you grew up on Halo this game would be exciting, but I think I'll replay AvP Classic 2000 to remember what fun feels like.", "appid": "10680", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970502966", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571745600.0} {"text": "This is not what we remember from PUBG PUBG is getting worse every day, maybe even soon it will become like CS:Go Cheaters are on the rise and despite the bugs it has ... I'm not saying it's trash, its a good game, but it would be great if they could get rid of the cheaters and bugs. 5/10", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198440130122", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594641600.0} {"text": "лучше бы еще один дс сделали вся боевка целиком состоит из мерзейшего парирования, которое ничего у меня кроме анальной боли не вызывает, потому что в серии соулс я этим никогда в жизни не пользовался и супер бесполезный протез, который почему то выставляют чуть ли не главной фичей игры", "appid": "814380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073046009", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553342400.0} {"text": "bad", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198137766256", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497873600.0} {"text": "Ennyi órával kenterbe kell lőnöd ugye azt vágod??? :D:D", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004872356", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1455883200.0} {"text": "CS GO это: - Слил катку? Понижение. - Выиграл 5 каток подряд? Эм ну ок, мы подождем пока ты сольешь и понизим. - С тобой в тиме нуб и ты его кикнул? Бан! - Отрубился сервак? Бан! - Кинул молотов но еб###ны тимейты бегут через него? Ну чтож - бан! - Плохо играешь? Бан! - Хорошо играешь? ВАКбан! - Читер? Играй дальше, нам же по##й на репорты игроков. - Russian? C Y K A B L Y A T", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198319044446", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "I thought this was really good game but, every patch is worse than one before, caracters have no backstory and are buggy, developers don't care about community. It woud be ok if you needed to pay only for skins, but you need to pay for the caracters too, I understand, that is the way to make people play your game but before caracters did cost only 3.5K now they cost at least 13K witch is too much, a lot of bugs like: Getting in other team's spawn, don't reciveing gold at the end, abbilitys just go on cooldown but don't do anything. I quited this game a long time ago, I had 100 Hours on this game and spent a lot of money on it. Caracters are rip-off of Overwatch, and started riping eachother, developers ran out of the ideas so they are telling the same story. That is it from me, If you like this review rate it, at my opinion, it is beter to spend 40€ on Overwatch, I rate this game 2 of 10 Hey it is me again I forgot to say that every time a new character is out it is too op to be in game, after 1/2 weeks caracter gets nerfed and becomes broken. Cya", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198250196260", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1475236800.0} {"text": "I don't know why I was VAC Banned but it happened, so much for a clean ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ record. Thanks a lot Valve.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198205047753", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1483963200.0} {"text": "Щас бы не уберать ограничение на 6 гб RAM ЛЯЯЯЯЯЯЯЯЯЯЯ P.S уберите ля и всё у вас будет хорошо ЛЯЯЯЯЯ и отзывы отрицательные пропадут", "appid": "327690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198188870867", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1501761600.0} {"text": "pushed off bridge", "appid": "629760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076235662", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Быстро надоедает. Баланс плахой всевремя одни и теже действия.....задротно.", "appid": "645630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198285798547", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572868800.0} {"text": "I've been playing this game since the day it came out. It was supposed to be a remaster of Contract Wars, Absolutsoft's browser fps. And it was just that, for a while -- A balanced and fun shooter with a less arcadey feel than most other fps games that I've played. However, the game was super buggy, and it died quickly since it was a paid game, while Contract Wars was f2p. Fast forward 3 years, and the game has been \"\"remade\"\" several times, each straying further and further from what made Contract Wars so great. Now, we have a generic, buggy, and unbalanced game that is now arcadey in all the wrong places, while still retaining features that shouldn't be in an arcade fps. This game might be fun for a dozen hours, but as a veteran who only has access to high level servers, the game is overriden by people who abuse OP weapons and attachments, and know exactly where to camp on every level, so that the conquest game mode is unwinnable for one of the teams. If you live in North America, have fun playing on 200 ping servers as you get sniped from behind walls. 4/10. ps, they've been ignoring the feedback from non russians, such as myself, although me and a few other people have put in 300+ hours and know what this game needs more than most of the other players.", "appid": "374280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198326898712", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1477137600.0} {"text": "Stardew Valley was more enjoyable.", "appid": "105600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198138708907", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591876800.0} {"text": "This game used to be about gathering, survive and having fun. The reason why I don't play the game anymore is because of the players. Most people kill you even if you run around naked, without any things and it happens all the time! Edit: Still hate this game, but plays it because its fun 10% of the time. Plz help.", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198820314811", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1548504000.0} {"text": "Jogo para degenerados.", "appid": "1157340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198971189108", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "23", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599393600.0} {"text": "安裝玩dlc,之前雲端存檔紀錄都不見", "appid": "741350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198259184981", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511006400.0} {"text": "Tytuł to strata czasu: - sterowanie jest toporne. - atak polega na zbliżeniu się do wroga i klikaniu w ikonkę miecza. Zero informacji czy zadaliśmy cios czy też może nie doszedł celu, ile zadaliśmy obrażeń itp. - postać potrafi zginąć bez żadnego powodu, ot tak. - brak możliwości konfiguracji głośności odtwarzanej muzyki czy też jej wyłączenia. - zero informacji o tym co trzeba zrobić na danym poziomie. - przeciwnicy stoją w miejscu i na nic nie reagują. - dostępny jest jedynie język rosyjski - brak losowości - za każdym razem ten sam układ pomieszczeń i wrogów.", "appid": "1346860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198122092726", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599912000.0} {"text": "Игра норм... была бы 2002-2003 году. но игра вообще не оптимизирована. Картинка Артефачит играть невозможно 2/10 и то 2 за Ностальгию", "appid": "253920", "steamid": "profiles/76561199030967495", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585915200.0} {"text": "Update 30/12/2018 Game performance is horrific since last 2 patches. I used to have steady 60fps in all situations and now its not above 1fps all the time. All at low setting. The fps metter shows me like 50 but its 1 Im sure of that. Its unplayable 2.5/10 ------------------------------------------------------------------------ This is going somewhere, the thing I dont like is the characters voice commentary, they are so annoying! Id really like the option to disable the characters commentary. Like Anarchy, Slash, they are so childlish and elaborate. Look for example Keel, in Quake 3 the voice taunt was really a cold blooded killer and souless war machine, with no humanity at all. Now it is like some cringe ghetto not so grown man wannabe attemp fail. With lots of show off and foreworks and its really cringy. The strogg sounds like the typical nazi stereotype, it even sounds exactly like Hans from Killing Floor 2. Not defiant at all, maybe dont try to make them be. It really lost that charming darkness that I really enjoyed from past games. I love the inclussion of team and solo instagib. Still missing characters like Flisk and Phobos, or even Bones, but please you have to get rid of that cringy unnecesary voice commentary. 6/10 for that. And still lacks a propper server browser. Pre instagib and unholy trinity part: The game was indeed upgraded a lot, the netcode is way more playable, and the performance got improved too. Exept for times there are too many CPU bots. It hooked me, I have to recognize you this. Now I can remember those great old memories from Quake III Arena fragging. Its developing his own charm. I hope the improvements keep coming! Still not a propper server browser. But my review has changed to very recommended. You will be thrilled. --- Old Review --- The game itself its amazing. A proper Quake III successor. Said by a true fan from the 90s Quake legacy. The problem that kills the experience is the lack of a server browser. I mean 1 of 2 hours of actual playtime I have, was waiting, very long several, minutes to find a server. Most times it stuck looking for god knows what or who. You cant have an online Quake Arena without server browsing. Its an insult.", "appid": "611500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030168536", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1526731200.0} {"text": "Играл в нее еще на релизе, стимовская версия не запускается от слова совсем. Наверно, 10 винда во всем виновата. Если уж прям сильно хотите пройти, скачайте лучше ремастер 3 ас, она как раз-таки входит в этот сборник, пускай и с незначительными техническими проблемами, но вроде как \"УбейСофт\" додумались выкатить патч, который исправляет всю ту поеботину с лицами, тенями и прочей ересью. Берите по скидке тем, у кого 7 винда (не 10). Как я уже говорил, не запускается, даже танцы с бубном не помогают. P.S. а лучше скачайте пиратку))0", "appid": "260210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198133934732", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562414400.0} {"text": "Nao recomendO porque o jogo as vezes estou a jogar bem com fps bons ping bom e do nada crasha o jogo e sai me e deixa de responder, o jogo e bom mas por causa disso deixa me arrependido de ter comprado", "appid": "239140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198427911063", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572609600.0} {"text": "Все, что есть в сериале - это действительно хороший чардизайн, который выстрелил и сумасшедшие фанаты разноволосых сестричек Уникален тем, что в нем нет мыслей авторов.Видели жуткую картинку, где \"плюшевый\" мишка сшит из кусков мяса? - Это оно.Практически всё наглейшим образом украдено с безумной кучи других тайтлов и проектов. Мы регулярно наблюдаем, как аниме заимствует друг у друга идеи, но только не Re:ZERO. Re:ZERO - это и есть заимствование.Фреш микс из миллионов напизжeных идей. Для меня это победитель без конкуренции в рамках конкурса Если не знакомы с аниме индустрией, но решили попробовать стать частью общества Kappa Pride, то хороший выбор для начинания.Многие [вещи/приемы] в повествовании вам будут не знакомы.Не сомневаюсь, что вам понравится и вы, даже, с удовольствием досмотрите Re:ZERO, словив датфил на пару дней или недель.Но это очень слабое аниме для любого человека, который с индустрией уже хоть малость знаком. Если всё уж совсем плохо , то можно и посмотреть в роли пустого, абсолютно бездушного тайтла, но с красивой рисовкой, приятной анимацией и достойным чардизом. Так сказать, глаз порадовать.", "appid": "600930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198050749262", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "40", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490875200.0} {"text": "Наверно единственным плюсом этого пула будет то, что он является одним из самых красивых пулов в стим. и все. Какое то дурное управление мышью, играть геймпадом в разы удобнее. Онлайна в игре тоже практически нет. Баланса нет..Зато есть куча доната. А донат тут на все. Столкнувшись с игроком задонатившим на \"супер - кий \" поражение тебе обеспечено. Игра с друзьями присутствует, но тут тоже свои минусы. Общаться с ними в игре возможности нет. увы. ну а так, это обычный пул, в который можно зайти вечерком и сыграть пару партий с другом онлайн или на одном устройстве. Покупать не советую, даже по скидке.", "appid": "616240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198424736189", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1543060800.0} {"text": "Game is OK Multiplayer is Dead, and it won't rise. They didn't put the DLC on for sale, and I'm not paying $10 for a stupid \"True Ending\" DLC. This is the Dead Space 3 + Real ending DLC, of Dead Risings.", "appid": "543460", "steamid": "profiles/76561198003082995", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498219200.0} {"text": "♥♥♥♥♥ ungar i esportaLLLLLLLL!!!!!!!!", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198974428095", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572091200.0} {"text": "You win first game- you lose all others.", "appid": "397900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198220923860", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589371200.0} {"text": "An absolutely garbage game... The match-3 sections are too numerous and often tedious, and you'll either spend hours on a puzzle before realizing the game stuck its pieces in a position where they can't be moved at all, or you'll just realize it's faster to activate a speed hack and skip everything to death. The hidden object scenes are unimaginative, the other puzzles are done to death and offer zero challenge, except in patience, because the animations are horribly slow. The story is ridiculous and terribly written. The ending doesn't even bother to do more than show two sentences of text. The graphics are subpar for a hidden object game. Possibly the worst game I've finished in a year. I don't know why I finished it, actually. I kept thinking, \"you know it's not going to end on a good note, don't you?\"... And I was right. To the bin!", "appid": "1002280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081340622", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591272000.0} {"text": "its not worth the money, only tryhards", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198366874996", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584187200.0} {"text": "Age of Mythology é um jogo sensacional, um grande classico, o melhor age na minha opinião. Porém a versão em HD da Steam não colaborou com o jogo... muito lag quando se joga em multi-player e nenhuma movimentação para criar uma comunidade ativa no jogo. Infelizmente , um ótimo jogo, com grande potencial, que foi deixado de lado.", "appid": "266840", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084747329", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1505736000.0} {"text": "very bad full of cheaters and clearly non existent anti cheat", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057057684", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1599048000.0} {"text": "Симулятор водителя под бутиратом.", "appid": "292380", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992840575", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1409227200.0} {"text": "You issued a game ban (later turned into a VAC ban) to my girl with absolutely zero grounds for cheating, when all these years she has been nothing but a loyal supporter and lover of your game. She has been crying non-stop because of the valuable skins she has collected along the way—all because of your ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ Trust Factor system that can’t tell the ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ difference between someone playing extremely well and a blatant hacker/cheater. Your Overwatch system is also absolute crap; getting other players (who could be trigger-happy in accusing someone of cheating) to pass judgment on other players instead of having a dedicated professional team handling cases. Never have I ever encountered a game where legitimate players are being punished for playing extremely well and knowing the map like the back of their hand, while spinbots spinning harder than a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ Beyblade ruin the game and just buy a new copy the very next day. I was at least trying to play the game for fun playing casually with some friends every now and then since I simply don’t have the time to grind and get to the top and maintain it. But because of the ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ VAC ban you imposed on my girl and the stress that came along with it, you just earned yourself a hater. I’ve loved Counter-Strike ever since the old days, but I will definitely never ever recommend this joke of a game to family, friends, YouTube viewers, and anyone who might be foolish enough to be enticed by your ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ system. There’s a reason I stuck with Left 4 Dead 2 over the years—at least your company did one thing right.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198124623521", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587643200.0} {"text": "wtf is this crap? ..", "appid": "462060", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993269342", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "13", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1462622400.0} {"text": "Fast & Furious: Showdown или Форсаж: Схватка(как её назвали в русском прокате), по замыслу разработчиков, проект должен соединить между собой все четыре части фильма. Игра откровенный шлак, за несколько лет в Steam я никогда не писал столь негативных обзоров, но поиграв в \"это\", ничего кроме разочарования по бесцельно потраченному времени у меня не осталось... Начнем с цены, от игры за 999 рублей (в СНГ игра стоит $19.99, а в США игра стоит все $29.99) сделанной по известному фильму, известной же студией Firebrand Games (выпускавшей хорошие гоночные симуляторы до этого) и выпущенной известным издателем Activision ждешь несколько вещей, интересного сюжета, красивого графического оформления, реалистичной физики И драйва ! А что получаем ? В игре (середины) 2013 графика уровня 2004 года... Издатель постыдился вставить видео презентацию, в магазине Steam игра представлена несколькими скринами из кат-сцен. Физика напрочь отсутствует, вы легко можете сносить весь автотранспорт, который встретите (независимо от его и ваших габаритов, причем всё это подлетает в воздух так, как будто вы на сверхзвуковой скорости их сбиваете), сносить деревья, колоны зданий... Сюжет не интересен, он хоть и пытается следовать фильму, но кривые кат-сцены(точнее с кривой анимацией, а иногда и без неё, моделька просто сидит в машине, а на фоне идет диалог) никак не способствуют усвоению сюжета, игру хочется выключеть, а не быть соучастником событий сюжета... Никакого драйва, участие в гонка навевает скуку. Музыка во время гонок совершенно не в тему, она может и из фильма, но до уровня NFS или самого фильма не дотягивает. В центре Москвы(первая миссия) трафик такой, как будто гонка происходит после полуночи, а не днем, машин мало, на рекламных щитках всякая ерунда... Это игра сделана хорошими разрабами, на хорошем движке, но при этом откровенно халтурно, не советую покупать, да и просто играть в это!", "appid": "224340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198089075184", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "101", "votes_funny": "12", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1421064000.0} {"text": "Bloodlines of Prima - фейспалм. Тот случай, когда после запуска игры ты утыкаешься в пустой список серверов. А свой создать нельзя. То есть скачать-то этот трэш можно, но сыграть уже не удастся, ибо негде. Как итог: п@здец, товарищи. 0 серверов из 10", "appid": "686090", "steamid": "profiles/76561197982504799", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1606132800.0} {"text": "trash game full of hackers/smurfs/toxic players do not recommend for a fun time.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198249622792", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589716800.0} {"text": "Я не рекомендую брать данный софт даже по скидке, а за полную стоимость – тем более. Его проблема в том, что разработчики хотели сесть сразу на два стула: сделать простой и удобный видеоредактор, с которым справится даже начинающий пользователь, и дать профессионалам многофункциональный инструмент для монтажа. С первой задаче создатели справились: в Мовави действительно можно клепать короткие ролики, то есть продукт работает. Однако радоваться этому факту как минимум странно (он же должен работать априори). Поэтому минусы данного редактора перечеркивают все достоинства, коих и так не очень много. Плюсом можно выделить наличие конвертера (очевидно вдохновлённого любимцем всех пиратов Nero), который со своей задачей таки справляется. Тем не менее, я не рекомендую тратить никакие деньги на этот продукт. Если хотите монтажа – купите ту же стим-версию вегаса. Он выйдет дороже. но при этом вы будете сразу учиться работать с полупрофессиональным инструментом.", "appid": "973600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198049713085", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590580800.0} {"text": "НАСТУПИЛА ОСЕНЬ ПОЛИВАТЬ ЭТО ГОВНО ЕЖЕГОДНОЕ.CУКА БЛЯТЬ НУ НАХУЯ ВЫ ДЕЛАЕТЕ ОДНО И ТОЖЕ БЛЯТЬ.СУКА ВСЕ ТОЖЕ САМОЕ БЫЛО В БЛЕК ОПС 2 Я_ЭТО УЖЕ ВСЕ ВИДЕЛ.НовыЙ ДВИЖОК АгА КОНЕЧНО ТОЖЕ ГОВНО 2000ГОДА (НА КОТОРОМ ВСЕ ЧАСТИ QUAKE СДЕЛАННЫ)СУКА СТРЕЛЬБА КАРТОННАЯ,НАПАРНИКИ ТУПЫЕ ГРАНАТЫ КАК ПЕТАРДЫ НА НОВЫЙ ГОД .ГДЕ ВЫ УВИДЕЛИ ГРАФОН К ЛЮБОЙ ТАЧКЕ ПОДОЙДИТЕ ВСЕ МЫЛЬНОЕ.НАДОЖЕ ТАК ОПЯТЬ НАЕБАТЬ СУКА.ВСЯ АУДИТОРИЯ КАЛДЫ ЭТО ШКОЛЬНИКИ КОТОРЫХ НАЕБАЛИ ЧТО В ИГРЕ БУДЕТ НОВЫЙ ДВИЖОК И ТУТ ПОНЕСЛОСЬ БЛЯ МАМА ДАЙ МНЕ КОСАРЬ НА НОВУЮ КАЛЛ ОФ ДЮТИ.МУЛЬТИПЛЕЕР ТОЧ В ТОЧ ТАКОЙ ЖЕ КАК И ВО ВСЕХ ИГРАХ СЕРИИ (МАЛЕНЬКИЕ КАРТЫ НА 16ЧЕЛ).БЛЯ ДА МЫ У СЕБЯ В ШАРАГЕ ИГРУ ЛУЧШЕ СДЕЛАЕМ.ВЫКЛАДЫВАЕТЕ ТРЕЙЛЕРЫ ПАЧКАМИ А НИХУЯ.РАЗВОД ДЛЯ ЛОХОВ.ОБЩИМ СЛОВОМ В ИГРЕ НЕТУ НИ ГЕЙМПЛЕЯ НИ ГРАФОНА НИ МУЛЬТИПЛЕЕРА НИ ЗВУКОВ.ОБЩИМ СЛОВОМ ХАЛТУРА КАК В ГОУСТЕ.НЕ ПОНЯТНО ПОЧЕМУ МНОГИЕ ГОВОРЯТ ЧТО КОЛДА УДАЛАСЬ 3/10(ИЗ ЗА ХОРОШЕГО СЮЖЕТА) P.S.БРАТЬ ТОК РАДИ СЮЖЕТА НО ТРАТИТЬ 1000Р", "appid": "209650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077732472", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "62", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1415016000.0} {"text": "probably the ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ game ever lul u not getting paid and make the game f2p lmfao", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036822626", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520510400.0} {"text": "9 minutes. That's how long I played it.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198275572983", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1513512000.0} {"text": "Berbat. Üstüne basa basa söylüyorum B E R B A T ! Saçma sikik yerlerde Auto Save sistemi , oyundan çıkmak istersen ana menüye dönememe , direk oyunu kapatma , eski oyun sistemini ve mekaniklerini bırakıp bug çorbası yeni saçma sikik bir mekanik koyma. Bu liste uzar gider. Bioshock Remastered oyunlarından sonra oynadığım en berbat ve sorunlu oyun. Bioshock'ta sürekli çökmeler yüzünden güzelim oyundan tat alamıyorduk, bunda buglar yüzünden sinir kanseri oluyoruz. Legend ve Anniversary ne şahaneydi. Ne gerek vardı böyle bug dolu sikim gibi mekaniklere? Benim gibi seriye sadıksanız ve oyunları atlamadan oynuyorsanız alın oynayın ama onun dışında almayın , aldırtmayın. Legend'i Anniversary'i oynayın ama bu içine sıçılmış oyuna hiç bulaşmadan direk Tomb Raider 2013'e başlayın.", "appid": "8140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074610758", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1513684800.0} {"text": "狗789中了ps4就开始吹这游戏，搞的我也买了一份玩，QNMD 打开的时候我真没想到我要花这么久才能通关（还是be），所以我要毫无排版地说一大堆，玩的越久我废话越多： 剧情方面随便提一下，想象一下在一个拥有一大堆制服女高中生（丧尸或者吸血鬼），博物馆里飞出来的mp40和第三帝国战车，梦回一战的线列步兵，还有可爱的剑盾女仆装不死人的狗血世界里一本正经（感觉上）的讲个丧尸生存类的故事会有什么剧情呢？这游戏就是这样的剧情（说实话看了这些我反而好奇起来后面会不会出现日本武士和河北元首了）。不过这种游戏更重要的还是可玩性，那么来说可玩性： 这游戏操作类似生化，只能往前走才能跑，不拿枪走路慢爆，拿手枪反而更快也是牛，举枪瞄准红点和弹道很多时候压根不准，得亏不需要爆头，所以我能直接送女仆盾战士一套9mm膝盖爆炸套餐问题不大。下面是我比较不爽的地方： 一是换子弹不能紧急翻滚取消只能和沙笔一样站在那到换完。然后我按斜向移动然后翻滚会变成直接往正前方滚，还不如压根不做侧滚直接给我个朝角色面对的方向前滚算了。 二是有剧情演出角色会自动收枪，你收就收吧你收枪的时候行动速度能不能不要这么慢，我都不知道我多少次一套演出之后进入战斗我没反应过来枪收了走俩步发现自己慢成乌龟然后急忙切枪出来跑了（最终boss还有之前一个被数个女仆+先列步兵包围的场景最明显）。以上是我对这游戏操作方面的怨念。 三是部分无战斗场景跟着npc走，npc大概是放了一个信仰18的奇迹——和平缓步，然后只能一路无话（复读机女仆：主人！早上好！）并且用超级慢的速度跟着npc慢慢走完一条超长的路，不好意思我熬夜准备一口气打通关耐心不太够用。 武器方面，枪我就吐槽一个.45口径的手枪单发威力怎么小于9mm的冲锋枪？然后想问一下剑盾这个武器有啥用？不能完美挡住正面的所有子弹，也没法一边防御一边移动，掏出来当火枪手的定点靶子么？如果剑盾的风格是走几步停下来防一波再走几步慢慢靠近之后攻击，那我属实不太想冒着重打一大段的风险去试验这个战术（而且我感觉八成不行）。 流程上，本来都和前面几关一样简单粗暴（一个地方翻来覆去走找东西拖时间保护二五仔累赘们顺带打几个弱智丧尸和星际玩家）我还能给个好评。 但是后面城堡出现线列步兵之后就开始喂x 我是不知道靠着这不知道飘到哪的红点和慢的一批的动作怎么正面无伤打一排火枪手？ 没办法靠着卡视野bug屈死大部分火枪手了吧（别和我说这是官方指定玩法），最后一个走廊里给我从空气中凭空刷个正面3火枪背面3火枪的豪华阵容，我打死前面3个还没反应过来就被后面3个枪毙，然后一大段都得重玩，游戏体验真的好。 这豪华阵容瞬间打掉了我所有医疗包之后，我到达最终章打boss，身上就1个医疗包（如果我有2个医疗包可能就没难度了但是我没有），那么最终boss一阶段卡柱子ak俩弹夹秒了不说，二阶段让我之前说的那些操作上的恶心之处全部淋漓尽致的体现了出来：换子弹站着被干，看见boss蓝球之后想斜向紧急回避结果变成直线正前方翻滚往蓝球上撞怒吃一整套被干，想卡柱子结果发现boss攻击能穿墙墙只会让我自己想跑的时候被堵着干。翻滚动作被boss一个大火球打飞然后卡出平移bug一直平移直到被boss下一套攻击骑脸干（这个bug我触发了3次，也许这就是命吧）。让我对这游戏的操作超级加倍不爽，虽然掌握了移动方法后打赢了boss，但是我毫无成就感只觉得特别难受。更别提输给boss之后还有一个结局强制进入一大堆对话不能直接重来也不能esc滚回菜单重来气得让我直接强退重开游戏了。 好了，最后千辛万苦打完了boss之后进入了个鬼泣1最终战一样的地方，说了一些没什么卵用的话女主自杀了？特么我玩了这么久还是个bd？有没有搞错？", "appid": "1097310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198064728961", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "29", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1564142400.0} {"text": "Feeling lucky? Then play this game", "appid": "601510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198340107409", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Полная дичь! Оформляю возврат! Скучная, однообразная, вобщем унылое говно, не стоит заявленной суммы.", "appid": "427290", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084938880", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528200000.0} {"text": "rocket league but ♥♥♥♥ version", "appid": "485610", "steamid": "profiles/76561199076037542", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596888000.0} {"text": "Essa porcaria depois de baixada e atualizada não permite que eu crie conta, fica falando que o administrador bloqueou meu acesso, sendo que nunca joguei isso e nem nenhum outro jogo dessa empresa, nem conta nesse treco eu tenho, que droga é essa!? Esse povo tem problema, sério...", "appid": "495910", "steamid": "profiles/76561197987811744", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1559131200.0} {"text": "I hate this game", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198258373035", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595419200.0} {"text": "Is it me or this is about as boring as 2033?", "appid": "287390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198043498102", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600603200.0} {"text": "Хорошая игра, хорошее комьюнит, рекомендую не играть", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198043925131", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1504267200.0} {"text": "Леди и джентельмены, расисты и мафиози, представляю вам свое видение очень спорной Мафии 3. Уже ни для кого не секрет, что с технической стороны игра отвратительна. Графика просто ужасна, то и дело появляются какие-то непонятные баги, связанные с освещением (странное свечение вокруг персонажа), тенями (то они есть, то их нет) и отражениями (наш герой как полтергейст то отражается в зеркалах, то нет). Общая картинка даже на высоких настройках выглядит отвратительно, днем город представляет из себя набор серых домиков и не более, но ночью ситуация становится лучше. Мало того, что игра плоха в графическом плане, так она еще умудряется нещадно лагать как на минимальных настройка, так и на высоких. Очередная жертва порта с консоли. В целом, передать атмосферу шестидесятых разработчикам удалось. Благодаря высокой детализации города, авто, одежды на людях и музыки, которая великолепна (однако это является заслугой музыкантов тех времен, оригинальный же саундтрек невзрачен и не запоминается). Но в то же время, насладиться атмосферой не получается из-за глупого ИИ, плохой графики, отсутствия многих геймплейных фишек (речь о которых пойдет ниже) и многого другого. Приедь на точку - убей всех - уедь на другую точку, сделай так раз 5 в определенном районе и он станет твоим. Вот, чем вы будете заниматься на протяжении примерно двадцати часов. Никакого разнообразия, хоть разработчики и пытались разбавить рутину, угоном катеров и грузовиков для ваших лейтенантов, сбором коллекционных предметов, но положениее они не спасают вообще. Убрали многие возможности, которые присутствовали не только во второй, но и в первой части. Больше вы не сможете заправить бак своего авто, кастомизировать это же авто, переодеть персонажа, получить штраф от полиции, которая очень тупа и обращает на вас внимание только в том случае, если вы кого-нибудь убьете, так что смело можете гонять по встречке и превышать скорость. Вы можете заявить, что это мелочи, но ведь они нехило так влияют на ощущения, полученные от игрового процесса. Есть во всем этом ужасе и плюсы: водить авто (хоть физика повреждений и ужасна) и стрелять очень приятно, особенно на высоком уровне сложности и играя не по стелу. После захвата каждого района вам придется выбрать, кому его отдать. Тут у нас три варианта, о которых я скажу позже. Каждый из лейтенантов предлагает вам свои услуги, котороми вы можете воспользоваться, если отдатите территорию одному из них. Вот тут Мафия не ударила лицом в грязь и показала нам уровень. Хоть сюжет банален донельзя, наблюдать за его поворотами и продвижением невероятно интересно благодаря хорошей режиссуре и мелочам, над которыми разработчики знатно постарались. Очень жаль, что сюжет подается через захват районов, всю суть которых я уже описал. Прием с документальным фильмом понравился, давно такого не видел. Все персонажи детально проработаны и развиваются по ходу прохождения, даже Линкольн Клей. У главного антогониста и его семьи есть нехилая мотивация совершать те посткупки, которые они совершили. Наши консильери так же являются интересными личностями, но их образы, к сожалению, раскрыты не до конца. Кассандра - чернокожая девушка с Гаити, которая, разумеется, возглавляет местную банду гаитян. Томас Берк - ирландец, глава ирландской банды. Вито Скалетта - протагонист второй части, к сожалению, самый неинтересный персонаж из тройки лейтенантов. Прочие персонажи, встречающиеся в игре, тоже отличаются своими харизмой и историей. Особенно Донован, напарник нашего героя. Являясь сатирическим персонажем, он все-равно может высказывать стоящие и серьезные мысли, над которыми вы точно поразмышляете. По моему скромному мнению, Донован является главным украшением игры, а их дуэт с Линкольном даже может посоперничать с дуэтом Джо и Вито. От сюжетного поворота в сцене после титров я просто выпал, это было великолепно, давно такого не видел. Разработчики из Hangar 13 явно старались, но не дотянули, то ли из-за сроков, то ли из-за бюджета. Стоит отметить, что для дебютной игры Мафия 3 неплоха, но не дотягивает до ААА уровня. Сюжет и атмосфера в игре великолепны, жаль, что геймплей сводит их на нет.", "appid": "360430", "steamid": "profiles/76561198056876932", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "192", "votes_funny": "11", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1477051200.0} {"text": "Ну во первых это не игра а нервососалка,конченная игра 0 баланса в игре конченная игра в общем", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198856870458", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542110400.0} {"text": "Играть перестал уже давно, но обзор решил написать только сейчас. в 2015-16 годах игра была очень хорошей, хорошие обновления, хорошие сервера, все было хорошо. Но потом все пошло в худшую сторону... Если новые звуки оружий было чем то прикольным, новое оружие - револьвер тоже, но, когда в игру добавили батл рояль (АКА ВЫПУСТИЛИ ПУБГ И МЫ ТОЖЕ РЕШИЛИ СДЕЛАТЬ ТАКОЙ РЕЖИМ ,ТИПО ЭТО КРУТО И ВСЕ БУДУТ ИГРАТЬ) и ее сделали бесплатной, все пошло наперекосяк. Платная игра, стоившая 449 рублей стала бесплатной, появились читеры и все в том роде. Новый интерфейс, который не зашел многим людям (в том числе и мне). Мм, потом платные скины на людей, даже забыл сказать, что ввели перчатки. ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥а это сделали? А гейбу нужны деньги. Тебе не нравится? А им ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥. Скоро введут платные цвета глаз для персонажей, скины на ботинки, скины на гильзы, платные звуки ходьбы. И как люди могут до сих пор играть в это?", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198175501501", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1471435200.0} {"text": "Del gioco in se vi sarebbe da parlare per ore, tanti buoni spunti e tante tante cose che non vanno. Se da un punto di vista narrativo e artistico questo gioco riesce a rappresentare una magnifica conclusione della saga, purtroppo sotto ogni altro punto di vista si dimostra lacunoso e incompleto. Tutto ciò comunque passa in secondo piano PERCHE' TANTO IL GIOCO E' STATO OTTIMIZZATO CON IL RETTO INTESTINALE. Con una GTX 980 risulta praticamente ingiocabile, per colpa di un framerate che raramente supera i 50 fps e che spesso e volentieri scende intorno ai 15/20 donando a tutta l'esperienza un piacevole \"Effetto Vomito\". Per ora tenetevi i vostri soldi allo stato attuale non ne vale la pena. R.I.P Equilibrio (2011-2016)", "appid": "374320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198089539324", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1463659200.0} {"text": "Alright, I've been playing a fair bit (Level 11) and so far I can say this is not worth $40, it's a fun game in any case though especially with friends but the amount of waiting time to find a 400 MS game is ridiculous, by the looks of it there are no Australian servers so it just matches you with global players. Now this would be fine if it didn't take 10 minutes to find a game. For a $40 game you'd expect quality but it looks like they rushed out to finish this game without putting any hard work in. The facial expressions are absolute rubbish along with interaction with items (DOORS). Notice how in the intro's rather than create a variety of player models to get killed it's always that one guy for any level. Like I said this game is fun but it doesn't have a lot of replayability and it does not have the servers. This review would be different if the game was say $20 but I've had meals at McDonalds more satisfying than this game for $40 Edit: People are pointing out that the server issue has been resolved but even then my other points still stand. Thanks and God bless", "appid": "438740", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993464221", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "209", "votes_funny": "16", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495800000.0} {"text": "I literally just stopped mid game to say that this game is actual hot garbage. The theory is orbit around a black hole as many times as you can while avoiding incoming obstacles. Decent idea with trash implementation. Once you get up around 50ish orbits all of a sudden RNG kicks in and instantly reverses your direction directly into the cloud of objects you just avoided ending the round. Then lets say you actually do well on the reversal ... then they throw in double reversals ... either way you're ♥♥♥♥♥♥ by RNG. Game is good for nothing but farming achievements.", "appid": "615610", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967473096", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523016000.0} {"text": "Ficou péssimo.", "appid": "252950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198111074255", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1605787200.0} {"text": "Loads came crashes :D 69/666", "appid": "311210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198119421902", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446811200.0} {"text": "writing this for a badge", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198096242806", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479902400.0} {"text": "Das Schlechteste race game was ich je gesehen habe", "appid": "310560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198154762971", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495281600.0} {"text": "fix it on win 10", "appid": "413150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198123316139", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561550400.0} {"text": "I remember playing this game and having a great amount of fun. Then I got some other games and stopped playing this game for probably a year. I just downloaded the game again and they have ruined it. It is not as good as it used to be. I recommend if you are a old player and want to start playing this game again, Don't do it! It is not worth the time.", "appid": "209870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198061702323", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1448539200.0} {"text": "Hayatta kalma oyunu seven insanlara tavsiye edeceğim ilk oyunların başında gelir, oyun genel olarak güzel fakat bir süre oynadığınız zaman sizi sıkabiliyor açıkçası bu türün pek hayranı sayılmam. Grafikler güzel, detaylara fazla takılmazsanız oyunu rahatlıkla oynayabilirsiniz. Oyunda değinmek istediğim bir diğer konu ise \"BUG\" olacaktır, oyunda çok fazla sayıda bug ile karşılaşıyorsunuz hatta söyle söyleyeyim karşılaşmama ihtimaliniz yok o derece, bu detaylar dışında oyun akıcı fakat yazımın başında da belirttiğim gibi oyun çok sıkıyor. Oyunu arkadaşlarınızla oynamanızı öneririm eğer tek kişi oynarsanız oyun sizi çok bayacak ve direk bırakacaksınız, incelemeyi bitirirken son bir not daha eklemek istiyorum. Ben bu türün pek hayranı değilim, bu türdeki diğer oyunları da oynadım fakat benlik değil, o yüzden oyunu olumsuz olarak işaretliyorum şayet siz bu türü severseniz tam sizlik oyun diyebilirim.", "appid": "242760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198353790299", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1585224000.0} {"text": "Dead game", "appid": "686600", "steamid": "profiles/76561198055125568", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1549886400.0} {"text": "I rarely don't finish a story-driven single player game. I actually can't even remember when the last time was, because I usually find something to enjoy no matter the amount of drawbacks. That is not the case with Deus Ex: Mankind Divided. This steaming heap of boredom is probably one of the most forgettable experiences I've ever found myself trying to enjoy. That says something, because I've read \"To Kill A Mockingbird\" AND \"Catcher in The Rye\". Deus Ex: Mankind Divided isn't a bad game. The mechanics are rather enjoyable, the views are sometimes amazing, the prologue reminded me a great deal of Spec Ops: The line's main setting in Dubai, and it was very beautiful. There were a lot of throwbacks to earlier DX-games, and everything feels like it should make for a very enjoyable experience. However! This is where I try to explain why I find this game so horrible. First of all: Every person the player meets feels like they've been written by an 8 year old with a bog-standard character creation sheet from a D&D-session. It just feels like every reply is formulated, every line is taken out of some sort of matrix of the most stereotypical replies to pressure, taunting, niceties, etc. It's just boring. Bland. Annoying in the end. I never felt like I was in the story for any other reason than its own progression, and that does not a satisfied player make. At least not this player. The locations were (until my early out-bowing) very well-made, although they did feel slightly down-scaled. I found myself constantly trying to sneak around like I always do, but it didn't feel as rewarding as it did in Human Revolution. Again, I just couldn't shake the feeling of me only being around for the story to progress. I didn't sit around thinking \"♥♥♥♥ yeah, I'm gonna save the world here\", there was no feeling of imminence or importance. Just a feeling of \"meh\". To sum it all up. I didn't enjoy the game. I didn't wake up Saturday morning thinking only about playing on and seeing where the story took me. I just felt like replaying a good game instead. Sad. TL;DR: Don't buy this game if you expect good writing.", "appid": "337000", "steamid": "profiles/76561198014713184", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518350400.0} {"text": "Such a lack of content...", "appid": "868380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198847762623", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589716800.0} {"text": "Repleto de gente toxica...", "appid": "550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198310568367", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525348800.0} {"text": "Каждую игру достаются орки...", "appid": "1416260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084128932", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1604491200.0} {"text": "По трейлеру игра создает впечатление чего-то непонятного, но очень веселого и задорного. И первое время игрового процесса намеки на это есть: можно гонять на тачках, давя между делом инопланетян и ломая стены, кидаться во врагов взрывными бочками, придумывать как спасти людей из инопланетного плена, активируя кнопки и преодолевая ловушки. Но спустя некоторое время ты понимаешь, что нового игра тебе не может предложить. Количество врагов увеличивается, но не появляется новых средств их уничтожения или взаимодействия с окружением. На каждом уровне придется нажимать кнопки и ломать стены, а для уничтожения врагов швыряться в них бочками, причем на картах есть автоматы выдающие эти бочки бесконечно и к ним придется бегать не раз и не два, что очень \"увлекательно\". Вобщем дропнул игру на 2/3 примерно, процесс скатился в рутину.", "appid": "712180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198058255013", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579867200.0} {"text": "This is the worst game i've ever played. It looks like ♥♥♥♥, and the game just doesn't even work very well.", "appid": "273110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198116681910", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1413028800.0} {"text": "Es macht Spaß für ein paar Stunden doch bittet auf dauer keine Langzeit Motivation und ist sehr unfair. Positiv: -Es gibt viele Waffen -Man kann Autos tunnen -Große Welt - Man kann seine eigenen Klamotten designen Negativ: -Zu viele Hacker -Unfaires Ballance in der Spielwelt -Ohne Premium schafft man so gut wie gar nichts - Das Spiel benötigt viel zu starke Hardware um überhaupt flüssig zu laufen. Fazit: Es bittet für ein paar Stunden eine nette Unterhaltung besonders wenn man es mit freunden spielt doch die Hacker die unfaire Ballance und die benötigte Hardware rauben einem doch sehr denn Spielspaß.", "appid": "113400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198135849745", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1464523200.0} {"text": "1 haftaya sıkılırsınız", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198274698450", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586174400.0} {"text": "♥♥♥♥ game! i unlock cards and uninstall this ♥♥♥♥", "appid": "4920", "steamid": "profiles/76561197967886318", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1386244800.0} {"text": "Not so fun", "appid": "703080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198097101173", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576152000.0} {"text": "Нет. Спасибо alienware arena за бесплатный ключ.", "appid": "375230", "steamid": "profiles/76561198273342892", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1489492800.0} {"text": "Immortal Realms: Vampire Wars, the RANT review: Having played the beta for over 20 hours (i had to push myself tbh) it already was clear that this game would fall short. The concept is nice tho, i won't deny it, but the execution is very poorly done to say the least! (they basically left the beta running for over 6 months while changing little to nothing, how or why one does that goes beyond my comprehension?) This game tries so hard but delivers little, making it look, act and feel underqualified & unpolished in pretty much all aspects. (confirmed: missing card mechanics, disappearing units, corrupted save/load files, etc..) It has choppy/glitchy motion & user interfaces, little to no real strategic values, bland and boring maps, not to mention the severe lack of diversity for 'terrain & cover systems' and whatnot (which does practically nothing for archer/ranged types). Unit types that are not offering much, except some basic stats like buffs & boons even on highest tier and leveling them up should also have been made more transparent. Terrible story, bad acting, uninspiring voices (grunting and moaning basically) low quality FMV, mindless plot,.. Boring!! (Ooh, i would almost forget to mention about the awkward camera movement or functionality.. It's as if you're always mistaking left from right by the simplest of actions!) The battle maps pretty much all look the same really, they're way too small, feel overly cramped, are full of stupid choke points to get bogged into, and offer practically zero contribution to the trategic value of the game (in other words, potential wasted).. It's also worth mentioning that whenever an enemy lord plays a card, you need to focus in quickly or miss it, leaving you wondering what he/she actually played?! The soundtrack (strong point) and overall visuals aren't bad, i'll give them that. But as the game stands now, there's plenty of patching and polishing up to do in order to make things look, feel and behave like it should because my impression is that at some time during the development they ran out of steam (or didn't even care to read our comments) and decided to just leave it at that. This concludes my rant for now but no doubt i'll be back after delving longer into this abyss of boredom and bugginess.. Personal verdict: 6'5/10 (generously overrated) Not recommended for the current asking price!! Ps: Launch day was horrible (missing dlcs etc)!!", "appid": "1024480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198029242857", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598788800.0} {"text": "пока зайдешь в игру умрешь от старости у меня gtx 1050 ti и проц I5 8300 2.3 грц 8 оперативы . захожу в игру 15 мин на сервер 30 мин . Крутая игра", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198813045982", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1563796800.0} {"text": "+ Ze začátku docela zábavná hra, memes pobaví + Sběratelské kartičky, 15 achievementů - Velmi laciný \"příběh\", jeho 30 levlů jsem dohrál za 2 hodiny - Celý proces se začně opakovat a je to dost nuda - Achivement s 5000 bramborami jsem dělal 4/6 nahraných hodin a jsem rád, že můžu hru po tom nudném a vyčerpávajícím výkonu oddinstalovat Na desítky minut zabaví, ale víc nic. 4/10", "appid": "554310", "steamid": "profiles/76561198134125222", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1522670400.0} {"text": "Things that happened since 2013: - My mother's uncle died from Chronic Obtructive Pulmonary Disease. - My cousin's wife gave birth to NOT ONE BUT BUT TWO CHILDREN NOPE NOT AT A SINGLE BIRTH! - My other cousin got over her cocaine addiction. - Leonardo Da Vinci won the oscars. *cough* Caprio. - I graduated from highschool and I'm two years into university. - A military coup happened in my country, as well 5 different elections. Meh that's my country's unstability but whatever. - My brother got through 2 relationships. - Trump became the president of United States. - Brexit. - I spent 1200 hours playing this game with unbearable bugs and glitches. - Learned how to play the piano. - Malaysian aircraft accident. - We get to see J. Lawrance's nudes. - Bieber got arrested. - Ebola epidemic ended. - Same sex marriage became a thing in the USA. - Paris climate agreement. - New Star Wars film. - Autonomous cars became mainstream. - Giant pandas are no longer endangered. - Netflix added offline downloads BUT THIS GAME IS STILL NOT ON BETA. WHAT THE HELL. edit: Wow, so much hate coming in, the comment section is full with people telling me that I don't know how game development works. At Slumdog Millionaire movie, there's this scene where a rich guy gives a bottle of coke to some poor Indian kids living in poverty. These kids are so happy because they've never drunk coke before. You can make poor people happy with small things, because by default they are poor so their needs are obviously much less than a regular person. The regular DayZ player plays DayZ in poverty as well, a poverty of updates. This is how Bohemia keeps their players \"happy\", they give us small updates. Updates which take 6 months to finish and don't bring much new things to the game.. I was also one of these people. Bohemia sold 2.5million or maybe even more copies for this game. That's more than $60 million. They promised us Beta on 2015 Q4, we didn't get it. They said they wanted to change the game engine, it took their full year. They said the game will be on Play Station, but that's nowhere to be heard. They said they'll add basebuilding 2 years ago, it's not here. They said they'll add injury system, blood on hands when you skin an animal/human. Pooping, marijuana smoking, making the altar radio station fully fledged. Helicopters, bikes, motorbikes, car functioning and maintenance, full damage system for vehicles, stamina and endurance, realistic animal AI. They added wolves, but they can do 180 degree spins while you're running from them. They said they'll make all building floors enterable, they said they'll put vegetation all around the walls of the buildings. They said they will make the Tisy military base contaminated. They said they'll improve zombie AI. They said they'll add zombie hoardes, where are they? Where's the character soft skills? Where's the planes? Character lifespan? Visible scars? They promised us the player controller and new animation system to come around the summer of 2016 or the end 2017, but they still didn't implement it yet. Improved crafting system that allowed us to live off our lives in the wild WITHOUT visiting the cities etc. If I want to pitch a tent, I still need to run around the forest to find a place that both my character can fit in and put a tent. They promised a new tent placement system (link here: ) they said they'll add it in 3 months. They didn't. Here in the Trello you can see what they have in \"progress\" with the exact dates they've been added and have an overall idea what I'm talking about: The list goes on. You can see their old status reports here: please scroll all the way down to 2015 era and see what they promised to us. I'm an experienced DayZ player, I both played SA and topped lots of hours of play on the mod. Sure, this is a fun game. But I don't recommend it to any friend that asks me. If you're not patient as much as I am, this game is not for you. I still play this time to time, but let's be honest. An open alpha game, that made a revenue of 60million, a huge company like Bohemia, can't complete the alpha stage prior to its release, IN 3.5 YEARS? There's something wrong there. Maybe it was Dean Hall, maybe it's with the dev team. But you can clearly say something is wrong there. People are telling me that Beta is soon, you should take a look at the status reports that said beta was soon, around 189318 million times before. I remember them saying on twitter that they don't want to rush beta, so it will be on version 0.81 (current version is 0.62 and they said 0.63 will be beta) We've never been this close to beta before.They said it will be soon, by soon they probably mean 2036 or something. Considering we are not hit by an astreoid by then. lol. If they hit \"beta\" with the current speed they are developing, it is possible that they'll either release an incomplete game and continue developing after the full release, which is probably okay for most people. Or the game will take another 3 years to complete. edit 2: ohh btw, I just remembered. There's another excuse they say, \"alpha is for adding features you dumb ♥♥♥♥\" Very good point. Where are the features that they were supposed to add on Alpha? Will they add them all on Beta? Alpha means adding features, Beta is where these features are improved and the bugs are fixed. If they don't add the features they promised on Alpha then they'll continue adding these core features in the Beta phase which means then we'll be likely to see an Alpha-like Beta. Where they continue adding the features they promised years ago. Finally, I hope I'm wrong with all this and the DayZ dev team steps up their game. If they do, I'll surely delete this review.", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198010837586", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "979", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1496318400.0} {"text": "Not worth the money. Buy PUBG instead", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198234519816", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1511438400.0} {"text": "Sadly the PC community is dead in this game. If you really want to enjoy this game go to PS4/Xbox. P2P which means MasterMinds (MM) abusing Lag Switch. Many MANY cheaters, as if infinite grenades, molotovs, energy to spam creatures. The balance is not that great and Matchmaking doesn't make it better. For example a lvl 2 Annete (first MasterMind) against full premade of 4 people that are 50+ lvls. There are 200-400 people playing daily a couple are newbies and most are abusing any explots. (Even RE 5 Mercenaries has more people playing) The devs won't add any anticheat or servers so this game will eventually die in the PC community. Was fun until it lasted. Maybe there will be a new peak when something new appear, it happened when Nic was added, but that peak lasted for a few hours.", "appid": "952070", "steamid": "profiles/76561197972766048", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594382400.0} {"text": "это игра не для меня", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080915448", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1458475200.0} {"text": "MMORPG with guns that means your gun is weak and fast reflexes are useless in this game", "appid": "1085660", "steamid": "profiles/76561198058230907", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1570708800.0} {"text": "Г0BHO", "appid": "1046930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198201187469", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1561896000.0} {"text": "-The scariest thing about this game is the graphics. This game may look good if you watch the trailer but be warned it is nothing like that. You may only play 3 PvE matches a day unless you pay although after playing 3 you will be glad you don´t have to play another; the graphics look like they are from 2007 and the voice acting is awful. You will be forced on to the repetitive team deathmatch games within 20 mins of gameplay. Another problem with this game is that it falls within the pay to win side of free games; most of the wepons are locked to premium money only. You will constantly find yourself getting your ass kicked by the people who have payed for better gear. Despite all the bad things about this game you can still get some fun out of mele matches which fall under the so bad its good catagory for me and the mutation matches which are satisfying as long as you are one of the mutants. As much as I hate this game at least it is free and for a free game it does have good production value; most of the free games I have played do not have a story line and as rubbishy as this ones is at least it tries. I would not recomend this game although I do respect the people who made it for at least trying to give it some sort of story instead of just having the generic multipayer fps. I would rate it at 4.5/10.", "appid": "223650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079407131", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "60", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1418644800.0} {"text": "nosense", "appid": "204340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198277785200", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498219200.0} {"text": "Pior killer já lançado, não vale 1 real.", "appid": "971790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198083542059", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": "16", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544788800.0} {"text": "ga zeeb", "appid": "335330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198130722771", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498737600.0} {"text": "PUBG 2020 experience: cheater after killing me said to me in voice chat \"♥♥♥♥ you\"", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198145644913", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596715200.0} {"text": "R.i.P.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561197987672934", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544356800.0} {"text": "Rimworld's just better. The community around this game also seems... toxic, for lack of a better word. I made a single post on the community forums and seemed to be met with hostile responses. Not a good sign. It just seems to be a rip-off of rimworld, with worse graphics and even more lacking gameplay.", "appid": "457140", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087883181", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1552132800.0} {"text": "You know I was quite enjoying the game, despite the annoying \"open world\" wich itself was a puzzle to get to the next mission, poor voice acting and some other things. I do not recommend this game because I was about to finish the game but at one point I ♥♥♥♥♥♥ up and I died, so I loaded at the latest checkpoint but then the mysterious bug appeared so I couldn't move at all and controls didn't work. I wasn't feeling like playing through the whole chapter again so I just quit. If you want you can still get it since it is very cheap and you will probably not come across this bug yourself. So I'm justl little salty that ♥♥♥♥ happened to me. The Idea of thief is really cool and unique.", "appid": "239160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198340138163", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546430400.0} {"text": "This is a tough game for me to recommmend, would love it there was a 'Neutral' button on Steam. It's beautiful and the music is amazing, but the game feels shallow. The ending is nice, but it comes after slowly walking for 90+ minutes. The last chapter feels most enjoyable, I'm not sure who would want to play through the first two though to get to that point honestly. Suggestions for improvement - Keep the user engaged more consistently through the narrartion. More talking, even if it's minor thoughts. - Interactions. Something to feel like you're actually engaged in the world - Make it more linear, if the point is pushing the story forward and the are no 'Easter Eggs' or 'rewards' for exploring make it so someone can't 'Get Lost' - Subtitles - Could be more interesting, could be used as typograhic art that scrolls or changes in size and font to fit the mood. They felt drab and did little for immersion, so I turned them off - Abilty to walk faster...jog even. Less of an issue if it was more linear, but going 'The wrong Way' then back tracking is tiresome here - Camera: Make more dynamic, small bobbing as the character walks", "appid": "203810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035396704", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1416744000.0} {"text": "This game have potential and great community, but the lag and fps problems are so annoying. a lot of bugs too and the world feels repeated same creatures on every island and no interesting stuff to explore after. Overall needs more work and more quality of life updates and weekly updates.", "appid": "834910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198075848428", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1572955200.0} {"text": "Disgusting how they split the game in half. It's a clear cash grab and exploition of their customer base.", "appid": "295110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074785120", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "17", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1456056000.0} {"text": "--- --- +Good progress system +Peaceful ambiance +Beautiful scenery --- --- +Buggy +Unpolished +Bad tutorial --- --- Dark forester brings you into your own peaceful forest to build and defend against waves of baddies in a sort of tower defense/rogue-like/rpg mix of engaging gameplay, leaving the player to build, protect and farm their way to greatness. --- --- : Simple, most comparable to ARPG's. Right click to move, 1-5 to use magic, tab to attack. You can edit the inputs if needed. Very basic. : The mechanics are the most interesting part of this game. There is an open forest and the player can build wherever they would like, except on the very border of the map. While progressing, more buildings unlock and there are more units to place but it's limited by your level as well. In between waves of the PvE element of the game the player can choose to attack other players for resources which is almost a must because the waves of PvE monsters become increasingly difficult. That's basically it. Build, then defend or attack and keep building. : The game makes itself seem much more difficult than it is by including an overly lengthy tutorial in one huge mouthful rather than splitting it into spots when necessary. After you get a hang of what's going on, the game is very simple to the point of boring before increasing in difficulty again as waves increase. : Progression is just like your basic RPG game. You gain xp and resources, level up with xp and build with resources. It seems fairly balanced as long as you're attacking other players as well as defending your base. However, if the character dies or the main house is destroyed, progression is brought back a few levels or in some cases all the way back to the level 1, giving the game a very tense, rogue-like feel to it. --- --- : The environment is nice and is set in an autumn forest leaving the player in a lush world of orange and brown that really feels quite peaceful. : The player and monster models feel quite aged and plain, nothing to really talk about here and about what one expects from an indie game like this, if not just a tiny bit better than one would expect. : There's not much for animations while fighting but I found that the death animation was pretty cool, although they felt out of place, with explosions and lightning effects. : The user interface is pretty bad. Filled with unnecessary clutter.When you click on your monster it brings up a huge window that's mostly empty, the building ui doesn't disappear during the combat phase leaving a large black bar down the side of the screen. --- --- : Bugs are abundant in this game everywhere. From buildings randomly disappearing, to poor save states leading to game restarts, game crashes, hefty and unstable loading times and many more. The game is barely playable in its current state and only so if you're willing to run the risk of a complete restart on your progress. : The game runs well on max graphics for me, I don't experience any lag or stutter and it runs smooth. As mentioned under bugs however, the loading times can be long and even a couple of times the game just refused to load for me and resulted in a corrupt save state. --- --- : If the bugs were taken care of and the was less of a risk of a corrupt save, this game would have a great amount of replay value. It seems to stretch on quite far, but starts to feel like a grind fairly quickly, having to keep your resources up from attacking other players, many of whom are at base level with no defense. : I, personally, would not be happy with purchasing this game for 15$ in its current state. I see many people get it on sale or from when it was on early access for less than a dollar and I feel that's a fantastic value for what you're getting. However, even if the game was in a pristine state, polished and bug free, I don't feel like 15$ is a good value without the addition of much more content. I'd value the game in it's current state at under 5$. --- --- Overall, the game seems to be very interesting with loads of replay value and is a great concept, however all of that is overlooked by the bugs, horrible tutorial, and a poorly designed user UI. I understand the dev is still hard at work making improvements so definitely keep an eye out for improvements to the game in the future, if nothing else, I can surely say that this game is worth following and keeping on your indie radar. --- --- \t\tCPU \t\t\tIntel Core i5 @ 3.60GHz \t\t\tCoffee Lake 14nm Technology \t\tRAM \t\t\t16.0GB Dual-Channel Unknown @ 1066MHz (15-15-15-36) \t\tMotherboard \t\t\tMicro-Star International Co. Ltd. Z370-A PRO (MS-7B48) (U3E1)\t \t\tGraphics \t\t\tASUS VG236 (1920x1080@60Hz) \t\t\t4095MB NVIDIA GeForce GTX 970 (EVGA) \t\tStorage \t\t\t1397GB Western Digital WDC WD15EARS-00MVWB0 (SATA ) \t\t\t298GB Western Digital WDC WD3200AAKS-75L9A0 (SATA ) \t\tOptical Drives \t\t\tDiscSoft Virtual SCSI CdRom Device \t\t\tHL-DT-ST DVDRAM GH24NS50 \t\tAudio \t\t\tRealtek High Definition Audio I recieved the game for free for review purposes", "appid": "349450", "steamid": "profiles/76561198000526549", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1537531200.0} {"text": "negativando só pelo meme msm, espero que o exodus flop...", "appid": "287390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198035700047", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1548849600.0} {"text": "oyun iyi ama girmiyor bu hata yüzünden hayır verdim çok saçma ama güzel oyun girmiyor hatası çok", "appid": "12210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198274693649", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1480420800.0} {"text": "一直丟給我已使用過的金鑰匙！！！ 根本無法玩多人線上遊戲！！", "appid": "24960", "steamid": "profiles/76561198259042999", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1536753600.0} {"text": "Реально говно игра", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198916260211", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574337600.0} {"text": "Ponen una actualizacion y la cagan mas de lo que estaba.. Ricos fps.", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120821619", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "37", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545566400.0} {"text": "I like & have many reigions from Toposim... But this add-on contains big error. Maybe it works in the native version of FSX, but It's not compatible with ORBX (I have global, vector & openLC). After installing add-on I can't start flight: I have error message \"You computer has run out available memory...\" when a flight starts to be generated. I was 