й кроме всяких там голов, пушек, золотого сундука и сломанной мини-карты с чатом, но я бы лучше играл в оригинал, чем в такую недоработанную фигню.", "appid": "729040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198199806223", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1555156800.0} {"text": "GameGuru製でFPSじゃないって点だけは評価できるかもしれない", "appid": "809780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198122976068", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1558958400.0} {"text": "Я люблю этот жанр, да и сама графика старых времен мне импонирует. Но в раннем доступе, это как сидеть на мокром кресле - пока высохнет, уже прогниет внутри. Почитал негативные отзывы, я приготовился вкусить все \"радости\" этого проекта, принимая факт того, что я подписался на нечто почти живое. Оказалось, это почти живое умерло и воняло еще до того, как я начал играть. При входе в игру меня стильно приветствовала заставка с названием, а внизу была надпись . Я обкликался на клавиатуре и мышке, после чего обкликался на геймпаде. Это вообще прожимается? Молитвы были услышаны, игра запустилась . Запустилась она, благо, не на польском, да еще и с маленьким разрешением экрана. А выглядят настройки так, будто ты играешь в \"почувствуй себя тупым\". Окей надеюсь, что настройки - это то, к чему мне больше не нужно будет возвращаться. Запустилось. Персонажи начали говорить ужасно раздражающим . Интереса ради, я отключил возможность этого бурчания. Вуа-ля, в скудных настройках есть возможность замены этого бреда на английский язык! Бедный тот бедолага, который не нашел эту опцию и у него произошел отвал ушей. Помянем. Продолжим... Управление с геймпада? Забудьте. Оно есть, но, лучше не стоит. Перешел на клавиатуру и какого черта?! Почему это так плохо работает? Никакого тебе курсора, подходи к предметам и жми . Будьте готовы к тому, что персонаж будет ходить туда-сюда и не слушаться вас. И знаете, тестировщики, получив этот проект, просто сказали - . Начал я играть за прикованного цепью робота Беллу. Приковал меня некто Роберт, зеленый крокодил. Он дал мне сомнительное поручение - приготовить коктейль из 4х ингредиентов. На выбор у меня были половинка человеческого мозга, отпиленная нога, ананас консервированный, щепотка черного перца , оливковое масло, сыр и помидор. Есть ли у меня рецепт коктейля? Нет. Даст ли мне рецепт этот зеленый выбл*док? Нет. Я потратил на это 40 минут, приготовил ли я его? Нет. Инвентарь жмется на , далее нужно листать на и при выборе жать на . Я не понимаю, зачем было делать такой ужас? Подобные вещи я расцениваю, как неуважение к тем, кто будет играть в это. К этому управлению невозможно привыкнуть, оно дaунcкое и ничто его не спасет. Я бы дал этому проекту второй шанс, но абсолютная чушь в первом задании и топорное управление напрочь отбило во мне желание пытаться в это играть. Может быть на стадии релиза. Может, может. Нет.", "appid": "579120", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993039039", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1593259200.0} {"text": "nope, just nope! the bad quality is maybe good for a few laughs, but then you should refund it. i´ve seen pretty much everything in an hour of playtime. i got it gifted for my bad games streams and it fulfilled my expectations. ;)", "appid": "401190", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970700143", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "8", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1534248000.0} {"text": "キャリアモードの難易度調整に疑問あり。 序盤なのに車の設定を煮詰めてリトライしても勝てないレースがたびたびあったり、逆に終盤でも大差で勝ってしまうレースがたびたびあったり、ライバル車AIの強さ調整ができてないように思います。 ライバル車AIの強さは数値調整できるので、ちょうどいい難易度にできるけれど、おかしい難易度のレースがたびたびあるので、その都度調整するのは面倒です。 単独のレースを設定して遊んだり、ネット対戦がメインなのかもしれません。 ちなみに同じようなジャンルのGTやForzaは普通に楽しめていました。", "appid": "378860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198005715013", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Downloaded the free trial and played with 3 friends, game is unfulfilling and trying to create a lobby so the three of us to connect cannot be done unless we find the same lobby in the custom games page. No hand holding in this game..atleast from my experience.", "appid": "859570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198400116593", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588420800.0} {"text": "Я даже забыл что могу оставить обзор на недоигру (буду называть ее так), от недоразработчиков, так как играл на бесплатных выходных. Сама недоигра мне понравилась, наверное из-за первого впечатления, потому что я в нее играю первый раз, раньше ей не интересовался из-за слабого железа (точнее из-за завышенных требований), у меня пошла на средне-очень высоких. Ладно, я сюда пришел не о геймплее говорить, а о том какие недоразработчики жадные (yблюдки), что даже на зимнюю распродажу не поставили скидку, это просто апогей.", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198027927170", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1545307200.0} {"text": "- flat dumb patriotic story - very short gameplay (if you dont try to collect all, but it is so boring) - stealth ... nah ... most of the time is just run and shot ... witch just make all to look more and more and more boring previous parts of the game was much better and fumy to be play", "appid": "612880", "steamid": "profiles/76561197983849145", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562673600.0} {"text": "So, this game yeah. It's not that great. The best way I can describe it to you is, it's alright. The games takes a lot of time to play by yourself, so you've got to make friends. Can't do that? Probably shouldn't play unless you've got more spare time than an asian networker. The, even still, the gameplay is a bit wonky at best. Tunnels can't be filled in, the terrain is pretty hard to traverse, and materials can't be discerned until they are already in your inventory or if you know the texture. The amount of time it takes to learn how to play this game alone is pretty harsh, which is to be expected since you're literally building a kingdom right? But even then the game provides almost nooooo help at all. You have to look up where you MIGHT find materials, and this isn't even considering that you can get killed by players at any time. At the moment, I have the game and love, all it's flaws and all. But, I wouldn't recommend getting it yet, till it's at least out of early access.", "appid": "290080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081258853", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1457352000.0} {"text": "Bir sürü bug var. Klavye ve fare tuşlarını değiştirmek çok sorunlu. Hikaye çok basit yani alt metni yok. Türklere kısaca şöyle diyebiliriz vuruş hissi yok ^^. Bu oyunu oynamak zaman kaybı. Bu oyunu es geçin direk \"Resident Evil Revelations 2\" oynayın.", "appid": "222480", "steamid": "profiles/76561198397429538", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1601467200.0} {"text": "love the efx lost head and legs. the game is not for alle and it's ♥♥♥♥ sry to say", "appid": "629760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198167073446", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "cam greu jocul, nu se compara cu lol la controale si astea, aici iti trb skilluri reale :)", "appid": "570", "steamid": "profiles/76561198424230517", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593432000.0} {"text": "Better than World of Tanks, but with a confusingly similar name. High tier battles are utterly ♥♥♥♥♥♥ for balance. Nice WW2-era gameplay, though. My recommendation is to stay away, unless you're a serious AFV fan.", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072670107", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "I would not recomend this game to anyone. My first reason being that the controls are absolutly terrible. My second problem with this game being the skill gap jump from the first 2-3 levels to the 3-END levels, It seems like it holds your hand till the end of the \"Prolouge\" and then drops you off into a levels that you may or may not be able to pass. Overall my experience was very bad, and I did not enjoy the game one bit.", "appid": "96100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198044735960", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1462190400.0} {"text": "Not worth 10$", "appid": "391540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198255449088", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1475841600.0} {"text": "it sucks i wasted money on this ♥♥♥♥ at first i wanted it really bad but when i bought it i got ♥♥♥♥♥♥ in the ass sucks full of spammers and laggy hosts B.story is really really short C.dlcs sucks [looks cool but not that worthy at all] D.i bandai namco sucks because they dont care about people who play their games they care about the money E.a waste of money [belive me]", "appid": "349040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198142083575", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1524139200.0} {"text": "Haven't played since the Ghosts disappointment. Figured I would try it since it is free and in beta... was disappointed again. Poorly optimized, very few weapons to choose from, hit detection is terrible, sounds are awful, Michael Bay copy and paste, at point blank the shotgun is useless. There's more issue but I'm not in the mood. Waste of time. Should've ended the series after Black Ops 2 or Modern Warfare 3.", "appid": "696790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198048056245", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506600000.0} {"text": "フリープレイ時のレビュー。 初心者なのに遥かに格上の相手や味方に囲まれるというこの世の終わりようなランクシステムが導入されています サバイバーの場合はあっという間にキラーに殺されてしまうでしょう キラーの場合はさらに深刻で挑発や煽りと受け取れる行為が頻繁に見受けられます 高速屈伸、目くらまし用のライトを高速で点灯させる、出口で集まりコンビニ前の不良のようにたむろするなど。 さらに統率された動きからおそらくボイスチャットを使用しているパーティーも多いです（非推奨なだけで禁止ではありませんがアドバンテージは非常に高いです） 上記の理由からフラストレーションとは無縁の人じゃないとこのゲームは楽しめないと思います。", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198104007195", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1568894400.0} {"text": "👎", "appid": "241560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198278568605", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490097600.0} {"text": "Mt bom o jogo, jogabilidade diferente porem acostumavel, trilha sonora boa, historia envolvente. O unico problema é a incopatibilidade do jogo com o windows 8, ou seja, o jogo depois de um tempo de gameplay começa apresentar uma serie de problemas de compatibilidade, como por exemplo fechar sozinho. Recomendo para quem tem windows 7 ou XP, mas para quem tem Windows 8 para cima acho que não compensa devido o trabalho que da para resolver esses problemas...", "appid": "8850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198191569481", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1450872000.0} {"text": "Game randomly drops to 10 FPS in the middle of the game and stays there went in their discord to see if anyone knew a fix and they told me to shut up.", "appid": "1103950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198376194419", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1598097600.0} {"text": "Garbo lmao", "appid": "843380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068953887", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1598184000.0} {"text": "Hra na hovno!", "appid": "19800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198187764574", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485086400.0} {"text": "Игра остой на 50 лвл уже все с донатом ходят и тупо невозможно убить!!", "appid": "921060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198354933485", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1560340800.0} {"text": "I want that 20 minutes back!", "appid": "313040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198082881386", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603368000.0} {"text": "- Şuanlık ♥♥♥ sade bir tasarım benim hoşuma gitmedi menü özellikle çok kotü her girişte kullanıcı adı veya şifre girmemiz gerekiyor oto giriş yok. - Botlara karşı veya eğitim modu bulunmadığından oyunu anlamak zorlaşıyor - Oyun yeni çıktığından tabi buglarda var şuanlık fakat geçiceğini düşünüyorum şuanlık oynamaya gerek olmadığını düşünüyorum oyun hakkında bilgililendirici videolar çıktıktan sonra oynanabilir. - tahtadaki vuruş animasyonları hoş buldum fakat diğer menü tasarımı tahta , sıra sende vb detaylar beni etkilemedi umarım değiştirirler ve bu güzel oyunu bizim için daha iyi bire hale getirirler .", "appid": "1114860", "steamid": "profiles/76561198232350696", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1566302400.0} {"text": "Another Pay to win system. it was fun some time ago, but if you want to be under the best, do it like the rest, pay with real money. Level your hero, have a pat, join a team, and buy the ingame currency donuts with real money. If you want tor train your charater faster or do missions faster pay. Increase your team stats collecting coins gathering xp gaining attribute boosts just PAY.", "appid": "482920", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087810639", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1482580800.0} {"text": "The content of the game itself is alright. Although, it is so much unoptimized that I don't wanna finish it. It just run likes sh*t.", "appid": "447040", "steamid": "profiles/76561198126652558", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "22", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554811200.0} {"text": "Dont do that trade restricitons. CS:GO has same situation with H1Z1 so ppl still trade/sell their items. Valve did this to prevent scams, gambling, etc. but Valve gave a chance to scammers because ppl dont want to wait for a week to sell their items and they will start to trade with real money transactions. Also they said that for preventing gambling but that will never fix gambling problem because these sites will do balance system so you will play with balance. The good thing is they dropped their email to get feedback. We need to wait until a new announcement.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086775089", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1539777600.0} {"text": "oschgraddla schbui...sauaffn", "appid": "755790", "steamid": "profiles/76561197997471779", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1555329600.0} {"text": "This game is no good anymore. I used to see a lot of popular YouTubers playing this game, and so when it went on sale for half off I jumped on it. There are only around 600 people online at a time, so it might take a little over 2 minutes to find a game. The servers are so very laggy. One moment I'll be jumping down the stairs, the next I'll be being carried by the dad. Even with all this I still played with my friends, and it was fun for the first 20 minutes and then it really started to get repetitive. I do not recommend this game, and I am refunding it.", "appid": "427730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198322601842", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1484654400.0} {"text": "dont buy this game and save ur money: - 60-70 pers of the broken quests and unmarket on the map - some stars of the level up or wath ever call its buged and u cant rankup ur abiltys - make u do much fights against enemy ..monsters..or dragons with low abilty and sucks weapons at the bigging of the game (iam alweys using the glitcsh of the map to win the fight like go up on big rock and shot 100 arrow with bow) - and the much stuiped think is the dragon can be killed by frozen troll or 7 of 1m pigges tall or giant...he should be stronger then every createur in the game expecte the player or some other caracters - DO NOT BUY IT.. i have 84h recored in the game..belive me its 84h of boring and fixing bugs and much rage :D", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198395258738", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597838400.0} {"text": "Баланс просто бомба,умирать каждый раз от танка,когда ты с пукалкой бегаешь.", "appid": "227940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198275029949", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1544616000.0} {"text": "This is quite honestly one of the laggiest and glitchiest games I have ever played. My PC is perfectly fine. I have a gtx 980, so my computer isn't the problem. Playing this game is extremely painful. You teleport around, objects get stuck in the walls, and simple tasks like cleaning your mop take immense concentration to not cause the bucket to teleport you across the room and kill you. I've died countless times just by walking into wet floor signs and random clipboards and bullet casings strewn across the floor. I mostly bought this game for its multiplayer, and trust me, I could write for days about how awful that experience was. The underlying gameplay for Viscera Cleanup Deatail isn't nesesarily boring, just almost impossible due to the buggy and uncontrollable physics.", "appid": "246900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053549889", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1546084800.0} {"text": "No asian server in this game? I think this game already have good engine but the server is dead now and bad for asian player, so if you r asian, just dont buy this game.", "appid": "219640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198396183576", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1538654400.0} {"text": "This is a hard one to grade. Fall of Light has an awesome OST and great visuals, but misses the mark as a Souls-lite. Whereas in Dark Souls you're primarily fighting enemies repeatedly until you learn the best way to take them down, in Fall of Light you're fighting iffy hit detection and controls that sometimes don't respond. At just over four hours in, I'm on my 33rd overall \"rebirth\" and essentially trapped just past the first boss. Thanks to weird save spot / respawn location choices you must replay a decent chunk to escape the current area complete with a half dozen enemies. The real interesting bit is where said enemies continually zerg rush me once I free the little girl, yet when I was coming into this area initially they only attacked in pairs once I came into their line of sight. I've now been at it for more than 90 minutes in this spot and am seriously considering throwing in the towel, seeing a completed hit yet it not registering on an enemy multiple times before each death of my character is super disheartening. Worth a peek if you end up with it from a bundle, Fall of Light: Darkest Edition overstays its welcome with technical issues and an iffy save system. Not recommended.", "appid": "633950", "steamid": "profiles/76561198002069169", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602072000.0} {"text": "Não abre mais, simplesmente do nada para de abrir", "appid": "12110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198166071435", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533729600.0} {"text": "Disgraceful. Just started the game and the intro was so buggy the carts were jumping about until I eventually got projected into the air and started spinning at 100 miles per hour. In VR that kind of thing can cause extreme sickness to people. How does this stuff pass through quality control?? I would understand if this was a free community-made VR port, but not a £40 release by the developer!!! EDIT: And Steam has rejected my refund because it was outside of the 2-week period, despite the fact the game dOESnT WoRK Fuming", "appid": "611670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198122369466", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1597060800.0} {"text": "While I do think that the compaign mode could use a bit of work if they made another killingfloor VR title, the main beef I have with this game is the GOD AWFUL CONTROL! Okay so this game supports locomotion which is a good thing as I think teleporting is for VR ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ and granies who cant last a minute without throwing up, however the locomotion in this game somehow makes the game EVEN WORSE! Turn locomotion on and you're gunna be in a whole bunch of greef, first of all teleporting and locomotion modes lack a method of ingame turning around which means that you gotta watch that wire dangling behind you on that VR rig (the game says it has a way of turning around but I tried every combination of buttons to try and turn in game but it never worked) secondly the locomotion is SOOOOOO JIITTERY! itl make you cringe how bad it is... I was playing in a coop session with someone online so maybe it was a result of ping between me and the host (the other person) but even so ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥! The weapons are just... ass theres the sniper rifle which you get given at one point you have to defend a... thing whatever it is from the horde... the idea is to pick them off with the sniper which is so unnatural to use its much easier to just give the rifle the middle finger and just get out both pistols and pick them off with those... cause you're literally only 30 feet away from them all anyways! Overall couldve been a good game... but this is just a craptacular game... Good graphics though, Il give it that!", "appid": "690810", "steamid": "profiles/76561198041405506", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1533211200.0} {"text": "Ah man... This was my last try with the CoD franchise. Good thing Steam has a refunding option now! Can buy a lot of better games with the $100 that was refunded. Starting with DOOM, Shadow of Mordor and Shadow of War.", "appid": "476600", "steamid": "profiles/76561197961034809", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1510056000.0} {"text": "똥.겜 왜 인기 많은지 모르겠네요", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198386350683", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593518400.0} {"text": "this game is full of non-sense ♥♥♥♥. for EX this game have a item which named 300rnd ammo box. but its cant store 300 rnd ammo. only 120 or less ammo. and dev said its make non-sense with this little box can store 300 rnd of bullets. ♥♥♥♥ off dayz.", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561197996038501", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1435924800.0} {"text": "The concept for the game is great, and the gamplay mechanics, story, and atmosphere are all great too. However, the game has been in Early Access for a long time now, and little progress has been made. Until the game comes out, I don't recommend it just quite yet. Although I am confident when it does come out it will be pretty good.", "appid": "236370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090591159", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "36", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1465560000.0} {"text": "f@cking scammers, i dont play for stupid skins, i dont want play with unlimited cheaters that able to create a free steam account... at least make the sking tradable to let me sell it and get my own refund", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198015940343", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1520683200.0} {"text": "-20$ very very bad game", "appid": "299740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117305434", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1450612800.0} {"text": "yes", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198271772726", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1500292800.0} {"text": "오타쿠", "appid": "438100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198116879519", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1539950400.0} {"text": "Rockstar is killing mod support. They just keep on releasing ♥♥♥♥♥♥ DLC. Thumbs down. Bad Customer relationship!", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992204855", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497528000.0} {"text": "No save option in multiplayer (can't create profiles) and the floor bug is annoying.", "appid": "361420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073917939", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1484395200.0} {"text": "С самого выхода ничего не меняется,сервера и оптимизация до сих-пор убогая", "appid": "489940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198425591030", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1580040000.0} {"text": "Redrum: Dead Diary is basically just a linear sequence of small and easy object puzzles and a stripped down version of the original Big Fish Game. I am at a loss, why they decided to create a steam version which has even less content or quality than the initial release. If you are searching for a HOG like Grim Legends, Enigmatis etc. this is not what you are searching for. You don't move around, there are no animations and the \"story\" itself is badly written and told in static pictures in forms of a diary page, notes or an e-mail. There are four types of puzzles - shape based, word based, search the same item x times and match Image snippets. If you only after a small & very easy HOG game without any challenge/penalties or in search of a relatively fast 100% Achievement game appr. 1 hours (My time includes 2 crashes & looking it up on BigFish), then this might be for you. However, not for the full price! There are much better HOG you can get for the same amount of money.", "appid": "541720", "steamid": "profiles/76561197968312284", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532001600.0} {"text": "I liked they previous games, they were all good but this one... clearly hasn't been tested by anyone...", "appid": "1185520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198326097650", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1574337600.0} {"text": "Главное дерьмо 2018 года, главное дерьмо твича, игра полна багов и главное ЛАГОВ. Сервера в этой игре видимо находятся в деревне, ибо как обьяснить пинг на Европе под 340. Обычная рыгота от Hi-Rez Studios (Дауны которые не могут придумать свою игру). Кароче не надо тратить место на своём диске и своё время на этот кал.", "appid": "813820", "steamid": "profiles/76561198204753148", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1529668800.0} {"text": "я эту хуйню ебал", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198838602667", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1527940800.0} {"text": "It's a nice game but it seems difficult to figure out what to do in