oming attack? Hit B to dodge. X, Y, X, Y, X, Y. If you want to vary things up, you can try different permutations of X and Y, but it doesn't do much. There are combos you can do by hitting three attacks one after another, which momentarily stuns the enemy, but there's very little difference between them and dodging an attack breaks your combo anyway. There's no variety in the combat at all. You're constantly fighting the same two kind of enemies, normal and big enemies. They do occasionally have weapons or a shield. You'll be fighting a big thug with a shield in one level, then in the next level a big police officer with a shield. Your moves remain the same throughout the whole game. How about letting me use that baseball bat I disarmed from an enemy? Isn't that beat'em up 101? Around the second level I got tired of beating up countless groups of enemies, so I tried just walking past them... it worked. In fact, you can walk past about 80% of the enemies in this game. Occasionally there will be a gate you can't climb over until you clear out a group of nearby enemies, but any other type of object (electric box, ladder) you can interact with while in combat. For some reason Kick-Ass has a Spanish accent. The voice acting is atrocious. Besides having little to no emotion, almost all of the voice actors mispronounce words (parkour = parker, goth = ghoth). Every other time you climb a ladder, for some reason Kick-Ass spouts \"Damn. Why the hell am I doing this?\". You'll be hearing the same taunts over and over throughout the game. Besides the issues with clipping, invisible walls galore, the camera obstructing your view in combat, and the lack of mouth movement when characters speak, I actually like the graphic style of the game. If they had put a bit of effort into making the combat fun and varied, maybe put some things to do in the levels besides beating up on groups of thugs every 30 seconds, they might have had a decent game. The game also screws up your system font every time you launch it. Many thanks to the German reviewer here for finding out what the game does: The game disables ClearType in Windows. To re-enable it, go to the Control Panel and search for \"Adjust ClearType text\". Check \"Turn on ClearType\" and hit next a few times to make your fonts normal again.", "appid": "304170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198017975643", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "33", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1423310400.0} {"text": "Не удовлетворило и непонятно почти ничего. Интереса даже не вызвало.", "appid": "604330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198207491752", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602849600.0} {"text": "Too slow and clunky. :/", "appid": "355180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086671694", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1499860800.0} {"text": "Ya ulan monolith oyunu mis gibi yapmışsın feci şekilde sarıyor sonunu da mis gibi yapsana abicim. Lan hayatımda oynadığım en berbat ve saçma sona sahip oyun bu. Oyun son göreve kadar cidden çok güzel LOTR hayranı olarak baya bi sarıyor ve gaza da geliyorsunuz kombolar 1vs 50 girmeler falan ama oyunun sonu hiç olmamış. Ayrıca 2 dlc de berbat gerçekten. Aklınız varsa dlclere hiç bulaşmayın. Ben sırf bitirmek istediğim için onları da bitirdim ama az sövmedim he. Eltariel'in dlcsini belki alabilirsiniz çünkü normalde ana oyun tam bitmiyor resmen eksik kalıyor ve ee nolcak şimdi diyorsunuz. O yüzden alın oynayın ama küfrede küfrede oynayacaksınız önceden uyarayım. İnsanlı dlc ise resmen hardcore modmuş bitirince anladım lan meğersem hiç ölmemek lazımmış ölünürse taa yeniden başlanıyor falan filan. Komik ve gereksiz yanı salak saçma küçücük outpostlarda 5tane warchief var abi hem de 25-45 level arası. Talion'la oynansa tamam derim hani rahat yok ederiz falan ama Baranor sadece insan hiçbir özelliği yok abi ve sadece onlarda yok sürekli spawnlanan orclar ologlar falan offf tam 15 kişiye saldırdım şarkısını açıp oynamalık. Neyse kısacası bu oyunu alın ama sakın son görevi yapmayın abi ha çok yapmak istiyorsanız benim gibi diğer tüm yan görevleri yapın herşeyin bokunu çıkarın öyle son görevi yapın.( Allah'tan şansa son görevi en sona bıraktımda oyundan erkenden soğumadım :dd) Şimdiden iyi sövmeler beyler bayanlar :))", "appid": "356190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198125005398", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586692800.0} {"text": "Ta gra to gówno problem z uruchomieniem a pc spełnia wymagania", "appid": "1174180", "steamid": "profiles/76561198904157170", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "7", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575806400.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "236850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066411399", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1519041600.0} {"text": "хуйня, а так всё нормально.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198164662320", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511524800.0} {"text": "Скачал, поиграл, удалил. Такой фигни в жизне не играл...", "appid": "662320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198128025846", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518004800.0} {"text": "Выглядит хорошо только на картинках, по факту это не симулятор и даже аркадой трудно назвать. Если сравнивать с миссиями в ИЛ-2 штурмовик, то здесь нет начала и нет конца, просто сами бои, которые скучны до ужаса, и все это заправлено частичкой слоумо как в Sniper Elite. Добавили возможность самим поковырять самолет, заменив какие то части в двигатели или оружие. на этом смысл заканчивается, что касается того момента когда вы после боя на земле бегаете.......то это сплошная порнография...вот по другому и не скажешь....поговори с этим поговори с тем, включи радио, почитай записки, собери грибы, найди бутылку бухла.....ПРОСТО БРЕД....САМАЯ НАТУРАЛЬНАЯ ЧУШЬ....", "appid": "675170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004488311", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550923200.0} {"text": "пмп", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198966878242", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593000000.0} {"text": "oyunu önermem çünkü gıcık olduğum yanı bir silah satın alıyorum onu sınırsız bir şekilde kullanamıyorum 24 saat veya 30 günn kullanabilirsin diyor oda çok para istiyor.Bu oyun gerçekten beni zor duruma düşürüyor", "appid": "459510", "steamid": "profiles/76561198376858814", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499256000.0} {"text": "каака", "appid": "291550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198156653106", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593864000.0} {"text": "Цитируя слова великих: \"Было намного лучше, но на этот раз как-то не удалось\"", "appid": "814380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066914428", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1569499200.0} {"text": "跑图操作是真的难受,除了画风感觉没有优点了和朋友一起本地玩也很难受,不推荐购买", "appid": "619780", "steamid": "profiles/76561198157311072", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600257600.0} {"text": "There are very, very few story missions. Instead, most of the game are filler side missions, which you are probably already tired of doing when you completed SR4. Remember the well crafted missions back in SR3? Yeah there's none of that. How about the soundtrack that made SR3 and SR4? Which song is this game's \"Holding Out for a Hero\" or \"The Touch\"? Well...there's not a single song in this game, all you hear is ambient noise and explosion most out of the time. As for the superpowers, Blast, Buff and Stomp are basically the same, Teleknesis got replaced with Summon. Super Sprint is exactly the same as before. The only thing really new to this game is that you can flap your wings to fly instead of gliding in SR4. I admit I really enjoy it. But at the same time, they took away Death From Above and Force Field for no reason. So don't be confused that you only got 6 powers now. In the end, all you've got is a sandbox that's less interesting that Steelport in SR3/4 and a game that lacks the production quality of SR3/4. I know that this game is an expansion standalone. You shouldn't except too much from it. But Far Cry 3: Blood Dragon was also standalone, look at what UBISOFT did with that game? The only reason I don't feel cheated is I've got this for $5.43 because of a price error. I can't recommend this game at $20.", "appid": "301910", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090629272", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "39", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1421841600.0} {"text": "SİLAHLAR AZ SIKIYO", "appid": "550650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198440697481", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1538308800.0} {"text": "в ссср было лучше", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117632971", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1433332800.0} {"text": "WoW. this shocked me..", "appid": "316390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198174245414", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1430049600.0} {"text": "Отвратительно. Многие скримеры представляют собой просто трясущегося аниматроника, а некоторые \"скримеры\" это просто картинка. Ощущение будто игра была склепана за пару часов", "appid": "871720", "steamid": "profiles/76561198068822968", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1531656000.0} {"text": "Story is fine the only problem is it's gameplay design in some parts you will run out of materials and cannot craft your ammunition where you'll be stuck or for example in some parts of the game an army of soldiers come at you as fast as they can and won't give you time to swing your sling and when you die you just have to watch an unskippable cutscene over and over time until you get sick the game obviously is for finishing once and enjoy it's story not gameplay it didn't satisfy me as i said the story is fine but a game without a good gameplay would be better a movie not a GAME... 5/10", "appid": "752590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198184001643", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "47", "votes_funny": "25", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1588939200.0} {"text": "Well,I like the game,but my pc cant run it,my other pc can,but its at my cousins house,soooooooooooooo.....yeeee......", "appid": "232090", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970496392", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1449748800.0} {"text": "Спустя несколько месяцев после релиза разработчики, казалось бы, смогли оптимизировать игру так, чтобы можно было играть с комфортом хотя бы на средних настройках. Однако теперь при выходе из игры производительность компьютера падает настолько сильно, что загрузка страниц в браузере длится вечность. Это устраняется только перезагрузкой PC. Хотелось бы так же отметить маленькое количество карт, отсутствие возможности выдергивать чеку из гранат на бегу и бежать с выдернутой чекой - персонаж по каким-то причинам предпочитает передвигаться со скоростью черепахи. И помните... Если перед вашими глазами террорист запрыгнул в комнату и закрыл за собой дверь - не вздумайте открывать по ней огонь. Это самая крепкая вещь, когда-либо созданная человечеством и вообще любой разумной расой в нашей Вселенной (вспомним лючок мехвода у Т-34-85 из War Thunder). Прямоугольник из древесины с ручкой кладёт толстый болт на очередь из какого-нибудь MG3. Хотя даже в Half-Life 2 при стрельбе по тем же прямоугольникам пули выбивали из них куски. В остальном Darude Sandstorm на голову выше оригинальной игры.", "appid": "581320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198099747654", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561291200.0} {"text": "Полное беспросветное говно с накрученными положительными отзывами. Драйвом и глубиной кримсы или алиен шутера, о которых говорит автор, тут не пахнет даже близко. Брать можно только ради +1 и карточек на 99.9% скидке.", "appid": "467560", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004656847", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465387200.0} {"text": "if it had zombies and outposts this game would have been excellent and my goto game", "appid": "704270", "steamid": "profiles/76561198095665054", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582113600.0} {"text": "What utter and complete garbage. It's a pseudo-horror walking simulator with bad walking and bad scenery. You have the choice of using a lantern, which means that you can wander around without being able to see because it's pitch black or wander around without being able to see because the lantern is HUGE and RIGHT IN YOUR FREAKING FACE and puts off a METRIC CRAP-TON OF LIGHT to the point where literally everything around you is simply a wash of hazy white. So once you accept that you will be squinting and ruining your eyes throughout the entire ordeal, you realize that the \"plot\" consists of finding some notes and then wandering from one dimly-lit place to the next dimly-lit place that you can see ahead. You're supposed to meet \"Mr. Ben,\" who is, of course, nowhere to be seen. There is an occasional jump-scare in the form of some static image that suddenly takes over the screen, and then you move on. Don't bother exploring...you're never rewarded for it, and there's literally nothing interesting to see. SPOILER ALERT: You'll continue to wander for 10-20 minutes (depending upon whether you make the mistake of exploring like I did), and then come to the final bit where a guy from the KKK will jump out and stab you to death. The End. No, I'm not @#$!ing kidding. And then you see your coffin and Mr. Ben's coffin right there and three dudes in hoods are doing jaunty Fortnite-style dances near them. Seriously? The only way this ends is to be killed by a bunch of racists and then be taunted by them dancing around like they won the lottery? If this is someone's idea of original or even acceptable material, they should be locked in a portable toilet and kicked down a hill. This is a new low as far as I'm concerned. Everything about this game is bad, except the fairly-decent ambient sounds. The dev should be embarrassed for having written it, and I'm surprised that it hasn't been banned for content. TLDR: It's a low-rent horror/walking game with no options or point. Everything about it is bad, and it involves being killed by racists who celebrate your death. You should not only avoid it, but if you meet the jerk who coded it, you'd be within bounds to punch them in the face. 0/10 - there's a special place in hell for people who write games like this", "appid": "1010540", "steamid": "profiles/76561197975413392", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582200000.0} {"text": "I honestly would enjoy the game, if it worked..", "appid": "513740", "steamid": "profiles/76561198308621810", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1527422400.0} {"text": "1st thing is 1st this game is Fun & remains enjoyable until a certain time, The WOWs- *It's a 2k pocket game just like 2k NBA Playgrounds, characters are goofy yet looks good. *Fun game to play with friends *Great creation mode. The cracks- *Everything is locked, Even Drew Mcintyre is a locked character !! *Real lazy work with intros, every character simply kicks out from an wooden box !! I mean seriously?? *Every heard people cheering for the fiend as \"Bray wyatt??\" or even a huge pop for Baron corbin?? No?? play this game... *surface level moveset, characters have movesets based on their class like all the high flyers have same moveset, or all powerhouses have same... The game could've been a true successor of WWE All stars but its no where near....", "appid": "1142100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093444568", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "18", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1600862400.0} {"text": "No steam no buy ............./´¯/)......................................(\\¯`\\ ............/...//.........................................\\\\...\\ ........../....//............................................\\\\ ..\\ ...../´¯/..../´¯\\........................................./¯`\\....\\¯`\\ .././.. /..../..../. |_...EPIC STORE. |..\\....\\....\\...\\.\\ (.(....(....(..../.) ..)..........................(...(.\\....).....)...).) .\\................\\/.../.............................\\...\\/................./ ..\\.................../................................\\..................../ ...\\.................(.................................)................../ s*cks my ball gearbox", "appid": "49520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069433027", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1554724800.0} {"text": "Did not recommended", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198383316832", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1501848000.0} {"text": "ห่วย ไม่มีการพัฒนาต่อ แถมยังจะมาสร้างเกมใหม่", "appid": "350220", "steamid": "profiles/76561198150311003", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1533297600.0} {"text": "As a player of Insurgency with over 200 hours I was excited when the Day Of Infamy mod was getting its own release. Within two hours I applied for a refund... I feel the term \"early access\" is now just used way to much and this game still looks and plays like a mod, it doesnt even feel anywhere near as good as it did. Its like a the ♥♥♥♥♥♥ up love child of Day Of Defeat Source which is ten times better than this pile of dung They should of kept this as part of Insurgency and let the community mod and make maps for it, there is just not enough substance for a stand alone game and it needs a hell of alot of polishing (especially the textures)", "appid": "447820", "steamid": "profiles/76561197981569815", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1470312000.0} {"text": "Graphics is great but doesnt mean the game is good, but the combat system and weapon arsenal is terrible, a perfect spec ops stealthy operative assasin from behind enemy lines should have a good range weapon option but this game has none, bow is ugly, useless and terrible in stealthy operation, it has low damage and very low rate of fire. if they want more range weapon and dont want to break immersion they should added CROSSBOW for high rate of fire and MUSKET RIFLE for one shot high weapon damage option. this game has good potential if they just put more serious work on weapon arsenal. another boring game hack and slash with no stratigec involve. buy cold soda and ice cream before you play this game or you get thirsty (2/10).", "appid": "582160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198034134757", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596196800.0} {"text": "Хоть и сравнивают игру с Zup, но ничего подобного в ней нет. Однокнопочная недоголоволомка. Всего лишь нужно, чаще всего, нажать на один квадрат, чтобы пройти уровень - всё происходит без участия игрока. От него лишь зависит когда именно нажать на этот самый квадрат. Никакой сложности и казуальности. Хоть я и прошел эту недоигру, но крайне не рекомендую её, тем более к покупке.", "appid": "1021260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073647656", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1553342400.0} {"text": "Spiel gekauft installiert, Findet kein Match. schreibt 1 Woche lang mit dem Support um zu erfahren das man Instant gebannt wurde ohne das Spiel 1 mal gestartet zu haben. mit dem Kommentar man habe ja Pech gehabt und es ist wie es ist. sehr schwache Aktion. Jetzt habe ich einen Bildschirmschoner für 20 Euro. Macher die einen Fick darauf geben das mit ihren Spielern ist", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073167907", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603195200.0} {"text": "я потратил свои деньги чтобы сидеть и играть в игру, а не потратить целый час своего личного времени на настройку и удалению античита: итог нихуя у меня не вышло. спасибо за игру❤", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198219743245", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550059200.0} {"text": "isnt like a normal visual novel", "appid": "698780", "steamid": "profiles/76561197960987921", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542801600.0} {"text": "ChineseUnknown's Hackergrounds", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198087349666", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1517140800.0} {"text": "You ruined the game. June 2017 - When GTA V died RIP", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198039516613", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1497528000.0} {"text": "Купил по акции за 13 руб, карточками оправдал и хватит. Были бы сейчас 90-е я бы залипал в нее, но на данный момент, игра не стоит своих денег.", "appid": "270090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198007992440", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1419595200.0} {"text": "в онлайне много читеров с деньгами", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198090586031", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561809600.0} {"text": "Sigo sin entender a esos (muy positivos) pero bueh, esta muy bueno y todo que el juego sea \"a la antigua\" y todo eso pero al final terminas un poco desepcionado a pesar de que esta barato y simplemente esta en Desarrollo. No es tan fabuloso y no lo recomiendo, termine haciendo que me devuelvan mi dinero ;)", "appid": "436530", "steamid": "profiles/76561198057323990", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1470312000.0} {"text": "Oh this? piece of $hit.", "appid": "307880", "steamid": "profiles/76561198085345106", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "5", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1488456000.0} {"text": "Das mit abstand schlechteste Spiel, dass ich in meinem Leben je gespielt habe... Man hat kaum ne möglichkeit als Anfänger gut zu werden, da 90% aller Spieler 12h pro Tag suchten. Es ist Kiddy und Cheater vereucht :/ Es macht (für mich) keinen Spaß. Allgemeim, das Spiel kostet aktuell 60€. Mit den DLCs ~45€. Das wären mehr als 100€ und es kommen noch diese Waffenskins dazu. Auf jeden Fall: NICHT KAUFEN! Der scheiss is niemals 60 € wert -.-", "appid": "202970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198093410588", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1412164800.0} {"text": "Oyunun ilk trailer'ı yayınlandığında YouTube'da tam 3 milyon dislike aldı. Infinite Warfare bu kadar kötü bir giriş yaptı maalesef. Çünkü oyuncular bildiğiniz star war'a dönüşmüş CoD değil eski seriyi arıyordu. Hikaye modunu hiç beğenmedim zombi modu ise diğer Call of Duty Zombilerine göre geri kalmış fakat eğlenceliydi. Multiplayer modunu bizzat çok beğendim gayet akıcı ve seri tasarlanmış bir online mod ile karşı karşıyayız. Daha önce bu tarz hızlı oyunlar oynamadıysanız bu oyunda büyük zorluklar çekebilirsiniz. Çünkü her an her yerden düşman karşınıza çıkabilir. Harita tasarımları ve class sistemi gayet başarılı olmuş. Silahlar güzel tasarlanmış ama oyundaki shotgunlar sizi çileden çıkarabilir. Çok abartılmışlar sniper mesafesinden shotgun'a öldüğümü biliyorum.Fakat her güzel şeyin bir kötü yanıda oluyor. Oyuna para yatırarak oyun içi kutu açabiliyorsunuz ve bazı özel variant silahlara hiç emek harcamadan sahip olabiliyorsunuz. Bu cidden can sıkıcı bir durum. Variant olarak silahların damage-range-accuracy gibi değerleri artıyor. Ve nuke atmanıza yarayan variantlar da mevcut. Ayrıca oyundaki en rezil şey controller kullananların aim assiste sahip olması. Oyunda öyle şeyler gördüm ki adam resmen aimbot açmış gibi rahat rahat oynuyordu. Bunların dışında online mod benim için çok keyifliydi. Kısaca oyuna oyum negatif yönde. Almadan önce mutlaka tekrar düşünün online modda yaklaşık 1500 kişi var. Kısacası bu oyun CoD'a yakışan bir oyun olamadı. Zaten yapımcı kendiside itiraf etti. Oyunu yanlış zamanda çıkartttık diye....", "appid": "292730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036173898", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "163", "votes_funny": "105", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479643200.0} {"text": "Imagine beating your head into a brick wall and hoping it gets better the harder you hit your head. That's this game.", "appid": "236390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066050396", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446292800.0} {"text": "Фу блять фу нахуй", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198392079347", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1518177600.0} {"text": "Не скажу что игра плохая, она очень даже ничего, с хорошей оптимизацией, сюжет на троечку, без лагов и багов. Нооооо, она как будто недоработанная, слишком мало контента, мало оружия, половина боссов это немного изменёные рядовые мобы, мало контента, в коопе конечно зайдёт, но точно не за такие деньги. 600р максимум ей цена.", "appid": "617290", "steamid": "profiles/76561198066803057", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1571400000.0} {"text": "Runs like garbage, i7-860, 16GB DDR3, GTX960. Bought this for four friends, not a single one thinks the game is any good, nor can they run it smoothly.", "appid": "290080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198016990076", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1459857600.0} {"text": "Je confirme, le DLC crash!", "appid": "333800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198019908693", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1505995200.0} {"text": "免费了！退我68块钱", "appid": "433850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198306008012", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1521288000.0} {"text": "Мда игра так себе.Самое лучшее в ней это - графика.Как для игры на мобилку норм, ну и для пк норм.Ужас этой игрули - лаги.Я владелец мощного пк но как, как Карл 60 fps и резко 30 и так 25-45 раз в минуту. Короч не советую", "appid": "394760", "steamid": "profiles/76561198178150655", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470225600.0} {"text": "no,just dont like this game,seems ripetitive....thanx for free week btw.", "appid": "397540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198107669471", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596974400.0} {"text": "This game doesn't have much content.. Loading a game is really slow. take forever.. the game itself is slow such as lvling, building, questing etc. you will spend more time walking looking for rocks and sticks. Then you will playing the game content.. it takes over 60 hours of game play to unlock a second building. no matter how much you collect resources or craft materials.. you still wont unlock much of anything.. this game is a joke..", "appid": "1129580", "steamid": "profiles/76561197995363980", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1601208000.0} {"text": "i played 300 hours gta online loading screen. too much hackers & bugs. rockstar's don't even need to fix these bugs.", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076458446", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1532347200.0} {"text": "Это все тот же калл оф дути...", "appid": "696790", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120980181", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506772800.0} {"text": "Отзывы КРАЙНЕ ПОЛОЖИТЕЛЬНЫЕ. Ждал прямо, xyй знает, гема какого-то. Прямо на кончиках пальцев. Не дождался. Это квест, да. Точнее АДВЕНЧУРА. Так правильнее будет. Надо бегать, решать в массе своей однотипные задачки, частенько на время – убивать боссов по паттернам и учавствовать в, яeбy как назвать – по сути это кутэе, по большому то счету, в гонках по прямой с внезапными препятствиями. Формат мне не очень по душе. Дoлбoeбики в отзывах стима хором воют о прекрасном, цепляющем за душу ну просто blyad' как никогда, сюжете. Прямо трагедия такая что наворачиваются слезы, прямо ну eбaть его eбaть. Моя ошибка была в том, что даже зная дoлбoeбизм кончелыг из стима, я все равно немножко ожидал, что что-то такое таки будет. Естественно не дождался. История супepeбaная. Думал с минуту – супер таки или не супер – но именно супер, да. Погоня за злым полковником на дирижабле, негр-мститель и дочь ученого ищущая папку на (точнее ЗА) линии фронта. Да, понятно, что сделать рисованный в мультяшном стиле квест из натурального сидения по пояс в грязи в окопах, под обстрелом артиллерии – xyй бы вышло, и создателям игры надо было мутить что-то в таком детском духе, со злым злом, вечно убегающим от положительных героев на дирижабле, милыми собачками и голубями в касках - а война и трупы в канавах какбэ на фоне и не совсем всерьез. Я это понимаю. Но ведь мне обещали прямо трогательную душещипательную историю, причем ХОРОШУЮ – а этого ниxyя нет. Я прекрасно понимаю все, что они хотели сказать. Да, все эти мультяшные побегушки происходят на фоне газовых атак на города, пулеметчики косят твоих временных товарищей по этим самым побегушкам, раненым отпиливают ноги хирургическими пилами, чтобы не было гангрены, а по обе стороны фронта – обычные люди, часто очень даже неплохие, которых просто раскидала вот так ненужная им лично война. Я это понимаю. Но. У них это ниxyя НЕ ПОЛУЧИЛОСЬ. Вот реально – задумка кристально ясна, и ты даже пытаешься ей проникнуться по мере сил. Но не выходит, потому что контраст этой самой задумки и происходящего на экране слишком силен. Уж слишком eбaной выглядит история (к тому же содержащая неизбежные и нaxyй не нужные упоминания о героизме туземцев, воевавших на стороне антанты в числе нескольких тысяч. Серьезно – про битвы с участием белых людей рассказывается просто как про битвы – ну мол были такие, но вот если негры или гурки – то это были непременно героические обезьянки, и никак иначе. Ммммм. Нет). Да, трагедия там, xyeдия – внучок болеет в оккупированном городе, ранения, плен, контузии, смерть, глад и семь казней египетских – но по факту то выглядит это все чуть ли не а-ля комедия с мистером Бином. Исторические вставки и справки, которые должны дополнять атмосферу, на самом деле, blyad', еще больше способствуют этому неприятному контрасту. Во вставках то все серьезно, это всё (почти всё) было на самом деле, это действительно была ужасная война и люди гибли глупо и страшно. А на экране злобно хохочет усатый полковник с дирижабля. Тем не менее, возможно, вставки это таки лучшее что есть игре. Я люблю историю, а особенно военную историю, но даже для меня там было достаточно интересного. Для большинства же это и вовсе, наверное, будет как экскурсия в параллельную вселенную. Хотя в любой книге о той войне подобной информации будет больше в разы, если чо. Но это не всё. Кроме этого - было скучно. Очень. Более того – скучно было настолько, что я даже полез смотреть подсказки по прохождению, чтобы не eбaть себе голову с очередным набором труб, которые нужно выстроить в правильном порядке. Я, blyad', прекрасно понимаю ЧТО ИМЕННО от меня требуется. Это очередные eбaные трубы. Или очередные два подъемника, на которых нужно что-то переместить в определенном порядке. Это, blyad', скучно. В этом нет челленжа. И именно поэтому это адвенчура, а не квест – тут нет ГОЛОВОЛОМОК, тут есть геометрические задачки. Мне просто впадлу думать, в каком именно порядке я должен расположить в этот раз этот eбaный водопровод, чтобы он таки потек. А классические головоломки же упрощены до предела. Украсть хлеб, чтобы приманить голубя, чтобы выдрать перо. Ну такое чот.", "appid": "260230", "steamid": "profiles/76561197962981738", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1490616000.0} {"text": "I cannot recommend Dead by Daylight at all. First of all, the game is extremely unbalanced. Second, the game is a p2w, every DLC killer down to 1-2 (including Pyramid Head) are OPs can teleport or even turn off their terror radius. Thirdly, most players are small children who should not play this game (you can only see what they write in the text fields after each game, most of them are toxic) or they are adults who behave like 12 year olds. The developers give me the impression that they are not working on any of these problems and are simply using season passes and co. want to make easy money.", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120988656", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592568000.0} {"text": "Quite ♥♥♥♥♥. Still not what was advertised, but a cool game.", "appid": "275850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004453448", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1498219200.0} {"text": "The game is horribly unstable in it's current state with the latest drivers. Random crashes, glitched weapons (the models get stuck inside one another), and no Steam overlay. I cannot reliably play the game, let alone enjoy it. Very disappointing from Machine Games, which I didn't expect. UPDATE 11/11/2017: After verifying the game files, a new download of 1.3gb has appeared to fix the game issues I've been having. Accessing the Steam overlay still crashes the game, but so far I haven't encountered any of the original crashes or bugs I had.", "appid": "612880", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993440921", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "175", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1509278400.0} {"text": "é um lag delicioso que nossa, da pra jogar avonts a 1FPS, jogo bem rederizado(Sarcasmo), Nenhum Bug Otimo Recomendo se você quiser passar raiva =D", "appid": "221100", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071015969", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1471608000.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "252490", "steamid": "profiles/76561198237943718", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1476532800.0} {"text": "For a game that's been in development this long with the amount of money they've made it's really really rough around the edges, or as my friend calls it \"clunky\". It looks really pretty but constantly run into weird mechanics that are half-assed and unpolished. As well for as much time spent on the in-game models it seems very little time was spent with the UI and UX, especially the map -- something that seems to be common with MMO WWII Sim cash grabs of it's time like Hell Let Loose. Maybe try it again in a year see if it's improved.", "appid": "736220", "steamid": "profiles/76561197962624598", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587816000.0} {"text": "개인적으론 올해 최악의 이식 게임입니다. 출시 초반 진행 불가 버그를 제작사가 아닌 유저가 먼저 패치를 내놓는 등 출시만 해놓고 나몰라라는 여전했고 블루 스크린을 수없이 보게 만든 게임 캐릭터 모델링은 엄청났지만 이식도와 재미면에선 낙제점으로 인해 차마 '작품'이라곤 해줄 수가 없네요.", "appid": "658260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198004889712", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "21", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511352000.0} {"text": "jak sie znajdzie polski serwer albo banują albo chociarz mam dobry net wywala no ja sie pytam CO TU SIE ODPIERDALA Z TĄ GRĄ", "appid": "700330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198854856895", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578312000.0} {"text": "Friend gifted me this game a while back, perhaps a year ago. The 3.4 hours I have currently logged is all me and him playing, and we pretty much got all out of the game that you could get out of it at the time which is just expand your raft, float around, collect resources, rinse, repeat until you reach the \"ending\" I still have hope for this game, and wish that when it fully releases there will be more to do, but for now, its going to have to be a negative from me.", "appid": "648800", "steamid": "profiles/76561198153552506", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1587816000.0} {"text": "Не лучший симулятор ходьбы, в который я играл. Если вы знакомы с такими вещами, как What Remains of Edith Finch и Firewatch, то ничего нового тут для себя не найдёте. Эта игра сюжетно сильно уступает Firewatch и не дотягивает до Edith Finch по степени проработки окружения. Исследовать отель поначалу очень интересно, старинное здание постоянно издаёт жуткие звуки, щёлкает, трещит, ветер завывает, за углом то и дело мерещится всякое. Но ко всему этому быстро привыкаешь и уже не обращаешь внимание на попытки игры тебя напугать. К тому же, отель оказывается не таким уж \"огромным\" и \"проработанным\", как нам обещали в описании. 90% дверей либо закрыты, либо ведут в помещения, которые не имеют никакого смысла. \"Сюжетные\" помещения проработаны лучше, но в них маловато интерактива, чаще всего нажал кнопку - и всё, господа, проходим, не задерживаемся. Шататься по дому в той же Edith Finch было в разы интереснее, его населяли весьма яркие личности и каждая комната носила отпечаток характера владельца. Здесь же у нас просто обычный заброшенный отель, большинство локаций которого совершенно стандартны и никаких \"историй через окружение\" в себе не несут. Сюжет сумел меня зацепить, так как я люблю такие детективные истории с мистическим уклоном. Вот только концовка подпортила впечатление и слила всю интригу. Она не то, что плохая, она... я лично не понял, каким образом трагедия десятилетней давности привела к тому, к чему привела. Такое ощущение, что сценаристу просто приспичило не взирая ни на что натолкать в конец побольше ДРАМЫ, что он и сделал. Графически игра выглядит вполне достойно, работает гладко, никаких вылетов или багов замечено не было. Распланированы локации тоже очень хорошо, ты всегда понимаешь, где находишься и куда попадёшь, если пойдёшь по этому коридору. Даже с моим запущенным географическим кретинизмом я не заблудился ни разу, при том, что на карту вообще не смотрел. Если графика просто хороша, то вот звук шикарен. Отель звучит именно так, как и должно звучать старое, ветшающее здание. В сочетании со спецэффектами, которые то и дело создаёт снежная буря, получается прекрасная звуковая картина, которая затягивает в себя, особенно если играть в наушниках. В итоге, я даже не знаю, рекомендовать или нет. Скажем так, если вы играли в вышеупомянутые Firewatch и Edith Finch - лучше проходите мимо. Если же для вас это первый симулятор ходьбы - то The Suicide of Rachel Foster вполне может вам понравиться. Я буду говорить исключительно за себя. А мне, скорее, не понравилось, потому и палец вниз.", "appid": "1057750", "steamid": "profiles/76561198080390728", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1582977600.0} {"text": "Sucks.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198117437584", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1510574400.0} {"text": "Решила предаться ностальгии и сыграть в ту игру, с которой и начался мой путь. Вновь побегать по Миртане, выбрать свою сторону, спасти мир. Но нет. На моем компухтере, который плавно и легко тянет третьего Ведьмака на максималках, она даже не запустилась. Точнее появилось скромное окошко, а после тыка в кнопочку \"Новая игра\" вылет с ошибкой. К тому же, не обнаружила здесь нашего богатого русского языка, что меня не мало поразило По доброй памяти я потавила бы 7/10. Сейчас же, я даже единицу ставить затрудняюсь: потому что за что? Одназначно нет, по крайней мере этой версии. Время порыться и вытащить на свет мои старые диски Для написания данного отзыва пришлось ожидать, пока наберутся требуемые 5 минут, прежде чем сносить ее к чертям", "appid": "65540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198445414304", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1528027200.0} {"text": "Играл в эту игру довольно долго,пока не поиграл в доту.Prime world конченая игра,не советую.Одному играть вообще не реально,нужно собирать только пати,т.кПолно раков и неадекватных игроков.Мои друзья так и продолжают в нее играть,и постоянно сравнивают эту имбицильную игру с дотой и лол,с выводом,что она лучше...Короче вообще не советую.Герои вообще не сбалансированы,сначала выпускают героя,которого купить реально только за донат.Первую неделю он имбовый, его все покупают,когда стата падает,его так фиксят,что просто деньги в жопу!!!Вчера вышла обнова,которая в конец испортила игру.Теперь там можно покупать таланты,и обратно же за донат,короче без доната там не выжить.Вообщем вывод таков:Игра гавно,вообще не советую в нее заходить!", "appid": "235340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198106348392", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1414670400.0} {"text": "战争代入感基本没有，还是斗技场体验。 阵营战系统鸡肋，奖励加个更字。 服务器加成的手感迷是真的迷。 本来策略选择就少，加上系统平衡迷就变得更少，碰上厨的那是真的厨。 打一阵真希望自己是在玩刀魂", "appid": "304390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198036962104", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1494417600.0} {"text": "Buggy mess of a game on pc.", "appid": "208650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198018844445", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1550232000.0} {"text": "steam tried to confuse me ???", "appid": "219750", "steamid": "profiles/76561198342269232", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "13", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1495800000.0} {"text": "jeu de ksos car j'ai payer 20e pour ne pas pouvoir avoir la traduction française", "appid": "22330", "steamid": "profiles/76561198268358869", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1572436800.0} {"text": "Пример того как STEAM начал скатываться добавляя такое в магазин. GG товарищи, GG. Копатель УХАДИ!", "appid": "278970", "steamid": "profiles/76561198074469868", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1433246400.0} {"text": "(Review text hidden)", "appid": "286940", "steamid": "profiles/76561198198388946", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "57", "votes_funny": "10", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1486296000.0} {"text": "For me, having played an MMORPG intensively in a raiding guild for almost 4 years, this story line is plausible. I think that fact made it even more uncomfortable for me to play this game. Why I clicked through the first wave of grinding to get to a boss mob that dropped no loot was beyond me. Then to see your character making these decisions that I personally thought were, at best, flighty. Its a shame the character didn't ruminate over her situation until the end. In the end, it just brought back memories of online friends that had been through a similar situation, and all the time lost raiding some damn buncha pixels in a game for 4 years. However, for someone who has never been addicted to Evercrack, or WoW, this might be a way to see inside that world (from a young naive female gamers perspective).", "appid": "408120", "steamid": "profiles/76561197999108035", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1470225600.0} {"text": "0/10 igra jest zła i bezsensowna", "appid": "550650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198290230155", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1575288000.0} {"text": "I personally find the game somewhat tedious. there is a lot of micro-management especially late in the game(E.G. having to manually schedule the trains for maintenance). This game still feels like early access to me, as it lacks a lot of features that the older Railroad Tycoon games have(E.G. Mini-maps,detailed expense reports). I would opt for Railroad Empires before purchasing this game.", "appid": "797400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032325631", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1584187200.0} {"text": "Если вы стимулируете психику только чаем, то я бы не рекомендовал эту игру. Плюсы: + Tower Defense (обожаю этот жанр) + Весьма вариативная прокачка башен Минусы: - Отсутствие кампании (нет сюжетного прохождения). Это превращает игру в бессмысленное дрочево предложенных уровней с целью увидеть сколько бессмысленных очков ты набрал. Нафига мне рекорды? Зачем вообще играть в эту игру? Что даёт прохождение уровня? Зачем проходить все уровни? Если вы наркоман - ответ очевиден: затем. Даже передоз пуэром я перенёс гораздо легче, чем раздражение от этой старообрядческой поделки. - За эту игру хотят денег. Мне не важно каких. Если вы наркоман - сберегите средства на покупку наркотиков. - Если бы эту игру делали наркоманы, она была бы куда ярче. Враги очень неинтересные (внешне). Впрочем, дизайн некоторых башен вполне неплох. - Я 66 минут пытался понять nakhuya я в это играю", "appid": "578350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198228019204", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1595160000.0} {"text": "the server is $HIT", "appid": "304050", "steamid": "profiles/76561198328526144", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1499342400.0} {"text": "Wanted to play this with a friend. Logged in using my Hi-Rez account which I used for Smite. *Gets in launcher* *Paladin is waiting for verification* I opened up my email to check. I clicked on the link provided. The page said it succesfully linked. I restarted the launcher and it was the same thing, \"Paladin is waiting for verification\". I checked back my email and saw 10 verification emails sent to me. I then continued to send a ticket to support and typed the details and added a few screenshots. <<--That was 5 days ago. No reply and this >>\"Paladin is waiting for verification\" is still on the launcher. PS; I tried looking up solutions for this problem and I can't find a solid solution that really solved it.", "appid": "444090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198114025917", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1493380800.0} {"text": "УЖАС", "appid": "578080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198367945991", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526644800.0} {"text": "Bir hayatınız yoksa ve paranız bolsa alın tam sizlik", "appid": "836620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198311284368", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1536408000.0} {"text": "Aucun mérite. Aucun gameplay potable. Une pompe à fric. Même après 1000 heures de jeu, aucune évolution correcte au fil des MAJ et surtout AUCUNE mesure prise contre les cheaters omniprésents à tous les niveaux, sans compter les \"smurfs\". Ballistique irréaliste et complètement wtf, on te vise le pied et on te met une tête. Je déconseille ce jeu, une vraie perte de temps et d'argent.", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561198084022012", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1450267200.0} {"text": "einfach scheiße", "appid": "370240", "steamid": "profiles/76561198132881151", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1526040000.0} {"text": "изи хоррор,местами непонятный и абсолютно не страшный.", "appid": "281370", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042403955", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1425297600.0} {"text": "Dafür gibt es keine Worte, auf ganzer Linie gescheitert.", "appid": "311210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198073687186", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1456142400.0} {"text": "The game is great, but I can not recommend it at this moment, because servers are often down... Developers should really work on the stability of the game until I change my rating in this state its price does not match what the game offers. Currently accounts for a maximum of $ 20 When the game is properly repaired, it can be a great time with it.", "appid": "717690", "steamid": "profiles/76561198052336290", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "66", "votes_funny": "24", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1542628800.0} {"text": "Продавать пушки по цене игры это наглость. Могу понять рублей 50-150 за пакет. Но 700 рублей просить за возможность пострелять из минигана это перебор. Игра сама на уровне выше среднего (Можно оспорить из-за орудий издающих пердеж вместо выстрелоа), но пушки за реал оставляют неприятный осадок. В первом KF цены приемлимые.", "appid": "232090", "steamid": "profiles/76561198401717014", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603800000.0} {"text": "\"не все вещи остануться\" Идите нахуй", "appid": "888770", "steamid": "profiles/76561198187375050", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529841600.0} {"text": "Bad just bad .. gta 3 for example is a better game that this ..", "appid": "10150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198165760088", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576411200.0} {"text": "Второсортный ТаймКиллер. Больше похож на поделку первоклассника. (Хотя бы бесплатный...) с такой себе графикой (не графодрочер. просто уточнил) и НЕВЕРОЯТНО странным звуковым оформлением. Типо Тут можно услышать: И непонятные возгласы пьяных бомжей которые были скачаны с бесплатной звуковой библиотеки (ну ок это просто придирка) Но какого фига тут делает Улюлюканье Лю-Канга из МК когда он Байсикл Кик делает? Вообщем просто накидали всего что попало Ну а как геймплей? Да так себе... Как по мне. Игра заслуживает НУ МАКСИМУМ 3-4 звезды из 10 (Данный ГовноОтзыв был переделан. Раньше он был другой *но тоже полон желчи и недокритики* но пришёл тогда первый из и сказал \"Так если это поделка перво классника. Сам лучше можешь сделать?\" и данная \"Сначала Сделай Потом Критикуй\" Логика вразумила меня. Поэтому я переписал отзыв", "appid": "394380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198234772536", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1511784000.0} {"text": "wow... I played destiny 2 and thought this game is..... ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ game I've ever played, then I met with runescape", "appid": "1343400", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032929535", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1603368000.0} {"text": "♥♥♥♥ end", "appid": "567640", "steamid": "profiles/76561198072914360", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506772800.0} {"text": "уж лучше получить битой по голове чем ещё раз пройти вот это", "appid": "49540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077844819", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1428235200.0} {"text": "no", "appid": "730", "steamid": "profiles/76561197976583644", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529323200.0} {"text": "I HATE THIS GAME!!!!!!!!!! THIS GAME IS ♥♥♥♥!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Honestly too rough to be any fun. Hunt more like C*** - no interactive tutorial at all, just a crummy manual. not even a sandbox or practise range mode to experiment in - Lack of sound when Alt Tabbed out, or even a notification in the Taskbar to say the game has started - Matchmaking is super ♥♥♥♥♥♥, you get rank 9s as a rank 4 or below so you die super fast. Or a rank 15 with superior weapons - doesn't tell you how many other hunters you could face in solo, or how many remaining - TTK is ultra low so you're gonna die really fast - game glitched on me. I found ONE clue for the Butcher and it says I have all 3. Butcher area was empty - keybinds are so horrible and unintuitive. Trying to set custom mappings for the tools and consumables is annoying. If you have x2 syringes and x1 firebomb does that mean you use the Tool 2 slot or the tool 3 slot? There were times it wouldn't even LET me select the item I wanted it was so terrible - speaking of tools and consummables...grenades and offensive tools are in consummables?!? This makes learning the game 1000000x harder than it needs to be and even makes keybind config annoying to do - no dedicated melee key just this crap annoying hold right mouse to aim them fire nonsense - dogs and some of the enemies were just straight up bullet sponges, and wish the right mouse to left mouse nonsense you'll die some stupid deaths ONLY things I liked about this are: - headshotting zombies with my guns or one shotting them with machete or axe is always fun to do - usual stuff like graphics and audio is great, I like the gritty realistic look they were going for - different Hunter rotations mean you try out new weapons each time - you start off with like $3000 so you don't go bankrupt so soon whilst you're learning the game Suggestions: - add an interactive tutorial so newer players can get used to the game's mechanics rather than trial by fire - add a COMPLETELY solo based mode. No other Hunters so us newer players can learn the game without getting shot in the back by other Hunters. Also means we can practise against the Spider and Butcher too Disabled comments so I don't face the cancerous \"get gud\" crowd but honestly this just pissed me off so much. I'd like my 3.3h back please!", "appid": "594650", "steamid": "profiles/76561198053356572", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1534161600.0} {"text": "Порадовали только русские свиньи", "appid": "393420", "steamid": "profiles/76561198025347365", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1449316800.0} {"text": "O jogo em si é bom... Porém a Usabilidade dele é péssima! Os tutoriais e modo carreira são péssimos para se evoluir no decorrer do jogo. Fica aí a dependência de vídeos no youtube e haja paciência.", "appid": "107410", "steamid": "profiles/76561198000732920", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1485604800.0} {"text": "This game was a massive letdown for me. I went into it thinking it would be a game about (apparent) isolation in the wilderness, and what I got was a game that featured constant radio chatter, with no flow whatsoever. The game is broken up into days, and the days usually feature tasks you need to complete before moving onto the next day. The game is very stop-start which impacted on the enjoyment of the game for me. The game features a free roam mode which, although I haven't tried yet, I know I will enjoy much more than the story element of the game (You need to complete the story to unlock the free roam mode). The story is not very long at all, 3-4 hours maximum. At full price it is a hard 'no recommendation'. At £3.74 (75% off), it is personal preference if you still want to buy it or not.", "appid": "383870", "steamid": "profiles/76561198016420741", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1529928000.0} {"text": "diablo", "appid": "238960", "steamid": "profiles/76561197963446785", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1561723200.0} {"text": "I felt like it has the potential to be a good game, in a friendly environment. However, in online games literally nobody followed objectives, just kids were killing eachother and cursing in russian so that's a no from me, there's enough of this in CS:GO.", "appid": "774861", "steamid": "profiles/76561198076530230", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587729600.0} {"text": "As long as they will support paid-mods as long i wont support this game/publisher anymore. SO ♥♥♥♥ YOU STEAM AND ♥♥♥♥ YOU BETHESDA!", "appid": "72850", "steamid": "profiles/76561198006679254", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1430049600.0} {"text": "This looks very promising, beautiful scenery, but unfortunately there is an FPS cap on this game that makes it very frustrating and cumbersome to play. I cannot recommend this until the developer updates the graphics engine to faciliate 60fps.", "appid": "489070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198032785977", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1486555200.0} {"text": "*Controles confusos. *Uma quantidade de bugs absurda (Passar 30 minutos tentando matar um boss e quando o hp dele está pela metade cair cenário adentro sem uma forma aparente de sair e observar o boss se regenerando, perdendo todo seu progresso não é exatamente o que eu chamo de diversão. Mesmo que você consiga \"unstuckar\" usando o mapa do jogo [Coisa que eu só descobri gastando um bom tempo no google procurando por uma solução que não fosse criar um novo personagem]. *O preço absurdo dos reparos de itens. Ou você conserta o item ou anda nu esperando juntar almas o suficiente para comprar alguma coisa decente. *Ainda não entendi direito a ideia de Ascender. Ao longo do jogo você recebe várias vezes uma mensagem dizendo que você já pode Ascender, mas nenhuma explicação plausível é oferecida. O que você sabe é que o char morre. Ponto. Não fica claro se você será obrigado a escolher um novo deus para seguir, se algum equipamento fica com você, se ascender faz você voltar ao começo do jogo... Enfim. *O ser humano que conseguir matar The Beast F'taga na faca, por favor me mande uma msg.", "appid": "233630", "steamid": "profiles/76561198097123331", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1404907200.0} {"text": "P2W Allah'ı.", "appid": "788260", "steamid": "profiles/76561198123649050", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1549972800.0} {"text": "Décu car le ouija est anglais..", "appid": "391720", "steamid": "profiles/76561197986607675", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1479988800.0} {"text": "这么垃圾的游戏为什么我停！不！下！来！！", "appid": "383080", "steamid": "profiles/76561198069223349", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "14", "votes_funny": "16", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1438257600.0} {"text": "I love hidden object games, but this is probalby the first one where I just said \"forget it\", I want my 2,5 hours back. So annoying since you know an object is going to be important, but you can't pick it up until the game is ready for you to, the mindless back tracking is ridiculous, things just all of a sudden change state [empty boxes all of a sudden have just the item you need, just becasue you turned to the right page in the journal AGAIN even though you might have been smart enough to remember what ti said the last five times you read it], you in no way get to use your brain in this it is all just chase the green exclimation point around the map since nothing is logical. And when you finally get to do a hidden object or other minigame, they are so insanely easy and without challenge there is a feeling of being ripped off for your efforts. Don't waste your time, there are way too many better Hidden Object games", "appid": "326190", "steamid": "profiles/76561198026957403", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1444564800.0} {"text": "Is very gay.", "appid": "1097150", "steamid": "profiles/76561198975978315", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598788800.0} {"text": "Игра получает от меня нагоняй за кривой бой с боссом в 4 эпизоде. Бой с боссом предполагал в какой-то момент закликивание кнопки (очередной QTE) и никак это закликивание не получалось. Проблема обсуждалась и в англоязычных сайтах, оттуда взял подсказки на отключение вертикальной синхронизации и на создание макросов или автохоткей-скрипта, чтобы по нему одна клавиша делала множество срабатываний. Да, потом я обошел эту проблему сторонними методами и продолжил добивать сюжет. Но это не извиняет испорченное впечатления от 4 эпизода.", "appid": "261110", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009602505", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1596283200.0} {"text": "СУКА РОК СТАР Я ВАШ РОТ ЕБАЛ ЗАЕБАЛИ НАХУЙ ВИДИТЕЛИ МОЛ СЕРВЕРА РОК СТАР НЕДОСТУПНЫ ДА ИДИТЕ НАХУЙ Я ЗА ИГРУ ДЕНЬГИ ОТДАЛ ДАЖЕ В БЕСПЛАТНЫЙ НЕТ ТАКОЙ ХУЙНИ ДРЯНЬ ЕБАННАЯ ВЫСРАННАЯ ПАРАША", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198397127363", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1562068800.0} {"text": "Well, no. And i really wanted to like this game!:-/ Been following news since it was announced, been disapointed during beta and confirmed my impressions during free weekend. The idea of the game is great, bunch of mercenaries clearing Bolivia out of drug cartels while unlocking tons and tons of stuff, like weapon accessories and various cosmetics. Game runs great given my setup is quite trash and even gtx750ti is able to handle medium/high details while very rarely going under 40fps if you are not insisting on very high resolution. Shooting feels great, there is huge variety of weapons and custom parts, sure, its not Tarkov, bud its still great when it comes to \"gun porn\" element. AI is decent enought, both enemy and your squadies. Now you probably ask why thumbs down?! .... couse DRIVING anything feels like crap! I never experienced that bad driving in game, and my gaming career started more than 30yrs ago in 8bit era, so i have seen a lot of bad driving. But really, what Wildlands is offering us is so bad that i just can not enjoy the game even i love everything else about the game. Tought OK, i will just use helicopter to move my team around, and you know what? It sux as well, even its not that bad as wheeled vehicles, but it still, sux pretty hard. Sorry Wildlands, wanted to love you, but found out i cant:-/", "appid": "460930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042623305", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523707200.0} {"text": "The cutscenes look like the characters are made out of clay and the cutscenes voice acting sucks. The voices WITH the cutscnes are out of sync and the gameplay is confusing witth so many combinations. It's not even worth the 50% I paid and I'm getting a refund. I tried to give this game a chance and it isn't worth it sadly. Maybe with some more updates? I can't even score it because i had to refund it after 20 minutes.", "appid": "338390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189818942", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1478001600.0}